ou hear me??\""], "SScW99PW": ["\"(Oh, thank god... There it is.)\""], "vLR4h9yf": ["\"GrImE SouL. I waS nOt eXpeCtinG ", "to bE SuMmoNed So sOon.\""], "KTvzYd9p": ["\"Well, yeah but... uhh.... I-...\""], "pPh9fyd2": ["\"(....Get it together.)\""], "5yy4wT4d": ["\"Are you sure there are souls ", "here? I don't see any...\""], "FQ3kxdyJ": ["\"I aM ceRtaiN.\""], "d5xSkHzk": ["\"SouLs aRe ResTLess BeinGs.\""], "nXhx7rY2": ["\"It iS nOt uNcoMmoN. tHey WanDer ", "ofF iF noT kePt aN eYe oN.\""], "1lm0lJpW": ["\"I was kind of under the impression you ", "were looking for specific ones...\""], "5tbdBsTV": ["\"YouR mIsunDerStanDinG iS iRReLevant.\""], "2YYHBgBj": ["\"NeXt tiMe yOu CaLL foR mE, I eXpeCt SouLs.\""], "H1X2Zqvs": ["\"If yOU do NoT hAve aNy SouLS wiTh yoU,", "I sHaLL aSsuMe You aRe oFfErinG yoUrs.\""], "QV6s3lbt": ["\"(So that's why it accepted", "my terms so flippantly...)\""], "CbS9NDh0": ["\"(Why did I believe for a second I was going", "to outsmart this thing on its own turf??)\""], "WZDMcRq1": ["\"(God, I'm as dumb as Ashley!!)\""], "K1ld9lTY": ["\"(.......I'm not seeing any souls?)\""], "h98yG2JX": ["The candle is burnt out."], "4skpW94k": ["The candle is burnt out."], "FwTmj0ZG": ["The candle is burnt out."], "lbrtg286": ["There's nothing to step on."], "w9PLmLfM": ["\"(I have a suspicion the Entity knew there'd be", "nothing here, but I'll go ahead and ask anyway...)\""], "YSsm8Hpt": ["", "You cut yourself and draw a small blood circle!"], "BksPctvk": ["There's nothing to step on."], "GbT9jdPt": ["There's nothing to step on."], "4BbsmwQ5": ["There's nothing to step on."], "xL9WSNnX": ["The stone bears an image of the sun."], "6w96BxLl": ["Nothing happens."], "s63QHJ48": ["The stone bears an image of the moon."], "SrnW1WPV": ["Nothing happens."], "yRSwC0NK": ["The stone bears an image of a star."], "qgbXn1FD": ["Nothing happens."], "BzQJ5RQK": ["This episode is titled..."], "Sy8x6Spp": ["[You can continue here once ", "Episode 3: Burial has updated.]"], "P