st standing there watching!!\""], "vKYcGp2y": ["\"That's right! We should all do our best! ", "Even if you're not dressed properly!\""], "H3V5gyxK": ["\"Which might be the reason why", "Lord Unknown won't hear us....\""], "LVRy5LVf": ["\"What am I supposed to do then?\""], "x136bJ8p": ["\"I don't wanna end up like our neighbor...\""], "2cqfYRp5": ["\"You could buy some robes from the--\""], "j9kRhwjF": ["\"Summon!! It's that simple.", "Just invite it over!\""], "wMKFSn7Y": ["\"Just don't ask it something for", "nothing, and it'll be fine.\""], "btwrH6LZ": ["\"(She has no idea what she's talking about...)\""], "F0mX1M8T": ["\"(But she's the one who got it done ", "last time, so what do I know.....)\""], "268cDzK8": ["\"....You know what? Fine.\""], "ytBPWwDq": ["\"But if it kills me, then that's on you.\""], "j8JZPTLg": ["\"Hehee!\""], "0Stv0lwN": ["\"Demon, demon! Come on out!!!\""], "bL4W4YK1": ["\"Um..... Come on out....?\""], "GqvhbJYF": ["\"Say it like you'd actually ", "want something to show up!!\""], "1XKSZfJl": ["\"Come on out! Come on out!!\""], "fjNl36yt": ["\"Come out! Come out!!\""], "sYTW8xJj": ["\"(Come out, and don't kill me or her...)\""], "mTSXKRBV": ["\"(Ah, the third guy is fine though.)\""], "4wgcWxtw": ["\"L-LORD UNKNOWN!!!\""], "DYSgT210": ["\" . . . . . . . . . . . . \""], "hGTng7Hr": ["\"OH! It's..... a bit bigger than ", "the last one, huh? Hahah..!\""], "dSjSYzyH": ["\"LORD UNKNOWN I'M SORRY!! ", "I'M SORRY ABOUT THE CAKE!!\""], "XwpkNyPl": ["\".......................................\""], "69S2MpHt": ["The Entity is saying something, ", "but you can't make out the words."], "yNhCfpZv": ["\"Sorry, what??\""], "1x650B9W": ["\".......................................\""], "qgJhKlKP": ["\"Man.... I can't hear it properly. Can you??\""], "W4J5crlS": ["\"M-maybe Lord Unknown doesn't speak human?\""], "vMjN0vVW": ["Failing to establish the means to ", "communicate, the Entity grows bored."], "Pb6Jhp3c": ["Lord Unknown's presence begins to fade..."], "lqfD42d4": ["\"WAIT, WAIT, WAIT!!! DON'T GO!!\""], "xc2zygv4": ["\"I've got a favor to ask! Look, ", "you can take that guy's soul!!\""], "f7sDwl8g": ["\"W-WHAT?!?!\""], "pPZn7tLX": ["\" .. .. .... . . ... ... . . . .. .. . \""], "KwjpythK": ["\"........\""], "rQJggHLm": ["\" . . . . . . . . . . . \""], "G3rWT8QW": ["\"................Huh. Well, that was..... interesting.\""], "ddhywM65": ["\"Interesting!? You--!! You said--!!\""], "mR5vWvNj": ["\"Yeah, I know what I said! But look,", "it didn't take your soul anyway.\""], "CsrglfLr": ["\"So, so what??\""], "j02qr5kB": ["\" 'So what!?' You-- you \\fi bitch!! \\fr\\c[6]\""], "QPnlkDZC": ["\"What was that?\""], "RJ4l2hXb": ["\"\\fi Tch...... \\fr\\c[6] \""], "P2WL4x1p": ["\"Yeah, you watch your mouth, \\fi bitch. \\fr\\c[2] ", "There's two of us and one of you!\""], "NWBVcmgl": ["\"You're both horrible! No wonder ", "Lord Unknown just up and left!\""], "4YZlx8MK": ["Because, as we all know, demons hate horribleness."], "DVKPFqL8": ["\"What is this guy, an idiot?\""], "MGM2P97H": ["\"Did you just now figure that out? You idiot....\""], "7t9VWZqW": ["\"Hey! Takes one to know one, \\fi idiot! \\fr\\c[2]\""], "Cbfm75kG": ["\"Who's an idiot???\""], "JyXZM9yt": ["Asked the idiot."], "JsgvxgC9": ["\"Forget this. Let's get out of here.\""], "cVftmt9j": ["\"Good!! Go!! And don't think for a second ", "I won't tell Six Eyes what happened!\""], "p60bgnng": ["\"Who gives a shit...?\""], "W4KpcH7z": ["\"And with that many eyes, you'd think ", "he'd have seen it coming! HAhahA!\""], "3MQ8Nk1W": ["\"That.... doesn't even make any sense?? IDIOT!!\""], "J4D5s23L": ["\"Why, you--!!!!\""], "ZdP8t3ss": ["\"Ley, c'mon. We're going.\""], "0LWCzyvn": ["\"Good riddance!!\""], "DKdTldGT": ["\"You can be damn sure we're never ordering ", "from your catering service ever again!!\""], "FrDQpHLw": ["\"Oh, hey. Could you get the elevator for us?\""], "B9wWvTnw": ["\"ARGH!!!\""], "JCjG1ks8": ["\"Out with you!!\""], "5r6N3nFM": ["\"Man, what was that guy's problem??\""], "DGXmVCx2": ["\"Us.\""], "SBQylY9P": ["\"Pfft! Whatever.\""], "52C2XNtl": ["\"Well, since we're here, wanna give this a go?\""], "1Fl0n6v4": ["\"Would you be up for it?\""], "PD37K1l6": ["\"Nah, I'd hate to summon a demon. Sorry...\""], "5ND5BV0P": ["\" ? ? ? \" "], "D6v9Qc8q": ["\"\\fi Yeah, \\fr\\c[2] I'm up for it, dumbass!! ", "Why else would I offer??\""], "bL1fG5g7": ["\"Jesus... Just checking. You're ", "the one who has to talk to it.\""], "vPwMQNCV": ["\"Ask it to get rid of the visitor in our room.\""], "fc99Tj15": ["\".........Why can't you talk to it?\""], "zPh7J1x5": ["\"For whatever reason things ", "went well for you last time...\""], "8CF3x8j1": ["\"Alright, fiiiiine.\""], "hpyRgc68": ["\"Hey, friend. Come here for a bit.\""], "kZjBxVWz": ["\"Y-yes? Did you find the cake?\""], "r8JSrVkc": ["\"Say, is this blood or paint on the floor?\""], "m0g4rHY9": ["\"Paint! But when we call for Lord Unknown, ", "it is traced over with real blood!\""], "0r1JKKKK": ["\"Oh my. Whose?\""], "TQfNkxz0": ["\"We buy it from the butcher shop.\""], "MRrSNzCS": ["\"........Well, no wonder nothing shows up then.\""], "DNvYzx6X": ["\"Uhh... What do you mean?\""], "zgWJwVJk": ["\"You're summoning with stale blood that's ", "been sitting on a shelf who knows how long.\""], "GGhcS5zz": ["\"No wonder nothing shows ", "up. I wouldn't either!\""], "wqMmzklh": ["\"I trust Six Eyes's methods. Maybe you two", "should focus on fixing your catering...\""], "pSDH1qkC": ["\"I heard if you offer your blood, ", "all your sins will be forgiven.\""], "8myKf4GV": ["\"Where does it say that....? ", "N-not that I know of any thieves!\""], "Zxj8LYXJ": ["\"Lord Unknown said it. Don't tell ", "me you didn't know that much?\""], "FfndxZJw": ["\"Some devotee....\""], "lgQYdy2K": ["\"....How much blood do you think it is?\""], "674x4xLK": ["\"Enough to draw this circle should be plenty.\""], "sQXp6b5y": ["\"Umm... just for fun, maybe I'll try it.\""], "9S6tWZCm": ["\"Great idea! Give me your hand for a bit.\""], "MK3ZwW0X": ["", "You cut his finger with your cleaver."], "0nSNW6bB": ["\"There you go.\""], "1pwNRD2g": ["\"Neat! I'll draw the circle with this!\""], "NfLwxjtP": ["\"Then I'll light the candles......\""], "Crb2RlX9": ["\"And don't forget the music!\""], "yXh7Z6n6": ["\"Where's the play button??\""], "4lc7Y4Qf": ["\"I doubt you can control the audio from here...\""], "wDNpKCTx": ["\"Then where??\""], "kmY4WxZs": ["\"How should I know??\""], "KQXS9BWz": ["You don't have the means to leave."], "0h7YCP96": ["\"Hello, Son.\""], "QZh0NhY3": ["\"Hi, Dad...\""], "0nt1gT5m": ["\".............................................\""], "qlklgZBK": ["\" . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . \""], "7cZhGpNW": ["\"...........Bye, Dad.\""], "Y8flKg9X": ["\"Oh, no! No, I'm not jumping!!\""], "bTpB3tRL": ["\"H-huh??\""], "PhSwLk2N": ["\"Right........ It's just a job. ", "I can always find another.\""], "FYL6LMrB": ["\"Your mother always said I was ", "too good for that job anyway.\""], "29765jPP": ["\".........I-... Wait, you got fired?\""], "m8k1Yzpb": ["\"Well.... Life goes on. I guess...\""], "6HbVhSDq": ["\"Precious, precious life.... ", "We're all important, Anders.\""], "CjGglp04": ["\"It's Andrew.\""], "wpc0ksRy": ["\"\\fi Sigh.......... \\fr\\c[3]\""], "kgm3r6bC": ["\"I'll go see what they've got for", "me at the unemployment office.\""], "TJgQ8s9J": ["\"Great talk, Son!\""], "TJ4xSFj1": ["\"I love you, Andy--- Andrew. I love you.\""], "ZqBMcpmb": ["\"...........I wish you did...\""], "s2Zv7hNc": ["\"Nu-uh! You can't do that. ", "You don't have enough mana.\""], "V7qSnyf3": ["\"Can too! It said my spell cost is halved!\""], "NmKw0lYQ": ["\"Dude. It didn't say that. Let me see!\""], "S4fTp0zv": ["\"Ugh, Andrew... It's your sister again.\""], "3ggnHsSh": ["\"(Arrgghh......)\""], "tMnwhS32": ["\"HEY!! Watch it!\""], "0Dqn0qvM": ["\"Hmph! Why are they putting onions ", "in the smashed potatoes??\" "], "RQ5MWrg4": ["\"\\fi Sigh..... \\fr\\c[1] I don't know, Leyley.\""], "K0y6D5xQ": ["\"Why even call it 'smashed potatoes' when it's ", "'smashed potatoes, onions and some green stuff'.\""], "8ffB0Zsp": ["\"....Dill. The green stuff is dill.\""], "1065VcRV": ["\"Whatever. It's gross.\""], "MWjpxnRc": ["\"Speaking of gross, please don't ", "talk with food in your mouth...\""], "3JC8vmvn": ["\"Oh, you don't like that?\""], "sxSxq7vC": ["\"How about this?? Ohm nom nom nom!!\" "], "m5JKS5m4": ["\"Forget this. I need to be somewhere.\""], "FGzg1PMz": ["\"Y-yeah... Me too!\""], "YK14DYH3": ["\"GRAVES!!\" "], "2xg7R8Sw": ["\"I believe I told you to wait ", "outside the principal's office.\""], "pxd2QvrV": ["\"(Oh, she means her... Thank god.)\""], "tX9gm6d7": ["\"But it's lunch time?\""], "yHNzZJxG": ["\"Not for you it isn't, miss. ", "Get back over there at once!\""], "pkjNQWdq": ["\"....What did you do now?\""], "w2M2RPxc": ["\"Nothing! I just called her what she is.\""], "KX9Dv1tR": ["\"A CUNT!!\" "], "7qs281Ff": ["\"Miss Graves, I \\fi will \\fr\\c[6] call ", "your parents about this.\""], "qzkKvjJZ": ["\"Good!! Call my mom! She'll call you a cunt too!!\" "], "95XN27lb": ["\"Y'know, just yesterday she ", "said you're a dried up ol'--!\""], "h8gHgXbG": ["\"Holy crap, she's annoying.\" "], "p01JwkLM": ["\"Yeah.......\""], "23HPrBtP": ["\"Why didn't you tell her to get lost?\""], "Tpp8g2mT": ["\"Mrs. Kent?\""], "1bfp2BYW": ["\"No! Ashley.\""], "qv1SLKKf": ["\"..............Why didn't you?\""], "NNbvR9Yw": ["\"I dunno. She's your sister, not mine.\""], "Sy8HXlXq": ["\".....................\""], "1hdp68v9": ["\"Ah. She left her bag.\""], "mGtQ1rf0": ["\"Wanna go throw it in a toilet? Hahah!!\""], "2SKy2hpv": ["\"C'mon, don't.\""], "DMX1tvgt": ["\"(I'm the one who would ", "have to deal with that....)\""], "cXlXxZ9f": ["\"If she were my sister I would've ", "punched her lights out already.\""], "ckmRbDqm": ["While you'd love to do that, you'd just as ", "much love to punch your friend for saying it."], "SLmdC4st": ["But alas, no one gets punched."], "MDK2KH8R": ["\"How come you never play Magical ", "Magic Cards of Magic with us?\""], "GgJ1036N": ["\"Those things cost \\fi a lot.... \\fr\\c[1]\""], "k3ytGVg5": ["\"So? Ask your parents to buy you some.\""], "R4fkchlX": ["\"...............\""], "tg0D0626": ["\"Okay, you got me. The real reason ", "is that I suck at that game.\""], "XBwlKL7D": ["\"Haha! I knew it.\""], "XwvBDNqm": ["\"I'm happy just watching you two play.\""], "DCYxT2QW": ["\"Well, if you ever change your mind, I'll", "teach you my super tactical winning moves!\""], "sn5CpfpW": ["\"Yeah. Thanks............\""], "LD2M9vWq": ["", "Got Leyley's Backpack!"], "jL5nwlsj": ["\"Hehee! He came to talk to us!\""], "7QcCCjwb": ["\"He he he!\""], "kXs3fF3X": ["\"(Why are they laughing? Did I do something??)\""], "77Zj4gYq": ["\"Hi!\""], "VCs6DCl4": ["\"Uhh.... Hi?\""], "TLXNCNCK": ["\"Heheh! I did it! I waved at him!!\""], "dgtPBRGm": ["\"(I don't get it............)\""], "2YNmx8HM": ["\"Hehee! Hi, Andy!\""], "NM4b8dRx": ["\"...........Huh?\""], "wdbfT7jn": ["\"Shh!!! No, no! It was Andrew!!\""], "1nGVmT6l": ["\"Oh? I thought Ashley said Andy...\""], "YTvWd6WD": ["\"Say, I was wondering if you could invite ", "Ashley to sit with you guys sometime...\""], "0K55RN4m": ["\"Oh..........................\""], "LcQ9VcqT": ["\"Umm..... Sure, I guess. ", "Will you sit with us too?\""], "frr8Y2Bp": ["\"(That defeats the point...)\""], "yjBJVsnz": ["\"Well.... I guess I could. Sometimes.\""], "32LMbYkk": ["\"Great! Looking forward to it.\""], "1883kLZk": ["When returning Leyley her backpack, one would ", "benefit from having said backpack with them."], "nWjQhnD6": ["Pick up her backpack, dumbass."], "40Wt8Z7L": ["Mmmm-mm!! Delicious goop."], "VDLHg3X0": ["The smell of burnt coffee wafts from the office."], "BkVvn7q2": ["\"Please don\u2019t bother him without a reason. ", "The principal is an extremely busy man.\""], "XBHjvVBJ": ["\"I can never seem to get ahold of your parents.\""], "Y4mSC5Xz": ["\"Could you ask them to please ", "start answering the phone?\""], "nbcrgff0": ["\"They can't. They're both at work.\""], "S7cBzKPm": ["\"(Except today as it happens, but ", "she doesn't need to know that...)\""], "gFlbrSRs": ["\"Ahh. Well then, please ask them to call me back.\""], "vP37cSM5": ["\"Will you be picking the phone up after six?\""], "KMC2L0J6": ["\"\\fi Sigh............. \\fr\\c[6] Never mind. I'll have your ", "sister deliver them a written notice.\""], "pMSMWbW1": ["\"(She'll be delivering it straight ", "to the nearest trash bin...)\""], "Mz99bytY": ["\"You should take care not to call your ", "sister such an infantile nickname.\""], "1kF0gFP2": ["\"What's wrong with it? She ", "came up with it herself...\""], "v0frjx0X": ["\"Language is meaningless if we don't ", "refer to things by their real names.\""], "jrvp6H3Z": ["\"..................I'm sorry, Mrs. Kent, but ", "my sister isn't a thing.\""], "Z71X6rJs": ["\"You know what I mean, and I do not", "appreciate the tone of your voice.\""], "RR0KNRs4": ["\"I apologize. Going forward, I'll be taking your ", "opinion into consideration. Thank you very much.\""], "Wy2vdNDB": ["\"Good. You are excused.\""], "glLccqw2": ["\"Welp! I'll see you later, \\fi Leyley. \\fr\\c[1] \""], "w2JjCbLd": ["\"Hehe! See ya, Andy!!\""], "y03Df63h": ["You hear Mrs. Kent mutter something under her breath."], "S6gMCYrS": ["Something about apples not", "falling far from the tree."], "YrzZrQw7": ["\"Well, well, well! If it isn't Andy.\""], "H3jtS0Bk": ["\"I knew you'd come after me.\""], "5NrjTn4G": ["\"Yeah, wonder why...\""], "y1F5QRym": ["She smirks as you chuck her backpack to her."], "fJBPdK9G": ["\"You really should start sitting ", "with your own friends at lunch.\""], "46w2B1BT": ["\"You're going to be left out otherwise...\""], "k1DwHZpc": ["\"I'm already left out!!\""], "wYzYcgWc": ["\"What about those two you were ", "doing that art assignment with?\""], "PdCFPfVm": ["\"Ughhhhh... But they're so annoying.\""], "lZNKrKx2": ["\"Sounds to me like you'd fit right in then.\""], "53848vrw": ["\"Wait! Wanna skip class together??\""], "pNMBSb26": ["\"You'll do no such thing!!\""], "ZTnjd9Gj": ["\".............Please try to make some friends, Leyley.\""], "sjVJqFlK": ["\"Then, wait for me after school!\""], "TjGypDqH": ["\"We'll see....\""], "hHNH3Jrd": ["\"Err! Hi! Excuse me, hahah! ", "I've been looking for you....\""], "9Z9wKKMn": ["\"....Is something wrong?\""], "8xv4FxWd": ["\"Umm... M-maybe you don't remember me, but-...\""], "NkqT6vnW": ["\"Julia, right?\""], "Dsy4pqCK": ["\"You're Ashley's friend.\""], "gbJV2C1g": ["\"Does she, uh.... use that word?\""], "ZdWtjv15": ["\".......Sure.\""], "vxdFyPTd": ["\"Really? What a relief...!\""], "hFVRhv2r": ["\"I actually thought she kind ", "of hated me.... Ahahahha!\""], "dZT8Svvm": ["\"(Oh, she does.)\""], "sX7J2GDj": ["\"Not at all. I don't think so.\""], "pyWRGxk0": ["\"Thanks for being her friend. ", "It means a lot to m-- her.\""], "cDJ1jGgC": ["\"Umm... So, uhh... Have you heard the ", "rumors? About Ashley and... you.\""], "zc4bW79w": ["\"(Why in the ever loving fuck ", "would she ask me this?)\""], "S3dFqv45": ["\"....I may have heard something, yes.\""], "bsWlfvYG": ["\"Ahahah.... Good. Or I mean no! It's bad ", "there are rumors, but-... uhh... errr....\""], "TtyfVblc": ["\"I- I'm messing this up, aren't I? Sorry.....\""], "kgg33zkt": ["\"No worries. Just say what you wanna say.\""], "W2QGgLQS": ["\"Um... I think everyone knows they're ", "not true. The rumors, I mean...\""], "TwW2jFrG": ["\"So I just wanted to let you know that, ", "in case you needed to hear it...\""], "9qyH2JlQ": ["\"I figured as much, but it's ", "still nice to have confirmation.\""], "Vm1FCWk4": ["\"Thanks, Julia.\""], "JSLjXy1b": ["\"Ahaha...! N-no problem! No problem!\""], "w0YSL96w": ["\"A-anyway! Try not to let it bother you too much...\""], "tYQLJW1q": ["\"That's all! B-bye!!\""], "zGwKkssZ": ["\"............\""], "XbvNHlyG": ["\".......................\\fiSigh..... \\fr\\c[1]\""], "jd7nbTD1": ["\"Hey, are you free after school?\""], "3VSMk6bc": ["\"\\{ YES!! \\}\""], "083fkmwq": ["\"Ahah!! I- I mean, yes. Yes, I am.......\""], "qJrGGnyN": ["Well, that didn't take much..."], "tJLqvrc2": ["\"Your father will be here with the car soon.\""], "CDMp6bkw": ["\"Go get your sister.\""], "c79nBkd9": ["\"Ughhh.... My headache is killing me.\""], "rpgK0jF5": ["\"Go deal with your sister.\""], "knPvq3yy": ["\"All good to go?\""], "kG7vM6BZ": ["\"You didn't cause a scene, did you??\""], "zS04ycBQ": ["\"Nope! Everything is fine.\""], "zqxjxQXp": ["\"Except the gossipy hag's ", "gonna report us again.\""], "Dp28LHYb": ["\"...........Great. Just what I fucking needed.\""], "WxJpVg1Z": ["\"I- I don't think she will! She ", "just told us off for being noisy.\""], "JWn4Bq5R": ["\"...........Sorry.\""], "dr950y8c": ["\"Whatever. We need to get going.\""], "FXZzWydM": ["\"Do better, Andrew.\""], "9dcfRSnR": ["\" . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . \""], "P8w3VZCD": ["\"What was that, you blabbermouth?!\""], "l5jtmmpM": ["\"Bleeeeh!!\""], "m6Y5g7JD": ["\"Maybe next time, you'll wait for me ", "after school like you're supposed to!\""], "1FgxtGpx": ["\".....................\""], "zdVrv2VJ": ["\"May god grant death upon this ", "creature.\" is what you thought."], "qyKZgdb3": ["\"Are you two coming or not?!\""], "Wzj61JcM": ["", "Got a Shoe!"], "MS5Y093K": ["", "Got a Shoe!"], "L53wNBV1": ["\"Andrew, stop dilly-dallying around!\""], "hPpJ7scH": ["\"Hey, Mom... do I really have to come?\""], "XNmjzmN0": ["\"There's another test on Monday. ", "I'd like to study so that--\""], "ZwPCS82V": ["\"Tests at your age don't count for squat.\""], "Hx6lbcCr": ["\"Besides, you can study at your grandparents'.\""], "V83CxY1p": ["\"Now where is Ashley?? We need to get going.\""], "86dQvqbx": ["\"I think she got detention.\""], "bTywT1r6": ["\"Not again... What was it this time?\""], "qgFC6Pwf": ["\"Actually, don't tell me. Bet it was ", "Mrs. Cunt being on-brand again.\""], "5BY0G7g8": ["\"She always, ALWAYS, gives me the stinkeye.\""], "kNJD4TyH": ["\"Like, ohhh, I'm sorry! I'm so ", "sorry you have to do your job.\""], "WncpQWq3": ["\"Y'know, the job you're getting paid for?\""], "YmyZnWZr": ["\"Why did you even become a teacher ", "if you hate kids so much??\""], "5JLl5CJ4": ["\"I put up with this shit every day, ", "and I don't even get paid!\""], "HjDgW6Qh": ["\"Hell, I have to pay FOR IT!!\""], "3ZQjr2Ds": ["\"Finally! There you are.\""], "qCfBwWx1": ["\"Don't bother taking your shoes ", "off. We're just about to leave.\""], "6W3qjvBh": ["\"Andy! Why didn't you wait for me?!\""], "yt217gjr": ["\"I didn't say I would?\""], "0HxBKndB": ["\"Yes, you did! You worthless sack of shit!!\""], "1w1RvtbZ": ["Leyley fully intended to hit you with her shoe."], "Fl1Wv40d": ["Thankfully her aim sucks."], "wywPfxF6": ["\"Ashley! You do that again and you're grounded.\""], "41mDP8F4": ["\"DEAL!! I don't wanna see ", "Grandma and Grandpa anyway!\""], "KbKByB7S": ["\"You think I do!?\""], "cFg8gvtb": ["\"Stop being difficult and put ", "your shoes back on this instant!\""], "kmrff4KK": ["\"ArgH!!! I hate you!! I HATE YOU!!\""], "1xh8hWmF": ["\"I can't deal with this now......\""], "w2NYxJxD": ["Or ever."], "cWJkJPDp": ["\"Andrew, could you take care of it?\""], "GvJwgswL": ["\" . . . . . . . . . . . . \""], "B5n3JnXl": ["\"Well? Hurry up before she makes a scene.\""], "ztK7975n": ["\"Got it..........\""], "dTfcMWh1": ["\"Oh yeah... Mrs. Kent has been ", "trying to contact you.\""], "WwTPNY2w": ["\"I know.\""], "9tPkR4Dq": ["\"....So what did she say?\""], "XNbkhCGM": ["\"Hah! As if I didn't hang up ", "the second I heard her voice.\""], "qVL9yxsf": ["\"The last thing I'm spending my day-off ", "on is listening to her bitch and moan.\""], "VF1ZXJwj": ["\"Fucking bitch can't even get my name right.", "She keeps saying \\fi 'Ren\u00e9e'. \\fr\\c[6] instead of 'Renee'.\""], "lP5sK070": ["\" 'B-buh- but are you sure?' \""], "gPkqwpGv": ["\"Yeah, pretty damn sure I know ", "my own name! Thank you very much.\""], "4gwWtm00": ["\"Fucking \\fi 'Ren\u00e9e'. \\fr\\c[6] Eat my ass, ", "you dumb ugly cunt!\""], "pWnt6nhN": ["Your mother is in a great mood today. As usual."], "sTtyvFLy": ["Tread lightly."], "NW2shMk7": ["\"Well, uhh... She can't get ", "Ashley's name right either...\""], "hJ7XRR1b": ["\"Um... Y'know, the whole Leyley thing...\""], "LwgDHSkZ": ["\"She keeps insisting to either use 'Ashley', or to pick ", "a nickname that's actually derived from her name.\""], "h29RTWB4": ["\"For fuck's sake... Ashley can call herself Screwdriverio ", "if she so pleases! What the hell is it to her??\""], "xbMkCsLN": ["\"R-right! Right... For a teacher, Mrs. Kent ", "sure is on the slow side, huh?\""], "T6JlL05x": ["\"Hahah! That's right!\""], "SpG3YgZH": ["\"(Phew...)\""], "vX8ZCJWw": ["\"I swear to god! I wish she'd take a", "long hike off a short cliff already.\""], "stcXzLGl": ["\"I-...................... Please don't tell", "anyone I said any of this.\""], "qJ5Bgp72": ["\"Oh, yeah. How many times do I need ", "to ask you to take the trash out??\""], "PKy7LLdq": ["\"I- I'm working on it....\""], "w5zGDF6K": ["\"Fucking disgusting. This is what", "I have to come home to every day...\""], "Fm5wZlqS": ["\"I'll go ahead and take them out now!\""], "5SJ8z3QX": ["\"No, you won't! Go deal with Ashley.\""], "VbWn3Hsr": ["\"................Right....\""], "QNv0wr0L": ["\"\\fi Andrew. \\fr\\c[6]\""], "h4RyShRC": ["\"......Yes?\""], "6jQn0Vzs": ["\"I think you forgot something.\""], "pjZKHYZ3": ["\" . . . . . . . . . . . ? \""], "XvRgVyDk": ["\"Oh!! Her shoes. Right...\""], "yMmvM8hJ": ["\"Get it together...\""], "H8L9vXLZ": ["\"Sorry.....\""], "FDjl29HX": ["Ashley needs a pair of shoes."], "fFypsZV4": ["\"I thought I told you to fetch Ashley.\""], "wG0C31gS": ["\"Why does everything I say fall on deaf ears??\""], "sl7cyDMp": ["Turning on the TV now would ", "send your mother into a fit."], "Q3RRWX93":