re six."], "9fdrBfjs": ["This ghost is stuck at work until six o'clock."], "BXtpZYPN": ["", "Got a Lime Ghost!"], "1lhnxzLm": ["This ghost is happy to see you."], "vQgXPnzY": ["It gives you MONEY."], "VlVxd2Lh": ["You can't quite remember for sure, but you're ", "pretty certain this isn't how shopping works..."], "mTxXCGmg": ["Both of you are confused."], "z5hBs4tZ": ["This ghost is waiting for you to do something."], "gNgwZTPH": ["This ghost took your GROCERIES \\fi and \\fr your MONEY!!"], "W6RPH4DT": ["Then it gives you back your GROCERIES."], "kqwTGmnn": ["Nothing has changed about the GROCERIES."], "Jkzb634J": ["However, this is correct. This is how it works."], "C73VdRDj": ["This ghost can't leave this spot ", "until he is late for dinner."], "6bctFHxh": ["", "Got a Lilac Ghost!"], "M9dfBRWx": ["Neatly organized consumables."], "5rj4czvw": ["Consumables."], "V3f87Lf5": ["", "Got GROCERIES!!"], "gPFXFLJg": ["Perishables are stored ", "inside the cold container."], "P4mNNzrV": ["Perishables."], "hQQN1GHV": ["", "Got GROCERIES!!"], "hCCCksCL": ["This ghost is hungry."], "TX88lK0W": ["Hungry ghost."], "zdJFBk5f": ["", "Got a Pink Ghost!"], "K4qxN8vc": ["There's nothing to cook."], "nKmnRKwc": ["You've got nothing to cook."], "pd0vwXWl": ["Wait, wait, wait...."], "St6DVsRF": ["You have both GROCERIES and MONEY."], "t8WjsTdB": ["That cannot be. Something isn't right."], "Sf91dBJS": ["Hurry up and fix it before they find", "out and something bad happens!!"], "J6w6tcx1": ["", "Turned GROCERIES into FOOD!!"], "wGYj4B6N": ["MONEY belongs elsewhere."], "Wz0v2pSl": ["", "Turned GROCERIES into FOOD!!"], "x6pppSLv": ["Who should sit here?"], "bLPFZcKR": ["Lilac ghost is already sitting elsewhere..."], "3ldhvynm": ["Lime ghost is already sitting elsewhere..."], "Qcqwx93b": ["Pink ghost is already sitting elsewhere..."], "10Y14l3S": ["Not everyone is seated yet!!"], "wKz29LWk": ["Not everyone is here yet."], "8BYv3CNg": ["Unseated Lime Ghost!"], "s9dm1P7t": ["Unseated Lilac Ghost!"], "Dpdczh4Z": ["Unseated Pink Ghost!"], "fwV8XqvY": ["Dinner is peaceful!"], "dWx7r01Q": ["\"This tells me absolutely nothing.\""], "xBQg9vQq": ["\"How can a Grime Soul have such a mundane-...\""], "BSrJ9GNh": ["\" . . . . . . . . . . . . \""], "RdHDhwFH": ["\"\\fi Ahh. \\fr\\c[5] I see......\""], "nqQ1zw50": ["\"You have misdirected me well, Grime ", "Soul. Now I am actually curious.\""], "vF3vkyrY": ["\"You must be quite the liar to have such ", "an instinct intact in your current state...\""], "gv9m5Bj9": ["\"\\fb You want to show me what ", "lies underneath this facade.\\fr\\c[5]\""], "6YjSCHGm": ["The last thing you want is for the ", "big, scary being to see anything."], "jnttQJ1k": ["You want to escape, but there's nowhere to run."], "yp6XhsjB": ["\"...Stubborn.\""], "fGzRWkKn": ["\"\\fb You think about the things that hurt. \\fr\\c[5]\""], "H9jSJVvZ": ["You try not to."], "xxCPKwpQ": ["But you can't help it."], "bKfz9sZY": ["Something makes you recall memories ", "and thoughts you didn't know you had."], "N7t2Q1pN": ["Something tells you this arrangement won't work..."], "GltW4j4Q": ["Nutrients sit on display."], "Wj5GhfCK": ["Nutrients."], "fD4r2JqV": ["", "Got GROCERIES!!"], "my1xYDlV": ["Who should sit here?"], "3XDVjj9j": ["Lilac ghost is already sitting elsewhere..."], "K1x3QZZV": ["Lime ghost is already sitting elsewhere..."], "f2MJ0KZ4": ["Pink ghost is already sitting elsewhere..."], "wKKGdnDH": ["Not everyone is seated yet!!"], "VthZVFTT": ["Not everyone is here yet."], "m3c6dfkP": ["Unseated Lime Ghost!"], "gfHDS5fQ": ["Unseated Lilac Ghost!"], "5b79SNtG": ["Unseated Pink Ghost!"], "YRVcsLhJ": ["Who should sit here?"], "cRxpw8Z4": ["Lilac ghost is already sitting elsewhere..."], "2fcRMTqD": ["Lime ghost is already sitting elsewhere..."], "QYLYGzZb": ["Pink ghost is already sitting elsewhere..."], "s2vvhph3": ["Not everyone is seated yet!!"], "KprfH6nM": ["Not everyone is here yet."], "MmN5xx6F": ["Unseated Lime Ghost!"], "RhxXLqXx": ["Unseated Lilac Ghost!"], "6sJQYMSx": ["Unseated Pink Ghost!"], "Pdpx0P0x": ["Who should sit here?"], "wdm80kCd": ["Lilac ghost is already sitting elsewhere..."], "sCpCbGzb": ["Lime ghost is already sitting elsewhere..."], "1HDKZT6y": ["Pink ghost is already sitting elsewhere..."], "9cMzQ7GL": ["Not everyone is seated yet!!"], "CxPCqRn4": ["Not everyone is here yet."], "PcS4dgFw": ["Unseated Lime Ghost!"], "hgrZjmFt": ["Unseated Lilac Ghost!"], "L5LDkgHJ": ["Unseated Pink Ghost!"], "mYH5y6md": ["Dinner is set."], "XrwlYyZN": ["Dinner is set."], "JLj23yPG": ["Dinner is set."], "mJQ1wbhZ": ["Cleaning cloths and such."], "5fcrBmL0": ["A cleaning cart full of cleaning equipment."], "VHB8zcyV": ["Consuming anything from this cart would kill a person."], "4yS45hW7": ["Not that you remember what a \"person\" is."], "pzsXsn8S": ["Industrial laundry cart."], "T1hgd0tG": ["There's nothing on the plates."], "p9tRbRGb": ["The plates sit empty."], "0XkyGN6D": ["A family portrait!"], "HHZs58JP": ["It shows a lime green mother and a lilac father.", "As well as a green son and a pink daughter."], "vgnV6jRX": ["Mother is lime green. Father is lilac.", "Son is green. Daughter is pink."], "zBlS0B7m": ["Finished studying \\fi How to Be ", "a Walking Disappointment! \\fr"], "zczhgtsM": ["\"I was right. You are not quite there yet.\""], "vsFBbt6k": ["\"Maybe in time. But for now, ", "I propose a friendship.\""], "3CDpZWN8": ["\"I will mark your soul so that I can", "find you, should you call for me.\""], "k6wmRLrH": ["\"What do you say?\""], "5SJN4HyR": ["You don't understand what any of that means."], "sNvYNtml": ["But you nod profusely just to appease this thing."], "Dsn91r94": ["\"Delightful.\""], "txq8ZR4X": ["\"Farewell, Grime Soul. I look ", "forward to your hatching.\""], "LwBr8MWy": ["\"Ah, before I forget...\""], "yMJnClKX": ["\"Here. The promised vegetables.\""], "dYJ99vs1": ["\" ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? ? \""], "FLMQksfy": ["You are Andrew!"], "t7nJKrSw": ["When your mother first laid her eyes on ", "you, she looked something like this...."], "B902JfPN": ["\"Ugh............. It's a \\fi boy. \\fr\\c[6]\""], "xbGJsWft": ["Welcome to this world."], "QqkW3Y8v": ["Hope you enjoy your stay."], "fCrhx5k4": ["\"Perfect!\" it reads on your test."], "vsZ6tqnD": ["This has got to be a mistake..."], "WT9FqY37": ["\"Well done, Graves. Keep it up ", "and you'll be going places.\""], "mlgL1X7W": ["\" .. .. . . ... . .. . \""], "gTsgZ2mz": ["Your first-ever full marks!"], "NtRbgbGK": ["Maybe you really could be going places?"], "ByW452sW": ["And maybe those places could be so far ", "away you'd never have to come back..."], "pVTyQnyX": ["A study board."], "vhK2t9wP": ["The lesson looks unfinished."], "tTZbLzDr": ["An unfinished lesson...."], "h4xWf09m": ["", "Wrote down some Knowledge!"], "3BJCp33S": ["An unfinished lesson...."], "N9StXVph": ["", "Wrote down some Knowledge!"], "jfJzv6Wd": ["An unfinished lesson...."], "v3bbhNzG": ["", "Wrote down some Knowledge!"], "CXvPRsX3": ["An unfinished lesson...."], "Brpw1Bgg": ["", "Wrote down some Knowledge!"], "wnLZryH3": ["You need something to clean this with."], "XyXLtJnN": ["You need something to clean this with."], "qmlsQlJC": ["She looks very proud of herself."], "nNsgqjSp": ["This isn't working."], "QqHXq6l5": ["You'll never get the walls clean ", "with Pink Ghost around."], "QsMBSQfX": ["You need something to clean this with."], "Z5Rr6PsG": ["You need something to clean this with."], "ZwPP1hvd": ["You need something to clean this with."], "S81hZQzr": ["You need something to clean this with."], "H9Q8TYjM": ["A cleaning closet."], "ZqwCR7B1": ["Cleaning supplies."], "C1mt7SgY": ["", "Got Cleaning Supplies!"], "cR4P4V5q": ["This device allows people to yell ", "at you from great distances!"], "qLCsFXkh": ["A phone."], "Gz81lJjz": ["\"Hi. Did you finish your part ", "of the group assignment yet?\""], "Y60BSFBR": ["\"Not to rush you or anything, but", "you've kind of left us hanging...\""], "hcThv2V3": ["\"Well....\""], "sVkXjyq5": ["\"Just get it done, alright? Bye.\""], "xP1cQVKm": ["There are things you must take care of before ", "you have the luxury of doing your homework."], "JNVth10n": ["You can't right now."], "PfTtDC3t": ["Here sits your unfinished assignment."], "drVDjFFV": ["And unfinished it shall remain, until you've ", "sorted out the more pressing matters at hand."], "Znckzd9Y": ["In a little bit....."], "kgXBHYJv": ["You'll get yelled at if there ", "are doodles on your notebooks..."], "81bH8MD2": ["But you'll also get yelled at if ", "there are doodles on the walls."], "CpBk0FLM": ["Get yelled at by....."], "yyM9dJ2j": ["Teacher. Definitely."], "6JCxCKLk": ["His yelling is more of a scolding anyway."], "SCvfSczD": ["You'll get marked down for bad behavior, but ", "you can probably talk your way out of it."], "mLqszsv2": ["", "Got a Book!"], "lB3c23KV": ["You choose not to sacrifice your notebooks."], "VkwVcPSW": ["Let Pink Ghost draw on ", "the walls if she so pleases."], "5HHzPnkd": ["Mom will get angry..."], "VpntwTyK": ["But then again, when is she not?"], "LMtCdS2K": ["Forget this! You'll just take Pink Ghost's ", "pencils away after all. This isn't worth it."], "6KLMNZlp": ["Nothing worthwhile is on. Ever."], "7KB8cQcc": ["There's nothing good on the TV."], "XCHRRvkL": ["Turned on the TV!"], "pPQtwYSK": ["Pink Ghost loves this thing..."], "36r0WhN1": ["Be it fundamentalist talk shows or drama from ", "a bygone era, Pink Ghost will watch anything."], "lQPTBvVJ": ["That's probably where she picks up some", "of her... more interesting language."], "ngbPkknZ": ["Pink Ghost loves this thing."], "rgzn4hzk": ["TV has Pink Ghost distracted."], "fbNDZFPQ": ["", "Handed Pink Ghost something to draw on."], "xjkxLyd1": ["Pink Ghost seems happy."], "bZNH985L": ["Take Pink Ghost's drawing pencils away?"], "CFwfFb2F": ["Pink Ghost's heart shatters..."], "MFFvprCS": ["Then you must find her some paper ", "before she grows bored of the TV."], "bRSdqqT9": ["She needs paper."], "HZjvvTSx": ["Pink Ghost's heart shatters..."], "s5CbM7H1": ["It is for the good of the both of you."], "mqV7zsz3": ["You couldn't care less if it upsets her."], "7VLYxKlb": ["Pink Ghost wipes something from her eyes."], "CNZZKtsc": ["", "Got a Key!"], "dv0fPPHz": ["", "Got a Key!"], "JXv7czYr": ["", "Got a Key!"], "M524Ppnf": ["It's laundry day. You should get it over with."], "kmZl98RB": ["And don't you dare waste water by ", "running a half-empty laundry load."], "KLnn0BPj": ["Needs more Laundry."], "S3j7Vfs7": ["The machine won't get the ", "clothes clean without Detergent."], "ylKjpXmv": ["Detergent."], "ytqN3sRG": ["", "Got Detergent!"], "M41mV68H": ["", "Got Laundry!"], "grFqTr9T": ["Pink Ghost is excited to show ", "you her artistic endeavors."], "PmyFD9Fj": ["Goddammit. You're the one who has to clean this up."], "jkT8StnQ": ["", "Got Laundry!"], "Ssj3WNq7": ["", "Got a Key!"], "RL4yCKgN": ["Be quiet. Don't bother the neighbors."], "7BSJFybV": ["", "Got Laundry!"], "Pwp8fYl1": ["", "Got Laundry!"], "DxcYlHcP": ["", "Got Laundry!"], "3qcwBc3v": ["You need something to clean this with."], "G87VQb1d": ["You need something to clean this with."], "gqLRT79b": ["\"I know it's tedious, but just ", "bear with it for a bit.\""], "qmJMyzYy": ["\"Can't you do this much? I thought ", "you were better than this....\""], "qhjBLfGl": ["\"I'm not asking for too much here, am I??\""], "xgfgbt6S": ["", "Got Knowledge!"], "gZKG50qk": ["\"Look, just shut up and do as you're told.\""], "TLw4Q7G3": ["\"Since when were you this unreliable?? Stop ", "acting like the world owes you something!\""], "Jy25n22r": ["", "Got Knowledge!"], "Qj9M3XQp": ["\"Oh, boohoo! Poor you!!\""], "v5p6BKQp": ["\"Shut the fuck up you spoiled little shit.\""], "BKvfFWTq": ["\"You've got no idea how good you've got it!!\""], "r0Gn1bsN": ["", "Got Knowledge!"], "wDlRnZj1": ["\"Do you think \\fi I \\fr\\c[6] like this!?\""], "tyNyBjJb": ["\"Do you think this is what I ", "wanted my life to be like!?\""], "ltlMkr6K": ["\"Every single day I go work at a dead-end ", "job, getting shit on left and right!!\""], "zptQyXCW": ["\"I work my ass off to keep a roof over ", "our heads, and food on the table!\""], "J7fq1jcL": ["\"Yet you can't even watch over your sister?\""], "xpv0W5lC": ["\"What kind of ungrateful, selfish, ", "lazy brat did I raise?! Jesus Christ...\""], "rW0MY9FK": ["", "Got Knowledge!"], "LxSsVnZJ": ["\"...............I was not expecting a Grime Soul.\""], "DjvVCkBV": ["\"How did you manage the ritual? I wonder.\""], "SbzBtYvw": ["\"It is unlikely you will be of any use.\""], "W9sFffFx": ["\"Surprise me, little one.\""], "vqR0Y999": ["Your confusing existence persists."], "j5myg4S8": ["Go to..."], "3Zlf61k2": ["Go to..."], "07YpyWnN": ["\"I am \\fi so \\fr\\c[1] sorry for all the noise...\""], "55RTCt65": ["\"Tch, tch. This is the hallway. ", "Not your playground.\""], "wrrhD95T": ["\"Didn't your mother teach you ", "anything? How embarrassing.\""], "ZQCQ1X9F": ["\"......You're not actually filing ", "a disturbance report, are you?\""], "DQNK2xk8": ["\"Wouldn't you like to know.\""], "fN31x2BH": ["\"Run along, young man. I can't stalk ", "the new neighbors with you bothering me.\""], "v20drCh9": ["She's probably too invested in this", "to actually file a report about you."], "mQyPxMFb": ["Hopefully."], "8Wg7rbHF": ["\"A snoopy old hag and an idiot to boot, am I?\""], "MQzyGbSs": ["\"Err-- umm... G-goodbye!!\""], "3wj85yl2": ["Found Leyley!"], "dxlWh0m1": ["\"Alright, that's enough...\""], "Gcgkx2G9": ["\"NO!! I don't wanna go! Grandpa ", "is mean and Grandma is ugly!!\""], "0tBGh7c9": ["\"It's just for the weekend...\""], "7VCPb60y": ["\"I SAID I DON'T WANNA GO!!\""], "blmlhtRy": ["\"Aaahh! No!! It's a dead end!\""], "sn4vTFRT": ["\"\\{NooOooOoOo00Ooo!!!!\\}\""], "TMxPbk2D": ["\"Leyley, please, I--\""], "WkDLXDvS": ["\"You two again.\""], "lcW2RV6G": ["\"Err--- G-good day! How are you?\""], "w51wjW50": ["\"I could be a lot better, thank you very much.\""], "Q3JHKKy2": ["\"You \\fi do \\fr\\c[6] realize it echoes in these halls, hmmm?\""], "RpZX0GMY": ["\"I'm sorry. We'll be quiet...\""], "ZZPM6GXd": ["\"And who asked for your opinion, ", "you wrinkly old fuck?! Get lost!!\""], "WSn6cSNF": ["\"Tch, tch. Looks like I'll have to file ", "another disturbance report about this.\""], "5MW6MKbp": ["\"\\fi Ooooh nooooo. \\fr\\c[2] Not a disturbance report!", "I'm pissing myself from fear here.\""], "pmwn00NF": ["\"Let's see. At four thirty, on Friday. Residents from", "406 are screaming and running around the halls...\""], "VCbLwhxK": ["\"You'll be screaming and running around ", "after I pull a knife on you and--!!\""], "88L7gKFZ": ["\" \\fi L-Leyley! \\fr\\c[1] For god's sake...\""], "wRFT1P8t": ["\"..........Teenage parenthood is such a tragedy.\""], "QYggZwPr": ["And off walks your neighbor."], "rTYqcMD2": ["\" . . . . . . . . . . . . . \""], "KvsnDPZs": ["\"What? It was a joke. ", "I'm not gonna stab her.\""], "d5gQ2rqQ": ["\"......Will you just put your shoes on already?\""], "P0Rs6LvZ": ["\"Hmmm... Nope!\""], "T5lp1GMP": ["\"(This isn't going anywhere.....)\""], "xfj9BHRn": ["\"Okay, how about this? ", "We'll make a game of it.\""], "8J8tB6NY": ["\"Oh?\""], "t18S9QJf": ["\"You go upstairs, and I'll hide ", "your shoes somewhere in this hall.\""], "Q9m93Bnf": ["\"If you can't find them, then I win. And you ", "have to suck it up and put your shoes on.\""], "8qWYnwG3": ["\"And what's in it for me if I win?\""], "t4h6sPFk": ["\"I'll do your homework for you.\""], "6r3KFThH": ["\"But only if you prove you found", "your shoes by wearing them.\""], "JXyzXrxX": ["\"Heh! Easy. I'll go count to fifty!\""], "PqdmpT76": ["\"And don't think you're clever, ", "Andy. I saw what you did there.\""], "wcv39zbp": ["Leyley runs off again."], "vDNy5qpf": ["Hide a shoe here?"], "22rzMtVM": ["Hide a shoe here?"], "cx1GvwWB": ["Hide a shoe here?"], "NKpc3W0y": ["There's no way she'll be able to", "reach to search through these boxes."], "3zSWCQSr": ["Perfect."], "ZvXDh6md": ["", "Both shoes hidden!"], "jRF2Y2kL": ["\"HAHAA!! Here I go!!\""], "Mkxlm6gY": ["", "One search later....."], "kyf1tWj1": ["\"TADAAH!! Told you I'd find them!!\""], "QMZBbNCw": ["\"You've got some work ahead of you, because ", "I haven't done my homework in weeks!\""], "8ZxBvlGK": ["\"Yeah, yeah... Listen...\""], "0ccDGrYd": ["\"......Okay. I can't find the other shoe.\""], "SpYBRH54": ["\"But I found one! So it's ", "still my win, right??\""], "R2PgdLMS": ["\"That wasn't what we agreed on.\""], "n5kqbJBh": ["\"UNFAIR!! Look, I found one, so--\""], "mbdhKyXh": ["\"(This isn't worth it.....)\""], "MjV4FP75": ["\"Yeah, fine. You win.\""], "2R7Mkr2R": ["\"HahHAHa!! Sweet!! Told you I'd win!!\""], "k7BFgygL": ["\"Yeah, okay. Whatever. But listen....\""], "YWWsXbVt": ["\"AARGHH!!! Where the hell did you put them!?\""], "BFp7SsJW": ["\"You're cheating! You have to be!!\""], "5Tk3vdRL": ["\"........Hah.\""], "82bkcC44": ["\"You threw them out the window, didn't you!?!?\""], "hjZvVYFZ": ["\"Nope. You just suck.\""], "9YyvBPmY": ["\"I-!!!\""], "L1D5y2Sn": ["\"It's my win.\""], "x7rqF0yr": ["\"RRggghhhh!!!! FINE!! Fine, you win you stupid ", "ugly lame boring annoying dumb jerk!!\""], "pzKGc65l": ["\"What a graceful loser you are.....\""], "brm4mk8V": ["\"Screw you, loser! I hate you!!\""], "nrcP0fSk": ["\"I hate you! I hate you!! I HATE YOU!!\""], "qHV1NJVV": ["\"(Even when I win I lose...)\""], "g5FlBnWY": ["\"That's fine.... But listen.....\""], "DVj53wf0": ["\"Don't tell Mom that neighbor saw us...\""], "wYdLT07z": ["\"What does it matter? The ", "snoopy old hag is an idiot.\""], "RpPSC0X0": ["\"I don't know. It matters to Mom...\""], "DfszFg6C": ["\"So keep it between us. Okay?\""], "KfxzSPHH": ["\"Okay fine. Whatever.\""], "Ljb6BBbY": ["\"No, not 'whatever'. Do you promise?\""], "82WNn5rt": ["\"I proooooomise.\""], "kBT0NvKs": ["You get Leyley to wear her shoes ", "like your mother asked."], "k7LXxn5D": ["Hide a shoe here?"], "0tT75Mvb": ["Hide a shoe here?"], "dR37nP1Y": ["She'll likely breeze past this plant ", "to go searching deeper into the hall."], "8GkRWLmb": ["The sucker."], "TJK55400": ["Hide a shoe here?"], "tLynZf0v": ["It's a simple swing made out", "of rope and a wooden board."], "nBd7ls9f": ["You vaguely remember pushing Leyley on this, back", "when you were still living here with your grandparents."], "Kbw4C03T": ["And you vividly remember your grandfather ", "beating your ass after she fell off the swing."], "9WkHS0Bw": ["No one has been swinging on this thing ever since..."], "7rCp6gTP": ["Swing made of rope and wood."], "F2Z3xlCL": ["This could make a platform ", "if it wasn't tied to a tree."], "g6mVkszJ": ["It's tied up."], "5JYqJd1P": ["You're not done here yet."], "FxsdDmHb": ["On the ground lies a Trowel."], "0Hfqwht7": ["You've no plans to do any gardening."], "H1l2XD9p": ["A Trowel."], "4p33npB9": ["", "Got a Trowel!"], "gTKVY9JT": ["\"Welcome, welcome! It's so good to see you all.\""], "Z8LT2lW6": ["\"Thank you! How wonderful that we could ", "all take some time off to catch up.\""], "YGx3MY0F": ["\"Wonderful isn't the word I'd use.\" "], "fhSFb0BF": ["\"Let me guess, you're broke again. ", "How in debt are you now?\""], "H7ZFq0HV": ["\".........I wouldn't remember ", "off the top of my head.\""], "Yfv4KDX8": ["\"How much debt were you in ", "after finishing your degree?\""], "7pVsW3S4": ["\"Oh! No, what am I saying? ", "I forgot you don't have one.\""], "d2yCMD19": ["\"That's right. I have a fucking career.\""], "WrfzvKGD": ["\"S-sweetheart, sweetheart.... Let's ", "not swear. The kids might hear.\""], "lPZzCv2D": ["\"Tch. Right. The kids have grown at least...\""], "8yvZBqZp": ["\"How are you, Andrew?\""], "g34RTNZ7": ["\"I'm good, thank you. I did ", "really well on a test.\""], "YGL8YmFY": ["\"As you should. What about you, Ashley?\""], "n77HSGcs": ["\"Why aren't you dead yet?\""], "50BB42g6": ["\"G-gah!!\""], "HczbKmHm": ["\"Hahah!! Y-you're so funny, Leyley!\""], "dj5J4bGN": ["\"Really, after you were so ", "excited to come here all week!\""], "cn3hRP2k": ["\"The hell I was??\""], "dKTThCQN": ["\"......Why don't you two jokers ", "take your bags upstairs?\""], "H77f4lX8": ["\"R-right. Got it.\""], "pBXPwYLF": ["\"Okay, so here's what we'll do....\""], "KByGmXvf": ["\"I'll go get you a change of clothes", "while you clean yourself up.\""], "RzqD5Sbq": ["\"Then we'll pretend we've been out ", "here at the yard the whole time.\""], "SP37lPyV": ["\"Won't they spot us as soon ", "as we walk in, though?\""], "6F4bh66w": ["\"Well, um... Let me think......\""], "YsLJ8gh8": ["\"I'm tired......\""], "r01P0KJL": ["The bathroom window is closed."], "MPSYMrx3": ["The bathroom window is closed."], "3j06FQGy": ["You untie the rope."], "WPrXnFw1": ["", "Got a Swing!"], "4pWn81Nf": ["\"Stop scowling at me! I ", "didn't slip on purpose.\""], "M6mLDTnq": ["\"I'm not scowling at you!\""], "F3NB1zLC": ["This bucket collects rain water that ", "is then used to water the garden."], "yTPbRX4h": ["Fascinating stuff."], "fwKf96Ww": ["Rain water in a bucket."], "3sQxGRqL": ["\"I'm not using that water ", "to wash up! It's cold!!\""], "5cBdmPBD": ["\"It wouldn't get the job done anyway.\""], "xPKl2bGb": ["Cold rain water in a bucket!"], "DwR3Smjc": ["Rain water in a bucket."], "W3tLZNGs": ["", "Filled Watering can with water!"], "F7JPRNPF": ["A bucket of water."], "CVDLk0y5": ["\"Lift me up!\""], "YYNB0tPW": ["\"I- I told you! I don't wanna dirty my clothes.\""], "jdZ0KXKX": ["\"You can be such a little princess sometimes...\""], "zxPMQYF0": ["\"I'll be a prince over a mud goblin any day.\""], "VnzpbfLp": ["\"Up yours!\""], "13QHwZX9": ["\"I'm holding this in place. Climb up.\""], "XFVfSW8R": ["You need something to dig with."], "Y0WGDVW9": ["Here's where you could plant a sprout if you had one."], "XLsbwDGW": ["It needs water."], "lp4shZmK": ["A watering can can water watering cans."], "pZLqjptH": ["This one can't though, because it's empty."], "NGTBGx0k": ["Watering can."], "f9wFSzld": ["", "Got a Watering Can!"], "r7LG7VPZ": ["", "Note the lack of water inside it."], "Wm0JXWww": ["Inside the box sit some sprouts."], "JdkLK89S": ["A box full of sprouts."], "7J0R04l6": ["", "Got some Sprouts!"], "nCZ1n21H": ["Look at that! It is the fruit of your labor!"], "xgXQgrrn": ["It delights you not."], "GGzyQlq8": ["\"(Why am I always getting punished ", "for Ashley's screw-ups??)\""], "t0VCTPf2": ["\"(Because I'm older and supposed ", "to keep her out of trouble??)\""], "8fYblDt1": ["\"(Why?? Nobody keeps \\fi me \\fr\\c[1] out of trouble.)\""], "jFkLzgyC": ["\"(Unfair.........................)\""], "hwnkRz8g": ["\"Andyyyyy!! The mud is gone.", "Let's go play something!\""], "jMd4vl28": ["\"..............I can't right now.\""], "SD27TkVc": ["\"Why not?? Are you still", "mad you got yelled at?\""], "Z2kwZH3C": ["\"That was your own fault!\""], "g7R18y7S": ["\"Please just go.... I need to ", "take care of the garden.\""], "c3k4WcT9": ["\"What's so great about ", "this stupid garden!?!?\""], "B04p5QrT": ["\"Wh-- \\fi Stop!! \\fr\\c[1]\""], "X8V6Zv8V": ["\"THERE! No more garden to ", "care for! Now we can play.\""], "BPhb9xFP": ["\" . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . \""], "JrR5qrSX": ["\"Well? Are you game or what??\""], "jkwjYRWD": ["\"Dinner is ready.\""], "0YdyTpNR": ["\"Okaaaaay!\""], "x35GjMQ7": ["\"You're still not done here??\""], "G2XLq8K9": ["\"Get it together, Andrew........\""], "MKQTFyMn": ["\"......................\""], "kG8FBdRs": ["\"(FUCK FUCK FUCK FUCK FUCK FUCK FUCK!!!)\""], "Nytycyd7": ["Boohoo. Now hurry up and do it over."], "zYrYw3rz": ["\"(It's fine.)\""], "9hGZpZzM": ["\"(It's fine.............)\""], "m2X0YqvJ": ["\"(I just need to get a scholarship ", "to some school far away...)\""], "tRWwMpKk": ["\"(She can't follow me there.)\""], "QrBhlzrl": ["You need something to dig with."], "B9QBX6jk": ["Here's where you could plant a sprout if you had one."], "74S4Pffb": ["It needs water."], "5J2XlfQn": ["You need something to dig with."], "dKjJr3sF": ["Here's where you could plant a sprout if you had one."], "sCV3gVym": ["It needs water."], "NlP4tgLT": ["You need something to dig with."], "T9P1TdRg": ["Here's where you could plant a sprout if you had one."], "dNkZj037": ["It needs water."], "CBtpC66y": ["You need something to dig with."], "rmVv0Dj8": ["Here's where you could plant a sprout if you had one."], "sHGwk6b8": ["It needs water."], "PG3Sqs6p": ["You need something to dig with."], "2lZ8Js1P": ["Here's where you could plant a sprout if you had one."], "pKh6HFTf": ["It needs water."], "s63tfht2": ["You need something to dig with."], "QmSm4rYr": ["Here's where you could plant a sprout if you had one."], "vccv7yMR": ["It needs water."], "8H1zynZv": ["You need something to dig with."], "fKpnXv0t": ["Here's where you could plant a sprout if you had one."], "gd6PzPQJ": ["It needs water."], "V6LHgBXg": ["You need something to dig with."], "qSLWbDcj": ["Here's where you could plant a sprout if you had one."], "W92snBGr": ["It needs water."], "0DNnws3K": ["You need something to dig with."], "DkbdcYf5": ["Here's where you could plant a sprout if you had one."], "rwTTp5pg": ["It needs water."], "gNzVz08Y": ["There's a church service on TV."], "bfGwFj4T": ["Shopping TV. Buy now! Buy everything! ", "But wait, there's more!!"], "5pSwX9YK": ["Buy more to get more!!"], "MBfPBfnq": ["Buy now to get one free!", "Buy three and get two!"], "YPByPrYt": ["Don't think about it!"], "bPc89WHr": ["Buy, buy!! It works for real!", "Buy now! Buy tomorrow! BUY!!"], "mLlCHQzJ": ["Your mother is cleaning the bathroom."], "qbrQJFLR": ["So at least you don't have to do that."], "sJDG5NbT": ["\"Thank you for planting ", "the sprouts for me, dear.\""], "2nQphMWF": ["\"I was actually asking your", "mother to do it, but....\""], "St5YH0Pn": ["\"W-well, it's not my place to say anything........\""], "N4Bxnb1C": ["\"Oh, umm... Everything you need ", "should be in the garden!\""], "7yVqpKrn": ["The women are chatting away."], "MtFsQJyt": ["\"Oh hello there, little darlings!\""], "w3FpT3jY": ["\"Here. Why don't you go ", "pick us some blueberries?\""], "SrfSdd1s": ["", "Got a Cup!"], "hMdXgJGK": ["\"Huh? Why??\""], "7nyd4CKj": ["\"Why, this pie dough could use a few berries.\""], "1yh9xGxk": ["\"I was supposed to study...\""], "VhdjVJNx": ["\"It's good to take a break sometimes, Andrew.\""], "zp8QjhGF": ["\"Right......\""], "Wnzgp7Bm": ["\"Come on then, Leyley.....\""], "qTPgjTHx": ["You overhear a conversation..."], "xnL3vFms": ["\"You know, I must say I am quite impressed.\""], "5WnLYLG9": ["\"I had my doubts about how you could ", "handle a child, let alone two.\""], "CR54VVP8": ["\"But it seems everything is working out fine.\""], "sqNG7f4D": ["\"...........Thank you.\""], "zBqVnb60": ["\"Though, like my husband says, maybe ", "you had them a little early...\""], "Tv6MHzqY": ["\"Well, compared to you, for sure! Didn't ", "you have your son right before menopause?\""], "GJ6zvxMQ": ["\"Which, of course, I find wonderful ", "and impressive as well.\""], "zG7zyTgs": ["\"Oh... Yes, uhh... Yes, thank you.\""], "Z77HJ5Wf": ["\"I do worry about Ashley though...\""], "1YfNrc0j": ["\"............Ashley is going through a phase.\""], "hZ5xlNPX": ["\"I feel like you say that every time...\""], "vrdcGN1B": ["\".......Do I really?\""], "CqpNr1zn": ["\"Please don't take this the wrong way, dear.\""], "t3fRxxcw": ["\"As much as I love the kids, you could", "have avoided all this money trouble.\""], "5ZzFZPWW": ["\"..........................\""], "dHWHW7WJ": ["\"Wow, I never thought about it that way.\" "], "JmJr8TTB": ["\"I'll turn back time right ", "away and get an abortion!\""], "8F3DqKTc": ["\"G-goodness! That's not what I was getting at.\""], "Gc5bsrvB": ["\"Really? What were you getting at then?\""], "Qd5McpNc": ["\"Umm... It-... it doesn't matter.\""], "ym00PjPQ": ["\"W-what were you saying earlier? ", "Your dishwasher stopped working?\""], "2Pz4X0jw": ["\"Ahh, yes. You won't believe what happened!\""], "g2G2R3dh": ["Your mother launches into a spiel where she ", "begs for money without ever asking for it."], "fqhD20C6": ["\"Don't wander off too far, dears.\""], "7Cj247n2": ["\"Now that is plenty of berries! Thank you.\""], "LdCZWcRQ": ["\"Can I go study now?\""], "HSSJByB8": ["The adults keep on chatting."], "1ZP7QHKD": ["You take that as a yes."], "pLH6Bty0": ["Your grandfather has such a booming ", "voice it's hard not to hear him..."], "dc2hJsrD": ["\"Son, I swear to god, you're wasting your life.\""], "wBJP8ZLL": ["\"Father, I'm happy.......\""], "fLk95QDS": ["\"Doesn't look like it!\""], "RCT18Wqt": ["\"You should've become a lawyer!\""], "PyNfHPmx": ["\"That.... doesn't really fit me.\""], "RLMcrzDc": ["\"You should've made it fit you!!\""], "LQsP58cs": ["\"......If you say so.\""], "6XV8ZKWt": ["\"You had such a bright future ahead of you.\""], "1gkf0gXp": ["\"This fucking bitch ruined you!\""], "lNSPLStp": ["\"D-d-don't--!! Don't talk about my wife that way!\""], "ZmSWCtMs": ["\"\\{ SILENCE!! \\}\""], "3x07qPJz": ["\"I'm the man of this house! When ", "I speak, you shut up and listen!!\""], "TYlZRfb9": ["\"Good. I can't believe how fast ", "you've forgotten basic manners.\""], "sp0xrDK7": ["\"Must be thanks to your...\""], "SmfP6bWw": ["He spits. Right on the floor ", "for your grandmother to clean."], "SVyzjN3b": ["\"....\\fi wife. \\fr\\c[7]\""], "N3lNP8kH": ["\"What kind of whore of a woman ", "gets pregnant at fifteen anyway??\""], "Tr72j7MS": ["\"Disgusting!!\""], "CkdzPdd7": ["\"It takes two to do that....\""], "zRxGY792": ["\"She tricked you into it, I tell ", "you! She just wants my money!!\""], "GtF37X3h": ["\"As if I'd give you any now! Even after ", "I die, it'll all go to the church.\""], "rklZNRbH": ["\"....................That's very pious of you, Father.\""], "DMxnSdxN": ["\"Honestly, if I hadn't gotten the kids tested ", "I wouldn't believe they're even yours....\""], "Xqp2YBzr": ["\"Y-you did--- you did what??? When???\""], "8jFG0q39": ["\"Yeah, yeah. They're yours. Unfortunately.\""], "7RgHqnSk": ["\"Andrew is a good kid, so that's fine.\""], "zk3KGszx": ["\"But the girl is just like her mother.\""], "GBFjjJHS": ["\"Don't spare the rod with ", "that one, believe you me.\""], "vrsSfxnJ": ["\"I'm-.... We're not raising them using violence.\""], "JTz0Zv3m": ["In fact, they're not raising you at all!"], "YBXCWw04": ["\"Let's make Andrew into a lawyer. And the ", "girl we can send to boarding school.\""], "s2q6dzFL": ["\"N-no, Father.....\""], "MpvNyG1h": ["\"Then you're not getting a dime from me!!\""], "9VyQp1lB": ["\"We're not here for money.....\""], "xgVSJJD3": ["\"That's a lie and you know it.\""], "BpCBQXYd": ["The one-sided conversation continues on..."], "DkDgczC8": ["Your father seems more alive today than usual."], "4SklbyYM": ["Or angrier anyway."], "MtjrXqC7": ["\"Err........ Son, you're blocking the TV.\""], "f5mYYmLc": ["\"Um.... Do what your mother tells you.\""], "yrcpM3rW": ["\"She has your best interest at heart...\""], "BDlRkYfb": ["\"Say Andrew, have you ever thought ", "about becoming a lawyer??\""], "m4dwGmcJ": ["\"Father, stop it.....\""], "kYy6BRdk": ["\"....Where's Ashley? I thought ", "I told you to keep an eye on her.\""], "fmZxV3pl": ["\"Err-... Oh, she's just--....\""], "Mq3ZzJ1g": ["\"W-we're just playing hide and seek!\""], "T6TlQ5RY": ["\"That's fine. As long as ", "you don't make a ruckus.\""], "s6gdVQg5": ["\"I trust nothing is wrong.\""], "mjyWHG2L": ["\".......Nothing is wrong. Why do you ask?\""], "CYMVCTF3": ["\"I get a sinking feeling when ", "it's quiet for too long...\""], "5T5JFkjh": ["\"You'll understand when you ", "become a parent one day.\""], "kl6mHYHG": ["\"No, I get it...\""], "Xct4n4PX": ["\"Whenever Ashley shuts up for two minutes", "she's either dead or up to something...\""], "6szmlsxJ": ["\"HA! Right? Exactly.\""], "SqMPS4mv": ["\"Hey. Have you seen Ashley?\""], "VnfBPbSf": ["\"Oh my. Wasn't she supposed to be with you?\""], "kzxN1GRR": ["\"Should I ask your mother to help you look?\""], "YqqXQd7Z": ["\"N-no!! No. Don't.\""], "Fpyx7dcd": ["\"A-actually forget I asked...", "I think I know where she is.\""], "Z87Vcwbk": ["\"..........If you say so, dear.\""], "DSNQR1Wg": ["She's busy setting the table."], "xRJ1QJC2": ["Grandmother is wiping off the table."], "BhsNvqsN": ["\"Oh! I'm so sorry, dear. I was told ", "you won't be eating tonight.\""], "75Zbd5mn": ["\"I suppose that was to be expected...\""], "F0ZmpSGk": ["\"..........If you say so, sweety.\""], "yZGPzBSS": ["\"How about I make you an extra-", "large breakfast tomorrow?\""], "mMCsw4Kq": ["\"Sure! Thanks. Good night, Grandma.\""], "S44dbMpH": ["\"Sleep tight.\""], "XMhvRrXY": ["\"Good night, sweetheart.\""], "xkXFbg5T": ["\"It's almost time for dinner.\""], "mp5YB77X": ["\"And stop running around. They'll think ", "there's something wrong with you...\""], "H3zkx0d8": ["\"Oh yeah, your grandma needs ", "something done in the garden.\""], "mzVk0TpW": ["\"Wh--... right now? I'm a little busy.\""], "hgb3wmbw": ["\"Listen, she's an old lady ", "having to house four guests.\""], "lVjtMfFT": ["\"The least we can do is be useful.\""], "zvYYtzn7": ["\"Alright.... But can it wait a minute? I--\""], "JKBQWFfZ": ["\"Who the hell is in the shower!? ", "I didn't see anyone go in.\""], "VKSjGpTz": ["\"(Why the hell is she in the shower!? ", "I didn't bring her clothes yet!)\""], "NBvsxZDc": ["\"What the--\""], "t8YyP0Bn": ["\"(And she didn't even lock the door!? C'mon!!)\""], "yndpfBVB": ["\"\\{What is this mess!?\\}\""], "zbyVXCZ9": ["\"Is something the matter?\""], "GmqLZZnT": ["\"Why is there shit all over!?!?!?!?!?\""], "VZwJ28dh": ["\"It's not shit! It's mud!!\""], "8N1NVFT7": ["\"O-oh no! Watch for my ", "towels! They're hand-knit!\""], "s1GrW2yS": ["\"IT'S NOT MY FAULT!!\""], "T3TzMh3t": ["\"Andy told me to clean up!!\""], "g4PPKhbH": ["\"I did my best! IT'S NOT MY FAULT!!\""], "3hZ3xd49": ["\"I DON'T GIVE A FUCK WHOSE FAULT IT IS!!!\""], "2JwxzSXl": ["\"Good lord. Women never shut up, do they?\""], "mxM5t6yb": ["Grandfather turns the TV volume louder."], "z79C5NX1": ["There is nothing you can do but wait for the end..."], "zx7LY3r4": ["\"Andrew! What happened?\""], "t8bvFwFn": ["\"W-well she fell into a puddle...\""], "1BbxtXFx": ["\"I could tell that much! Why ", "didn't you come get me?\""], "XlxKF95x": ["\"I didn't want to bother you........\""], "BDSKJJLm": ["\"That's not it, right? Why ", "did you try to hide this??\""], "n7wGnwkZ": ["Everyone is staring now."], "PVHmc8sK": ["\"I- I just--....\""], "lVWLxMFF": ["\"B-because she wasn't supposed ", "to be that far in the woods...\""], "FQcFZjjS": ["\"And why was she there?\""], "ftcF44Nw": ["\"I don't know... She went by herself.\""], "X0w82qVf": ["\"Ahhh. There we go.\""], "Xnt8M9VJ": ["\"Now why exactly did you let her go alone?\""], "NVXzWLQL": ["\"I- I was studying.....\""], "XNBGhyRx": ["\"Sorry........\""], "720HyYVG": ["\"I'm beyond disappointed in you.\""], "79H8tKGr": ["\"You really couldn't watch over your own ", "sister for a couple of goddamn hours, huh!?\""], "R0f5fVVy": ["\"L-language, my dear!\""], "B3J0fcbT": ["\"What? We're lucky nothing ", "worse than this happened!\""], "4RWTXTww": ["\"What if Ashley got lost? Or ", "actually hurt?? What then!?\""], "Rlp8qC8j": ["\"...T-true, true..................\""], "qV5DMt1l": ["\"Andrew sweetheart, you were ", "very, very irresponsible.....\""], "cqd7ClwM": ["\"Please go upstairs for a bit, and", "reflect upon your actions, okay?\""], "m4WdJDMV": ["\"No!! That's what he wants to do!\""], "lHqTj9rz": ["\"Andrew, you're going to the garden, and you", "will plant every single sprout in the box!\""], "CV7SCW6Z": ["\"............Got it.\""], "khWj40sX": ["\"......................\""], "6xtwqr1K": ["\" . ... .. ... .. . . .. . ... .. .. . . \""], "KjNSFX8g": ["\"Alright. Pull me up!\""], "0sM5Hq97": ["You're not strong enough to ", "pull her up this high..."], "ZDF30w5V": ["\