 .. .. . . . \""], "FqVC9x1P": ["\"Looks like you're fresh out of ", "excuses not to hang out with me.\""], "NqrG8YqJ": ["\"THAT'S IT!!\""], "cN9h7BCv": ["\"Get over here!! You've had ", "this coming for a long time!\""], "7wbXgS3z": ["\"MO-OOOOM!!!!!\""], "nfCNDmpR": ["\"What is it \\fi now?! \\fr\\c[6]\""], "24Bldqzc": ["\"Andy hit me!!\""], "zbmvvvHH": ["\"No, I didn't!!\""], "slFP9HSn": ["\"(Yet.)\""], "LNHRfhCB": ["\"Uuuuuggghhhhhhrrrrhh..........\""], "hxfXM87C": ["\"Sweetheart, go bother your ", "grandmother for a change.\""], "C4F1HNqV": ["\"But-..!?\""], "yXk11qTk": ["\"\\fi NOW. \\fr\\c[6]\""], "9NQxWjtM": ["\"Nggrrghhg!!! I hate all of you!! HATE!!\""], "h00plXkT": ["\"As for you........\""], "dJ87t1xb": ["\"You picked a \\fi fine \\fr\\c[6] damn time", "to start acting up, Andrew.\""], "qrJmDLqd": ["\"M-me?? Look what she did to my books..!\""], "pNBLbrfm": ["\"Why'd you leave them where ", "she could get to them??\""], "lTH9RBsz": ["\"Oh yeah, I forgot. She's ", "allowed to do anything!\""], "7SJzyQ91": ["\" \\fiAndrew. \\fr\\c[6]\""], "QQTtWwKW": ["\".......................\""], "JK30m5z8": ["\"\\fi Sighhhh..... \\fr\\c[6] Okay. Sit with me for a bit.\""], "LPT2vxpN": ["\"Okay, look....\""], "8rLt3jQq": ["\"You're a really smart boy, Andrew.\""], "XWPmkKWr": ["\"In fact, you're the smartest boy I know!\""], "NyxQ4BRT": ["\" . . . . . . . . . . . . . . \""], "7D4y0ktG": ["\"Far too smart to be picking ", "fights over every little thing.\""], "tTrYPK4d": ["\"Especially as a guest at someone else's house. ", "You're making yourself look like an idiot.\""], "70nNHYSb": ["\"And you're making \\fi me \\fr\\c[6] look like ", "an idiot who raised another idiot.\""], "psdFBW5D": ["\"....Sorry.\""], "mCfnkZ6n": ["\"And if we're all idiots here anyway, ", "should I also start smacking you around?\""], "Wb2z25kZ": ["\"Well!? Should I?? Would that help anything?\""], "WpKLVhL3": ["\"If I punch your lights out right ", "now, will that fix your behavior??\""], "bvQy952s": ["\"No.......\""], "jPHXv8QZ": ["\"I'm sorry I tried to hit her....\""], "7mS3TndB": ["\"I won't do it again.\""], "XbgxrlBB": ["\"Why can't you get along with Ashley? ", "She looks up to you so much.\""], "Pb1glVRP": ["\"..................................I'm trying.......\""], "hFlnq5S2": ["\"But she's everywhere.\""], "W1fVTcjW": ["\"All the time.\""], "kzFpNH1S": ["\"It's--.... I'm going to suffocate. ", "She's eating me alive.......\""], "hRBwCn3b": ["\"That's just how it is when you have a sibling.\""], "vmpN2cHd": ["\".....................\""], "pzzzPF9P": ["\"Ashley is still small, so she doesn't ", "know how to keep her wits about her.\""], "k81mfNkb": ["\"It's on you to keep her safe and sound.\""], "RWr7vKHN": ["\"You\"."], "H1QtfBW9": ["Not \"us\"."], "zXZG4jJy": ["\\fi You. \\fr"], "GnGc53Y1": ["Leyley is Andy's problem and no one else's."], "LqRggt9N": ["\"Won't you be a good brother to her?\""], "6yyYF84d": ["\" .. . ... . . .. .. .... . .. . . . . .. . . .\""], "6fCxW4nc": ["\"Oh, I see.\""], "fy8kH9KR": ["\"I guess you won't, huh?\""], "fJCpxshK": ["\" \\}. ... . . .. .. .... . .. . . . . .. . . . I will.\\{\""], "YzVgb20x": ["\"There you go! I knew I could count on you.\""], "Y2Q1yffm": ["\"Look! Grandma gave me ", "a book! Read it to me!!\""], "W2mXhgzx": ["\"Ask Andrew.\""], "llF7XmJ8": ["\"Good night, little hellions.\""], "4P5L2pq8": ["\"..........You're not still mad, are you?\""], "TJBg1mK1": ["\"No. Of course not.... Did you ", "want me to read you something?\""], "Sv0Bv3GJ": ["\"Yes. This!!\""], "NwD8pRQt": ["\" 'Once upon a time, in a land far, far away...' \""], "pNTmWFp2": ["\" 'Or actually not \\fi that \\fr\\c[1] far, ", "you could visit at any time.' \""], "6sTjtYD4": ["\" 'But if you'd ask your mother why we", "never go, she'd tell you it's too far.' \""], "fCMPwPy4": ["\" 'It's that kind of far away, but I digress...' \""], "GW2h6h3f": ["\" 'O-one day, a young--'.................. \""], "lWvQ7zsq": ["\" ? ? ? \""], "3XgskTh7": ["\" . . . . . . . . . . . . . .\\} *Sob!* \\{ . . . . . . . \""], "L6dgL6m8": ["\"Are you, uhh..... okay?\""], "zRcgwnq1": ["\"....................Do you wanna be friends, Leyley?\""], "2ktcymmT": ["\"I thought we already were.......\""], "cMnMjWbx": ["\"I'm sorry, I don't really--.... ", "....I just don't like you.\""], "bd7JpsK2": ["\"I don't think you like anyone, honestly.\""], "SW1S7X1M": ["\".....................\""], "7JLP462z": ["\"Plus no one likes me. So you ", "not liking me is just the same.\""], "fygjvm2x": ["\"But at least you're nice about it.\""], "W9ygPgRM": ["\"Or you \\fi were \\fr\\c[2] nice about it....\" "], "jmcYqn1y": ["\"I take it back... There's ", "something I like about you.\""], "HCy3XfPm": ["\"Really????\""], "3ZTz3Xtw": ["\"Yeah. Your perceptiveness. Though ", "you don't seem to utilize it much...\""], "nlW0hlYZ": ["\"Percsti- what???\""], "LKN7KX3C": ["\"....Let's say instincts.\""], "CdsXM9Mk": ["\"What? Like some sort of animal??\""], "V1357FxF": ["\"It fits, right? You animal.\""], "9cN7d0nW": ["\"Ahh, whatever. It still ", "means you like me the best.\""], "cXSC4yL9": ["\"Even if your 'best' is like.... ", "a smidge above 'not at all'.\""], "dnG9t9x0": ["\"Hah! See? You're fun....\""], "13Pb9gCk": ["\"You're the one who needs to see it! ", "I've been fun this whole time!!\""], "rkLZlLwb": ["\"Aaaand now you suck again.\""], "z6hMcLT2": ["\"What?? WHY?!\""], "4rXzfyWz": ["\"So fucking obnoxious.....\""], "wf5LbQDg": ["\"Ohh, 'obnoxious'? Lookit meeeee! ", "I'm Andy and I know big words!\""], "SCq0kMqj": ["\"Pfft--- Shut up, you.\""], "tRrvXSnw": ["\"Passable\" it reads on your test. \"Do better.\""], "WwwFp26B": ["\"Did you even try?\""], "YYbfBVjQ": ["\"(Why would I?)\""], "JZ0CW2vp": ["\"(It doesn't benefit Leyley.)\""], "NfJXv778": ["It's just the two of you now. ", "Or maybe it was always like that."], "0qX5pHnt": ["Just you, and the pile of shit ", "that is your little sister."], "p6WWMx2h": ["Andy and Leyley, and Leyley and 