": ["\"Being with you makes me feel like I ", "can do anything. Even staying alive.\""], "8ZyP0rxl": ["\"It's a little funny how we went from planning a ", "murder to planning a family in a matter of minutes...\""], "sGD6Yqrz": ["\"Curious things, those pregnancy tests.\""], "8LZR3KgJ": ["\"I love you. -Douglas\""], "3Gnv7Rj5": ["Oak tree. Someone has carved the number 8 on it."], "3ndN26wX": ["8."], "P7VD82bX": ["Maple tree. Number 5 has been carved on the bark."], "0QCbQw8G": ["5."], "VKLJQcdR": ["Birch tree. Someone has written the number 3 on it."], "sdPybvJ0": ["3."], "lhG2m5dX": ["A cheap combination lock blocks your path..."], "2xFJlBtk": ["You climb through the now open window."], "1kxwdkM4": ["It won't open."], "RxTw5p7X": ["That should be enough blueberries."], "3fNpLS7p": ["\"Why do we have to do something like this??\""], "z5r8JNrz": ["\"It's probably to keep us busy and out of the way.\""], "mL5ZljWV": ["\"Let's just hurry up and be done with it.\""], "tDK9xV84": ["A stick."], "8Y3BBLsc": ["", "Got a Stick!"], "8dFWhVdv": ["A rock."], "c2nzFqLk": ["", "Picked up a Rock!"], "HzJjlcf4": ["A stick."], "gnS9B4m2": ["", "Got a Stick!"], "cklFbM4H": ["\"Now kids, please pay attention....\""], "sx5ntgM3": ["\"My friend wants this car ", "back exactly as he lent it.\""], "rq89JJXC": ["\"Please, \\fi please \\fr\\c[3] don't make a mess.\""], "kRTR4f72": ["\"Kids...? Are you listening??\""], "ClvMrp0G": ["\"Andrew!!\""], "gFDBVQc4": ["\"H-huh? Yeah? No mess. Got it.\""], "hqJNmr89": ["\"Once we're there, you had both ", "better be on your best behavior.\""], "0w0KZbSP": ["\"I don't need a single excuse ", "for your grandpa to rag on me.\""], "ZSNn5ZMk": ["\"Oh, love... I doubt he'll need any excuses....\""], "0tz318cF": ["\"H-honey! What's that supposed to mean??\""], "LbccJwPM": ["\"You know my dad... He'll always ", "find something...\""], "RvzwvsgD": ["\"Ughhhhhrrhhh.....\""], "XFVfp8MY": ["\"We don't have to go. I-I'll take on more night ", "shifts to pay for the new dishwasher!\""], "Q4GpwDdC": ["\"Out of the question! That's ", "bad for your health.\""], "D8yc4q4r": ["\"Anyway love, if your dad asks about ", "the car, say we just bought it.\""], "ZJyFVb8c": ["\"That goes for you too, brats! If they", "ask anything, we're doing great!\""], "1l4z2pbQ": ["\"The only reason we need their money is ", "because 'we just bought a car'. Got it??\""], "492PFys5": ["\"Got it, Mom.\""], "37wfBLz7": ["\"And you, sweetheart? Did you get it??\""], "qTNrHlJN": ["\"Huh?? What? Why are you talking to me..??\""], "qHBDFvfk": ["\"................Make sure she gets it, Andrew.\""], "Z9sh3cdB": ["\"Are we there yet?? I'm boooooooooooooooored.\""], "wcL9mPMM": ["\"Why don't you draw someth--...\""], "V1yZP0dp": ["\"(No, wait! I didn't pack ", "her anything to draw on!)\""], "12rtFzJD": ["\"Yeah!! I'll draw the latest episode!\""], "TmPb1TXp": ["\"Gimme that! And look at this...!\""], "Bm4sGdQw": ["Her drawing depicts a lizard (?) holding a note", "with \"ditsurbanse report!!!\" written on it."], "8kLcJSDW": ["Right on top of your notes."], "P4pMWJ6P": ["\"Well? Well?? What do you think??\""], "NW92zGkY": ["\". . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . \""], "q2g135mf": ["\"..........It's great, Leyley....\""], "0DHKJXCP": ["The boards look somewhat flimsy."], "kjdxykML": ["But you're too weak to kick them ", "loose without hurting yourself."], "hnLFTPzT": ["You're not strong enough as you are..."], "jJXvQxZm": ["You knock the boards loose ", "with the aid of a rusty hammer!"], "KP0qvf1c": ["\"Let's not go this way. There might ", "be squatters sleeping down there.\""], "x3gdtcpd": ["\"Right! We should find weapons first.\""], "lCWvPgGs": ["\"What?? No! We shouldn't bother them.\""], "FNcs6lSr": ["\"Leyley, are you down there??\""], "6ZYjVSq8": ["\"(I'll just take a quick look...)\""], "TYvQVvwF": ["\"Huh. I was wondering why there was", "a combination lock on the window.\""], "nMJTM2q3": ["\"I guess some kids have turned", "this place into a hangout spot...\""], "s2J6wytz": ["\"I want an abandoned house ", "for a hangout spot too!!\""], "C526fTD6": ["\"Well, there is that warehouse...\""], "J501zBKH": ["\"Ah, no! What am I saying??\""], "VTftbVlb": ["\"These places are dangerous. ", "They might collapse!\""], "8YKTDqx2": ["\"We shouldn't have come here.\""], "Xnyg6pvp": ["\"You're the one who opened the lock.\""], "hWBw9n4j": ["\"Err--....... L-leeeet's just find some blueberries...\""], "7x5rcQYC": ["", "Got a Hammer!"], "7mMyF5Nl": ["On the ground sits an ashtray ", "and a lighter, but no smokes."], "NvFHfCLh": ["\"Aww man. I wanted to try!\""], "RMryMlPY": ["\"Wait... Maybe you can still light ", "these already burnt ones??\""], "62JBmC0p": ["\"What the hell, Leyley? ", "Smoking is bad for you.\""], "GZkJ9RM3": ["\"I think it looks cool.\""], "39w9C37j": ["\".......Doesn't seem to work for Dad.\""], "dgmdnYbK": ["\"But gangsters smoke in ", "movies and they're so cool.\""], "3vcNp83q": ["\"They smoke cigars, not cigarettes.\""], "mVbDllZc": ["\"Rockstars are cool too!\""], "0GjcDBRs": ["\" . . . . . . . . . . . . . \""], "yh07Ld5l": ["Something tells you she'll grow up to like bad boys."], "bfxGCKKC": ["\"Don't smoke, Leyley. It gives ", "you wrinkles. And cancer.\""], "tLJJr2CR": ["\"And rockstars won't date ", "cancerous, wrinkly women.\""], "709Y3QdP": ["\"HAhhaHAha!! I don't wanna date a rockstar!\""], "1BtHK4j4": ["\"I'm gonna marry you when I grow up.\""], "x18xZlx7": ["\"\\fi *Cough, cough!!* \\fr\\c[1]\""], "NWvPdGf4": ["\"Whoa there. Are you okay????\""], "1wFVyV6y": ["\"You're way too old to be saying", "stupid crap like that!!\""], "M5qsHdXR": ["\"I don't care! I want a shotgun wedding!!\""], "7pqS9r5X": ["\".................Do you even know what that is?\""], "fn9Nh1Ww": ["\"We start a shooting spree in a church!!\""], "F62HTgHs": ["\"Kill everyone to win a prize! ", "It's a vacation trip to space!\""], "6n0CLsTZ": ["\"The resort is called Honeymoon.", "I've heard it's super wonderful!\""], "lD