n giddy as in ", "lightheaded, then me too...\""], "J0M70fkg": ["\"It could be because of all ", "the mold... I don't know...\""], "JSXf7ppW": ["\"I even passed out for a second earlier...\""], "fYK06BC1": ["\"Wait, you were here already?! WITHOUT ME?!!?\""], "WhH4NG9z": ["\"I was looking for you!\""], "mRdsG9PV": ["\"Now seriously, let's get going before ", "the mold gives us asthma or something...\""], "672Bw3dj": ["\"One of the girls in my class has ", "asthma. She was born with it though.\""], "tZNT0w4f": ["\"I don't care....\""], "3w6Wdncj": ["A metal sheet is nailed to the wall."], "PB3bJfMq": ["You use a hammer to pull out the nails."], "nFF8PTSH": ["", "Got a Metal Sheet!"], "pg1Rw4PL": ["Looks like the metal sheet was blocking a vent."], "rdT6S5Mb": ["\"....Where did these flowers come from?\""], "bHHm0Pnr": ["\"What's with the flowers?\""], "l67PXCF7": ["\"No idea.\""], "NcNwlp0R": ["\"They kind of look like blood stains.\""], "y533v8r0": ["That should be enough blueberries."], "2zwNYVJN": ["\"(Sure I could jump down, but ", "how would I get back up?)\""], "q8v5tsMK": ["\"(There's got to be something ", "around here that I can use...)\""], "wbNR2yvq": ["You need something to help you climb up and down."], "KR47yHpb": ["\"Ooh! Let's keep going this ", "way! How do we get down??\""], "Qp2FF06J": ["\"This episode is titled Andy ", "and Leyley and the--!\""], "mthYpQPd": ["\"--Swamp They Didn't Enter.\""], "rz3nppv4": ["\"Hey!! Why not!?\""], "gT74mwL0": ["\"No. We're not getting lost in ", "the woods for your amusement.\""], "qS0tYZWd": ["\".....Though I do wonder if everyone ", "is secretly hoping for that.\""], "0TGfmWPp": ["\"Mom is for sure.\""], "MtQfJJhj": ["\"We get lost, meanwhile Grandpa ", "grabs his hunting rifle...\""], "Gb4z4DxL": ["\" 'Oopsie-daisy! Thought I shot me ", "some deer, officer! I swear!' \""], "j4DG3wFn": ["\"What officer? Grandma already has ", "a perfectly good pie dough ready...\""], "4DJlpFSz": ["\"HaHHaHhA!!\""], "fp8yHPM2": ["\"Mom thinks it tastes great while Dad goes ", "'Wait, didn't we use to have kids?' \""], "snDMbnJd": ["\"All this and more in the next ", "episode of Andy and Leyley!\""], "b5thBtnr": ["\"Well, that does it then. We're ", "definitely not going this way.\""], "BvK4m23m": ["\"Andy!!\""], "jTKvq8q4": ["\"Ew, ew, ew!! Andy help!! There are spiders!!\""], "3L0LBY0q": ["\"How did you even get over there?\""], "Bnmff5MG": ["\"I was climbing the tree! But ", "then the branch snapped...\""], "Z2jsqHbj": ["\"And now THERE ARE SPIDERS!!!\""], "gksYCMS2": ["\"........I'll come get you.\""], "1nHGjZzF": ["You need more stuff to step on."], "c3BHtp2m": ["You need more stuff to step on."], "NZV3Vh4W": ["There's nothing to step on."], "MrcXQZjv": ["You need something to step on."], "2n52YYTR": ["\"Be careful. This rock is a little wobbly.\""], "DSRJT5BK": ["\"I know what I'm doi--\""], "J3cctvJB": ["\" ! ! ! \""], "S6KYf7wR": ["\"........................\\fi Sigh. \\fr\\c[1]\""], "t9jw24Cb": ["\"Well, that's it. Mom is going to kill me.\""], "h1PKJL8H": ["\"It's not my fault!!\""], "3JdyM9XF": ["\"Just--... let's just go. ", "Don't worry about it....\""], "rzw4CX9Y": ["\"I can't really find anything ", "else to place down...\""], "dlDXrCSh": ["\"Aren't there more sticks or ", "something on your side?\""], "hCnswzDj": ["\"You want me to touch the spiders?!!?\""], "LkbV3QDM": ["\"I don't see any.\""], "8KtfqPjB": ["\"They're everywhere!\""], "TnfpWTYw": ["\"Oh, c'mon. I bet you saw one spider.\""], "SzQ58CS7": ["\"It was a million spiders at ", "least! Get me out of here!!\""], "sBm1RDdT": ["\"Fine, I'll figure something........\""], "tZgXbBF6": ["\"Hurry! HURRY!!\""], "RNsvPDmP": ["\"Before they lay eggs in my ears ", "and eat my eyes and my brain!!\""], "WYWbqfGW": ["\"And then I'll become a zombie and ", "you'll have to set me on fire!!\""], "5XVv05Dq": ["\"Sounds good.\""], "VgtwnRXL": ["\"You're such a jerk!!\""], "d9130R0h": ["Figure out a makeshift platform."], "GVG954PB": ["