, "V5yXt8qB": ["YOU ARE BEYOND FUCKED!!"], "5Z8gqhhR": ["This is it!"], "dDC7LpL4": ["This is the end right here. ", "It's over for you. OVER!!!"], "HTNMhHVG": ["Regardless, the damage is already done. ", "You'd look more suspicious turning tail now."], "RH8yVJFT": ["So you might as well wash your parents' ", "blood from under your nails before you go."], "rBJNFvr9": ["\"Anything else?\""], "3nnsj5hk": ["\"H-huh? Oh... Can I get the restroom key??\""], "z8JltJHj": ["", "Got a Restroom Key!"], "RhtLP6CZ": ["\"Here. Thanks.\""], "ZskG41Gb": ["You return the Restroom Key."], "G9rGgd6j": ["\"Cool. Thanks.\""], "GPxVPCSj": ["The cashier should have the key."], "JGDt1SC1": ["You clean yourself off and say your ", "(hopefully) final goodbyes to Mom and Dad!"], "BXcpJs5j": ["\"I wanna wash up too.\""], "FlPxT8Cg": ["\"No one's stopping you. ", "Just be quick about it....\""], "6YJ60R53": ["\"Like you weren't! What took so long? ", "Were you jacking off in there??\""], "cPh5rWr4": ["\"I have zero interest in bickering ", "with you right now.....\""], "nQtYslsG": ["\".............It's not bickering.\""], "5vwZjFNy": ["\"(Now that that's taken care of, ", "I should figure out our next move...)\""], "XBxWy9xx": ["\"(For now, we should probably--...)\""], "FBrylT34": ["\" ! ! ! \""], "3lVNs5yf": ["\" . . ... . .. . ... . . .. . ... . \""], "KmnVqkZB": ["Two officers of the law have appeared!"], "xHrNrblf": ["\"I swear, if I have to deal with one ", "more drunk driver I'll lose it...\""], "Jq4JpjlJ": ["\"Now, now.\""], "SpHQhXZT": ["\"(...C-calm down.... Calm down. Act normal!)\""], "FFHwC1b7": ["\"(They're not here for us. We're not even in the ", "same district as any of our victims anymore....)\""], "KRqwpLC5": ["\"(It's not like every officer in ", "the country knows of every crime.)\""], "p3f9zcqP": ["\"(...................Or do they?)\""], "SgdT0hyM": ["Best not to draw any attention to yourself."], "4VWLk1Xs": ["Gently, you knock on the door. ", "Hoping only Ashley would hear it."], "yxsqZ33H": ["\"OCCUPIED!! Get lost!!\""], "9PGW70Fx": ["\"As--\""], "qGxsDy5h": ["Nope."], "hyVdfCR6": ["\"L-listen, Ley. We've got to get going......\""], "YS1yxX6Q": ["\"What?? I can't hear you.\""], "nL24WSKn": ["\"We've got to go. Right now. Calmly.\""], "2yQyVPqj": ["\"I'm like half dressed! Give me a minute!!\""], "3vJCKV74": ["You look like a creep right now."], "q7q7mVdF": ["\"Oh, darn. Occupied, huh? Guess ", "I'll just browse while I wait!\""], "K0cvdGCQ": ["\"Are you fucking done yet? We need to go.....\""], "gZ1pzGny": ["\"Alright, alright!!\""], "3RMmmp9T": ["", "Got back the Restroom Key!"], "hZtR2kFq": ["\"Let me in right now.\""], "PnKP5wjc": ["\"I'm just about done!\""], "2VJSX4mx": ["\"\\fi Now. \\fr\\c[1]\""], "sNd2ywvq": ["You make a show of flushing ", "the toilet over and over."], "LtRj26dK": ["Like that'll somehow convince ", "the officers of your shitty lie."], "5GJtrFTP": ["Meanwhile, Ashley keeps trying to dry her ", "hair using the automatic hand dryer..."], "CnwqKZjF": ["\"H-huh? Wait. What the--- Why is it overflowing?!?!\""], "ZP8VwNqr": ["\"EWW!! Gross!! GROSS!!\""], "w2TmnDQt": ["\"Why is it still going!?!? MAKE IT STOP!!\""], "zZqH4lfH": ["\"That can't be good... Do you have another key?\""], "N4jNct2h": ["\"Here you go, sir.\""], "sVK5SqhM": ["\"Unhand the lady at once!!!\""], "YKWzPl3V": ["\" . . . . . . . . . . . . . . \""], "726cD4dP": ["\" . . . \""], "n6fcjPBs": ["\"Was that the police?\""], "s6brlYRq": ["\"...............Let's just leave.\""], "QRV741d9": ["", "You return the Restroom Key and slink away in shame."], "svJ6D1jn": ["\"Uggghhhh..... The food here suuuuuucks.\""], "4gsZDgC1": ["\"No one's forcing you to have anything.\""], "ms35b5fC": ["\"Boo! And we have to eat it cold too!\""], "jLDBPHt1": ["\"(Nothing is ever good enough.....)\""], "pRtgTBFR": ["", "Got Food!"], "v3Kkgxl0": ["\"Oh yeah. I need tampons.\""], "5nnCGNvy": ["\"I guess that's a good sign ", "you're no longer malnourished...\""], "GKtRM29z": ["\"Nor am I pregnant!\""], "27dKrcZk": ["\"That--...... Was that on the table? How??\""], "3vrj0dD7": ["\"How would I know what you've been ", "up to while I've been passed out?\""], "gCL6vtqC": ["\"...............Wow.\""], "p32GCm3B": ["\"Pfft-!! Haha!\""], "93Zpxcwt": ["\"How about you eat shit and die?\""], "v4h2rd6J": ["\"HahHAHah!! I'm kidding!! I'm kidding!!\""], "V7Z5Y3lq": ["\"Forget this...\""], "jh2YmxfR": ["\"Well, don't laugh or anything...\""], "wcQthKw2": ["", "Got Hygiene Products!"], "kqqklddN": ["\"Whoops! Sorry. Did I bump into you?\""], "nSBxYXps": ["\"N-no, no!! My bad. Don't worry about it.\""], "CdY3q9tP": ["\"You don't look so good... ", "Everything alright there, buddy?\""], "pZry443Y": ["\"You've got this! Just remember what I told you.\""], "6BRRwQzW": ["\".......What's the matter with you?\""], "g8Fx0Vnz": ["\"Everything all good there?\""], "2H4MW12r": ["\"I swear that guy is a teenage girl at heart....\""], "bL6Nb5PD": ["It is in this sacred spot that ", "many a man has lost his marriage."], "Swz75RDX": ["For the slot machine giveth, ", "and the slot machine taketh away."], "ZJ6sWHd4": ["A ton of magazines sit on the shelves."], "8hVWCSg8": ["\"You seem really on edge. What's wrong?\""], "T00QknHK": ["\"(Like she cares anyway?)\""], "5NrL3ygL": ["\"C'mon... You're weirding me out.\""], "j605Sj1j": ["\".............I can't shake this nagging feeling.\""], "DT3RmGgV": ["\"I mean, run down as it was, that house was ", "way out of our parents' price range.\""], "bwtcg8tK": ["\"\\fi Sigh....... \\fr\\c[2] Why are you still thinking ", "about them? They're dead!\""], "KhSkfqWG": ["\"I'm still unclear on what the whole ", "death certificates thing was about...\""], "g30HNq5F": ["\"I kinda figured it was some ", "organ harvesting side gig?\""], "7sDfSdmQ": ["\"I mean the letter in their room was clearly ", "about hush money from the water company.\""], "smg618Hw": ["\"But that's what's tripping me up...\""], "dN33rNgw": ["\"Imagine how much money the ", "company would have to dish out...\""], "CRLSRmWW": ["\"...If everyone who sold someone got paid ", "enough for a down payment on a house.\""], "lL72LX74": ["\"No matter what they did, they'd never ", "make their money back that way.\""], "1JcHPYcG": ["\"Especially if they also pay for collateral damage ", "like us, whose organs aren't even worth anything.\""], "QCt19pLc": ["\"I dunno. A tax write-off?\""], "84WBXkr5": ["\".........Hah.\""], "W2Nt54Lx": ["\"My point is, that's too much money.\""], "PBXfj265": ["\"So where did our parents' sudden ", "surge of wealth come from?\""], "gWJ8JQL1": ["\"The only other explanation I can come ", "up with is a life insurance fraud.\""], "C9g4sbCY": ["\"But I just don't understand how Mom would've gotten ", "us good insurance given the situation we were in.\""], "mtXCBc6z": ["\"Why not?\""], "SvjhYkjZ": ["\"They give you a worse and worse deal the more ", "costly you'll be for the insurance company.\""], "hL7nhlcm": ["\"So if we were full of parasites and supposedly ", "dying, our insurance money would be utter shit.\""], "DWYVzXtf": ["\"Okay? But what does any of ", "this matter at this point?\""], "H1vdldkZ": ["\"It matters a lot? We don't ", "have the full picture.\""], "Jb21HT70": ["\"Something isn't adding up.... I'm worried.\""], "SgYyG8md": ["\"You're \\fi always \\fr\\c[2] worried!\""], "8xvX4pRs": ["\"Hell, even when everything is fine, you go out ", "of your way to find things to worry about!\""], "4FZyQhqY": ["\"It's fucking tiresome. Get over it.\""], "Xw6mq0df": ["\"(Thanks for nothing, dipshit......)\""], "9XDQHsrL": ["Various magazines."], "ffQ6Sfkt": ["\"(Calm down.)\""], "kYg4T5DG": ["\"(I'm just some random guy ", "browsing magazines.........)\""], "NQDpPvSb": ["\"(What does this one say.....?)\""], "hBcXsYcr": ["\"Fisherman fishes random skeletons from the ocean!", "\\fb Again! \\fr\" reads an article on the sports section."], "HgRxDj9n": ["\"(OH, C'MON!!)\""], "GRZ6m83R": ["\" 'I've been fishing in this spot ever since I ", "was a wee lil lad,' comments the fisherman.\""], "6z0NDpwz": ["\"(Who cares?! Did they identify the bodies or not??)\""], "h4pyg8JG": ["\"(I can't tell whether the skull ", "has teeth intact or not....)\""], "SbpSV1lv": ["\"I think I'll grab a sandwich. ", "Did you want anything?\""], "WGPX0mLn": ["\"I'm good. Thanks.\""], "hFb6bHPQ": ["Quick! Make something up!"], "lT4G65nH": ["\"J-just some stomach issues... I'm okay.\""], "ptTzFSVw": ["\"Yeah, you look just about ready to shit yourself...\""], "v9fVz2Vl": ["\"I reeeeeally shouldn't have tried ", "eating that spicy chicken earlier...\""], "TL5nbDns": ["\"Lesson learned, haha!\""], "PTv3MtDD": ["\"Why not utilize the toilets here?\""], "XF6PGNck": ["\"Yeah, it's occupied though. ", "The wait is killing me.\""], "tD1fg9rF": ["\"................Alright then. Take care.\""], "dfRC6wYX": ["\"(They didn't buy it at all!!)\""], "0RpT563Q": ["The officers have their eye on you."], "4DXcL6Jh": ["\"(Crap. They're going to see which car we ", "enter and run the plates, aren't they??)\""], "X1W1fzhd": ["\"(And it's the hitman's car! Lord knows ", "what his license plate gives them...)\""], "1TmjZXFq": ["\"(Ahhhh, this is bad. This is so bad!!!)\""], "1rBHBtFS": ["\"(And what the hell is keeping Ashley?!?!)\""], "lnG7FycQ": ["\"Ah-haha! Was it that obvious? ", "It's our first date...\""], "ZYsChzVv": ["\"Ahhh, young love I see!\""], "3JcNsn1T": ["\"Ugh, don't get him started....\""], "wJvGdr85": ["\"Don't worry, son. We've all been there.\""], "7Xk8y4MD": ["\"A bit odd spot for a date though.\""], "VVv0LZFC": ["\"No, no, this was just a pitstop. ", "We're off to do some stargazing.\""], "vDF3RPt2": ["\"You'll make her see stars, alright.\""], "fD2VNmk8": ["\"........I'm sorry?\""], "ZgDPkzkN": ["\"Heh. Just tell her she's got a twinkle in ", "her eye, and you wish upon it for a kiss!\""], "Vvz0XtDR": ["\"......(What the fuck?)\""], "3D17KGFG": ["\"Works every time. Every. Single. Time.\""], "BK9