e of a consequence....\""], "gHCnNSvB": ["\"Like you've got it in you. ", "Go on then! Let me have it.\""], "jxB3kBML": ["\"Fuck this....\""], "Z85DzkF3": ["\"Yeah, didn't think so! HAhaHAhaHA!!\""], "vFyWqC6L": ["\"HEY!!\""], "npLbR0KF": ["\"Are you gonna return the key or what??\""], "ZYyJd1Cn": ["\"Oh, fuck.... Sorry man....\""], "ZSrBBh2B": ["\"Err... Here you go.... Have a good one!\""], "G5Zg1cKC": ["\"I think that went pretty well.\""], "F7QzbVdQ": ["\"I'm pretty sure that went like shit.\""], "tJDznbkF": ["\"The police didn't seem to care.\""], "CjfYY3tV": ["\"Hard to say... Let's just go somewhere ", "and wait for them to leave.\""], "j5hWtt10": ["Are you fucking stupid??"], "c6BNGRdh": ["\"Just so you know, I still love you.\""], "Pr6225h3": ["\"Cool. Thanks.\""], "ShSPXBTt": ["\"Sharing is caring, by the way. ", "Mind if I try the trinket?\""], "BCZ6VRF9": ["\"............Say it back.\""], "QRSBF0ss": ["\"Guess that's a no. Nighty-night.\""], "mVxVb22M": ["\"Andy. Say it back to me.\""], "DTX20VY5": ["\"..............\""], "9S5dLfxd": ["\" . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . \""], "VG9Pc6ll": ["\".........I love you, Leyley.\""], "lWCYyDnl": ["\"Fine. Be that way.\""], "Z3CxBkdq": ["\"I said exactly what you wanted me to.\""], "2BKsrhVz": ["\"Fuck off. How about that, Andrew??\""], "2Qr1YtDs": ["\"Oh, are we not roleplaying anymore? How come?\""], "mnJrdzt0": ["\"I take it back. You can eat shit.....\""], "C0t0WKF4": ["It's against your best interest to ", "upset Ashley given your situation. "], "zsr3nk0S": ["But god, if it didn't feel good."], "bRWG1R4C": [".......For all of five seconds."], "LMkKj2r1": ["Congratulations on sinking to her level!"], "trdnQx00": ["Ashley proceeds to give you the silent treatment."], "mNDdZ8YH": ["It's great. You can finally think."], "ZzGMLqdY": ["\" . . . . . . . . \""], "zYM3MGdm": ["\" ............ \""], "7pMMnckk": ["\" . ... .. .. .... .. . .. .... . \""], "twrvQbmP": ["\"..............\""], "b7ylv2Cd": ["\" . . . . . . . .