u'd ", "keep watch while I sleep.\""], "5RQ82rkk": ["\"Watch \\fi what? \\fr\\c[2] There's nothing going on.\" "], "ZYbQVv9F": ["\"My bad. I should've known ", "not to ask you for anything.....\""], "PGb7tjzV": ["\" . . . . . ? \""], "vJB3VJ74": ["\"......Welcome back.\""], "x3Z51cbS": ["\"You wouldn't wake up, so I thought ", "I'd try to use the trinket with you.\""], "K0pPqv1g": ["\"See if maybe I can come find you. Which I did.\""], "543YBh67": ["\"Probably shouldn't have. Not after all ", "the trouble you went to get there.\""], "CDlrqsfW": ["\"I'm sorry.... I shouldn't ", "have taken your trinket.\""], "n198P3f3": ["\"But with all this new info", "in mind, next time we should--\""], "XQ5QkcrT": ["\"What 'next time'?? You are \\fi never \\fr\\c[2] as ", "much as seeing the trinket again, you thief!!\""], "66h4Nz7w": ["\"Okay, that's fair. But--\""], "qXtV2BmJ": ["\"Nice vision by the way.\""], "4VcNnVjN": ["\"Uhh... What? I'm not sure if I had one.\""], "4MLHvNtb": ["\"Oh, you had one. I saw it too.\""], "6JzsLqnM": ["\"It wasn't enough for you to kill me, ", "you really had to play butcher too?\""], "sqHwCQwr": ["\"........Okay, wait... What are you talking about?\""], "3l0CTz4M": ["\"I was trying to put you back together.\""], "DJmk5ZNT": ["\"How nice of you. After chopping ", "me up in the first place.\""], "n1nprhtf": ["\"Do you really think it's me who did ", "that? Did you miss the giant demon??\""], "Bmtpzjm3": ["\"I \\fi know \\fr\\c[2] it was you, Andrew.\""], "Nzz9n8Kj": ["\"Because I saw it already in another ", "vision. Back at our parents' house.\""], "tfvWmmRJ": ["\"And you didn't feel like telling me this because......?\""], "PRFt6KMg": ["\"Oh, I'm sorry! Do you want me to explain myself, ", "or do you want to hear about the vision?\""], "7DF84SQq": ["\".........Go on.\""], "3BLZ44XY": ["\"Well, first you chased me down to kill me...\""], "NKJmlV6g": ["This is the part where you should act horrified, ", "and deny you'd ever do such a thing! Ever!"], "QWqHhWLS": ["\"Are you sure? Maybe we were running away ", "together and I was just behind you.\""], "4cXFmpmR": ["\"No. You caught me by the neck with the cleaver!\""], "QkT4MzC7": ["\"Oh.....\""], "HRkXppnt": ["\"(She could've just started with that.)\""], "BzvN2ctZ": ["\"And then what happened?\""], "cj2f3dB1": ["\"Well, what do you think happened!?\""], "90r56SWD": ["\"You killed me, you psycho!!\""], "PgYtv8rV": ["\"Oh, just like that?\""], "SGx2JWwt": ["\"What did you do?\""], "gMSXNhrX": ["\"I DIED!!!\""], "wtZWhQ8R": ["\"No. What did you do to make me want to kill you??\""], "Mlkp6JDv": ["\"Be nothing but tender and loving ", "and kind and gentle as always!\""], "LJ3GgsKx": ["\"Yeah, right....\""], "ZfFl1G0W": ["\"What do you think? I blew your ", "fucking brains out, obviously!\""], "gV6DLq0V": ["While it has never been above her to lay ", "hands on you, you're still surprised."], "xGyKdXlh": ["You thought she couldn't live without you."], "jMtSPBJC": ["But looks like that sentiment is wholly one-sided..."], "hhFKgv8L": ["\"....So, why did I try to kill ", "you in the first place?\""], "n7xw6VbD": ["\"You tell me!\""], "ffW0w3MT": ["\"(There are way too many ", "reasons to choose from...)\""], "jCtVJMTs": ["\"It doesn't matter now either way.\""], "qhHF632W": ["\"I was hoping the future would've ", "changed, but I guess it didn't.\""], "65fRdcHr": ["\"It still can. I'm not feeling ", "particularly homicidal. Are you?\""], "qtdN2WX4": ["\"No. But it's clear to me one of us is getting ", "buried. And it isn't going to be me.\""], "607P6Bjw": ["\"Which is why I'll let you pick once and for all!\""], "ftb42M2q": ["\"Who's in the coffin? Andy or Andrew??\""], "5ZVBFgrR": ["It's a bluff."], "hCp5bZ6w": ["Probably."], "ghZc6VMy": ["\"Hm? Can't decide?? Let me put it another way...\""], "THy6GF0N": ["\"Who's under me right now??\""], "wFh0BTJS": ["Once and for all, she says. Make your pick.", "You are..............."], "7VBBKrt8": ["Once and for all, she says. Make your pick.", "You are..............."], "mCLMN7VX": ["\"(This isn't worth it. It's just a name.......)\""], "vk42M4R2": ["By giving her what she wants, you'll at", "least get her off your back about it."], "xXkBTktX": ["She'll be in a good mood too,", "and easier to deal with."], "lNd5mB9G": ["Meanwhile stubbornly putting your ", "foot down on this gives you........ "], "fCV7ryXc": ["What exactly? "], "nkw4xLHc": ["Silent treatment? Attitude? ", "A thousand more arguments??"], "DGpYGrpv": [".....................Her respect?"], "0B3WWZM4": ["Who cares? Just be Andy for her. It's easier."], "MmlYwSDh": ["You like it when things are easy. Don't you, Andy?"], "w9M33qnV": ["You spineless little shitstain."], "7jrgZx0g": ["\"Who's under me right now, Andy??\""], "MVmPzx1k": ["\"Sounds like you already know...\""], "HqNgqxmM": ["\"That's right. It's Andy.\""], "B1kVvbl5": ["\"You're my Andy.\""], "gYLtdGYW": ["\"And you're mine, Andy.\""], "9dlzPFqP": ["\". . . . . . . . . . \""], "yPsv5GBG": ["\"Say it.\""], "F3JjNtyd": ["\"Say what?\""], "2kmQ3279": ["\"That you're mine.\""], "ksBRDLzw": ["\"You've always had a way with words,", "so I know you know how to beg.\""], "C6lxX7Gy": ["\".......Are you getting off on this?\""], "Mhs2qMrz": ["\"HaHhaHa!!\""], "ZjyyLt5Y": ["\"Say it.\""], "xjdyMVDz": ["\" \\fi Sighhhhhh.......... \\fr\\c[1] \""], "q5SBcQL8": ["\"........Yeah.\""], "s79KcWpT": ["\"Properly!\""], "MQj6xnLh": ["\"Aaaahh have mercy, please! I surrender.\""], "2qrn9Y7t": ["\"It is I, your Andy. At your ", "whim. And at your feet.\""], "Y3DywsTv": ["\"Yours, my whole life, which ", "I ask you not to waste.\""], "kYCFwvmr": ["\"Hah!\""], "lnJPjn9r": ["\"Now once again without the flair.\""], "6nMtHZVc": ["\".............\""], "70lCs75X": ["\"Be Andy.\""], "qPFdMM9f": ["\"..............I'll be whatever ", "you want. You know that.\""], "S9jYRyJj": ["\"Hehee!! No takebacks this time!\""], "jKPZzMNR": ["\"No takebacks...\""], "wzzlRGbP": ["\"Andrew.\""], "pHHkRH5W": ["\"I'll give you one chance to fix that answer.\""], "1yHSNHtR": ["\"OW!!!\""], "kxDm8rhW": ["\"What the hell!? You could've ", "poked my eye out!!\""], "v2ZkqNFZ": ["\"I can't begin to fathom why you'd think", "turning against me is a good idea.\""], "fMcb5Xql": ["\"I- I didn't!! I was just kidding.\""], "QH6xSx72": ["\"Yeah? Well, try that again.\""], "Vx4wpPSP": ["\"I will hurt you in ways that only I can.\""], "4LlbTg6t": ["\"Ohohoo, really now, big boy? ", "Don't you mean you'll kill me??\""], "t9pm3dHx": ["\"There's something to be said about ", "self-fulfilling prophecies.\""], "Z6YcGN7T": ["\"Wow. You really just said that to me.\""], "6LxNCjQP": ["\"Y'know this isn't the first time ", "you threw a death threat at me.\""], "Wk6T3HlN": ["\"Indeed, it is the second. What's your point?\""], "4lz7NqH6": ["\"I'm still not afraid of you.\""], "mrpjxDJy": ["\".....It's not that I'm trying to frighten you, Ashley.\""], "xzkhKQ6w": ["\"I'm giving you a warning.\""], "KCsvfQJh": ["\"You don't scare me, \\fi Andy. \\fr\\c[2] \""], "7jLNZ05f": ["\" ... \""], "k41XJJ2s": ["\"Who?\""], "nYG7VdLq": ["\" . . . . . . . . . . . . . \""], "lhdbb0Ps": ["\" .. . ... .. . .. .. . . ... . .. .. . .. . \""], "9WjRyX7B": ["\"What's with that look? You're the ", "one who put violence on the table.\""], "yS9NxXRJ": ["\"...I-!! I didn't mean to...................\""], "7c4G1MBR": ["\"Honestly it's all the same at this point.\""], "602NgQBQ": ["\"There's no getting out of this mess. The ", "only thing we'll be getting is arrested.\""], "PT4j4Nvv": ["\"So if that hurt, don't you worry.\""], "RD1KwQqG": ["\"Soon your shitty brother ", "can never get to you again.\""], "CRLCpg7M": ["\"............We could just leave...\""], "jPyybssb": ["\"Charge the trinket... Get better ", "visions. Go hide somewhere...\""], "C8Pm6fPL": ["\"And then what? Life with you will ", "always be one shitshow after another.\""], "ccRZhlKQ": ["\"What am I struggling so hard to preserve here?\""], "14bh1ryd": ["\"It-... Okay, I get it. I shouldn't have ", "pressed the Andy issue, and I apologize....\""], "rDN1Bpqp": ["\"(Blah, blah, blah....)\""], "crDQ2cXl": ["\"Maybe I haven't been the best sister, ", "or a friend, or anything really...\""], "Gjq10VKN": ["\"But that doesn't mean I can't be! I know it's ", "been rocky lately but we've had fun, haven't we?\""], "Z0hVtb1r": ["\"I promise I'll behave from now ", "on, Andrew. What do you say?\""], "cvrTttPX": ["\"Get fucked, beloved.\""], "r1Kt5bc3": ["\" . ... .. . .. ... . .. . . .... . .. . \""], "ZwSkhNhr": ["\"How many times do you think ", "I'm going to buy that shit?\""], "r2Gb7J27": ["\"So, uhh.... what are we here for?\""], "Bd3D6RN9": ["\"Just some food and bodywash.\""], "vRV4lv4Q": ["\"Oh, and I wanna check the paper.\""], "VlZS3bqN": ["This is some sloppy parking."], "0H77mqTg": ["Does this look like a gas station to you?"], "B6xNWsdd": ["\"For all we know the police are watching. We ", "shouldn't let them know this is our vehicle.\""], "h8XH8pD0": ["\"Well, it's not \\fi really \\fr\\c[2] our car.\""], "3582RDGR": ["\"Indeed, it's actually our home.\""], "sBgzDGS1": ["\"But let's pretend otherwise ", "until the officers have left.\""], "2S12Hy4D": ["\"Whatever makes you happy.\""], "xwQNX3l2": ["Wanna douse yourself in gasoline ", "and play with the lighter?"], "yW62yVST": ["Don't we all?"], "GFKMDxBg": ["Too bad."], "ztzkXTp0": ["\"Well, that wasn't so bad!\""], "9WtBP0ly": ["\"That was absolutely terrible!\""], "pCBDkpxR": ["\"Whatever. Let's get in the car and--\""], "Khjjp7v0": ["\"\\fi No. \\fr\\c[1] We're not getting in the ", "car until the police have left.\""], "yD6VDk0H": ["\"Uggghhhhh......... What a paaaaaaaain......\""], "DWjN54f7": ["\"Let's not loiter around here. We ", "look suspicious enough already.\""], "N282ZX95": ["\"How's that?? We made it!\""], "TKD6tZFM": ["\"I really don't know if we did....\""], "nZfvyxbQ": ["\"Yeah we did!\""], "pH3NmNgV": ["\"Let's get out of here....\""], "dKczc8Vp": ["Use the eraser?"], "x4jsnMdC": ["Use the eraser?"], "mdBdYXcb": ["Use the eraser?"], "q4tk0dJq": ["Use the eraser?"], "krTHZG5r": ["Use the eraser?"], "JMPZfbhG": ["Use the eraser?"], "70ZYHrdp": ["Use the eraser?"], "kzntB8N4": ["Use the eraser?"], "RkpcYtHt": ["Use the eraser?"], "zjTy1GWc": ["Use the eraser?"], "VrwSQd7k": ["Use the eraser?"], "SF0L5TDn": ["Use the eraser?"], "0cXlNv1r": ["\"Good god! Could you have ", "picked us a worse path??\""], "0G5mSPN7": ["\"Yes. Quiet, you.\""], "7r1ch8rK": ["", "Found a small box!"], "sXQTwlHj": ["", "Inside it is......"], "DWSttv8g": ["An engagement ring!!"], "0kMvz05k": ["\"..................Someone screwed up, huh?\""], "QCB5yrfz": ["\"What's it read inside?\""], "p36lfgS8": ["\" 'Edgar + Natalie = 4ever!' \""], "tpT4PggB": ["\"Yeah, I'd dunk that too.\""], "9W48qCCz": ["\"Either that, or Edgar is going to find a ", "key element missing during his proposal.\""], "CMz9xF4z": ["\"Think the ring is worth anything?\""], "JFXg2w2F": ["\"I guess we'll see.\""], "mMTNFwFp": ["\"Let me try it on!!\""], "P1Z8vyzJ": ["\"....Why?\""], "32d4nnTB": ["\"C'mon! When am I ever gonna ", "get to wear one otherwise?!\""], "SwP6RlZy": ["\"Suit yourself.\""], "c8Fqh4MY": ["\"Ooooh!! Look at that!\""], "nNyvdm47": ["\"Seems a tad big for you.\""], "gdFy8W7T": ["\"Tch. Fine... Pawn it.\""], "W38WNWkm": ["\"I was going to regardless.\""], "CB3gFYRL": ["\"What would you engrave on our rings?\""], "L5dQ5248": ["\" 'The biggest mistake of my life.' \""], "c2LrQYsz": ["\"HAHAhaHahaHA!!\""], "gPJfD33k": ["\"So now what?\""], "k9g9wNQF": ["\"We'll wait until the officers leave.\""], "0ZsTkWjf": ["\"Then we'll get in the car ", "and drive the hell away.\""], "FyZwvYrz": ["\"Big plans. And then?\""], "tykFP6HS": ["\"And--... and then--.....................\""], "Vwnv75ZD": ["\"(FUCK IF I KNOW?! I haven't had a clue ", "ever since we escaped our apartment!!)\""], "hdKjj7ky": ["\"(Hell, what would even constitute a ", "favorable outcome at this point??)\""], "jqFg0RJh": ["\"And then what?\""], "mZdtK6yS": ["\"(Do we really have to keep running ", "for the rest of our lives??)\""], "Vm1rmKtR": ["\"(Keep living hand to mouth, and hope ", "and pray neither of us ever gets sick??)\""], "yQxggH6M": ["\"You're just going to ignore me, huh?\""], "QY4SHvcZ": ["\"(Ahhhh, this sucks.... What do I do?)\""], "XKHhn6ms": ["\"(If it was just me, I'd be fine.)\""], "h0NJ0X45": ["\"(I could just make friends and start couch", "surfing until I've secured myself a new life.)\""], "bQYLLn9r": ["\"(But Ashley can't play nice for shit.)\""], "J1FjPQV6": ["\"(And she'll no doubt start freaking out ", "as soon as I spend time with anyone else.)\""], "f3X7YsZY": ["\"(Just what am I supposed to do??", "I can't fix this anymore, can I?)\""], "47w6D3cJ": ["\"There there. If worse comes to ", "pass, I'll just shoot them all.\""], "z6ZpLnCJ": ["\"Can you take this seriously?\""], "YQLYJfGL": ["\"I am being serious!\""], "33rtQSvZ": ["\"I've no qualms about shooting anybody, you ", "included, if that's what it comes down to.\""], "hMBYlmH4": ["\"Okay, whatever... Casual death ", "threats.... Nice. Whatever.\""], "92gSqjvv": ["\"I'm tired... Can you just let ", "me think for a minute?\""], "WmqYJQHP": ["\"Oh, c'mon.... Enough with the overthinking. ", "Haven't you noticed it doesn't help anything?\""], "ZN7kWqhS": ["\"There there, it'll be fine...\""], "dR5PMl0r": ["\"Not now. I need to think....\""], "ZwChB0lk": ["\"Enough with the overthinking. Haven't ", "you noticed it doesn't help anything?\""], "GmMFbQ7c": ["\"Ashley, please....\""], "J08Tys0K": ["\"I really, \\fi really \\fr\\c[1] would ", "like some space right now.\""], "JYwt3t2w": ["\"H-huh??\""], "1xxPh5nD": ["\"Sorry. Just give me twenty-- ", "No, ten minutes. Okay?\""], "rrtNZ4K4": ["\"I just need ten minutes to sit with my thoughts.\""], "dDfcCGVc": ["\"Why can't you share those thoughts with me??\""], "L0qlW1sZ": ["\" \\fi Sighhhhhhhh.............. \\fr\\c[1] \""], "vKmnQzkm": ["\"Why are you pushing me away!?\""], "Kc4VT3Vm": ["\"(Why did I even ask.....?)\""], "c7pfGFKR": ["\"Look, I'm not pushing you away...\""], "QTplhrpY": ["\"Yeah you are, jackass! Literally!!\""], "JKx68Ls8": ["\"All I wanted was to make you feel ", "better, and you tell me to fuck off!?\""], "32TkSfL8": ["Banging your head against the rocks would ", "be more fruitful than this conversation."], "PlfnTsH5": ["\"................Don't do this now.\""], "zNsJtpvS": ["\"Oh, I'm doing this?? I'm ", "in the wrong again, huh??\""], "x8Ffcmrs": ["\"I've done nothing but try to help you, yet--!!\""], "S116kHks": ["\"You know what would be really helpful?\""], "sbrXt0V0": ["\"Me jumping off this cliff, I bet!\""], "ncHvgCNZ": ["\"Let me use the trinket.\""], "mtlnB7nb": ["\"........................\""], "1ZGVFJ03": ["\"Why not?\""], "7PLK9KQ8": ["\"It-....... It just doesn't really ", "work on command like that.\""], "782pp4Jx": ["\"\\fi Sigh...... \\fr\\c[1]\""], "vCHM7Xv2": ["\".............Will you let me use it, ", "if I charge it back up for you?\""], "WXNMK5mn": ["\" . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . \""], "nbbkvqZN": ["\"Still no? C'mon. Play nice.\""], "k0JpYXwr": ["\" .. . ... . ... ... .. . .. .. . ... .. . . \""], "GfhN03wL": ["You're one tiny misstep away from getting ", "your comeuppance for all your heinous deeds."], "sHcfJctC": ["Yet this fucking bitch won't ", "cooperate with you for shit."], "9VJm4JcQ": ["\"(Alright then......)\""], "TyK7Pbd0": ["\"I should mention.......\""], "dJ5BsR3G": ["\"I'm only asking as a courtesy.\""], "LMhj0smr": ["\" ........................ \""], "ZGK2CYFp": ["\"......Y-yeah? Well, I should mention too, I ", "wouldn't mind Andy using the trinket.\""], "LQCLd86L": ["\"Jesus Christ... You're \\fi still \\fr\\c[1] pushing for that?\""], "KsBJWZWr": ["\"I don't understand why you can't ", "humor me on such a small thing.\""], "RtxSwXTQ": ["\"Ashley, I have humored you all my life.\""], "kcZhzdtH": ["\"You told me you'd be whatever I want you to be!!\""], "HFlf4n6H": ["\"I have never said that.\""], "S332v7qZ": ["\"When we buried whats-her-face ", "in that park, you did!!\""], "04bKL4dm": ["\"..............Ashley, I was a child.\""], "CQ5XJWFX": ["\"Things have changed a little since then.\""], "hbr8pPld": ["\"I--!\""], "NsL17X23": ["\"Wait, no. What am I saying? No, they haven't.\""], "88xQKr96": ["\"You're still the same thoughtless, ", "selfish fucking brat!\""], "4nmW53WF": ["\"Hey!!\""], "kZnkhGWv": ["\"But even still, up until we sacrificed Mom ", "and Dad, I thought I can make this work!\""], "2rYYmPx0": ["\"Fuck! For you, I would have--! No, I", "\\fi was \\fr\\c[1] going to be anything! We could've--.....\""], "XlvRH8sF": ["\" .  .  .  .  .  .  .  .  . \""], "KrXPWSSn": ["\"Could have what!?\""], "ZFmKf5gQ": ["\"It doesn't matter now.\""], "QglVtp9T": ["\"And why up to that point!? ", "You agreed to sacrifice them!!\""], "clDDtmYp": ["\"BECAUSE YOU'RE A THANKLESS ", "FUCKING BITCH, THAT'S WHY!!!\""], "t5gWq3nQ": ["\" ! ! ! \""], "nBkdFJPw": ["\"And by the way, you fucked ", "us over by stabbing them.\""], "W4pf4bbF": ["\"If you'd have let me plan it out, ", "we could've left them as they were!\""], "BW70VgFc": ["\"They weren't even dead. No one ", "was going to know what happened!\""], "KtlM6mLl": ["\"No one was going to connect it to us!!\""], "g1Jx2bpN": ["\"But noooo! Hell no! You had to go and--!\""], "SjpR2DTq": ["\"You were happy I did it!!\""], "wSDXJxRl": ["\"I was exhausted! You should've let me think!!\""], "XnKTfbVB": ["\"You weren't thinking shit, Andrew! You ", "were spinning your wheels like always!!\""], "B0mQgRkX": ["\"No. You never fucking let me think! ", "You never let me just exist!\""], "NQrPPRFP": ["\"Why can't you just leave me be?\""], "DRLS4fGx": ["\"Because you're panicking and I'm ", "trying to help you, you asshole!!\""], "KjFHHqzj": ["\"Do you honestly think I want succor ", "from the vilest woman on earth?\""], "JRYPdXBw": ["\" .  .  .  .  .  .  .  .  .  .  . \""], "T6VKjxgC": ["\"(Ah, crap... Too far, too far.....)\""], "RN7lmgbl": ["\"..............Ahah! I- I didn't mean that.\""], "XfDb6jwl": ["\"................Well, would you look ", "at that? The police have left.\""], "F0nSkY3s": ["\"............So they have.\""], "QsDRfsgY": ["\"Then it's fine to get back to the car.\""], "wJzHrdCS": ["\".......Well? Are you coming?\""], "076TFz4C": ["\"Tell me this is the last time we fight about this.\""], "WB5dJRgW": ["\"The trinket?\""], "WdTnL8Hp": ["\"Andy and Leyley.\""], "jjYJws34": ["\"I don't know. That's up to you.\""], "pFRwDt9P": ["\"I can't keep going round and round about this.\""], "D6wHmDCJ": ["\"Then maybe you should suck it up ", "and play along, \\fi Andy. \\fr\\c[2]\""], "32y0W632": ["\"\\fi Stop. \\fr\\c[1]\""], "lblLYpyf": ["\"I'm not asking.\""], "MgQK4YV3": ["\" . . . . . .... .. . ... . . .. . ... .. . Fine. Whatever. \""], "PZy9dgpm": ["She'll stop. For now."], "P0qyNkf5": ["But it won't last."], "PLFwY9Yj": ["It never does."], "X5pp7yBX": ["Soon you're back to where you were staying last."], "bQ8tkg5M": ["A camping site that allows for overnight parking."], "DpxbnmXy": ["He has locked himself in the car."], "fG0QQ0b9": ["\"Goddammit!! Who did you call??\" "], "TGzmrkjw": ["\"THE POLICE!!\""], "L61XXm8G": ["\"(Shit.)\""], "hbfwntYc": ["A map of the camping site. It's mostly the ", "main path and some recommended spots."], "bDgzF1Fq": ["Someone has scribbled \"New Experiences ", "Excite Numerous Wives\" on the corner."], "G83HnqPy": ["\"New Experiences Excite Numerous Wives\" ", "is scribbled on the corner."], "mbjYJGNk": ["Have Ashley clear this segment?", "[Skipping a segment does not affect the story.]"], "mbq59bsl": ["\"New Experiences Excite Numerous Wives\" ", "is scribbled on the corner."], "7m3t6l7l": ["Despite what she just said, if you called your", "ex right now, Ashley would throw a shit fit."], "rxB8Hpdy": ["Wanna see?"], "Sv70kPsV": ["Probably for the better."], "GtH4D1Nm": ["You pick the receiver up."], "RrWzrX3b": ["\"You're gonna call someone? What ever happened", "to not contacting anyone we know ever again?\""], "6TkXq1qt": ["\"That ship has long sailed, don't you think?\" "], "nhBxJWVd": ["\"At this point, we're screwed anyway.\""], "nL7ymfgn": ["\"You don't know that. If we're ", "careful, then maybe--\""], "PXgdrxjt": ["\"Where was this attitude when I cared?\""], "ZYp6gLSm": ["\"..............................\""], "6D8RCyWQ": ["\".....So who are you calling?\""], "61XNZCCw": ["\"That's the part that worries you, huh...\""], "gB07mpRG": ["\"Well, come on closer. I know ", "you want to listen in.\""], "WdSwYVsT": ["\"Hi. This is Julia speaking.\""], "5C4Dt7Qv": ["\"ARE YOU KIDDING M--!?!?\""], "4HbZdfk9": ["\"So much for behaving, huh?\""], "TWZmYkFn": ["\"................Do whatever you want.\""], "lDVJ5dCG": ["\"H-hello??? Anybody there?\""], "RPXWQpgX": ["\"Hello, love of my life.\""], "gd4XLRNl": ["\"...........\""], "K1gySmP7": ["\"Andrew!! Is that---... is it really you?\""], "WYtz7z0x": ["\"Uh-huh. Sorry for not calling you before, ", "I figured you didn't wanna hear from me.\""], "rH2RgHgC": ["\"\\fi *Sniff!* \\fr\\c[6] I-I-... I thought you died!\""], "fMBtF5C0": ["\"There was the fire and I couldn't--! ", "They wouldn't tell me anything!\""], "9htZvzl1": ["\"\\fi *Sob!* \\fr\\c[6] No one had heard anything about you!\""], "BVPsTssM": ["\"Awww, don't cry.\""], "3cLZf6gz": ["\"What happened??\""], "y96tcr22": ["\"I don't wanna talk about that ", "now. I called to talk about us.\""], "WHGPKMMZ": ["\"I'm out of here...\""], "LVQ47mRY": ["\"\\fi Stay. \\fr\\c[1]\""], "fL53gYSp": ["\" .. ... .. . .. .. .. .... . . . . . \""], "T1spgxWC": ["\".......Hello? Are you still there?\""], "vzzL7H3x": ["\"I- I am. I just-...... There's not ", "really an 'us' anymore....\""], "1VW6jYwt": ["\"Sure there is... Ah, unless ", "you found someone else?\""], "L81D86WP": ["\"T-there isn't anyone!!\""], "w1Qm9SKW": ["\"Or.... or I don't know if he's interested...\""], "WPC50X0G": ["\"I see. Does he fuck you better than me?\""], "pJP1X8QJ": ["\"\\fi *Scoff!* \\fr\\c[6] I'm-- I'm going to hang up, Andrew!\""], "sM7lfVjG": ["\"Haha! No, no. Sorry. None ", "of my business. I get it.\""], "nV13H4Sn": ["\"It just sucks that you moved on so ", "fast, considering you thought I died.\""], "3TkGtjg2": ["\"\\fi *Sniff!* \\fr\\c[6] I-.... I really haven't done anything with ", "him! \\fi *Sob!* \\fr\\c[6] He's only been supporting me through--\""], "dn1SSgKZ": ["\"Oh.... Huh....?\""], "vtqfsBDy": ["\" ? ? ? \""], "fB64GtwJ": ["\"Oh, yes... R-right! Listen we--", "You and I are broken up.\""], "1CV2Sv5W": ["\"I'm- I'm not going to take you back just ", "because you gave me a death scare.\""], "9zBP983H": ["\"............Is there someone with you?\""], "96zn1LBb": ["\"No...\""], "FSLntgH7": ["\"I need to go....\""], "XY0PzNyQ": ["\"Will you at least let me apologize first?\""], "MtvZq6h7": ["\".........................\""], "hBMBrjnl": ["\"You were right about Ashley. I handled", "the situation with her really badly.\""], "Y05C2WjG": ["\"I should've put my foot down when it came to her.\""], "HXMqypsY": ["\"But she promised she won't ", "be a problem anymore.\""], "Tb4P4LGT": ["\"Did....... she get hurt in the fire?\""], "8SyXkRyy": ["\"Wouldn't you like that?\""], "3L7r8VtW": ["\"O-of course not!!\""], "hVkGsb9D": ["\"Hah! Anyway, I'm sorry.\""], "1CKn0YS1": ["\"Not having heard from you really ", "opened my eyes to a lot of things.\""], "vWnbfDjC": ["\"Like how I took your patience for granted.\""], "Y4RKRWRk": ["\"How wretched I am without you...\""], "PqfYcVrh": ["\"Life without you is just one", "disappointment after another.\""], "z1Q1XTXX": ["\" \\} You're such an asshole... \\{\""], "wyvHfCs2": ["\"You're the most alluring thing ", "I've ever laid my eyes on.\""], "jKJKQMXK": ["\".........You made your choice, Andrew.\""], "2zkfz6nf": ["\"Yeah, it was you. Wasn't it?\""], "4fWLF6Pz": ["\"Umm....?\""], "1t6qV75T": ["\"I chose you, didn't I?\""], "Lfq1YYyJ": ["\"Every time I walked out the door and ", "came to you, I chose you over her.\""], "39l3jgH8": ["\"I mean...... I guess? But....\""], "b1tTGQg3": ["\"You guess? I left that half-wit to", "sit at home and cry. Over and over.\""], "nLqwCYmQ": ["\"And god, I knew she'd cry.\""], "SsBy2FxM": ["\"From being so mad.\""], "mLKJRYZ8": ["\"And oh so sad, the poor ugly thing...\""], "bg1qCfdn": ["\".....Is everything alright with you?\""], "5k6Zyc9c": ["\"This-... this isn't like you, ", "Andrew... Did something happen?\""], "Dl1bMMKX": ["\"Well, it's been awhile since you last saw me.\""], "tDsfFtqj": ["\"......I'm.... I really am glad you're ", "okay, but-- But I need to go. I'm sorry....\""], "yjJqmzJV": ["\"I guess you don't like me anymore.\""], "T9h7fDp9": ["\"That's--............ Huh?\""], "mcgH0PJL": ["\"T-that's right! I don't. Not anymore.\""], "yRVZPhHq": ["\"Just leave me alone. Don't call me again...\""], "Lqpfkrzz": ["\"....These aren't your words, Julia. ", "Is someone telling you to say that?\""], "Mj6qmmmx": ["\"I feel like I'm talking ", "to your sister right now.\""], "Hg3YkDs5": ["\"Please, I-... I don't want to fight. I--\""], "fsdZwpYB": ["\"\\{ WHAT THE FUCK DO YOU ", "WANT, ANDREW!?!?!? \\}\""], "WzmbJ4Yz": ["\"..........Hi Jane.\""], "LvS8qz7W": ["\"This is a bit of a private conversation, ", "if you get what I'm saying.\""], "Vyf8m6Zp": ["\" ................. \""], "LJ8R9mxZ": ["\"What part of 'leave me alone' mystifies ", "you?! Haven't you done enough?!\""], "VyK9jJgQ": ["\"And what did I do exactly?\""], "BS2gyNxY": ["\"Don't you even start with ", "me, you piece of shit.\""], "ynCzWD2H": ["\"Okay, whatever. That's fine.\""], "xq7rStSt": ["\"Say, are you always this overbearing, ", "or just when it comes to me?\""], "Nqb2svTw": ["\"That's rich coming from you! Did ", "you fuck your little sister yet??\""], "Vnl52wNx": ["\"No, but I fucked yours.\""], "5hFNdPxs": ["She hangs up."], "1v8grw6C": ["\"Pfft.... HahhaHAHhaHAHA!!!\""], "nw28kMJb": ["\"What the hell was your goal here?\""], "F2tlTqK3": ["\"Ahhhh, I got dumped so hard. Oh well.\""], "TkD74t5G": ["\"So she \\fi can \\fr\\c[1] behave. Somewhat.\""], "tQqmWkrh": ["\"\\fi Hmph! \\fr\\c[2] You dared to ", "doubt me? Shame on you!\""], "x8rCkTXQ": ["\"Despite your underhanded ", "bullshit, I emerge victorious!\""], "R243JN5B": ["\"Yes, yes. I was wrong. What a ", "somewhat good girl you are.\""], "rpWZskmr": ["\"HahHaha!!\""], "S1XQWp89": ["\"Oh, I see how it is! You slap ", "one side, and kiss the other.\""], "66Ys09Cr": ["\"So these are the brotherly ", "affections of Scumbag Graves?\""], "8HYwlPSp": ["\"It's the duality of man.\""], "D4bnnvbm": ["\"Yeah, well... You showed your true colors a little", "too much. You're never getting your ex back now.\""], "bkm5FMfV": ["\"Do you genuinely think I want to?\""], "D6Pg9rwg": ["\"I can't tell....\""], "zvpRKr4k": ["\"\\fi Some \\fr\\c[2] part of you seemed into it.\""], "5yh9xP6D": ["\"You're wrong.\""], "LtkCqpDm": ["\"By the way, your apology has been accepted.\""], "svjzVrL7": ["\"Well, gee... Thanks. Is that ", "what this was about?\""], "JnBm5dxw": ["\"Who knows.\""], "MKLJ0867": ["\"Let's start over. Just you ", "and me, like we agreed.\""], "Cm6Xnd2l": ["\"It's you and me and the demon.\""], "ZlrCK6yd": ["\"You and me, Ashley.\""], "ydZ2WX0G": ["\".............Me and you, Andrew.\""], "8TTSlJm7": ["\"Heh.\""], "FPwxW0RQ": ["\"Come on, then. Let\u2019s go ", "sacrifice some campers.\""], "4CYHpT9N": ["\"Y'know, I do have bullets.\""], "KHfxQlmY": ["\"Hm?\""], "W8lRL8r2": ["\"I think I know who you plan on calling...", "I'm just saying you better not.\""], "g2zzhV1s": ["\"Oh, so well-behaved you are.\""], "gNcvkmkv": ["\"I think I'm justified in stopping ", "you from making things worse for us.\""], "2x4gymFM": ["\"You know what? Fair...\""], "9HPCq2yp": ["\"But you're not justified in giving death threats.\""], "lz85XzLx": ["\"At this point, isn't it how we show our love?\""], "shzB3pMx": ["\"....Ha!\""], "fkFXgMqY": ["\"Fine, you win this one....\""], "h5zZrbv1": ["A payphone you could use to call ", "your parents if you had any left."], "wMD9gCmK": ["\"....We're back to where we started?\" "], "Q8ccTQbT": ["\"I must've taken a wrong turn...\" "], "jswq5x5V": ["\"Get it together.\""], "1Ryy897f": ["\"Hiiii there, friends!\""], "yb1tJp5Z": ["\"......Can I help you?\""], "xsf1LVdm": ["\"You sure can! Where do we pay the parking fee?\" "], "ZDvZSyZ3": ["\"We'll be staying for a few ", "days but the booth is closed.\""], "x6cn0M4b": ["\"Right... I guess you missed the workers.\""], "Bt4Lrtqd": ["\"Oh no... Do you think it's fine ", "if we pay in the morning??\""], "d8dsT9X5": ["\"(Fuck if I know? Why is he asking me??)\""], "37jh4s2Z": ["\"Yeah, that's fine. Don't worry about it.\""], "bB064hy6": ["\"Phew! What a relief!! Thank you so much.\""], "3R0bCST6": ["\"Uh-huh. Take care, it's pretty dark out there.\""], "jmtX7RrM": ["\"Will do! Thanks again.\""], "4SDX0L3Q": ["\"(How should I know?)\""], "rp4gN4Vn": ["\"Uh, it's.... probably okay?\""], "c1F64sJ0": ["\"Oh... Well... I guess we'll go ahead, ", "and ask for forgiveness later, haha!\""], "csns8Fww": ["\"Ahaha........ W-well anyway, take care.\""], "7S8Bk9QG": ["\"C'mon then, let's go find ourselves a camping spot!\""], "gFygTG3B": ["\"Mom, why was she sitting on him?\""], "D1q901mr": ["\"Err... I-I'll tell you when you're older...\""], "d6fDf4Dr": ["And off they go! Into the woods in the dead of night."], "Mn6gK4j2": ["\" . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . \""], "5yLq5G8l": ["\"...........Time to charge the trinket?\""], "HlKQPTxW": ["\"............................\""], "YQ1R8xCm": ["\"Aaah, you know I can't say no to a family value pack.\""], "qwYWnBnr": ["\"......Who am I to oppose you?\""], "CkJpWF7w": ["\"Now get off me. Even strangers think we screw.\""], "s6pk4lZ1": ["\"HahHAHAh!! Reminds me of high school!\""], "qk7gG5c8": ["\"Reminds me I want to kill you...\""], "TbsvqbQd": ["\"Yeah, no joke!\""], "Y0bthtMk": ["\"NOOOOOOO!!!!!!\""], "CnWYlsbK": ["Well, that's it."], "V9rkR10s": ["Go get your sister. Maybe you've got five ", "or ten glorious minutes of freedom left."], "QR4r3rQw": ["", "Got a Rock!"], "5RjppG0W": ["\"No!! NO!! Please go away!! PLEASE!!\""], "gc09K96Y": ["Return to Ashley?"], "YZCvK9wG": ["The child runs off."], "NQXrSGwv": ["So much for no signs of struggle."], "zybYP4xr": ["You bash the rock against the window!"], "zMDyC0c6": ["\"Nooo!!! \\fi *Sob!* \\fr\\c[4] Leave me alone!!\""], "nGLPRxVr": ["\"Hmm...  Can I try?\""], "9Hv9Bb7c": ["Have Ashley clear this segment?", "[Skipping a segment does not affect the story.]"], "RwW1PWNL": ["\"Well, if you change your mind, ", "let me take a look at the map.\""], "NLcYJRDS": ["\"Crap. We're back here again...\""], "jD4FDGl4": ["\"I had no idea my sense of direction was this bad....\""], "kTC2FZ6n": ["\"I have an idea. Want me to try?\""], "my5DbyQq": ["Have Ashley clear this segment?", "[Skipping a segment does not affect the story.]"], "Cc9SWDKq": ["\"If you change your mind, let's take a ", "better look at those flowers right there.\""], "j2G6W9m9": ["\"A-ha! There they are.\""], "tm4XnmXF": ["\"Quiet. We need to set up the", "ritual somewhere nearby first.\""], "LlkW4DQN": ["Three blue flowers."], "ddGn9RG3": ["Three blue flowers."], "VD7nFfJ5": ["Have Ashley clear this segment?", "[Skipping a segment does not affect the story.]"], "H9jWhNgv": ["Three blue flowers."], "hy2Njd97": ["One pink flower."], "CW9Zgf3s": ["One pink flower."], "CQy5f1FL": ["Have Ashley clear this segment?", "[Skipping a segment does not affect the story.]"], "5pWzJkvs": ["One pink flower."], "Kw7qJfRW": ["Two orange flowers."], "WX1CRJNN": ["Two orange flowers."], "YrWm4NV2": ["Have Ashley clear this segment?", "[Skipping a segment does not affect the story.]"], "wfCPmPsj": ["Two orange flowers."], "7LL820qX": ["\"Hi there, friends!\""], "PxYDDj3K": ["\"You're the people from earlier! ", "Thanks again for your help.\""], "nqvDG90t": ["\"Hope we're not bothering you or anything.\""], "hlMF9kGL": ["\"Not at all! It's nice to meet you.\""], "g846CClb": ["\"This here is my lovely wife! Her name is--\""], "KYfrPSq4": ["Whatever."], "tvJ26krq": ["\"And I am--\""], "P002GY2m": ["Irrelevant."], "ry81Nr1r": ["\"Pleased to make your acquaintance. ", "I'm Jacob, and this is my-.....\""], "FB4M6PcZ": ["\"My cousin, Tanya!\""], "fb2Z5sNt": ["\"...............................Oh.\""], "T1C77D2n": ["\"You're cousins.....?\""], "v607BQ2D": ["\"That's, uhh.... It's good to meet you Jacob and Tanya.\""], "C74gm7HD": ["\"Yes, um........ A-anyway, it's kind of late, so.......\""], "wt89Rktw": ["\"(What the hell is with this reaction??)\""], "L8h48wby": ["\"(Ah, wait... Do they really think we ", "were getting busy in the car??)\""], "CWQZ6FbR": ["\"(Fuck...)\""], "L5WH5djx": ["\"HAHAA! Got you!! I'm kidding! We're just friends.\""], "LTD4JJXB": ["\"Ohhhhhhh! HAHAHAH!!!\""], "6YvzkK3P": ["\"You got us good! I really thought so for a moment.\""], "HsVsY8Xg": ["\"That was mean, you look so alike I was convinced!\""], "ckyWdRtT": ["\"Yeah, we get that a lot for some reason.\""], "2T9HBwKk": ["\"What a thing to joke about!", "You're really something.\""], "vL3NylC6": ["\"Oh please, you prudes. What the hell is it", "to you if he was balls-deep in his cousin??\""], "DzXwGXzL": ["You now remember why you don't ", "introduce Ashley to people."], "xx79c3Nx": ["\"What?? He wasn't. All I did was sit on his ", "cock. It's not like he was even hard.\""], "2WZVWGXR": ["\"(Please stop talking. Oh my god....)\""], "8ZZbVthx": ["\"Besides, he could be full-on nailing me, and ", "there'd still be zero input required from you!!\""], "HBSSpHkZ": ["\"O-kaaay!! It really is getting pretty late. ", "Hope you guys have a great evening! Bye bye!!\""], "j7bx8ZJx": ["\"What. The fuck??\""], "NcnTSF1M": ["\"What?? I was trying to make conversation.\""], "pMVpc4YZ": ["\"How socially inept are you!? It's fine to be crass ", "with me, but you can't talk that way to strangers!\""], "hFzdJz6S": ["\"They're the ones who heard we're 'cousins' ", "and immediately jumped to inbreeding!\""], "56kpxX8T": ["\"Like, what is up with those guys?\""], "PjSxJlwy": ["\"Who cares? Now how are we ", "getting them to follow us???\""], "PmNXhcNn": ["\"Just go start the fire. I think I've got it.\""], "N7FS2QNc": ["\"I don't believe you've got this for a second!\""], "LdcGlq5R": ["\"Just go! I got it!!\""], "l43S9krD": ["\"HA! I told you they weren't banging in the car!\""], "mBY4Fxzl": ["\"..................\\fi What?? \\fr\\c[1]\""], "VLx50kDW": ["\"Haha! Sorry. My wife has such a dirty mind.\""], "CgHF5j6g": ["\"I-it's not that! I was just saying it was rude of ", "us to interrupt, no matter what they were up to!!\""], "916mcFq1": ["\"Err... W-well, I'd love to keep ", "chatting, but I forgot something...\""], "G5p7c9P8": ["\"Stay here, Tanya. I'll be right back!\""], "WHVSJcb8": ["\"Sure thing, Andy.\""], "t0tc8tB9": ["\" . . . . . . . . . . . . . \""], "5y7HTXD7": ["You better hurry up."], "6vC8GyWD": ["\"My friend, Tanya.\""], "TWXpCmrm": ["\"Hello Jacob and Tanya!\""], "0jsRdRzv": ["\"Friends, huh? Ohhh, I'm sure you are quite the friends.\""], "7dxVQdls": ["\"Pardon?\""], "pQjSqMTY": ["\"I saw what you were up to earlier in the car, haha!\""], "nNMDzY9n": ["\"Ooh la la, such friendship, am I right??\""], "T1XzQj71": ["\"Pfft-... Hahah!!\""], "Ssk3bgnY": ["\"(If he honestly thought we were going ", "at it, why did he interrupt us?)\""], "WhmCwXVb": ["\"Now, now. Let's not assume. It ", "might be a complicated situation.\""], "RQD4RcNT": ["\"It's complicated, I'll give you ", "that. Mind if we join you?\""], "jSbk77WP": ["\"No, no! Go ahead! Don't be strangers. Have a seat!\""], "lFQmqJ27": ["There are no seats to be had."], "cwRDYsgp": ["But you stick around anyway to listen ", "to the tale of how these two met."], "3R2T978n": ["It is mind-numbing."], "6fWN3FyJ": ["\"Wow.... That is easily the most ", "inspiring thing I've ever heard.\""], "kq3Sdzqy": ["\"However, nature calls. Excuse ", "me, I'll be right back.\""], "w8mmvls9": ["\"No, hold up, hold up. You're staying here.\""], "96Qkt3DY": ["\"Wh--... \\fi Alone!? \\fr\\c[2] With ", "these weirdo peeping toms??\""], "lC8vbSJm": ["\"The woman seems fine. I'll go ", "light the fire and call you then.\""], "xP56K8yt": ["\"Yeah, I bet the woman seems fine to you.", "I bet she looks real fine too, huh?\""], "BjrlznTb": ["\"Not this shit again...\""], "NV2Nq05B": ["\"She must be a real feast on the eyes after ", "you've been stuck with me for so long!\""], "wqg3WgWN": ["\"Yeah? Should I fuck you in the car ", "to make you feel pretty? Lay off.\""], "TgFDMwSd": ["\"BHAhHahaHA!! Wow. Kill yourself.\""], "6865D7GN": ["\"Not today. I'll see you in a bit, nightmare.\""], "LTmRHRQ9": ["\"Leyley, please......\""], "D2PygZT1": ["\"Hmph! \\fi Fine. \\fr\\c[2]\\ Whatever.\""], "x740FdpL": ["\"....Is it fine?\""], "cY6M638W": ["\"I said whatever! Just fucking go already.\""], "p7nllqSG": ["\"(...Isn't her behavior getting worse?)\""], "GGLpwMJz": ["There is no one inside the tent."], "BbmgRkQN": ["\"(Oh, crap.... Where's the kid??)\""], "4c6wjNBk": ["\"(I know the brat didn't go ", "this way. I would've seen him.)\""], "bRwBTWqP": ["\"(Alright, I think I've waited long enough...)\""], "VW5PgNhD": ["\"You again... What is it?\""], "0g5k8Yfz": ["\"I'm starting to wish we picked a different camping spot...\""], "NlvlwtLj": ["\"I'm just checking in to ask ", "if that treasure is yours?\""], "H6CGVNRn": ["\"Uhh.... Sorry, what?\""], "b125wvLg": ["\"That suitcase with a bunch of money and some ", "white powder bags. Did you guys drop it?\""], "MM2ZkL6P": ["\"Money...?\""], "dtW9byW6": ["\"Uhh... Y-yeah!! It's ours. ", "Thank goodness you found it!\""], "vRd5ZWFq": ["\"Say, where exactly did you find it??\""], "nd7QpRyw": ["\"Right over there! Come look.\""], "NPdNmkmK": ["\"So.... What do you do for a living?\""], "BcZMZTnG": ["\"Armed robbery.\""], "4Vllqz3P": ["\"Oh my god! Tanya! Come quick! ", "You've got to see this!!\""], "g19hvQfY": ["\"Guys, guys!! You won't believe ", "what I found! Come look!!\""], "4VFLV5VX": ["\"Oooooh boy! What could it be? ", "Let's go take a look-see!\""], "rpX0dMsQ": ["All the wood is soaked.", "Someone has put the fire out."], "YgNM1Wmk": ["No forest fires tonight!"], "pSkL9y0l": ["This is almost climbable."], "V3zTdr8L": ["A platform is needed."], "JdGwXXM4": ["\"......It's the fire that matters, ", "not the candles, right?\""], "RDmxct7J": ["\"I'd say so.\""], "Rs5R9LkD": ["\"Then let me find some dry wood and foliage...\""], "rWV7W2CS": ["Consider this a candle."], "vdxvx3nN": ["You pile up the burnables while ", "Ashley draws the circle."], "BdyQHr08": ["\"Tadaaah!!\""], "H5305XWm": ["\"The.... \\fi pen \\fr\\c[2] ran out of ink before I could ", "draw the runes. But hey, close enough. Right??\""], "Bk9n9gSv": ["\"Not a single thing in this setup is right...", "Will the demon even show up??\""], "jQRJy7xP": ["\"Haha!! I wouldn't. But let's try anyway.\""], "Bv2HRDmg": ["She throws her makeshift pen into the campfire."], "hCY92hKn": ["\"(Well... here goes nothing...)\""], "sBNcl5Sh": ["\"Hey... Come here for a bit, Ashley. ", "I need to tell you something.\""], "xl76MCnR": ["\"Yeah? What's up?\""], "bdLG3gpr": ["\"Okay, listen... This is ", "very, very important.\""], "rghzwlsH": ["\"What the hell? Why are you ", "talking to me like a child??\""], "6hWSn6cJ": ["\"I need to make this absolutely clear...\""], "wHjl2z9m": ["\"We are \\fi not \\fr\\c[1] killing these people.\""], "YkWhWG0c": ["\"Okay?\""], "JSgJdvZV": ["\"Under no circumstances can it look like ", "there was a physical altercation.\""], "phC25cbG": ["\"We are to leave the bodies completely unharmed, ", "so that no one will know what happened.\""], "ly4lxvzW": ["\"Oooh, look at you! Little Andy ", "thinks he can boss me around.\""], "lTQMR0pq": ["\"Ashley, this cannot become ", "a murder investigation.\""], "cRrtW2tx": ["\"We're caught on camera. We \\fi will \\fr\\c[1] ", "be looked into as suspects.\""], "yls2dC6K": ["\"Then they'll figure out we're ", "not dead, and track us down.\""], "83hnwTsT": ["\"Let the comatose bodies be a ", "medical mystery instead. Okay??\""], "b3NxhZ5w": ["\"Look, I'm not gonna do ", "anything stupid, alright?\""], "7Jrzvpy9": ["\"...........Do you promise?\""], "464pYdyQ": ["\"Andy, I prooooomise. Cross ", "my heart, we'll be fine.\""], "F8bB6nW2": ["\"(We're not gonna be fine at all....)\""], "JyhkPqv0": ["\"Yeah, whatever. I got it.\""], "w3JFWwH8": ["\"No. Not 'whatever'. Please ", "take this seriously........\""], "5zWsWqTY": ["\"I AM! Jesus Christ!!\""], "h362rmWn": ["\"Then act like it! I need to know ", "you won't fuck us over again.\""], "YpQ7nvXB": ["\"Don't you bark orders at me, Andrew.", "I'm the one with the loaded gun here.\""], "nHFXx5qT": ["\"Keep that attitude, and I'm ", "taking it away from you.\""], "R77JMkpB": ["\"Try it, asshole. See what happens.\""], "3TJmWJ8q": ["\"\\fi Sigh... \\fr\\c[1]\""], "jJRQ75Vj": ["She is Jesus Christ."], "DBVPDjyJ": ["\"You seriously don't have to spell ", "this out for me like I'm some idiot.\""], "GnfKq2Ft": ["\"I don't know. Sometimes you ", "do the dumbest things...\""], "PPbHyMmp": ["\"Like you haven't made your ", "fair share of mistakes here.\""], "zxpvX5KY": ["\"Yeah, mostly listening to you.\""], "JY5zB48w": ["Try as you might, the fire won't start."], "WwBbWNGs": ["The little bits of foliage are quick to burn,", "but the larger sticks won't catch fire."], "rHqFndnj": ["\"(God fucking dammit, I hate the outdoors!!)\""], "FpZRT5H3": ["\"(Isn't there anything else to light??)\""], "B3g2vvXs": ["Perhaps more tinder will do the trick."], "3sdJf8Tc": ["No flames emerge."], "PYc50RXz": ["\"(There exist people in this world who ", "find camping a delightful experience.)\""], "y44TJ9Sb": ["\"(I appear not to be one of them.)\""], "MPSYRFxv": ["In a last-