ikE yoURs coMe hErE to DiE.\""], "zfHQMV9d": ["\"Oh.....\""], "rGfbJBxQ": ["\"LeAve noW iF yOuR sOuL mEanS AnyThinG tO yoU.\""], "5ylmzCXB": ["\"And.... how do I do that??\""], "9cmCwz5M": ["\"iF yOu dON't kNow hoW, yoU caNnoT.\""], "FpH2Q30F": ["\"WhY diD yoU cOmE aLone, bRotHer?\""], "vs2dsfKJ": ["\"I thought I'd just see a prophetic dream...\""], "47NgqLqX": ["\"She didn't tell me this was an ", "actual place.... dream.... thing.\""], "v6mn05GX": ["\"It iSn'T yoUR tALismAn to uSe.\""], "Z932jZgG": ["\"GoOdbYe, BrOtHer.\""], "b0JTlDc6": ["\"W-wait! Isn't there something you can do?\""], "hsCGBXtK": ["\"C-c'mon... Can't we make a deal or something??\""], "4PCtgSXz": ["\"I nEeD nO GriMe sOUL.\""], "kV0rvGLb": ["\"EvEN LesS a GriMe SoUL stUcK iN a ViSion.\""], "Grkt4m29": ["\"GoOdbYe.\""], "mN6V2Csv": ["\"No, no! Wait! Please don't go!!\""], "4G540mCv": ["\"(Crap... What did it mean 'stuck'??)\""], "vfjrPSR7": ["You recall being unable to wake Ashley ", "up when she was sleeping some time ago."], "4PFW29Kl": ["The same happened with the ", "soulless husks of your parents."], "bt4JL9lK": ["\"(Great........ For now, I should--)\""], "DLpB1sY4": ["\"(..........Oookay..?)\""], "mBb289RM": ["\" .. ... . .. . .. ... .. . . . .. ... . . .. . \""], "ML3v6qPY": ["\"(No, no, no. Please no. Goddammit... ", "Leave me alone!!)\""], "dqrWbqsf": ["Whatever this is, it doesn't seem to be active."], "s321zlRP": ["", "\"YoU aRe nOT TaR sOUL.\""], "T2fMqx5L": ["\\n<? ? ?>\\c[5]", "\"LeAve.\""], "x13Rcq0c": ["", "\"This PLacE is NoT fOR yoU. LeAve.\""], "vPK6vlJ6": ["", "\"LeAve. YoU aRe uNweLcome.\""], "nWLK9LcF": ["Fuck this?", "[Skipping a segment does not affect the story.]"], "xHKvZcSr": ["Fuck this?", "[Skipping a segment does not affect the story.]"], "hwL8HJY6": ["\\{ Fuck yeah it's a wooden plank!!! \\}"], "0l4ZpCMv": ["Whether crossing balconies or burying ", "kids, a wooden plank is all you need!"], "kgnvNncg": ["Always at hand! Even in a demonic dreamland!", "It is fate that