at this is about..."], "PyHPCyBd": ["A sun symbol."], "rK7808mK": ["The symbol on the floor has reacted to the Sun Stone."], "C462zNgz": ["So that's why that happened."], "dR1TBwYb": ["\"Let's leave the stone here. It ", "probably belongs on that spot anyway.\""], "gHzC0Cs8": ["\".......................If you say so.\""], "G5WspvmV": ["A faint flame."], "C6hzVNwt": ["A faint flame."], "rWRK59JD": ["Added Firewood onto the fire pit!"], "p5JBZ2mP": ["", "Got a Sun Stone!"], "wNC5vrxZ": ["Clearly you could plant something here..."], "8w6NVKFk": ["It probably needs to be watered."], "3QQp7f70": ["", "Got Flower Seeds!"], "sKFcH5GT": ["", "Got a Bucket!"], "l6zPRprv": ["Water."], "2gNyYKnG": ["Presumably."], "GmV9rVfB": ["Liquid."], "YZ7spL8q": ["You filled the Bucket with water!"], "2jpvMf3V": ["Clearly you could plant something here..."], "V81prlMM": ["It probably needs to be watered."], "QnD66Mv5": ["Clearly you could plant something here..."], "NRHGs9XN": ["It probably needs to be watered."], "x5Zyctmv": ["Clearly you could plant something here..."], "ycqgGtGM": ["It probably needs to be watered."], "DmFFMwRb": ["Clearly you could plant something here..."], "xcVy6zW9": ["It probably needs to be watered."], "lBrBd6BV": ["Clearly you could plant something here..."], "hTcNZsMQ": ["It probably needs to be watered."], "Ryfy3Z56": ["Clearly you could plant something here..."], "rHDF06kp": ["It probably needs to be watered."], "bd47GBv0": ["Clearly you could plant something here..."], "xD1kCy3Y": ["It probably needs to be watered."], "wd2RsR9V": ["Clearly you could plant something here..."], "7CvcWz3D": ["It probably needs to be watered."], "YvwVpJ9r": ["Clearly you could plant something here..."], "5xPKzL2g": ["It probably needs to be watered."], "LcdQLTs2": ["Clearly you could plant something here..."], "FWXvJRQs": ["It probably needs to be watered."], "bzGYrLFl": ["\"HahHAHaha!! Wasn't that something, huh?\""], "4KScC3gj": ["You have too many thoughts to put into words right now."], "H9z1SFrM": ["\"Ahh, don't be mad.\""], "XqxgF6v9": ["\"Look, everything is fine. More than fine!\""], "CLHQnGYY": ["\"We're in the Demon Realm! How cool is that??\""], "8ghgG8Lj": ["\"Or actually I think this is the Realm ", "Between... Did the demon mess up?\""], "SHFKGG87": ["\"Well, anyway the police will never ", "come here! We're off scot-free!\""], "Q6q8lNsT": ["\"......................Is this a game to you?\""], "5RlQhJ8f": ["\"Huh...?\""], "wdy3zR4X": ["\"What the \\fi fuck \\fr\\c[1] did I say about the sacrifices?\""], "D5ympqbQ": ["\"Oh, c'mon. What does any of ", "that matter anymore?\""], "Z8D4sjKJ": ["\"Apparently it's more important for you to", "get your kicks than to follow our plans...\""], "YCGNGZ8p": ["\"Oh, our plans, huh? Tell me more ", "about the plans you messed up!\""], "cy3v3Kzp": ["\"Whatever happened to grabbing the kid, huh??\""], "nZ6S4STH": ["\"You were grilling the guy ", "\\fi before \\fr\\c[1] I messed up!!\""], "YbwngfzY": ["\"Boohoo. Things turned out fine, didn't they?\""], "KpV1x8v2": ["\"FUCK! Ashley... Every fucking time!!\""], "sc3c8bLw": ["\"I ask you for one fucking thing, and you ", "go out of your way to do the opposite!\""], "D7f6dpd0": ["\"Will you get over it?? We", "need to find the demon.\""], "7yjYtc5g": ["\".......Well?\""], "1N4LcsXS": ["\"........Andrew?\""], "0bZdxrtT": ["\" . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . \""], "FWf03DQW": ["\"\\fi Sigh..... \\fr\\c[2] Alright.\""], "HtXfwS0s": ["\"Look, I'm sooooorry about the barbecue.", "I didn't know it was such a huge deal.\""], "WSYTDY1x": ["\"Yes you did! Don't fucking lie to me!!\""], "ZbYKQtPT": ["\"I-- O-okay... I can see you're ", "very upset about this, Andrew...\""], "80f3K7Qf": ["\"B- but we're safe now! There's ", "no need to-- We can talk this out!\""], "Qyc9krT4": ["\"You're not going to hear a word I say anyway!\""], "wh3VZ6h6": ["\"That's--- Let's not do this. Not like ", "this. Not over something this stupid...\""], "gv54x110": ["\"Um..... You know what? You're ", "right! I screwed up. I'm sorry.\""], "x55sny5k": ["\"Just because I get stronger from eating ", "humans, doesn't mean I can do it whenever.\""], "qQfKHM7r": ["\"Not this stupid shit again. I'm so tired.....\""], "knDRhspP": ["\"Next time I'll be sure to ask you first.", "I won't decide things on my own anymore!\""], "CfFMQ4gR": ["\"I promise I'll--\""], "PnbnJW7W": ["\" 'Behave from now on'? \""], "FddKfJVJ": ["\" . .. . . .... .. .. . . .. . . \""], "Rl86DFNn": ["\"You're right. This is stupid...\""], "x2kyhzw6": ["\"This is so. Fucking. Stupid.\""], "mMP36kdT": ["\"I bend over backwards to take ", "care of you. And for what?\""], "BCnslLrh": ["\"So that you can spit in ", "the face of all my efforts?\""], "xKmF667h": ["\"N-no....\""], "DgDjsY68": ["\"I'm killing myself here ", "to keep this farce going.\""], "WvhBDN94": ["\"Do you understand that?? I'm ", "stressed the fuck out of my mind!\""], "47Z4TD37": ["\"I- I understand! And I'm ", "sorry.... Can we just go?\""], "gl9CCCgN": ["\" . . . . . . . . . \""], "NlQ6QmQK": ["\"C'mon, Andrew... We've come this far.\""], "RwCVSqqR": ["\"Yeah, no thanks to you.\""], "4ys9T11q": ["\"\\fi *Scoff!* \\fr\\c[2] Okay, now that's just bullshit!", "I've worked just as hard as you!!\""], "YpdWlCm6": ["\"Hell, we'd probably have starved ", "in our apartment without me!\""], "fv0fy5y0": ["\"\\{WELL MAYBE WE SHOULD HAVE!!!\\}\""], "0p2t7jjz": ["\"Maybe that was exactly ", "what we fucking deserved!\""], "BrZnDJWc": ["\"I-... I don't wanna talk anymore...\""], "wHFThLJ3": ["\"Stay here if you want. I'm going.\""], "BN0gCXHG": ["\"The hell you are. You stay ", "right where you are, Ashley.\""], "Qn1rlhKk": ["\"W-WHOA!! Whoa!!?? Hold up?!\""], "Q2PklWj6": ["\"....................Why did you do it?\""], "0xTNpQY4": ["\"Do what? Eat that guy? ", "I already told you.\""], "7m8mcFqY": ["\"After I specifically asked you not to......\""], "cDcMFdM7": ["\"Stop being so dramatic. We're all good.\""], "z4M0LdKM": ["\"Now 