e....\""], "S49wVzJz": ["\"Nothing is going to happen.\""], "YZx0q1Yd": ["\"We can't be sure...\""], "2w18V6Lk": ["\"If I was going to hurt someone, the last ", "thing I'd do is announce my intentions.\""], "DTLshCZN": ["\"This person wants to get ", "under your skin, that's all.\""], "6QbSSy9K": ["\"Don't let them.\""], "xLpfd3QZ": ["\"I can't help it.....\""], "d7qCf3N9": ["\"And maybe they're a crazy person?\""], "NXjn8DKn": ["\"W-what if one day they decide, ", "'Screw it! I'll really kill her!!'?\""], "LwCZ4Dmh": ["\"And you think a person that dumb would", "actually have the means to get to you?\""], "J5SySTsw": ["\"You're letting this little shithead ", "ruin your life for no reason.\""], "y8nVHFqQ": ["\"It hurts to see.\""], "ccrQl46y": ["\"..................Andrew.\""], "7sJq0nGv": ["\"It is really, \\fi really \\fr\\c[6] hard to ignore", "someone actively harassing you...\""], "jpK2WjS7": ["\"I get that. That's the whole ", "point of harassment, isn't it?\""], "S9q5XTdz": ["\"........................\""], "s89vxwBq": ["\"Do you wanna hear the kind of voicemails ", "I have to sift through every day?\""], "mR0mQfyl": ["\"Nah, I've had my fill......\""], "0xvMY6mJ": ["\"No... Please listen to some ", "more. Like I have to. Every day.\""], "Lmbzt83C": ["\"Well, the thing is, Julia. ", "You \\fi don't \\fr\\c[1] have to.\""], "s5YfMjT3": ["\"Please. Some of them are really interesting.\""], "8xKyLytL": ["\"\\fi Sighhhh...... \\fr\\c[1]\""], "bjHVPbhB": ["You watch him listen to Ashley describe your", "oncoming, painful and slow death in brutal detail."], "wmbdt1zG": ["And he looks like someone is listing him the groceries."], "Rr3sH2Tn": ["\"Is that it? What is this person, fucking twelve?\""], "Gg5jSWJY": ["Soon the tone of the messages change, and it's ", "back to how your boyfriend would rather fuck her."], "6vYdRLgM": ["You're scanning his face for some ", "sort of disgust or confirmation..."], "MFr87wgz": ["But unlike the other day, Andrew ", "seems over the whole thing."], "6T7YyLBT": ["\"Was there some point as to why", "you're making me listen to this?\""], "R6ckRDKq": ["\"It's just-..... So oddly specific.\""], "nNgcG3n8": ["\"I really get this feeling ", "it's Ashley after all.........\""], "XX0kvZv3": ["\"The voice is all distorted, but the ", "wording and stuff just seems so her......\""], "QgqcBMy3": ["\"Like who uses the word 'floozy' in this day and age?\""], "jJcGfgBv": ["\"I sincerely doubt Ashley would ", "say these things about me.\""], "58YbPjqX": ["\"A-are you angry? I'm not trying to insult her...\""], "9mKH3DCG": ["\"I'm sure she just wants a rise out of me ", "and says the worst things she can think of...\""], "0482xmK0": ["\"Not like she means it or anything. ", "She just wants to be mean.....\""], "FsZtF6VP": ["\".......................I suppose that's possible.\""], "qm2G6Fdx": ["\"S-so you agree it's probably her??\""], "K2JkXS6g": ["\"No. Isn't this just someone from college?\""], "Kj50WHC2": ["\".......You're really telling me some unknown ", "girl is pretending to be your sister?\""], "n7WxdGXz": ["\"Just so she can make me think you two.... are too ", "close, and therefore make me break up with you?\""], "jWWl2tKw": ["\"Well, it's working, isn't it?\""], "dfZcWpfS": ["\"...........It's just very specific is all.\""], "ZvhhBrlV": ["\"How is this specific?\""], "hh7Wrcxy": ["\"It's 'The Graves keep it in the family' ", "-joke from high school all over again.\""], "Nh5Qvb5D": ["\"People gossip......\""], "3WxG3Qr3": ["\"A-and you have to admit the ", "situation can seem a little off...\""], "BCkcn0r7": ["\" ! ! ! \""], "XpJB27pS": ["\"Julia, I \\fi reaaaaally \\fr\\c[1] don't appreciate these ", "insinuations coming from you of all people.\""], "n03VT75G": ["\" .. .. .. ... . . . ... . . . . \" "], "f4zK0fLZ": ["\"Oh...\""], "KhKNtNWn": ["\"Okay, no. No... I'm sorry. ", "That came out all wrong.\""], "YcRCRHPQ": ["\"What I meant was it's upsetting ", "you'd think so lowly of me.\""], "yGMLqSHL