Honest! He's my big brother. He only ", "exists to keep me safe and happy..!\""], "SmtRcgmF": ["\" . . . . . . . . . . . . \""], "Dk2nWwYj": ["\"Though I mean-... he did smack me in the car...\""], "vKgypnFr": ["\"But then again, I kinda asked for it...\""], "GgMlCYFb": ["\"Oh, and I guess he did kinda choke me, ", "but that was after I assaulted him.\""], "jpwbCLP7": ["\" 'Kinda' because he held me by the neck, but he ", "wasn't actually choking me, so I dunno...\""], "lGjCQdH7": ["\"Moreover, he raises his ", "voice a lot lately.......\""], "9XWssL5m": ["\"Like...... a lot.\""], "52k6tTN9": ["\"..............................\""], "KCmJNSK3": ["\"(Shit... I \\fi did \\fr\\c[2] avoid the vision, right??)\""], "Z1B3qh02": ["\"He cAnnot bE truSted, TaR SouL.\""], "VP1l47HY": ["\"N-no! No, no. It's fine. We're--\""], "KGhM8Bdd": ["\"No. It's not that bad. We're in a rough ", "patch, sure. But it'll be fine...\""], "RTzVSyl3": ["\"We're always fine! Because we're Andy and------\""], "H1VF5C7s": ["\"Yeah, okay. No, we're... friends? ", "Right? Yeah. Friends.\""], "zBLf74nq": ["\"Wait. Maybe we're lovers now....?\""], "d5Qr2vbf": ["\"A-anyway! He won't kill me, ", "I swear! He won't!!\""], "tsV2SZKG": ["\"And since your vision showed him being sneaky about ", "the trinket, it'll be fine as long as I out-sneak him!\""], "wkxwkjkX": ["\"When we're in the Human Realm, I just won't go to ", "sleep. Or hug him. Or let him see the trinket at all.\""], "GqsYZ67W": ["\"It's not like we'll even be there ", "for long. It'll be fine. It will.\""], "ZF0JxNrC": ["\".........P-please believe me.\""], "2X81VlzL": ["\"Do wHat yOu wiLL, TaR SouL.\""], "nBRx385t": ["There's no lock on the door, but", "you shouldn't leave this room."], "r5ShyGxg": ["It seems the Entity really doesn't like you..."], "3Dzhd6ns": ["Time to call it a day?"], "hwbWfrht": ["\"Heh! Well, would you look at that, ", "everything worked out for us.\""], "2L3fyXQh": ["\"......What do you mean?\""], "jsnD3Vwd": ["\"Now we've got all that stuff ", "you said was missing.\""], "wrcQMcbL": ["\"...Except food and such, but I'm ", "sure that'll get sorted tomorrow.\""], "4F37nDCw": ["\"I hate to be a nag, but we've no idea ", "what the Entity has in store for us...\""], "zKDW1hJ5": ["\"He's my friend! We'll be okay.\""], "0VYd8jzP": ["\"I don't know... It hasn't ", "been very friendly to me....\""], "YmkJ5Dhk": ["\"I think we should find a way out ", "of here as soon as we can.\""], "yN68zrZC": ["\"C'mon... Give this place a chance.\""], "q4v90cCY": ["\"I just wish we didn't owe it anything...\""], "ZMVY4vv5": ["\"Why'd you have to go and make ", "such a vague deal with it?\""], "Tgbpz03F": ["\"...What deal?\""], "3gHb38J0": ["\" 'What deal'???? The deal that we'll ", "'cooperate', whatever \\fi that \\fr\\c[1] means...\""], "fsBgZF6b": ["\"Ahhhh, I think that was ", "just a formality, y'know?\""], "6vFlVJ3G": ["\"Like hell it was, Ashley... C'mon...\""], "qRV0XRXH": ["\"Well, what else was I supposed to do? ", "We weren't gonna outrun the police.\""], "WN4MDfmB": ["\"I acknowledge that. And I understand ", "there was no time to stop and think.....\""], "cqgSTFCY": ["\"But with that in mind, we've ", "got to stay extra vigilant now.\""], "BqmvJR6m": ["\"So what I'm hearing is, 'You did the right ", "thing, but I'm gonna get mad anyway!' \""], "pBvTlb4H": ["\"Okay, this isn't going anywhere.", "Goodnight, Ashley...\""], "9SXWHnVs": ["\"So you \\fi are \\fr\\c[2] mad at me!\""], "KFkxx93J": ["\"I'm not...\""], "rZhk6j5k": ["\"Then prove it. \\fi Promise \\fr\\c[2] me you're not mad.\""], "PVg1bVv9": ["\"...............\""], "Ch9VjMnT": ["\".......Well?\""], "2tCHVJvT": ["\"I don't like what you're ", "turning this into...\""], "yLHrk5XX": ["\".....................Whatever. ", "Kill me in my sleep then.\""], "R11dHMPJ": ["\"..........I'd appreciate it if you didn't hold me ", "accountable for crimes I haven't committed.\""], "Wtc6R81r": ["\"What would it have taken you? ", "A split second of your time??\""], "2XLBpT0s": ["\"A split fucking second to ease my mind! ", "I'm sorry I ask so much of you!!\""], "hyjlcrFf": ["\"You're trying to reset the precedent where I jump", "through hoops like a moron to cater to your whims.\""], "mhzdqHPv": ["\"But I'm not your fucking Andy anymore.\""], "1Y5YMy7K": ["Damn it. He sees right through you..."], "q2s89wzH": ["You thought he'd let himself get lured back in, ", "if it gave him an excuse to act affectionate."], "XMKTBZsg": ["Shouldn't he be dying of loneliness by now? His ex", "has been out of the picture for months and months!"], "0Mc73lG3": ["Whatever. You ignore him until you fall asleep."], "VLrWPXyG": ["He doesn't seem to mind. Again."], "DRYnwhQH": ["It dawns on you none of your ", "games work on him anymore."], "yRSC1hcD": ["You are Andrew!"], "jJZ6KcR4": ["\".....Good morning. What do you wanna do today?\""], "4N6bLQHr": ["\"Yesterday the Entity said ", "it wanted to talk to you...\""], "2rBct9zy": ["\"You look tired... Maybe you ", "should rest some more?\""], "Xr86X95P": ["\"...Not right now. I need to figure", "out what this place is about.\""], "DwFj10bq": ["\"I can look around by myself.\""], "VZNTbzTq": ["\"YOU ARE \\fi NOT \\fr\\c[1] LEAVING", "MY FUCKING SIGHT!!!\""], "VQtclfjb": ["\" ? ! ? ! \""], "hqf3GVRB": ["\"Until I know exactly what our situation is, you're", "to stay glued to me. Do you understand that!?\""], "04D5tz4t": ["\"Oh my, such passion! Hahah!! \\fi Yes, sir! \\fr\\c[2]\""], "WclWZhCb": ["\"\\fi Sighhh..... \\fr\\c[1] I'm not playing. I mean it.\""], "pJbtvJ5J": ["\"Still feeling down? I'll ", "let you sleep with me.\""], "rXzGbGlS": ["\"..............Phrasing, Ashley.\""], "zqYlFZTS": ["\"HaHahHA! What? What?? There's only one bed.\""], "tGxCWcNv": ["\"It said 'you may go rest'. ", "Not that we had to.\""], "w9K86NNn": ["\"Oh, you meant that, not--... ", "Yeah, okay. Phrasing indeed.\""], "qfjY9pCK": ["\"Hah.\""], "8fBy6W8z": ["\"The Entity is busy having visions right now.\""], "DlZ3FbSz": ["\"We should take this opportunity ", "to properly look around.\""], "8WjTJ7D2": ["\"I hope it doesn't get a vision of ", "us snooping his stuff, haha!!\""], "G0jmyJM9": ["\"Then again, maybe it already ", "did and doesn't care?\""], "mYKfvBgq": ["Take a nap?"], "wYlKsB1C": ["\" . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . \""], "VxpB7qZh": ["\" .... ... . .... . .. . ... .. . . . . ... \""], "l8kCkQkc": ["You attempt to sleep your sorrows ", "away, but sleep doesn't arrive."], "qhGHDly5": ["So instead you stare at the ceiling for a few hours......."], "d5s7bV0k": ["\" .........?? \""], "myQcwk6M": ["\"(The fuck is this???)\""], "5W8wtzbb": ["\"I'm baaaa-ack!\""], "VcPj2ycr": ["\" . . . . . . . . . . . \""], "Ynx3NKW5": ["\"Somehow your face is even more", "sour than usual. How come?\""], "RKLvsqVb": ["\"Well, you sold me to the demon, for starters.\""], "b8GlzC89": ["\"Not really though.\""], "mCDsKXtL": ["\"Yes really though. Look at this!\""], "4wGjfcH8": ["\"Hah! Well, now I know you ", "can't run off. Nice, nice!\""], "y3QFrR6z": ["\"\\fi Sighhhh........ \\fr\\c[1]\""], "bWGTQwFJ": ["Not a shred of regret can be detected from her."], "x3VcWGWj": ["\"Oh, c'mon. Why are you sulking? ", "I've sorted everything out for us.\""], "S5cNzlrJ": ["\"We'll be safe here! Nothing can get to us anymore.\""], "P3djg8g0": ["\"............I'm just tired, Leyley.\""], "2sfvCCR4": ["\"What did the demon tell you anyway?\""], "ZRKsSCjB": ["\"It showed me how I'll be", "gathering souls from now on.\""], "5yQgqftf": ["\"Long story short, he'll send me to the Human", "Realm, where I'll summon it to offer it souls.\""], "Kcn9T4hR": ["\"And while I'm there, I can get some human ", "stuff like food and soap and all that.\""], "ZZhpbT6n": ["\"Then he'll summon me back here. ", "Away from all the consequences!\""], "rz3NKK0s": ["\"We'll keep summoning each other back and forth, ", "and get all the souls we could ever want!\""], "ts1yMG6h": ["\".........That sounds-...\""], "BlpKQ18J": ["\"(Way too good to be true. What's the catch??)\""], "G83B3wPp": ["You get a lingering sense that something is wrong."], "jXq2nmyN": ["But you can't for the life of ", "you point out what it is."], "1zl86cgh": ["Perhaps it is no longer your concern. ", "She's the one in charge now."], "GZtT8f39": ["\"Well............. That's good, I guess...?\""], "FGv7SpG1": ["\"You don't sound too happy....\""], "cNL6Mpr9": ["\"I just need some rest, Leyley. ", "Can you give me that?\""], "sBv1LnTG": ["\"But something tells me I shouldn't ", "let you be alone right now...\""], "RF14H9dx": ["\"..............I'm fine.\""], "zv17Rl6s": ["Doesn't matter."], "324qTkgQ": ["\"(Maybe it won't be so bad.........)\""], "G50dqDTQ": ["\"(She's right, we'll be safe here. Probably.)\""], "56Qb88MB": ["\"(Isn't that what I've always wanted in my heart ", "of hearts? For her to be safe and sound.)\""], "Dbv6zG3M": ["\"(Is this it then? I'll be stuck ", "here until the day I die.)\""], "nfZms6lW": ["\"(She collects souls for the ", "demon thing, and I do... what?)\""], "0gnzmj4L": ["\"(Sit here wasting away until ", "she wants something from me?)\""], "whgcDv40": ["\"(With no life or will of my own..... Just 'Andy' again.)\""], "7RG1q1sd": ["Kind of like your father, but at ", "least he got laid for his troubles."], "pNzlcpnW": ["But no matter. Ashley's happiness comes at", "the cost of yours. Always has. Always will."], "D5XcvYP9": ["But that's fine. You never ", "deserved happiness anyway."], "ywby7qwB": ["An empty glass bottle."], "02XDYyF4": ["", "Got a Bottle!"], "GNmqstVx": ["\"A bath tub, huh...\""], "K3sMDDsz": ["\"We've always had a shower, ", "so this is a first for me.\""], "dbR0MvHY": ["\"Same.\""], "BWv252n9": ["\"I'm gonna take a bath!\""], "cb7HBvhs": ["\"Right now?? And I thought ", "you're on your period.\""], "HkYf0H2j": ["\"That's over! Now turn around!!\""], "6Tyhjs23": ["\"(And don't try to keep track ", "of my days, that's creepy...)\""], "dJWPNjFf": ["", "You take a bath!"], "hCq6QZxz": ["It is far, far less glamorous ", "than you thought it would be."], "vR7FB6JR": ["Sitting in a tub filled with water wasn't the ", "magical luxury spa experience you were expecting."], "XM5XtKMJ": ["Turns out it's just... sitting in water."], "980WbnrC": ["She takes a bath. As if there weren't ", "a million better things to do right now."], "Tqfs84FV": ["\"..........I don't see the appeal.\""], "BVd5pzs2": ["\"I think you're supposed to relax ", "and read a book or something...\""], "v3X6dgvd": ["\"BORING!! What a waste of time.\""], "j1wmhp0x": ["\"Indeed. Now get lost, ", "I'm gonna take a shower.\""], "XnFycGm7": ["\"What the hell? You should've ", "just joined me then!!\""], "XfpC78w7": ["\"HA-HA-HA. No.\""], "lnhvBwJN": ["You take the time to make yourself at home."], "9Md5dxWY": ["Placed down Laundry and other random ", "shit you've been hauling around!"], "hBC6wvh9": ["You hurry up and wash yourself, while ", "worrying over where this water is coming from."], "LJpx0hbW": ["Do Entities pay water bills? Is there a health", "and safety committee monitoring the quality?"], "8BxrdKFt": ["Wouldn't it be hilarious if you", "actually got deadly parasites now?"], "vyhyRxYH": ["Meanwhile Ashley seems to have made herself home..."], "S6f1CSFj": ["\"(Why the hell is there a bathtub in here?)\""], "qqHF8NMY": ["\"(This place doesn't make any sense........", "Do we really have to stay here from now on?)\""], "Tvcn9kb5": ["You proceed to wail until exhaustion."], "5b7445sV": ["That's when you're overtaken by sleep..."], "m6s4dnfZ": ["Call it a day?"], "PDHxYlYX": ["\"Um... Are you asleep?\""], "wSK16Www": ["He pretends to be."], "fxGFr2sR": ["\" .......... \""], "CXGJnz4Y": ["\"..........Frowny face?\""], "Zyl1rxxH": ["\"Frowny because I have a lot ", "of stuff to think about.\""], "PDzLJy7F": ["\"Plus you're mad at me...\""], "bmR784Rp": ["\"I'm not mad. I just wish you'd listen...\""], "0Phk77zk": ["\"Yeah, well...\""], "Mp0j8wSl": ["\"I found out the demon lets us stay here because", "getting souls will be easier like this.\""], "M0DxmFj7": ["\"I summon it to the Human Realm, ", "it summons me back here...\""], "LWh1HSVW": ["\"It gets souls, we get a place ", "to live. Everybody wins!\""], "ns3kwN7b": ["\"You said yes to something, didn't you?\""], "N9ZfJybZ": ["\"Only to what I just told you.\""], "nRZbvP7g": ["\" \\} For fuck's sake....... \\{\""], "96CgxytF": ["\"Andrew there is \\fi nothing \\fr\\c[2] to be afraid of.\""], "0nrB3rXr": ["\"But I bet you'll go 'b-buh-but Ashley! Why didn't it", "summon us here from the start then? Wah wah waaah!' \""], "f7XbWv4M": ["\"Why didn't it?\""], "yWqHMcW1": ["\"Because it didn't know we needed a place??\""], "vglH7vSD": ["\"...I've made my thoughts on this ", "clear. I won't repeat them again.\""], "KdTCqVVy": ["\"\\fi Sighhhh.......... \\fr\\c[2]\""], "DVchnHNp": ["\"That's okay. Be mad. I love you anyway.\""], "gYcy4SC7": ["\".........................\""], "76fyLCCm": ["\"Did you hear me? Answer me, goddammit!\""], "TWmG7830": ["\"Say, what exactly do you ", "mean when you say that?\""], "NBHZhQNr": ["\"......I thought you're an English major.", "Isn't language supposed to be your forty?\""], "g3hZtRTR": ["\" 'Forte', Ashley. 'Forty' is a number.\""], "Sx1txlkv": ["\"And 'I love you' is a full sentence!", "What the fuck more do you want??\""], "n12pLf56": ["\"Explain how you love me. ", "Because I just don't see it.\""], "qxfRxmmb": ["\"The sun shines out of your ass, ", "and you're the best thing ever.\""], "Y8dX7RSG": ["\"Yeah? You think I'm all that?\""], "6QnZKtFZ": ["\"I do.\""], "lvxMskTJ": ["\"And yet I talk, and I talk, and I talk, and I", "scream, and I yell, and I beg, and I plead...\""], "hXRK2Ltc": ["\"But I'm just not getting through to you.\""], "Rx2xltfr": ["\"......Umm?\""], "lwpzd9wT": ["\"Not a single thing I say seems to reach you.\""], "yzt1pjJw": ["\"..........Okay, what is your problem??\""], "7jLx2wnV": ["\"Ashley, I'm fine being your ", "self-regulation by proxy--...\""], "J78qfy25": ["\"My fucking \\fi what??? \\fr\\c[2]\""], "PXdvM2gS": ["\"I'm fine being the stand-in mother, father, ", "boyfriend, whatever-the-fuck you feel like today.\""], "kPD1hNWr": ["\"But don't try to sell it to me ", "as something that it isn't...\""], "SQdzJJMx": ["\"Hoooly shit. I've zero idea what you're on about.\""], "wzSSy1Qj": ["\"Where is this coming from??\""], "SvlLB52X": ["\"You don't love me. Not one bit.\""], "nlLr6lmY": ["\"If you did, you wouldn't make these unilateral ", "decisions directly against my wishes.\""], "rhk2wWBB": ["\"This deal is for your sake!!!!! ", "Same with offering the police!\""], "rZgmc8HM": ["\"No it isn't. This is what you ", "want to do, and nothing else.\""], "hX5fflyn": ["\"Fuck, it always is! It's always ", "you, you, you, you, YOU!!\""], "z1Xvl5sX": ["\"Give me one fucking example ", "where we've done things my way.\""], "V8wJtL7y": ["\"No. Give me an example of you compromising ", "even a tiny little bit on anything at all.\""], "KBdyWmW6": ["\"...............I stopped calling you Andy.\""], "kN1n09DZ": ["\"Ooooh! Hallelujah! She hasn't called me ", "by the wrong name for a few days!\""], "pVVbfkjZ": ["\"Mercy me, do I stand corrected! This must be love! And ", "not just any love, but true love of the highest caliber!\""], "PVc5wpnk": ["\"I let you date your shitty ex for years on end!!\""], "H8SBYdvd": ["\"By god! A permission to date! Bestowed ", "upon me by my own little sister!\""], "rc9KSrRp": ["\"I'm so glad my sex life lies at your whim, ", "despite it not involving you in any capacity.\""], "JWZYvg7b": ["\"Argh!!! Enough! Get out of my bed!!\""], "mKfBCSXL": ["\"And don't come crawling back in, pretending ", "you can't sleep, you sick fuck!!\""], "Ly2mtgk0": ["\"Oh, you wanna play \\fi that \\fr\\c[1] game?\""], "MMcskTRB": ["\" 'Doesn't involve me' my ass!! You must", "think my brain is made out of shit, huh??\""], "yg5Zs09B": ["\"Who was the shit-for-brains sick fuck that", "asked me to inbreed with her the other day?\""], "cnZZjJ5w": ["\"I didn't ask that!! And anyway ", "it was a joke! Get over it!\""], "KK8sP0PJ": ["\"And who was all over me, grabbing ", "my junk? Was that a joke too?\""], "XDvJCfLj": ["\"GET THE FUCK OUT!!!!\""], "tlM2Tf1V": ["\"Thy will be done, beloved!\""], "zvfzrtwx": ["\"Tonight, in the starring role, playing the ", "part of your ex-lover, is Andrew Graves!\""], "hSqpdS4V": ["\"\\{ OUT!! \\}\""], "XypY9bDL": ["Ashley has cried herself to sleep."], "FSsrN7T0": ["\"(Man... I'm an asshole, huh?)\""], "mfL18GHm": ["\"(Why am I mad over something ", "she has no control over?)\""], "qxFfjcbP": ["\"(She's a selfish cunt. Of ", "course she'll act like one.)\""], "CWKpv3YP": ["\"(It's like getting mad at water for being wet.)\""], "40Hqj0rZ": ["\"(And I've slipped up big time...............)\""], "V9KKSxrx": ["\"(What was I thinking when ", "indulging her with 'promises'?)\""], "qptKbjyY": ["\"(Of course she was going to make a ", "power play of it... It's in her nature.)\""], "1BK30HrG": ["\"(Ahhh, I'm screwing up left and right. Get ", "it together! What the hell am I doing?)\""], "rfSClHh3": ["\"........Having fun?\""], "NHB3NT6K": ["\"Yup! You should join us.\""], "C3vSDccw": ["\"He mUsn't.\""], "lHl7S607": ["\".......Well, there you go.\""], "lHzjsymH": ["\"MaKe HasTe, TaR SouL.\""], "M5vjmzxC": ["You leave Andrew to his writings."], "8skPlmXM": ["Something fell out of the notes."], "DxvFl6Zy": ["\"Despite everything, and after ", "it's all said and done.\""], "k1J3yvRs": ["\"At the end of the day, ", "and the end of my wits.\""], "RZcrKY9h": ["\"There is the you.\""], "mhQP9wbW": ["\"Always you. Endlessly you.\""], "Q1J34g6y": ["\"Sad, miserable, pitiful, tiresome, ", "worthless, center of my world, you.\""], "X6bjHdjS": ["\"You with your teeth on my heart.\""], "yRs3JJW1": ["\"You, out of touch, and out of reach.\""], "ClF2qFgT": ["\"(Yikes, I forgot to scrap this.)\""], "ZP1M2T0K": ["The note gets a taste of your lighter."], "NtfggXkk": ["\" ?? ? ? \""], "0R767lWR": ["You don't much care for poetry."], "VDf3fSQ9": ["Just some paper."], "GMqyQz3W": ["Andrew's compiled notes. Take a peek?"], "pY0T9ygr": ["It's your notes. Read some?"], "nHv8hYSt": ["\"Entities are not demons, despite Ashley,", "and the cultists, calling them that.\""], "PBN2PLmQ": ["\"My hypothesis is that they're souls who cannibalized ", "other souls, though I have no solid proof of this.\""], "txyrPGkq": ["\"I look at Ashley and think, 'Ah, you're", "on your way to becoming just like this...' \""], "GpF3tlYb": ["\"She once mentioned eating others makes her stronger, ", "though that was regarding flesh, not souls.\""], "Zj2PqffG": ["\"But I wouldn't put it past her to be confused ", "which part you're supposed to eat...\""], "05khdmRv": ["\"God, I hope I'm wrong though. If my Ashl---\""], "DMTSNh0P": ["The rest has been scratched out and can't be read."], "H1BXnzqH": ["\"Apparently humans have souls that ", "can be removed from the body.\""], "MdbMLLCn": ["\"Souls, on their own, don't seem to remember ", "who they are\u2014just fragments, instincts.\""], "t0wfPJ0V": ["\"Souls can also be bottled up, yet the Entity lets them ", "roam about, and even provides them with activities.\""], "sxVHPDn5": ["\"I'm guessing this means souls fade ", "away if they're not kept engaged?\""], "YQSTFDbq": ["\"The Entity said souls darken ", "according to their own morals.\""], "LbPxRVCL": ["\"It has previously referred to me as a Grime Soul...\""], "GKdsVNLH": ["\"Which makes sense... I'm a piece of shit, ", "but I could certainly be worse.\""], "Hqrhdpw1": ["\"But what would this mean for Ashley who is a Tar Soul?\""], "3G1L6blj": ["\"Which raises the question: can ", "a soul ever be 'clean' again?\""], "p4C17yZV": ["\"Is there a cut-off point when you've gone so far", "off the deep end you become, say, an Entity?\""], "r3wqRVQ6": ["\"Or 'trinkets' as Ashley calls them...\""], "Pz4DbB4t": ["\"They likely serve multiple purposes, ", "but Ashley's lets her see the future.\""], "gnHY898V": ["\"I'm speculating, but I'm pretty sure it's ", "a lesser version of the Entity's power.\""], "Fz0MjM28": ["\"Notably, the Entity can track the talisman's ", "location\u2014even across realms.\""], "lGjsM950": ["\"That is how it keeps track of Ashley... ", "How it invades her dreams, her mind...\""], "Gm9jgkbX": ["\"It fucking turns my stomach...", "What does it want with her?\""], "sq5b78TH": ["\"I never should have suggested ", "summoning that damn thing.\""], "m2N7Sp4v": ["\"God, if anything happens to her because of me...\""], "mZ0KprB3": ["\"We have got to get the hell away from here.\""], "LWpP0fHF": ["\"Stop fighting me on this, Ashley. Please....\""], "XV9yy0n9": ["\"There is the Human Realm, the Realm Between, and then ", "from what I understand, a Home Realm for each Entity.\""], "RCXgVSDP": ["\"Not that I have any proof of this. ", "It's just a thought for now...\""], "QBghP307": ["\"And I assume that 'Lord Unknown', or whatever", "the cultists were summoning, is an Entity anyway...\""], "LqrXDRSW": ["\"Either way, you can't enter a realm ", "you don't belong in unsummoned.\""], "mZdsMcqv": ["\"The only exception being the Realm Between, ", "which seems like a free-for-all wasteland.\""], "5Tf56KBM": ["\"I think the Realm Between is ", "something akin to a limbo or a dream.\" "], "NTyCMvDr": ["\"Both Ashley and I have been there ", "in a dream, as well as in person.\" "], "CQ9RwbLF": ["\"I could not tell the difference between the two visits.\" "], "YvQLhgXL": ["\"This suggests souls can enter the ", "Realm Between when the body sleeps.\""], "Mn79TfCV": ["\"I'm curious about this, because the souls ", "don't seem to remember anything on their own.\""], "txlgQfhr": ["\"Yet during my vision dream visit, ", "I remembered everything fine...\""], "dfNz3LTs": ["\"Was it because I was asleep, and ", "not actually removed from my body?\""], "lTpb4DqN": ["\"It should be noted both Ashley and I ", "struggled to wake up from those dreams.\""], "vZ2sb5Yh": ["This is where you've chosen ", "to place your incredible mop."], "S8LhzmGr": ["Truly, it is a fantastic mop."], "69fdtM52": ["Absolutely stunning."], "kLD7hKkn": ["Masterful craftsmanship."], "GMkk55T5": ["Flawless design."], "4xC2CjJ1": ["Peerless construction."], "bJnq4B0f": ["You fall on your knees and ", "weep before true beauty."], "rBZPVRrY": ["\"......Do you need help?\""], "00ZPMY86": ["\"To think I own this! To ", "think this is now mine!!\""], "WFp0g4NW": ["\"\\fi *Sniff!* \\fr\\c[2] I have never been so ", "happy in my entire life!!\""], "7FJMGyfk": ["A dime-a-dozen, ratty mop ", "Ashley insists on hauling around."], "zsL1WWS4": ["It's probably still stained with your parents' ", "blood. At least now, it\u2019s in another realm."], "rnf5NQyJ": ["Dirty laundry. There's nothing to wash it with."], "2fw5LB46": ["A gun."], "c4Q9rvBB": ["The TV is playing cartoons."], "f8LJv0hg": ["The TV is playing cartoons."], "6hb5Tcgg": ["There's nothing but porn on the TV."], "phzbqKsS": ["There's nothing but porn on the TV."], "3GQch79W": ["The cage is locked."], "f9W0YkVh": ["", "Got a Green Plushie!"], "MQ1TgHX5": ["The drawer is stuck."], "fMyFC8X6": ["A bride and groom sit atop a giant wedding cake."], "8rWstrcb": ["Ahh, yes. Childhood sweethearts! "], "JR6swx0k": ["You talked to her a grand total of two times. "], "Mh9nfMdc": ["Never even held hands, because back ", "then you thought girls were icky."], "cxc0FcNB": ["Then you locked her in a crate and she suffocated."], "qwG6gsD4": ["What a beautiful love story!"], "d58GtGgf": ["Get serious."], "7dVPhBsX": ["She was never your lover."], "h8Lbv4Nz": ["You are so unbelievably full of shit."], "k33BXDB5": ["Oh, bittersweet first love."], "jwN3XqTQ": ["She was so gentle, so kind, ", "so patient, and so precious."], "ch6pLkXf": ["And she bored the shit out of you."], "n0KqhTDz": ["But hey, the sex was fine."], "D7lqV9Fk": ["Though you did fantasize about kicking her ", "teeth in so she'd give better head."], "2MmBqp59": ["It's a good thing she broke it off with you."], "388PHmR0": ["A door has unlocked somewhere."], "h63DtcNM": ["Behold, the lover of Andrew Graves!"], "8wyctQJq": ["She just needs an accessory..."], "DnqLMYH8": ["The plushie has a key. Take it?"], "kzqMkbg9": ["", "Got a Key!"], "Kc9mvB6l": ["Cut this childish damn thing up with your cleaver?"], "Sdr5ssnm": ["That didn't help anything..."], "3jl7W3nh": ["", "Got a Choker!"], "Z0ck7cyn": ["What are you, some fucking Andy?"], "rwJBzkbP": ["You've made your choice."], "brW92Yrl": ["An empty seat."], "pgl3jfQH": ["Place down the Green Plushie?"], "RQJfXBxr": ["There's something inside the crate..."], "Wq7wv1r3": ["", "Got Dusty Purple Flowers!"], "tt8NCzJV": ["This can't be removed..."], "0G61yb5Z": ["You covered the problem area with Love Letters."], "Z0fPRsCj": ["Out of sight and out of mind!"], "Q6zK4LKy": ["She was always happy to hear from you."], "dKT2dxQV": ["You wish you felt the same, you really do."], "r0yQ3kmz": ["", "Got Bandages!"], "mzzKRMQD": ["An uncleanable mess..."], "KPYDdcqg": ["", "Picked up a Love Letter!"], "SC8qZ0Hy": ["A permanent stain..."], "QmMqLtmv": ["This will never come off..."], "m7VQblX6": ["Heart-shaped strawberries."], "90bG2m2G": ["Maybe it's edible. Maybe it isn't."], "JF3YZlH4": ["You'll never know, for you", "aren't stupid enough to try."], "x2jlV08T": ["\"I'm counting on you, Andrew. ", "I know you won't let me down.\""], "xsLkj9Hs": ["\"I just want us to be a happy family. Don't you?\""], "KrPVwhDZ": ["\"Is it too much to ask that ", "you care for your own sister?\""], "B9sF6j5G": ["\"She loves you so much. Doesn't ", "that mean anything to you?\" "], "bNgX27jb": ["\"Why can't you get along? You're siblings.\""], "thbBhb7p": ["\"You're being selfish again, like always.\""], "LGZMZV97": ["\"Don't you dare embarrass me.\""], "lv5c2xcz": ["\"You have to take care of her. ", "You're the eldest for fuck's sake!\""], "rR09Hh7p": ["\"Why won't you be a good brother?\""], "C70tNGN7": ["\"You used to be such a good ", "big brother. What happened?\""], "t4jHJDd6": ["\"When you let her down, you let \\fi me \\fr\\c[6] down.\""], "YRm8cPmm": ["\"Andrew, you're all she has. ", "Try to understand that.\""], "gxtKX1fC": ["\"I thought you were better than this, Andrew.\""], "j68zsq1X": ["Gave the mannequin a Hat."], "d1lXZpHM": ["Gave the mannequin Playing Cards."], "1HWsQ4cl": ["A mannequin."], "RJ0p2czq": ["", "Got a Douchebag Mannequin!"], "Jp661k5p": ["", "Got Player Mannequin!"], "jDwXPtY3": ["Gave the mannequin a Hat."], "nz8cQqWR": ["Gave the mannequin Playing Cards."], "mqGQ0XD4": ["A mannequin."], "vf9BVxKl": ["", "Got a Douchebag Mannequin!"], "c1mmSGLk": ["", "Got Player Mannequin!"], "4RHn0Tfz": ["", "Got the douchiest hat you've ever seen!"], "2v1SkTsX": ["", "Got Playing Cards!"], "RbHr0Hp7": ["\"Main character, wretched liar's tale,", "Words spun like silk, truth does fail.\""], "mlbzZLxm": ["\"Each syllable a tangled snare,", "Deception's cloak, their only wear.\""], "dnJVRN8M": ["\"Sidekick with a playful grin,", "Games their joy, where they begin.\""], "k2Gm4tbz": ["\"Through twists and turns, they find their glee,", "In laughter and camaraderie.\""], "pzS3N0nl": ["\"Judgmental jerk, their words precise,", "With piercing gaze, they do entice.\""], "NTk622DH": ["\"Though scornful tongue may cause dismay,", "Their discernment guides the way.\""], "6ZQwThff": ["\"Obnoxious prot\u00e9g\u00e9, a gem in jest,", "Annoying charm, they do possess.\""], "d8HNMGCm": ["\"Beneath the noise, a sight to see,", "In antics wild, they roam carefree.\""], "l3RHzLYH": ["Place..."], "LdqPbdXk": ["Place..."], "D66bCVlr": ["Place..."], "PFPTlwFB": ["Place..."], "rZqpzK3C": ["Place..."], "Q5QMpn59": ["Place..."], "vN58q07v": ["Place..."], "qfmzr4WM": ["That wasn't it."], "cwbln4gH": ["A spotlight."], "WbSHQpVn": ["", "Got a Player Mannequin!"], "GmFjNNdT": ["", "Got Douchebag Mannequin!"], "h71gWkGR": ["Th