tity has gone over without you."], "6BzQXw4S": ["\"Whoa! No way!!\""], "qSf9L9Wy": ["\"WhAt dO yoU offeR, hUman?\""], "nQh5tf8q": ["\"Holy frick-e-doodle-poodle-roodle-roo! ", "It's a real demon!!\""], "qP85ZG8F": ["\"I thought you'd look ", "cooler somehow... Like me!\""], "fcF2RkTv": ["\"WhAt dO yoU offeR foR tHe nUmbers yOu seEk?\""], "BpkzbLty": ["\"Well, I've got this sweet signed ", "T-shirt of my favorite band!\""], "ZvQ4PMbd": ["\"I signed it myself!\""], "XxjfXykT": ["\"....What is this shit?\""], "pkqrHCYx": ["\"I think this is how the", "demon locks its doors?\""], "NJQv5s4G": ["\"........Nothing is happening.\""], "9H81nsgX": ["\"I'm telling you! It's a demon lock!\""], "bvVs0Dvn": ["\"You have to solve it to pass.\""], "lcw0ZJKK": ["\"This is such fucking horseshit.\""], "QGzcP9pQ": ["\"I like it!\""], "VGC2R85S": ["You need Blood to draw with."], "ZDpFDqT8": ["You need Blood to draw with."], "YYS4kFZv": ["\"Oh! Here! There's some souls right outside.\""], "Tl0wBY0N": ["\" .............. \""], "tqccWhFC": ["\"Well?? C'mon! Hurry up before they leave.\""], "Xk3nvgbN": ["\"Tar SouL. CoMe sPeak to mE.\""], "k1nLc13l": ["\"There! All set.\""], "pb7pMLj4": ["\"Come on back, Mr. Demon Sir!\""], "hsFLRJgP": ["\"Welcome baaaack!\""], "Tp50wXFR": ["\"What dO you oFfer?\""], "BT9vNfKW": ["\"I offer the two souls outside in", "exchange for free housing at your realm!\""], "4zJ9Jgz5": ["\"Oh, and this cultist bitch too.\""], "hddz7pVW": ["\"W-what???!!\""], "kG14kzkS": ["\"DeaL.\""], "FXC1335H": ["\"How's that?? Three in one go!\""], "vwLBtXrt": ["\"I'm home!\""], "bjFm5FmB": ["\".........Hello?\""], "PLMLV8zM": ["\"Let's get out of here...\""], "wcpRlY2K": ["\"Are yOu noT offeRing tHis souL?\""], "Q7M8g8f8": ["\"No. He needs to look after the guinea pig.\""], "Pl428Lxq": ["\"Offering souls.... Yikes, this is getting heavy.....\""], "01Nj6jtK": ["\"I wasn't really expecting anything to show up....\""], "PkYxsVhl": ["\"Um... Is it safe to summon ", "the demon by the window?\" "], "kM4xPDmC": ["\"I mean, it's a demon... ", "Maybe the sunlight hurts it.\""], "dNKk6j0h": ["\"Oh. Right....................\""], "v4KnDnqc": ["\"Wait, no. If that were the case, it ", "would've said something just now.\""], "wvsn1wpp": ["\"Now where'd you get the blood?\""], "Z0ff65xj": ["\"My arm. But I already patched it up...\""], "dMTfNLm0": ["\"Then hurry up and cut yourself again.\""], "0c8D3q3w": ["", "Got Blood!"], "3Ysg8MxM": ["\"Ummm... D-demons, demons! ", "Can you hear me?\""], "96mmP0J1": ["\"Help me pass my sociology ", "test! I'll pay any price!!\""], "TtJvKRmx": ["\"ThiS oNe.\""], "stJZ4Z6D": ["\"\\fi *Gasp!* \\fr\\c[6]\""], "vmZFYWkz": ["\"WhAt pRice wiLL you pAy?\""], "gbCBB5ng": ["\"W-wh-what?? Price??\""], "BWthgz3X": ["\"Duhh. If you wanna get a gander ", "at the test questions, pay up!\""], "vbyP4QmW": ["\"Err... uhhh... um.....\""], "czRWFLDc": ["\"A soul or two should do.\""], "3xsYtGBL": ["\"SeEinG a SpeciFic viSioN iS mOrE coStLy.\""], "DkYM7T1t": ["\"Okay, that'll be seven souls then.\""], "3qmHPgbt": ["\"It went up by a lot!!??!\""], "SZZJcW8z": ["\"It's not that hard to gather souls.\""], "3Gb1pBFZ": ["\"Can't you just invite some friends over?\""], "NQ75L1Nw": ["\"Uh... The test is tomorrow.... ", "Everyone is studying.\""], "xwhzm4SM": ["\"Hmm... Let's see what else ", "we can work with.\""], "z5LyygJ3": ["\"I caN sEnse otHer SouLs nearbY.\""], "FbX9nZY1": ["\"TaR SouL.\""], "99CGzvK6": ["The Entity speaks quietly, ", "so that only you can hear it."], "NZHWRfpc": ["\"I cAnnOt leaVe the summoNing cirCLe.\""], "QjPnkfmS": ["\"Oh, c'mon!!!!\""], "SS1993QY": ["\"I dO noT beLonG in tHis ReaLm anyMoRe.\""], "WZTyLyhP": ["\"So you're stuck where you're summoned.....\""], "rZTdcFtm": ["\"Well, good job, you idiot!\""], "WlMDhQpk": ["\"You couldn't have drawn the ", "circle in a worse spot!\""], "7sydphvH": ["\"W-what's wrong with it?\""], "mbWXRcgl": ["\"Never mind that now. I'll do it myself.\""], "qg9S4FR1": ["\"Well? Shoo, sh