uh... maybe I really am just as dumb as you?\""], "2Dx8y8CC": ["\"HahHAhHah!!\""], "j6qgfNsr": ["\"No, wait!? Screw you!!\""], "2CGrrzC9": ["\"So, am I dying in my sleep ", "tonight, or are we good?\""], "rmGNbPzT": ["\"Hm... We're good. I guess.\""], "5j1vy3Nk": ["\"But just barely!\""], "HfWvFLXv": ["Barely is enough."], "2lpGD7yw": ["\"Good. Then clean up this mess.\""], "6rctS6Nm": ["\"ME!? It's your fault!! You clean it!!\""], "ty0cyw55": ["\"(Okay, first I need to buy some tape.)\""], "1b9Hg85W": ["\"(As for Ashley, I'll just get ", "her chocolate... and some gift.)\""], "Yqy113fJ": ["\"(It doesn't matter what. She'll ", "throw it back at my face anyway.)\""], "56bZdsF4": ["", "Picked up Chocolate!"], "THTy3VWt": ["", "Picked up Tape!"], "8pB8vlZL": ["\"(.......There's nothing here that Ashley would like.)\""], "tvpldgpH": ["\"(She doesn't care for these ritualistic ", "gestures in the first place....)\""], "tDFbsj5Q": ["\"('It's not sincere!' she'll say. 'You just ", "did it out of obligation, didn't you??')\""], "ZswCKXXK": ["\"(Well, no shit. Because you'll throw a fit if I don't!)\""], "MsZFyQc3": ["\"(Then it's 'You don't give a rat's ", "ass about me! I knew it already!')\""], "3NFVd3Ly": ["\"(Arghhh! JUST WHAT DO YOU WANT, WOMAN?!?!)\""], "YKT8jShw": ["\"(What the fuck do you want!? ", "Just tell me, and I'll do it!!!)\""], "vXkwlbTC": ["\" . . . . . . . . . . . \""], "6tYptTjw": ["\"(Okay, whatever. This is as good as it gets...)\""], "0TgHmnmh": ["", "Picked up a Gift!"], "MDpNsgk4": ["\"(I still need some stuff...)\""], "746xGph7": ["You still need some stuff."], "bxjnF0mQ": ["\"I'll take these, thank you.\""], "YBQbFF0r": ["\"Gosh jolly!! I can't possibly do ", "my job before you find me my dog!\""], "qJvryZb3": ["\"...........................................\\fi What??? \\fr\\c[1]\""], "K8Wnrtb9": ["\"I'm sure he's in here somewhere. ", "Ooooh. that silly dog of mine.\""], "pB9v4zyJ": ["Just find this asshole's dog ", "so you can get this over with."], "NX099dXr": ["Find his dog."], "cj6t7hcl": ["\"Heh heh! As a thank you for earlier, I'll invite you ", "to play Magical Magic Cards of Magic with my posse!\""], "9Zcx9Tw8": ["\"There's a special discount for anyone ", "who completes my dog-finding quest!\""], "4x7X7pZK": ["\"For the measly price of--\""], "qB9CMXTQ": ["\"Please, just let me buy my crap and leave...\""], "cwSNLHn8": ["\"Right you are! Playing with a mastermind ", "such as myself might be too much for you.\""], "g1F9XMHw": ["", "You got your crap and left!"], "3TlZDmHt": ["\"(Okay, let's fix this drawing...)\""], "MVsPJpXl": ["The dog runs off."], "gB3NM95R": ["The dog runs off. Again."], "h6Qj1v2C": ["Guess what happened next?"], "z3XQ2Yt9": ["The dog ran off, but this time, it left something behind..."], "CmCrsmz8": ["", "Got a yellow Tennis Ball!"], "y2VRB9nk": ["\"That's our water bowl for dogs!\" "], "PqQMRkxz": ["\"Our customer's dogs can use it to stay hydrated!\""], "3c5GDZdb": ["\"This out of place object is surely ", "irrelevant to whatever you are doing!!!!\""], "TBB357jP": ["\"Heeeh heh heh heh!!\""], "pzRz60FC": ["\"My dog likes water! Almost as ", "much as it likes tennis balls!!\" "], "hBhWKGLc": ["You place down the Tennis Ball."], "PJXlNWL6": ["\"Bark bark! Thank you, gentle stranger!\""], "xR7dWJKb": ["\" ?!?! ?!?! ?! ?!? \""], "CBdW6rwf": ["You notice the sound is coming from ", "a speaker attached to the dog's collar."], "Dt2ByFQB": ["The shopkeeper is roleplaying as his dog..."], "WtTJ2Z4W": ["Instantly, you remember why you ", "tolerate Ashley's fits again."], "lvlkTf2l": ["The alternative is hanging out with people like this."], "rjHFc5f9": ["\"CONGRATULATIONS!! You've found my dog!\""], "kRZSk47B": ["\"Wasn't that fun? Wasn't that an exciting adventure??\""], "n61syFCr": ["\"Heh heh! I've been watching you from", "the security monitor this whole time.\""], "llR0nQsc": ["\"(That's it! I'm never coming here again.)\""], "7S9bqGvV": ["\"Hold up, buddy! You haven't paid yet.\""], "cK2vbKwX": ["\"You do realize I have you on camera, right? Hahahaaaaa!!\""], "ksjLL0Zn": ["", "The drawing is fixed!"], "w6bq8WrF": ["It's out of reach..."], "NGZC3BSS": ["Well, whatever. As long as the garden area is clear."], "S00FnKLr": ["The bucket is out of reach."], "7wR8t0SM": ["", "Got a Bucket!"], "vMZ5k5r5": ["The well isn't dry."], "Sv9RmkHH": ["", "Got Water!"], "P25MlVT4": ["The bucket is full already."], "fB9qs9Yj": ["", "Got Sunflower Seeds!"], "2YwSPwN6": ["Something could be planted here."], "Xftfr9W2": ["It needs water."], "w6pX0MZ7": ["It desperately needs water..."], "FJb5X3B6": ["It desperately needs water..."], "MfVgP0tx": ["Something could be planted here."], "5dfR9h8y": ["It needs water."], "nc4dt2sG": ["It desperately needs water..."], "51gRkZZP": ["It desperately needs water..."], "KdyxTsx7": ["Something could be planted here."], "YfbJsSKP": ["It needs water."], "M2Bj9m7p": ["It desperately needs water..."], "fv3XCSxD": ["It desperately needs water..."], "DjzDRJv7": ["Something could be planted here."], "dfdBvRl4": ["It needs water."], "XPBXQBvH": ["It desperately needs water..."], "b3tFH5BP": ["It desperately needs water..."], "KjysMSKH": ["A persistent weed."], "ZmnFc80B": ["Better get rid of it before it spreads."], "f89v63xQ": ["Something could be planted here."], "MS6yVxWy": ["It needs water."], "l6FLKgbG": ["It desperately needs water..."], "1JBcTHZx": ["It desperately needs water..."], "7SqKS8JL": ["\"Hey. Wake up, Andy.\""], "y0b1kRtk": ["\"H-huh......??\""], "tmdxDkfZ": ["\"Is everything okay? You look.... upset.\""], "11PgQX2W": ["\"I'm fine...................\""], "FsMyfc0h": ["\"I shouldn't have slept here... it's too cramped.\""], "5BcW65Jr": ["\"I don't mind.\""], "JTTkDbsv": ["\"I do. Get off me.\""], "rKKH8d47": ["\".......Well, fuck you too.\""], "1Hqlv0kl": ["A delicate yellow sunflower ", "blooms ever so brilliantly."], "MHnZXv62": ["If you care for it, perhaps happiness will follow."], "8q4j9WQP": ["A bloodstained tarp."], "TZn6gxhN": ["Hell no. You're not going back there."], "mF3l0nJT": ["You'd rather not."], "mBxSHgD5": ["There was nothing worthwhile in there."], "m901ymB4": ["Nah, you're done with that."], "hcBqSwg6": ["\"The little lady became a Tar Soul.\""], "MZzdsq4w": ["\"I-.... I guess so... Does this matter?\""], "DyzWJj3K": ["\"Very good. Where is she now?\""], "vDH9Dkr2": ["\"(This Entity too? What do ", "they all want with her??)\""], "tz9CtXQ1": ["\"Ah, well... this and that happened...\""], "11DyzrGD": ["\"And now, she has nothing to do with ", "me. I haven't seen her in years.\""], "DBYwsd49": ["\"How unfortunate.\""], "LLSWKbhs": ["\"However, your memories may reveal ", "a clue as to her whereabouts.\""], "pRLJwKFf": ["\"Let us search.\""], "tvdCW95B": ["\"No, wait!! It-- What does it matter?\""], "RkWYcYX4": ["\"I'm sorry I bothered you. ", "I honestly didn't mean to.\""], "mTps14Jr": ["\"I can't help you. Please just let me go...\""], "KX51LDPc": ["\"It is no bother at all. I am ", "certain we can help one another.\""], "LvVblyYB": ["\"\\fb You will let me in. \\fr\\c[5]\""], "8Pm2rfqm": ["Something inside you has been forced open."], "4qjth8Wg": ["\"We seem to have arrived at ", "the crux of your problem.\""], "2tTYBwg6": ["\"In a lot of ways, I suppose so.....\""], "M5dk9bzL": ["\"Hmm... I am unable to aid you ", "with this particular issue.\""], "Pcww4G9h": ["\"I cannot bring back the dead.\""], "K54QBnY5": ["\"It's not really about that....\""], "GPYp10Dh": ["\"After that visit, I told myself I'd do anything ", "to make sure my girlfriend lived a happy life.\""], "8VpV0Kwc": ["\"I owe her that much, but......\""], "rBs5mk7c": ["\"But?\""], "XqLmK58r": ["\"I dragged my feet about it for too long.\""], "xdRvZjcW": ["\"Why is that?\""], "JWm6z8Qh": ["\"..............Prior engagements, I suppose.\""], "pM7xqdKh": ["\"\\fb Be honest. \\fr\\c[5]\""], "y1jB02ry": ["\"It didn't ease my guilt enough to be worth it.\""], "KJ3h66hT": ["\"Now this we can work with.\""], "MRGTWlk1": ["\"What shall we do about that?\""], "KWQMkdQp": ["\"('We'????)\""], "q5FNHXx9": ["\"I, uhh........ don't think there's ", "anything to be done about any of it.\""], "VP55j3XF": ["\"Surely we can reach some solution.\""], "PB8YQyTN": ["\"Or was there something else I should know?\""], "jhBm2X8b": ["\"Err.... N-no, no. That's it. ", "That's all there is to it.\""], "DXBxkwFv": ["\"Ahh, there is, I see. Pardon my rush.", "\\fb Continue. \\fr\\c[5]\""], "YH5gwhGR": ["\"(Where is she? I need to see her.....)\""], "RrMKVnLn": ["There's no point in going there twice."], "Lc1Fw7kt": ["", "Found a Key!"], "RBZSPXSM": ["\"H-hi!\""], "ndgkkx6T": ["\"Hi... I was hoping it would be you.\""], "KnPFKxgL": ["\" ! \""], "RK2Z3mjc": ["\"Oh yeah? Who else would it be?\""], "12CVdXjg": ["\" ....................... \""], "0dmxVMWd": ["\"(Whatever, it's just a dream...)\""], "fYF0mm4N": ["\"Hehee! Do you like me? Do you ", "really like me that much??\""], "4sxDhbvl": ["\"If you like me so much then say it!\""], "HwvGt7hz": ["\"Who do you like the best?\""], "FRZK1Yr5": ["\"Who's your only one??\""], "CC97MH8r": ["\"Hahah! For me, it'll always be--\""], "P4C8nd39": ["\"Andy?\""], "nSXrhm8b": ["\" ? ? ? \""], "MsgMwZkV": ["\"\\fi GAHHH!!! \\fr\\c[1]\""], "tQMpXR1W": ["\"Whoa there. Is everything okay?\""], "VgVBDWSw": ["\"Seems like you were having a... \\fi nightmare. \\fr\\c[2]\""], "zrrtz1hX": ["\"Err.... uhh... Y-yes? Don't worry about it....\""], "rxh3mjSH": ["\"I think you were asking for me.\""], "1L7tZhcz": ["\"I-.... w-wasn't, right???\""], "F4mqYkdP": ["\"Well, no worries! I am here now.\""], "1VMQlndy": ["\"Let me make it all better.\""], "js6BbffR": ["\"What do you need from me?\""], "jdSY7bYZ": ["\" ! ! ! \""], "hMqG3BxQ": ["\"Sorry, I--.... I-I- I actually have to be somewhere...\""], "B5sTb8Tn": ["\" .. .... .. . . . . .. .. .... . . .. . . \""], "7fnck3Ff": ["\"(....What's with that look?)\""], "sxrbCWhZ": ["\"(No. I'm being stupid.............)\""], "1zybnTmx": ["Your parents appreciate the hell out of you", "for taking a shower in the middle of the night."], "89X6LLzF": ["\"(Oooooookay, now that my head is clear....)\""], "ZgNBDJHt": ["\"(WHAT WAS \\fi THAT!??!? \\fr\\c[1])\""], "5Vb7hNZt": ["\"(What just happened??? Was ", "that supposed to be a joke?!)\""], "q6M254XR": ["Wow! It's a phone."], "1gtJTFtW": ["", "[ You've already unlocked this vision. ]"], "W4RlVGRj": ["[ Vision Unlocked! ]"], "HdTXvW8q": ["", "[ Visions can be viewed in the Vision Room. ]"], "RtsrzS2S": ["", "[ That is, if you have access to the Vision Room... ]"], "QgfMMt1N": ["", "Got a Nail Gun!"], "cmN7Nhdh": ["", "Got a Gun!"], "8LlsntQ7": ["", "Got Limbs x2!"], "sqFFdd55": ["", "Got a Cap!"], "x01M6r5g": ["", "Got a Head!"], "X3YHZxgz": ["The arm seems to want something."], "Tfn9Lw2C": ["Place...."], "HDfNKP92": ["It won't take the Limb."], "prRCyLvs": ["It won't take the Marshmallow."], "s6KKdDlW": ["It won't take the Car Keys."], "BzBGJq65": ["It won't open."], "D77BX3C6": ["Inside the crate appears to ", "be nothing but blood stains."], "cHmW4tZT": ["But your eyes deceive you!", "It's not blood, it's flowers."], "9cTD0KC2": ["", "Got Red Flowers x3!"], "hrln2cRj": ["Arms protrude from the ground."], "C37t7zCz": ["They seem to want something..."], "LtxDWDYG": ["", "Got a Marshmallow!"], "h3gLNkwm": ["", "Got a Marshmallow!"], "1FSrsmwm": ["", "Got a Marshmallow!"], "v43MtkPD": ["The arm seems to want something."], "szxvLzN0": ["Place...."], "5kF7nYXB": ["It won't take the Limb."], "DMwnhFSV": ["It won't take the Marshmallow."], "qT55MPtl": ["It won't take the Car Keys."], "Lgd5hT60": ["The arm seems to want something."], "nKl9ksDx": ["Place...."], "GtxCJspL": ["It won't take the Limb."], "sf6lj0Mz": ["It won't take the Marshmallow."], "SRNFW5H4": ["It won't take the Car Keys."], "Msr5MdCF": ["The arm seems to want something."], "hTs91y3k": ["Place...."], "vCH0WnsX": ["It won't take the Limb."], "L4G4kXkq": ["It won't take the Marshmallow."], "R5xt8mYq": ["It won't take the Car Keys."], "TpXTT3sT": ["\"Am I worth it?\""], "2dB3npm0": ["\"Sincerely? Not at all.\""], "PNWFMTf1": ["Looking at all the corpses and sacrifices ", "here... you've built quite the streak."], "PSBZFRbN": ["What do you have to say for yourself?"], "Th8zg2Xk": ["The neighbor cultist doesn't count. "], "jrg9wcRQ": ["You didn't know he was still ", "alive when you chopped him up."], "t3n37p1p": ["As for Nina? That was an accident."], "r6kKrmL4": ["The warden and the neighbor lady? ", "Survival. Same with the hitman."], "pBkgCDly": ["But sacrificing your ", "own mother and father? "], "fY8QlG1x": ["Come on now."], "2PspgH5g": ["Ashley might have dragged you along, ", "but along you went all on your own."], "3zttGlYJ": ["Oh yeah, and there were the campers too!"], "rDcSGMws": ["But sacrificing them didn't ", "even register, did it?"], "7mjh7hLF": ["Andrew \\fi \"I'm normal\" \\fr Graves."], "dzR1YwLR": ["There's nothing to step on."], "wcRMJ8CX": ["There's nothing to step on."], "2kL972VP": ["There's nothing to step on."], "XNgYjRlF": ["The arm seems to want something."], "L26xN9lQ": ["Place...."], "0l43XyV6": ["It won't take the Cap."], "FmSqy9XM": ["It won't take the Gun."], "Kt5vQTnt": ["It won't take the Nail Gun."], "qT5PVbkF": ["It won't take the Head."], "cHWPzq9q": ["It won't take the Marshmallow."], "dqnfxFWm": ["It won't take the Car Keys."], "CFjdBQ30": ["The arm seems to want something."], "QgncWB1y": ["Place...."], "22tsKwlg": ["It won't take the Cap."], "lbvVxcKf": ["It won't take the Gun."], "L1MdYBzW": ["It won't take the Nail Gun."], "yNXJ6StV": ["It won't take the Head."], "5Vw3F25g": ["It won't take the Marshmallow."], "xtgXYt4m": ["It won't take the Car Keys."], "lGNmG8H9": ["The arm seems to want something."], "S5RJBk9M": ["Place...."], "6JwmmQ3g": ["It won't take the Cap."], "C8npWyLx": ["It won't take the Gun."], "XQ4sdq7V": ["It won't take the Nail Gun."], "g5662QKx": ["It won't take the Head."], "Y3vfwVPS": ["It won't take the Limb."], "4zjgrfFD": ["It won't take the Car Keys."], "s420DlLj": ["The arm seems to want something."], "XFtZBnHX": ["Place...."], "z2g6Vmhb": ["It won't take the Cap."], "Kv8k2Q3x": ["It won't take the Gun."], "HHWBHwPp": ["It won't take the Nail Gun."], "n0QjhyXP": ["It won't take the Head."], "xKK4pnqL": ["It won't take the Limb."], "vjVDYb2H": ["It won't take the Car Keys."], "4ZjcVBtm": ["The arm seems to want something."], "1HjMRCyh": ["Place...."], "jd0kblzW": ["It won't take the Cap."], "lr5KRV4X": ["It won't take the Gun."], "3rpltG87": ["It won't take the Nail Gun."], "PD0dcDrG": ["It won't take the Head."], "KLFMkfZK": ["It won't take the Limb."], "ywWz5Jyj": ["It won't take the Car Keys."], "bqW70Rj2": ["The arm seems to want something."], "s8kg3JvZ": ["Place...."], "TWR3HFdY": ["It won't take the Cap."], "ZzzrXWs8": ["It won't take the Gun."], "hZ5Z3G35": ["It won't take the Nail Gun."], "NN67516L": ["It won't take the Head."], "TQLbmJkt": ["It won't take the Limb."], "qLKh1FL3": ["It won't take the Marshmallow."], "Gr4SDXHc": ["", "Got Car Keys!"], "t2RKbYGr": ["The button is missing..."], "YqmK9pby": ["There's no button."], "0Sy5dmf6": ["Placed Pink Button!"], "SG2nGwhV": ["", "Got Sunflower Seeds!"], "wKP2ZRxn": ["", "Got a Key!"], "Lqzx4bRl": ["It's your bedroom. A reasonable request", "was made that you get lost for a minute."], "NcFz5tFN": ["\"I'm not done yet!\""], "Cy42H7GK": ["She's not done yet."], "5H1sPWzZ": ["Ah, what could you have seen?", "What would it have looked like?"], "BdBK8fRT": ["Fuck, it eats away at you."], "nvcVmh9V": ["You want to see..."], "HPffqlsd": ["It's raining outside..."], "kDJDC9Sj": ["", "Caught some rain water!"], "c9ZHZ7q5": ["It's raining."], "3X4xlDFP": ["", "Caught some rain water!"], "4Wl7HDQD": ["", "Got a Key!"], "t33THT08": ["", "Got a Heart!"], "lpxRn8GL": ["It needs water."], "ywnVMYhG": ["", "Got a Watering Can!"], "9LKGcGkk": ["", "It's empty."], "klMJ4lXt": ["It needs water."], "pd9979KC": ["It needs water."], "tNl8dDh5": ["It needs water."], "Z8KT7TWH": ["It's a carpet... A rug."], "mW9SW3HY": ["One might sweep things under it, if they so desired."], "8YSG6rb8": ["A rug..."], "gZGnKTY3": ["", "Hid the Heart under the carpet!"], "CLsXk0zs": ["What's this? There was something already there..."], "v5DpNP75": ["", "Found a Pink Button!"], "hkvQbhZD": ["The door isn't locked, but it is stuck..."], "T0rdg1lT": ["You don't have enough leverage to pry it open."], "vlBDNZP8": ["You use the Rake to pry open the jammed door..."], "5LTDQChw": ["The Rake snapped..."], "9TQqXr6Q": ["You stole a rake from God and fucking broke it."], "ppP0DHs2": ["But hey, the door is open now!"], "djvHFdlD": ["", "Got a Rake!"], "W3d9F1Fg": ["You'd better return it when you're done...", "These are holy grounds, after all."], "gvVD9cFv": ["The church doors are unlocked."], "4xXC6KLp": ["However, you don't feel comfortable going in."], "CQ6MMp5l": ["\"It looks like her family has ", "already cleaned the grave...\""], "7CblgfXs": ["\" .. . ... . ... ... . . .. . .. \""], "zVgn4wq0": ["\"....A-are you okay?\""], "s5RkrnkC": ["Pull yourself the fuck together."], "XSw6XRZS": ["\"Oh, uh... Yes, of course...\""], "7yFqVZdh": ["\"Are you?\""], "nJ9N57dM": ["\"Not really........\""], "8S6k9n4y": ["\"Oh...\""], "L0j1dNJh": ["\"Umm... Do you mind if I have a moment with her alone?\""], "5jJxpXgN": ["\"Not at all. Please.\""], "QH43qX0q": ["\"Maybe you could pick some flowers for her? ", "I-... I think she'd really like that...\""], "QRpvvyCm": ["\"Sorry, I'd like to talk to her alone a little longer...\""], "9DX0XBBG": ["\"She, uhh... she liked purple...\""], "FJJpPSKs": ["\"Maybe you could find her flowers with that color?\""], "kKtV4Tnc": ["\"Oh.... Err.. This-, uhh....\""], "G98WL2St": ["\"Wrong kind of flower?\""], "mYLZLTlz": ["\"Y-yeah, hahahha. She liked purple ones... Sorry.\""], "qgmlqZMg": ["\"I think she'd have liked purple flowers...\""], "RX1cVCM8": ["\" . ... .. . . .. ... . . ... .. ..  . ... . . . ... . .\""], "wB2qgGYn": ["\"You look... really uncomfortable.\""], "C37WPwsG": ["\"Maybe I shouldn't have asked you to come.... Sorry.\""], "v87p3Cw5": ["\"N-no, no! I'm just fine.\""], "PkR5pPpR": ["\"I- I think I'm just-.......\""], "BnDF8TZ6": ["\"Taken aback. Yeah.... That ", "something like this happened.\""], "4RnkJw0P": ["\"Like, uh... Sorry, how do I put this?\""], "N5JmZBYW": ["\"You never think something like this", "ends up happening to you....\""], "LD1TWQGS": ["\"It's just something you see on TV.\""], "4Dbjy2XP": ["\"Like it's almost removed ", "from reality, y'know?\""], "RbB47kMM": ["What the hell are you babbling about??"], "Bb2sy34M": ["\"D-does that make sense?\""], "cSQsvYtn": ["No."], "TKPnWBNS": ["\"..........Yeah, I think I know what you mean...\""], "J9NG73Rt": ["\"I guess to most people it's.......... just ", "something that happened to someone else....\""], "rxsB5R5c": ["\"Maybe that's why they keep telling me to get ", "over it, since it's been so many years already...\""], "jgCj53xF": ["\"Easy for them to say.\""], "CD1Fy6Bw": ["\"E-exactly!!\""], "nLB9NFbg": ["\"Easy for them! T-they don't get hit with a ton of ", "bricks every-- every time they remember it! \\fi *sniff!* \\fr\\c[6]\""], "995Y8p4B": ["\".............\""], "2NM50hLw": ["\"O-oh... Oh no, I'm sorry.... I- I got all riled up....\""], "syd0XrJw": ["\"Don't be sorry...\""], "PC517Gwr": ["\"\\fi *sniff!* \\fr\\c[6] She--... Nina was ", "like a second sister to me...\""], "Q6XwLz94": ["\"Our parents were friends, ", "so we always played together....\""], "g7Hfjf8z": ["\"I still can't believe-... \\fi *Sob!* \\fr\\c[6]\""], "WhLSshZ0": ["\"I can't--\""], "pv83r1Vs": ["\"--believe that I won't grow old with her by my side!\""], "ypMSwvTw": ["\"And some--- some sick bastard is still ", "out there, living their best life!!!\""], "2z6TTQTD": ["\"It makes me so-.... I'm.... I'm so angry!!!!\""], "Lj3nT4QH": ["\"\\fi *Sob!* \\fr\\c[6] I'm just so angry!\""], "383W4cw5": ["\" . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . \""], "8zXSxzqq": ["\"........What can I do for you?\""], "8CrHzFWn": ["\"O-oh.... \\fi *sniff!* \\fr\\c[6] Oh, I'm sorry. I didn't ", "mean to unload that all on you, ahahaha......\""], "rBWBzXLP": ["\"Don't apologize.\""], "XsC6krlR": ["\"Heh... Thanks for coming, Andrew....\""], "MBGJvGPj": ["\"T-this is a big part of my life, so I-..... ", "I guess I just wanted to share it with you.\""], "Brkmppst": ["\"............Thank you.\""], "SyzthL8G": ["\"Isn't there anything at all ", "I can do to make it better?\""], "FMYySXC4": ["\"Just having you here is enough.\""], "3470JlQ6": ["\"I love you, Andrew.\""], "VGptwFjs": ["\".........I love you too.\""], "rYsRvh8p": ["\"Heheh! I'm so glad... Don't ever leave me.\""], "TFkHrVMZ": ["Can you at least pretend not to be a ", "total piece of crap for one minute?"], "JTvvQ82C": ["You're supposed to be good at that."], "RF6dGtD7": ["Yes, these are flowers. But you can't pick these."], "PsdjxKdS": ["C'mon. Julia is right there..."], "NCGrqwDJ": ["There's no water. This mill ", "is about as useless as you..."], "FfJhpwvx": ["", "Got Purple Flowers!"], "ymgCbZb5": ["", "Got Flowers!"], "Pgd2tM52": ["You can't reach the stairs..."], "PtWB4kcT": ["They're out of reach."], "Y0sQvZTC": ["You can't cross this as it is..."], "FlvpkTMG": ["Back there is just more junk and dust."], "nR8zTGzd": ["Once upon a time this must've been useful."], "2SPdPzd6": ["", "Pulled loose a Plank!"], "53NRLr1Y": ["\"It's Nina's death anniversary.\""], "9f7WRTFV": ["\" . . . \""], "xcjLn1tj": ["\"She was a friend of mine..... And Ashley's....\""], "V4jnYRNG": ["\"Y-yeah... I remember.\""], "Mgy5SNdB": ["\"I- I know this is a weird ", "thing to ask, but...\""], "TkC1V1TJ": ["\"It would mean a lot to me if you ", "came to visit her grave with me....\""], "Lzf8QybT": ["\".................Yes, of course......\""], "CTjFlZXQ": ["\"A-and then, when we finally got there, ", "Jane dropped the whole bag! Heehee!!\""], "Rpd5q99W": ["\"It was so silly! You should've seen her face... Hehe!\""], "Hm3y5S8J": ["\"(There's been more distance lately.)\""], "nYrQQPcC": ["\"(Even when I have actual nightmares, ", "she won't come over anymore...)\""], "WBdB7T71": ["\"(.........Did I hurt her?)\""], "P7HM8mDv": ["\"(But she was just mocking me that night,", "wasn't she? It's so on-brand for her...)\""], "G0NkxTpD": ["\"(But even then, maybe I was too harsh? She's", "only joking around because she's lonely...)\""], "vrzwtT8Y": ["Now you wish you didn't have such a knee-jerk reaction."], "HNJQpWlb": ["\"(Ahh, why'd she have to come on so strong, so suddenly?)\""], "flVqHGG5": ["Because she's Ashley."], "1hDMGGzn": ["\"(Maybe if she had been a bit ", "more subtle about it, I--...)\""], "KvSrccH5": ["\"(No! Where'd \\fi that \\fr\\c[1] thought come from?", "What the hell is up with me lately?)\""], "LThf118T": ["\\fi Hormones. \\fr"], "8RKWL63H": ["\"(Bet there's distance now because ", "she's creeped out by me....)\""], "HyTkJyQ9": ["\"(She kind of admitted she's not even ", "into that sort of thing to begin with...)\""], "GJX1tv6j": ["\"(God, I'm sick... Why am I still ", "thinking about this?)\""], "V6Sm4jPg": ["\"(The distance is a good thing.)\""], "hc7pRP02": ["\"Andrew?\""], "nygvpD7S": ["\"Hm? Sorry, what did you say?\""], "gCzXmZX0": ["\"Should we maybe get an apartment together?\""], "gr4nG882": ["\"If- if it's the two of us, I think we can afford it.\""], "fVMjZJg0": ["\"......The university is right there though.\""], "m3W2WXYZ": ["\"Well.... Well, yeah, but... don't you ", "want to learn to live on your own?\""], "vLlfj6xP": ["\"That would be a waste of money right now.\""], "jRQd0DSg": ["\"...................Y-yeah... That's true...\""], "fJ0jkqrs": ["\"Aw, c'mon. You know I'd love to live with you... ", "but I should save and focus on my studies for now.\""], "HvKGk3X9": ["\"That way when we do move in together, ", "we don't have to stay here.\""], "vJMDxKGH": ["\"We could go anywhere we want to. ", "Somewhere nicer. Just you and me.\""], "f184B7Vv": ["\"D-do you mean that??\""], "zlvFfYc9": ["\"(.......Do I?)\""], "3RMQvh0m": ["\"Still, uhh... I'll probably ", "apply for a dorm room for now....\""], "6dXQkmV6": ["\"So you could.... y'know... Come over more often....\""], "XTnnJJvV": ["\"Hmmm... Uh-huh.\""], "3ghksc9q": ["\"W-what? What?? I- I just want ", "my own space is all. I promise!\""], "gXvLF1yy": ["\"(The distance is a good thing..........)\""], "BVw1b1DR": ["\"Isn't it a bit early for you to be out", "and about? Where are you off to??\""], "hdBJhrDK": ["\"What's it to you?\""], "0R7QZ5z9": ["\"Am I not allowed to ask?\""], "LwYKycrB": ["\"Go fuck yourself.\""], "TsTWVdXB": ["\"Good morning, sweetheart!\""], "LSSLWzVd": ["\"I've made you breakfast, you--\""], "0Cm8FBNG": ["\"TWO-TIMING WHORE!!\""], "dnVG29lt": ["\"......Thanks?\""], "0syyTrQT": ["\"Blah, blah, blah, blah, blah!\""], "svbgPhKx": ["\"Uhhh... Yeah.\""], "JMWcRgH0": ["\"Choose before I choose for you!!\""], "Pphp4q7f": ["\"(This again?)\""], "22XngxQH": ["\"(Is it the scent of her shampoo?)\""], "w6pD91nL": ["\"(I have got to stop sleeping next to her........)\""], "KpV6xLxN": ["\"(Is this even helping?)\""], "gPrVDcQG": ["\"(I'm... just making it worse, aren't I?)\""], "cQ0rW0SD": ["Place..."], "fDxzWXQC": ["A flower pot."], "nHHmqm2h": ["Place..."], "sLjx0fPt": ["A flower pot."], "79wRBqpW": ["NO BACKTRACKING ALLOWED!!!!"], "sMZKFF3R": ["Do you want to skip this segment?", "[Skipping a segment does not affect the story.]"], "l1sc7Z9t": ["Done."], "PyVvH3kg": ["Tadaah!"], "4HjwGBHF": ["WOW, WOW, WOOOOW!!!"], "cbwZYCGZ": ["Place..."], "6mqbgw1p": ["A flower pot."], "gfNRBwPY": ["Place..."], "8j5wvWbH": ["A flower pot."], "r3nfrT9S": ["Place..."], "tH0GK8hP": ["A flower pot."], "5NRZc7md": ["Place..."], "JLx6htYk": ["A flower pot."], "78LvdZ0P": ["Place..."], "5zLX17TD": ["A flower pot."], "WKWMTrMn": ["\"(Why is there a remote controlled car here?)\""], "mLC2kTTH": ["\"(It's wildly out of place... ", "and out of batteries too.)\""], "kkPXSvZG": ["Some junk."], "kYkSnh1Y": ["\"What's this?\""], "9Mv2XD3l": ["\"tHis sEcuRes a RooM yOu hAve nO buSineSS iN.\""], "1YHd5ZkS": ["\"Can you make it secure the ", "room my brother is in instead?\""], "t3wcBVzh": ["\"nO. iT iS aLreaDY in uSe.\""], "cYNkMRPf": ["It's a lock the Entity won't let you re-purpose."], "d0LWmkXY": ["You attempt to interact with ", "this thing, but nothing happens."], "DK4tgP0K": ["The device doesn't respond to you at all."], "m7hx1zVc": ["Nothing happens."], "rmcbVD7V": ["A controller for an RC car."], "V1HLzQ6z": ["It's a lock the Entity won't let you re-purpose."], "C2Yz0Cjr": ["Whatever this is, it feels similar to ", "the device Ashley used to lock you in."], "2NvmsYRg": ["However, this one barely responds ", "to you interacting with it."], "kWBkHVhb": ["It flares up slightly, like an empty lighter."], "GHM2Kkvw": ["\"(...Am I missing something here?)\""], "r07KZ3Np": ["It's barely responding to you..."], "ksbGLtZS": ["The device reacts to the Talisman."], "m7lwwwks": ["\"EntRy pRohibiTed.\""], "pq9YDxhG": ["\"Oooh! Is that right? What's in there?\""], "5VClxqKm": ["\"teSt nOt mY pAtieNce, TaR SouL.\""], "2WY79R68": ["\"Alright, fine... maybe later?\""], "rnC2BXc0": ["\"nO.\""], "bTJQ0KZc": ["\"There!\""], "CKmpWHSg": ["\"..........Okay, how do I make ", "this thing stay in place?\""], "vrWLbHyB": ["\"Ah! Let's try the creepy potted plant.\""], "GPP3qdht": ["\"There we go!\""], "XSDwk7DY": ["\"There! That should keep him locked up.\""], "M3RQ5T3y": ["\"Go ahead and put his soul back in.\""], "RKJQW5qT": ["\".........Please?\""], "7T1pZjN3": ["\"Not with \\fi that \\fr\\c[2] attitude!\""], "10hyqn3H": ["\"Listen, here's what's gonna happen now...\""], "1ZfYqtcM": ["\"You're gonna sit there and reflect upon ", "your actions until I tell you otherwise!\""], "J4QZbd5j": ["\"Eat shit! I'd rather you shoot me!\""], "h08Vjgf8": ["\".................Whatever. You'll calm down eventually.\""], "vdSHbqFV": ["\"I'll check in on you later...\""], "1FQmjN0M": ["\"Ashley, don't you go anywhere!!\""], "fkRH5Plk": ["\"Ashley!!\""], "zn6c8Byf": ["\"Leyley! Open this fucking door, you little shit!!\""], "xF0drX9G": ["A half-formed Entity of some sort."], "hGQk5kQk": ["It emanates confusion and anger."], "GdYDM7xM": ["You'd rather not disturb it."], "h5XN1fCs": ["The soul doesn't seem to notice ", "you. It's too busy daydreaming."], "MVqg7kKw": ["The soul looks at you looking at it."], "6f3X8wsj": ["Your company has been rejected."], "SQhJXHvt": ["\"....W-what? What do you want?\""], "0Ll4S04g": ["A wildly out-of-place picnic table."], "MBQjtTF9": ["This one seems interested in the flower patch."], "t8JNGVtb": ["This soul feels similar to Ashley.", "Only milder. Less than. Inferior."], "bk4mxgwy": ["Like a firework that never launched."], "2B51hTZy": ["How suffocating. It reminds you of yourself."], "TCkjxLCD": ["\"..........Hi Mom.\""], "1bZgNcPG": ["The soul doesn't remember you."], "DT0P9lBx": ["You are nothing to this soul."], "lycX5QrH": ["A skittish, unremarkable soul."], "gBCrW1bg": ["This soul is nothing to you."], "mY7891SD": ["This soul absentmindedly munches on a flower."], "qZ6w50YD": ["You place the trinkets you made on top of the orb."], "0MYXYMwK": ["Despite the orb being solid to touch, ", "the trinkets sink inside it."], "JGM5rPdQ": ["\"There! Is that enough orb stuffings for you?\""], "PndJpnxR": ["The Entity infuses the trinkets with its energy."], "KLBnHCSD": ["As it does, the Entity almost seems to shrink a little."], "z98nkVWF": ["\"(....Am I seeing things?)\""], "XSfGQX9f": ["\"Ah!! No, wait! I get it!\""], "CnV7shPR": ["\" ...........? \""], "ywJ2DnT7": ["\"It's because you are magic!!\""], "qRk9Z315": ["\".........'MaGic'?\""], "npdFnK1N": ["\"Or... y'know, a soul. You're a soul, ", "right? And souls are magic...\""], "4Ymp2W91": ["\"So if you use all your magic, will you disappear? ", "Because then there'd be nothing left of you.\""], "XjHRbZ8Z": ["\".......aBsorBing SouLs gRanTs oNe eNeRGy.\""], "xrdl3C5k": ["\"Yeah, yeah... but if you're out of ", "'energy' you disappear, right?\""], "8bVvVjrT": ["\"That's why you have to keep", "eating other souls, right??\""], "pP1p5Q29": ["\"CoRreCt.\""], "fxpsj2PT": ["\"\\fi Heh. \\fr\\c[2] I knew it.\""], "r09JzGCF": ["\"I like this demon stuff. It's such horseshit.\""], "wlCCtbJK": ["The Entity appears confused but won't say anything."], "NKC2bC9c": ["\"I mean that none of this stuff makes ", "any real sense, but it feels right.\""], "JdrTLXtp": ["\"It's easy to follow.\""], "5s4kPs3p": ["\"YoU aRe in-TuNe wiTh tHis ReaLm.\""], "8YdYNvyj": ["\"TaR SouL, fOrgeT nOt yOu aRe mY sErvAnt.\""], "59vmSNbm": ["\"Pretty sure I never agreed ", "to anything like that.\""], "hSn1JqT3": ["\"I sToPpeD yOuR bRotHer. YOu ofFerEd ", "mE aNyThinG witHout reStricTions.\""], "JlHHQCWy": ["\"EvEn if You AscenD, yOu WiLL ", "ReMaiN mY seRvAnt fOrEver.\""], "wmcsCbgy": ["\"Yikes... Can't you just say we're friends?\""], "LHNvKy2x": ["\"Also I don't know what the hell ", "'ascend' means in this context.\""], "q9yz25zl": ["\"ThE OrB iS rEaDy.\""], "kyw6LrZT": ["\"Alright! Let's go lock up my brother!\""], "G4f006yR": ["", "Got a Magical Magic Orb!"], "lpqjw8Yj": ["On the table sits an unfinished demon trinket."], "13TB3Vdl": ["\"Is making these a hobby of yours?\""], "JgL0vFk8": ["\"TaLisMans aRe cHeap and UseFuL mEdiuMs.\""], "Z5pbQX1q": ["\"Hmm... Maybe I'll try making some.\""], "cWD64n2j": ["\"What are they made of? Sticks and yarn??\""], "mPLXWV0l": ["\"ThoSe WouLd suFfice.\""], "QXMz5kVR": ["\"Well, well, well! I happen to have some right here!\""], "XmXvSvVl": ["\"Let's see here...\""], "8K208S5c": ["", "Crafted some ugly trinkets!"], "90FKX01H": ["An unfinished trinket."], "LH6QjR1G": ["\"Alright, let's try making some trinkets.\""], "fSJZZgxs": ["", "Crafted some ugly trinkets!"], "k89GrBKn": ["\"Tadaaaaaah!! What do you think??\""], "z050MJ0C": ["\"....PaSsAble.\""], "rrHmS39x": ["\"I think you meant to say 'incredible, master-level ", "craftsmanship made with obvious natural talent'.\""], "d6tDvtwF": ["The Entity does not play along."], "pFFnRrjN": ["\"God, I miss Andrew.......\""], "tn9r2f8k": ["\"ReFrain fRom uNneceSsaRy pRofaniTies.\""], "kb5zgDdQ": ["\" ? ? ? \""], "ZrCYXwvr": ["", "Got some Trinkets!"], "cwzfRvRl": ["One trinket remains on the table."], "QtYyP6lB": ["\"(That one didn't turn out so good...", "I'm just gonna leave it here.)\""], "5HXlcpr7": ["\"(This kind of looks like a crappy ", "version of the trinket Ashley has...)\""], "rG8T7qvV": ["\"(Well, it can't hurt to take it with me... Probably.)\""], "bNqFQcBt": ["", "Got Talisman!"], "D5FRhXGH": ["Underneath the covers rests a skeleton."], "yGsD17Yn": ["\"Oh my. And who is this handsome fellow??\""], "zySz5WQf": ["\"My ReMaiNs.\""], "dx035Z4T": ["\"Well, you've seen better days!\""], "sQNtDK41": ["\"How long has this thing been rotting ", "here? There's nothing left but bones.\""], "51d2TZlK": ["\"TiMe haS beComE iRReLevaNt.\""], "Drk7jkQY": ["\"Why are you keeping it here anyway? Just bury it.\""], "ZX4hcyY2": ["\"ThiS iS mY ReaLm.\""], "rBXSD407": ["\"(That answers nothing, but whatever. ", "I don't care that much......)\""], "vpXYsdNm": ["There's a skeleton under the covers."], "fMyN6RD2": ["The faintest hint of warmth can be felt from it..."], "YKB15ll3": ["\"(This thing isn't going to come ", "back to life and kill me, is it?)\""], "Rpnv1Tzb": ["\"This looks relevant. What is it?\""], "HbdvdjrC": ["\"A ConTainEr fOr eNerGy. MucH LiKe yOuR TaLisman.\""], "8cbTMytR": ["\"Yikes. I'd hate to be hauling ", "this thing around all day.\""], "Zzlc9jrB": ["\"One doEs nOt bRinG tHis wiTh tHem.\""], "CSLYymzX": ["\"It iS LeFt BehinD onCe aCtiVe.\""], "45gZkw0X": ["\"So activate it?\""], "yhh6wSbw": ["\"It nEeDs mAtERiaL tO aTtAch eNerGy iNto.\""], "TF3yYVzs": ["\"You mean just something to fill", "the orb? I can do that.\""], "1gk4llVP": ["\"Oh, I know!! How about ", "these trinkets I made?\""], "wRPt96X7": ["You need something to place inside the orb."], "j46gWsZz": ["This potted tree is just about dead."], "QBDlsvVL": ["But it's kind of stylish looking, so you leave it alone."], "MLCgXt2f": ["Fancy half-dead potted plant."], "1prtBzx4": ["Kind of looks like a hand."], "j9BBQpT2": ["\"Ooh! Let's use this to prop ", "up the orb all stylishly.\""], "54GL2d26": ["", "Got Tiny Tree!"], "XmNsvhn3": ["", "Got some Yarn!"], "kzlLKVBk": ["This plant is all dried-up."], "bzSHTdMc": ["", "Got Twigs!"], "cLmv1lKc": ["This one is dead."], "sQ1LtRzv": ["If you want flowers, you're gonna have to look elsewhere."], "tVlFt4Nj": ["\"(A giant window! Perfect.)\""], "6rvX5bn6": ["\"(...What is up with these locks, though?)\""], "0wRQtTL7": ["Place...."], "MGsppwwJ": ["Place...."], "Gx6ZhRhM": ["Place...."], "Pr9vzklL": ["You've got nothing to put here..."], "YN5zFcQw": ["", "Got Pink Flowers!"], "kb1TvwyQ": ["", "Got Yellow Flowers!"], "LJV0GB52": ["Place...."], "fLDKvJ0k": ["Place...."], "t3dhWrBr": ["Place...."], "Pz6GZT7J": ["You've got nothing to put here..."], "VJYh5yTb": ["Place...."], "S6rM1g8g": ["Place...."], "d6zrxprs": ["Place...."], "PKStL2YY": ["You've got nothing to put here..."], "3YXdvcdL": ["You and your soul army exit through the window."], "vt05P6J9": ["Things sure have escalated."], "9BWGd0Y5": ["Yet you feel oddly calm."], "ylj4xsY4": ["You are in control. Things ", "are going to be fine."], "5Sb7N3D2": ["\"(Ashley is taking a while.....)\""], "4kBpgKhp": ["Your arms are growing tired."], "FvK8KQCF": ["\"(Is she okay? Did something happen?)\""], "8YDN8KNl": ["\"(Did the warden do something? ", "What about the demon??)\""], "GBH57rCT": ["\"(Argh! Why'd I let her go alone??)\""], "ZqQYyhM4": ["\"(She's completely unarmed! ", "What if nothing shows up and--)\""], "Qn2FHpMp": ["\"Ummm... I--....\""], "xZ0VdMKY": ["\"Hm?\""], "QpDbzbTJ": ["\"I- I get it... You just want ", "to get out of here, right?\""], "B30rvLnq": ["\"....Right.\""], "tk9mD9M6": ["\"Me too. But I thought it was impossible...", "That's why I told you to go away earlier.\""], "dtnb0mGz": ["She can't see you roll your eyes."], "BzNFfQYw": ["\"No, no... I understand. We're ", "all just doing what we can.\""], "89jcVk3n": ["\"I'm sorry it has come to this. I ", "don't actually plan on hurting you.\""], "2hXBhPY1": ["\"Well, that's a relief, aahaha!\" "], "c8HFMchy": ["\"(Did she believe me? Probably not...)\""], "mgR0f2s6": ["\"Maybe we could help each other out?\""], "xZvBHs7M": ["\"Those guard guys kinda trust me, we could ", "use that to our advantage somehow.\""], "S5ct5Vll": ["\" ............................... \""], "SznVb6F9": ["\"Heeeey! That's not a bad idea. ", "What did you have in mind?\""], "h195Hp3Y": ["\"Err, well... um...\""], "Mr7HbJGc": ["\"Oh! I know. Let's go ask my sister. ", "She'll know exactly what to do.\""], "XsC1JZ1z": ["\"S-sure! Yeah, she's the girl ", "who just left? Let's go quick.\""], "Ck1zJL9q": ["\"But I'm a little scared to walk with ", "this blade on my neck, hahaha......\""], "bjr1YzT8": ["\"(It does get tricky... I don't want to accidentally ", "kill her before we know she's no longer useful...)\""], "l1Bd3mWP": ["\"(But I've got to check on Ashley...)\""], "4zrlltWX": ["\"(And I \\fi am \\fr\\c[1] holding a cleaver.)\""], "ngQR8XrT": ["\"(It's not like this woman is stupid ", "enough to try something if I let go.)\""], "TvL2ygvR": ["\"(It'd be in her best interest to play nice, ", "at least until there's an opening to escape.)\""], "p4sxztrC": ["\"You're right. Sorry about that!\""], "tHqrHPST": ["You lower your weapon."], "2Fy0vscr": ["And the second you do, she lunges for ", "a nail gun laying on the ground."], "lmXH60hS": ["She doesn't make it. You yank her ", "back before you even realize it."], "KcCwm7jh": ["And throw her onto the bed."], "4sVHb6JM": ["\"NOOO!!!!\""], "8ryh1knP": ["Where you proceed to strike her."], "w7CFCG7Y": ["Over and over."], "MqTDQ0zt": ["Unnecessarily. She's already dead."], "7y1w1wJ5": ["Why? Are you embarrassed? "], "PCwzSLKm": ["You thought you had the situation all figured ", "out. Haha! You're embarrassed, aren't you?"], "pgznF6TH": ["Fucking idiot."], "2hNq7L2g": ["\"(Never mind. What a dumb bitch!)\""], "Cg76Mr5n": ["\"(Dammit....)\""], "SQcy27w9": ["You clean her blood off of you."], "tXt4ZspN": ["\"(How do I explain this to Ashley? ", "What the hell was I thinking!?)\""], "zrzhTXVX": ["\"(Get it together, dumbass! You're supposed to have ", "things under control. She's counting on you...)\""], "QxRT5BpM": ["\"(Just to be sure....)\""], "GVLjPxzf": ["You check the pulse from her wrist ", "to confirm what you already know."], "5z2yvknv": ["\"(Dead.)\""], "8Hx4prsB": ["\"(Well, whatever... It was going to turn ", "out like this one way or the other.)\""], "NHv75rwH": ["\"(We can't leave witnesses.)\""], "VpRNJmbC": ["Still, you had hoped to maybe somehow ", "frame all your crimes on the lady."], "sKRVHDcP": ["Maybe sacrifice her to the demon, should ", "Ashley actually succeed in summoning one."], "rN0HsyCX": ["\"(What is keeping Ashley anyway? ", "I need to see her...)\""], "Vh4ntfwy": ["\"(Ah, thank god. There she is.....)\""], "smBMdKJg": ["\"..................What happened here??\""], "rT1rK4dW": ["\"hALt.\""], "8lccpJvs": ["\"wHat iS tHe meAniNg oF tHis?\""], "8MbsxTKM": ["\"Yeah, what the hell are you doing?!\""], "s0klVnZb": ["\"Nothing. I'm leaving.\""], "JS2KWnkT": ["\"I wELcoMed yOu tO mY ReaLm.\""], "5yV2Mn6m": ["\"YeT yOu RePay Me bY sTeaLing SouLs.\""], "8Vn37mjC": ["\"W-wait! No! He hasn't done anything yet!\""], "WqGS21vv": ["\"Look, the souls are all right here!\""], "GNsTdts8": ["\"HiS puNishMent is DeATh.\""], "jNmP9Tc2": ["\"NO!! Don't hurt him!!\""], "KRzplyZz": ["\"Please!! I'll--! No, no! I'm sorry!\""], "frs77CW7": ["\" . . . . . . . \""], "kWdHLyHc": ["\"I'll put him somewhere else! I'll ", "make sure he doesn't get out again!\""], "Shx5ylZV": ["\"I wiLL hOuSe hiM nO LonGer!\""], "0ff2nYYF": ["\"Okay! Okay, that's fine! I'll, uhh... ", "I-I'll take him to the Human Realm! Yeah.\""], "CC0BvBkn": ["\"Let's do that right now!\""], "0L248Bqs": ["\"C'mon, Andrew! Move it! Let's go.\""], "YybQjhs3": ["\"I said MOVE!!\""], "Vt3qPtxD": ["\" . . . . . . . . . . . \""], "CQ8F1cN0": ["\"God, are you kidding me?\""], "vCzLybzQ": ["\"DisPoSe of HiM, TaR SouL.\""], "yfv8qDGr": ["\"I wisH to NeveR sEe hiM aGaiN.\""], "pW4vMLW9": ["\"You won't have to see him. ", "Just help me move him...\""], "XT83DrYg": ["\"ThiS iS tHe LasT TimE, TaR SouL.\""], "DLZ2XlQ6": ["\"I hAvE enTerTaiNed yOuR wHims eNouGH.\""], "QVkCZYXY": ["There's nothing to step on."], "6h5qGNF5": ["There's nothing to step on."], "gH1RqD2s": ["There's nothing to step on."], "DLW3qHV7": ["\"Heh heh! I'm happy!\""], "RhD3dkRz": ["\"Glad to hear it.\""], "tddsXKKp": ["\"What about you? Are you happy? You better be.\""], "6bvGQjng": ["\"............Of course I am.\""], "s6Tngmpl": ["\"Hehee, that's right! Everything has worked ", "itself out, just like I always said it would.\""], "JMll8wV1": ["\"You too. You've finally worked yourself out.\""], "V7drftDz": ["\"I'm not sure what you mean.\""], "mHkyRdgm": ["\"You're back to being Andy.\""], "q50bxZbt": ["\"For a while there, you let me call you ", "Andy, but you weren't really feeling it...\""], "slLvH2m6": ["\"But now you've finally come around, ", "just like I always trusted you would!\""], "q28N4G25": ["\" .......... \""], "DWBf9PQg": ["\"I love you, Andy.\""], "XNKRLZ4s": ["\"I love you, Leyley...\""], "GShlSFQM": ["\"Hehee! As you should!!\""], "R89SDcgc": ["\"TaR SouL.\""], "4jGMtvv3": ["\"LeT uS CoLLecT SouLs.\""], "H3r2ZBry": ["\"Ugh... again?? Aren't you ", "getting super greedy lately?\""], "k7d71S25": ["\"Ah, whatever... I'll see you later, Andy.\""], "kFB0zWHw": ["\" . . . . . . . . . . . \""], "lHzHQRW7": ["She's done playing for the day."], "YPhQpvYF": ["It's back into the box with you."], "nH2NX4tj": ["LEYLEY WINS -END!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!"], "T1GRR41V": ["Boy! That sure sucked, huh?", "Absolutely nothing got resolved."], "WWN7kmsD": ["Bet you wish you had chosen ", "to grow a spine instead?"], "3vFRHH4d": ["Oh, okay. Pardon me for assuming."], "DlrzRckz": ["\\{YOU'VE CLEARED THE GAME! ", "WOOOOOOOOOHOOOOOOOOO!!!!!!!!\\}"], "nhwlXwgy": ["Well, lucky for you I shall grant you mercy!"], "GLRG58pv": ["We'll skip right back to that ", "dreadful decision you made."], "s9ChMklL": ["\"S-sorry! Give me just a minute.\""], "TrGrKh93": ["There's mail on the floor, ", "but it's just out of reach."], "GkckF51k": ["\"(Oh, c'mon....)\""], "1cdf2DxP": ["The mail is just out of reach..."], "BBGPwxRT": ["You lie flat on your stomach for a better ", "reach and use the Tongs to grab the mail."], "l2gDFzLT": ["", "Got Mail!!"], "SksQmxvW": ["", "They're all bills!"], "kT4W2c5R": ["Electricity, phone, water... ", "all past their due date! Nice."], "F2ZgpTJ9": ["\"(Guess the lights won't be on for much longer...)\""], "8jLQXWps": ["\"(Why haven't you taken care of these-...)\""], "NBrTMLLH": ["You check the name on the letters."], "mB6zfFRs": ["\"(...'Carl Cultman'?)\""], "HxrsYZVn": ["\"(Well, no matter. Now I know where I am.)\""], "6LSVH4Kj": ["\"(And I take back what I thought earlier...)\""], "F5NVXX6y": ["\"(She's got no forethought at all! ", "We're back in our home city!!)\""], "yDfSYpmJ": ["\"(Though I can't say I've ever ", "been to this side of it...)\""], "yMKYBTGd": ["\"(Still, we might run into any ", "number of people who recognize us.)\""], "KCF4shvW": ["\"Err... uhhh... I- I'm indecent!! ", "Just a second, please!!\""], "2MxTD4HD": ["\"Miss, please open the door.\""], "p1xMWp8x": ["\"We would prefer that you not make this an issue.\""], "m444lCty": ["\"A-alright! Sheesh!! FINE! But I", "haven't cleaned this place in days!\""], "p9BkRbHz": ["\"Good evening, citizens!\""], "YWRQXcSW": ["\"We've received a noise complaint. ", "Is everything okay in here?\""], "XY2hbbyJ": ["\"Yes....?\""], "XHrV4q04": ["\"(They sure got here fast.......... ", "Are we right next to a station??)\""], "7YRq2L3x": ["\"Mind if we take a quick look around?\""], "sSRd4Ns0": ["He looks around before you can answer..."], "HzZvkBWm": ["\"(Who am I supposed to call? ", "The police? Yeah, right...)\""], "VQcbXFGf": ["\"(Even if I could ask someone to come ", "help me, I don't know where I am.)\""], "v3W7Rmzr": ["\"(I should figure out my situation first.)\""], "SvNXhBnD": ["\"(Oooookay. Now that I know where I am...)\""], "z3Jnf0kv": ["Call the police?"], "Rx2ZpCpG": ["............................................Really?"], "4lyl1BC2": ["\"(That's right. Fuck it. Fuck this!)\""], "cWBybsFw": ["\"(I'd rather go to jail before staying ", "locked up as Ashley's little bitch.)\""], "lb5pg2x0": ["\"HAHA!! That's right. See if I care anymore. ", "I already tried to kill us both anyway!\""], "cjPSqWQV": ["\"Nothing matters anymore................\""], "mXPTJswX": ["\"Police. How can we help you?\""], "rZ9qQbtb": ["\"Uhh... Yeah. I'd like to confess a murder.\""], "MqkM63DP": ["\"Oookay. Can I just get your name first?\""], "7zp4sPwW": ["\"Andrew Graves.\""], "yTnhjgy7": ["\"Just a second.... Okay, here we go.\""], "6FL4tB4s": ["\"It says here that you're dead.\""], "STynj69N": ["\"..........Well, I'm not. Can I confess the murder now?\""], "FPn30mzs": ["\"Sir, do you understand that wasting ", "police resources is a crime?\""], "rq0N3h7V": ["\"I know it says I'm dead, but ", "that was this whole other thing...\""], "mJHCbNHr": ["\"My supposed death was part of an ", "insurance fraud my parents committed.\""], "MJgd4PFG": ["\"Yeah well, you're gonna have to take ", "that up with the insurance company.\""], "XT1ChPbQ": ["\"Now if that was everything.....\""], "G1WbqcyZ": ["\"Huh..? No. I don't care about that.\""], "lzDXY1zr": ["\"I'm telling you I'm alive, ", "unlike my parents whom I killed.\""], "lbkzckyZ": ["\"And I also killed this guy I didn't ", "know after he tried to assassinate me.\""], "MxYWXJZt": ["\"His license plate was--\""], "qgdxBm0R": ["\"Sir, either give me your actual", "name, or I'm hanging up.\""], "fzJZFlX2": ["\"There were also these campers at ", "this camping site the other day...\""], "2v29lrNN": ["\"Okay, I'm hanging up.\""], "BSvlLjMh": ["\"And while I didn't kill any officers, ", "I'm the reason they can't wake up.\""], "13z4DbJ8": ["\"............Did that incident leak to the news already?\""], "1TH345vv": ["\"And even before that, I killed two of my neighbors. ", "Though one of them I didn't know I killed until later.\""], "ZLWYk2mN": ["\"Oh. And this security guard, I think?", "I'm not exactly sure what to call him.\""], "5gHvFhLl": ["\"And many years ago, I killed ", "this little girl by accident.....\""], "n0dBQKnG": ["\"Well, aren't you a busy boy.\""], "TwZ9CtQT": ["\"And I killed my sister too. She", "wasn't dead either, but she is now.\""], "LwtCMXxr": ["No she isn't, but you don't want them looking ", "for her just because you're confessing."], "bH5PGzH6": ["What a good brother you are, even after all this."], "hcM3tx5t": ["\"Listen here, you little prankster!\""], "qvrmKn5J": ["\"If we weren't overworked with a bunch of coma mysteries, ", "I'd send an officer over to teach you a lesson.\""], "Wn4npCZW": ["\"There's actually one of those coma ", "mysteries with me right here.\""], "s9dR6JWY": ["\"Suuuure there is. Let me guess, ", "you're gonna kill them too?\""], "kTRz0gXR": ["\"I mean I might have to, if", "you don't come and arrest me.\""], "C875QDBP": ["\"I'll steal his identity and hope his friends won't notice.\""], "HV6Hl0js": ["\"Well, how about you do just that?\""], "Lbknk9nK": ["\"I, uhh.......... Sure?\""], "YkRWdFms": ["\"Sounds like you're all set. Would that be all? ", "Any other bullshit you feel like spewing at me?\""], "rVJb6TcL": ["\"I... guess that's all.......?\""], "WFc2sntf": ["\"Alright. Have a good night, sir.\""], "0b71ccyg": ["\"Uhh... y-you too? Thanks. Bye??\""], "ZZ7PcZq7": ["\"(.......What the hell was \\fi that? \\fr\\c[1])\""], "CVLzgkqQ": ["That was lucky."], "ZNhcy87K": ["Having given it some more thought,", "you don't want to surrender after all."], "3m4lF8Nq": ["Didn't think so..."], "hzB2jf1P": ["Call your parents instead?"], "DWVZnn7j": ["Call your friends?"], "DfZcc2p4": ["\" . . . . . . . . . . . . . . \""], "w3M2CWxN": ["You know. Your friends? You had some, right??"], "L758jXNN": ["Like your best friend all through school.", "What was his name again? Friend B?"], "njq4X6PP": ["Well, never mind his name! ", "What was his number??"], "9JY1JSRT": ["\"(Ah, crap... Julia's number is", "the only one I can remember....)\""], "5Yf3gnTG": ["\"(Well, here goes, I guess....)\""], "3ZKTZSNG": ["\"H-hellooo hello! You've reached my voicemail. ", "Please leave a message after the beep!\""], "KwGVmH2B": ["\"I'll try to get back to you ", "soon. Okay? O-okay, bye!!\""], "s9LqskbV": ["You hang up."], "35zbWSkD": ["\"(She sounded..... cheerier than I remember.)\""], "nKZpgT7c": ["\"(Anyway, I shouldn't leave a recording...)\""], "4DyxWGV0": ["\"(I'm sure I can talk her out of snitching ", "on me, should she have such intentions...)\""], "QCWKCGnG": ["\"(But I have no control over ", "who listens to her voicemails.)\""], "4hdmXrxq": ["You decide to try again later. Maybe ", "she just wasn't available right now..."], "FQkVMD2Y": ["Though, knowing the crap Ashley put her through, you're ", "pretty sure she just doesn't answer the phone in general."], "xgB1sJ8H": ["\"(Well, that's it. I have no idea ", "what else to try right now...)\""], "PffTRy29": ["\"(Wait for Ashley, I guess?)\""], "gDkvxHYz": ["Wanna save before you screw this up?"], "fTWNrMWr": ["You pick up the phone, but don't say anything."], "qgGyr0zG": ["\".......Umm....... H-hello? Is anybody there?\""], "spWVLsVb": ["Surprise! It's Julia, your ex-girlfriend!"], "SDMVw71L": ["And possibly your ticket out of these chains.", "Quick! Put up your best performance!"], "F72j9y6F": ["\"Err....... Y-you left me an empty message ", "yesterday... I was just wondering who you are?\""], "sBPSYk7c": ["\"Heyyyy there, you!\""], "Z8fcrTLR": ["\"..........A-Andrew?\""], "nMkgGwYK": ["\"Uh-huh. Surprise!\""], "TWDqfzbq": ["\"I- I thought you were dead!!\""], "2DHXmJS3": ["\"Why would I be dead?\""], "r1zYwdRv": ["\"Errr...? I- I heard there was a fire...\""], "KZrYjxdL": ["\"And nobody had heard from you or Ashley since.....\""], "t1ZyJwxV": ["\"Ahh, right. No, we weren't ", "living there anymore. Luckily.\""], "RBzsY2zZ": ["\"Wait... does that mean you didn't ", "know I was safe this whole time?\""], "f3SpV29S": ["\"I had no idea! \\fi *Sniff!* \\fr\\c[6] Y-you ", "dummy!! I was so worried!\""], "p4fJGwMJ": ["\"N-nobody would tell me anything... ", "I even tried calling the morgue!\""], "qWMldLPf": ["\"Aww, I'm sorry. I would've called ", "you right away if I knew.\""], "PCbbTCR8": ["\"Oh.... Well... I'm just glad you're okay...... So.\""], "HkV98xbq": ["\"Why, did you want me dead?\""], "Fcf6xqc6": ["\"Of course not! W-why would I??\""], "JRzvMxsq": ["\"Well, I \\fi am \\fr\\c[1] your ex...\""], "0tBmhZtl": ["\"\\fi *Sniff!* \\fr\\c[6] D-do you think I'm that horrible? ", "I would never wish death upon anybody.....\""], "Wp7X9lns": ["\"(We're off to a great start, huh...)\""], "158YpCKy": ["\"If- if you think I'm so awful, why do this??\""], "7WXpD0pK": ["\"Why are you calling me now?\""], "Ky84Yhw9": ["\"Because I miss you, of course.\""], "6X2ZVhrr": ["\"I think enough time has passed that we ", "could at least try being friends again.\""], "2Rfh0CNj": ["\"................I- I don't know, Andrew...\""], "fmHWDRMr": ["\"I just-.... it's probably best we ", "keep going our separate ways....\""], "6CmFy1lQ": ["\"(Well, this is unexpected... Usually ", "she'd be over the moon by now.)\""], "CxfFt1bk": ["\"Hey... I know I wasn't the best boyfriend, and ", "I know we haven't seen each other in months...\""], "03kvTLvS": ["\"But I've been thinking about you every day.\""], "mF7hQ65m": ["\" . . . . . . . . . . . . \""], "B6MRwMGd": ["\"(Still no? Did she find someone else..?)\""], "7fG8pvgV": ["\"Sorry... Am I bothering you right now?\""], "P9RnRRj0": ["\"Err... it's not that, but.... or a little, yeah, but....\""], "jYprMGTs": ["\"Ahh, look. I'm going to be honest...\""], "hcygbwvd": ["\"I'm so, so sorry for reaching out of ", "the blue just to ask for a favor.\""], "WZVrzd1t": ["\"But I really don't know who else to ask.\""], "QqBNP75q": ["\"Oh.......? W-what is it?\""], "svcSNyM9": ["\"Well, this and that happened, and a friend ", "of mine is playing a bit of a prank on me.\""], "vsqZqvYD": ["\"But it's a really inconvenient time, and I--\""], "TRPKfbcs": ["\"I-is this friend Ashley?\""], "5l3S01C9": ["\".............What makes you think so?\""], "1l8MnysR": ["\"With you, it's...... always Ashley, so........\""], "0nghJQGr": ["\"If this has something to do with her, ", "I don't-.... want to be involved at all.\""], "PJ3bTYj4": ["\"It's not Ashley. Just a friend of mine.\""], "WBnbYV74": ["\" ............. \""], "DdD3wwPY": ["\"Hello.....? Are you still there?\""], "rw7fmGgD": ["\"Andrew..... There's something I've", " been wanting to ask you...\""], "pdclgjbt": ["\"I- I know this is sudden but... ", "Why didn't you protect me?\""], "bMXxzJSN": ["\"....What do you mean?\""], "SHCQTPhM": ["\"When Ashley kept sending me those vile messages...\""], "k11wsdgN": ["\"Why didn't you stop her? H-how ", "could you just let it happen?\""], "66b11FXF": ["\" . . . . . . . . \""], "BcLVpJSd": ["\"Andrew, we both know it was her.\""], "bxsXDGh8": ["\"Please, just-.... don't insult my intelligence anymore.\""], "vb6DhL3r": ["\"Just tell me, why didn't you do anything?\""], "CzjnJtjM": ["\"It was easier not to.\""], "dm8w0DSj": ["\" . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . \""], "YVzHsMdQ": ["\"Had I addressed it, I would've had to pick a side.\""], "sR07MFx0": ["\"I would've picked you, and that", " would mean she'd be all alone.\""], "dgTPtd0B": ["\"And what does a person like Ashley do, ", "when she has nothing left to lose?\""], "9sFVYFx3": ["\" ...................... \""], "qHG741wQ": ["\"I did protect you, Julia. But I understand ", "you won't see it that way.\""], "SgMd0098": ["\"..................................I see.\""], "hm5mW6mJ": ["\"Guess it was my own fault ", "anyway... For being so stupid...\""], "ZBTl3Lnl": ["\"B-because you did warn me ", "about her.... Many, many times.....\""], "gwSWLtfz": ["\"I should've-- \\fi *Sob!* \\fr\\c[6] I shouldn't ", "have asked to be official!\""], "j5DpSwlg": ["\"It's my own fault! I'm sorry ", "about the ultimatum!!\""], "wKbd1rwW": ["\"Nooo. No, no, no. Don't be sorry.\""], "WRChkyH9": ["\"I'm in the wrong for agreeing to something ", "I knew was going to turn out badly.\""], "fKJzGqlg": ["\"I should've let you let me go right then and there.\""], "n20xvC59": ["\"But I just cared for you so deeply I couldn't.\""], "wNcv6HyP": ["\"And there was always the off chance that I was wrong.\""], "NVFxGt5G": ["\"\\fi *Sob!* \\fr\\c[6]\""], "rKS5CxYd": ["\"I think it's wonderful you still", "believed she would come around.\""], "lbt0QWxG": ["\"I hope you don't stop giving people a second ", "chance, just because she didn't deserve it.\""], "Bnf6mh26": ["\"You're very brave.\""], "mFprmJGv": ["\"Y-yeah...\""], "YQp3ZNYP": ["\"Thanks, Andrew.... For being honest.\""], "6Pz3g9Wn": ["\"Because it wasn't her.\""], "40WccHV7": ["\" \\fi Sigh..... \\fr\\c[6]\""], "XgKpCHxH": ["\"I know you think it was her, ", "I know Jane thinks it was her.\""], "ldQCF5jX": ["\"I know eeeeverybody in your ", "corner thinks it was her.\""], "lzv22yyQ": ["\"Well, I'm the only one in her corner...\""], "Hg0jpNbc": ["\"I know my sister, and I know it wasn't her.\""], "4vrnRTgJ": ["\"Okay, Andrew...... If you say so...........\""], "SN4RVgn5": ["You hope she thinks you're in denial or", "delusional, rather than full of shit."], "Gf7QtxsG": ["\"A-anyway, I need to go... Sorry....\""], "pwvBsJpH": ["\"What's with the cold shoulder?", " Did I say something wrong?\""], "XQw3GSyB": ["\"I, uhh.... I've been talking to Jane ", "about things. A-and my therapist...\""], "6X0pfRZg": ["\"And I think it's just-........................\""], "B874v6cX": ["\"W-well I've had a lot of time to think and-, a-and....\""], "02RnGvWH": ["\"Jane thinks it's better we don't talk anymore......\""], "0ylBzJSF": ["\"Jane does, huh......\""], "s3SFkt19": ["\" . ... . .. .. .... . .. .. .. .... .. . . . \""], "kzvdJjKV": ["\"Alright, I get it... I'm sorry. ", "I won't bother you again.\""], "90YQRHnh": ["\"But I don't suppose you could", "spare me one last kindness?\""], "H9Qwffsg": ["\"..............What is it?\""], "1tpBsFTn": ["\"I need you to grab me something from the hardware ", "store, and drop it through my mail slot.\""], "PmwsXjDJ": ["\"Don't worry, you won't have to see me or anything.\""], "PwcWGg3b": ["\"Though if you do, I'll pay ", "you back whatever expenses.\""], "JL9BHHpn": ["\"..................................................\""], "tsTnrTGG": ["\"I'll-..... have to ask Jane.\""], "LQBjFMxX": ["\"\\fi Sigh.... \\fr\\c[1] Look, just--\""], "HtXGf7nx": ["\"S-she said no.\""], "prsptRyS": ["\" . . . . . . . . . . . \""], "kZjtyRKN": ["\"Okay. Is there anything else ", "'Jane' would like to say to me?\""], "GKbylkY6": ["\"S-sorry, Andrew. I really am!!\""], "Kz8PgCVx": ["She hangs up."], "2ZLk8XXt": ["\"(Fucking really?)\""], "XxfYKfz2": ["\"I, uhh... have just one more question....", "It's been really bothering me, so......\""], "WM3YvlMZ": ["\"Please be honest..... Are you ", "and Ashley, uhhh...... i-intimate?\""], "jLnm8D5r": ["\"............Define 'intimate'.\""], "XlJL5H7p": ["Julia hangs up."], "g6GZKvjN": ["\"(Ah, fuck....)\""], "zYMmrhff": ["You call again. Several times."], "VYJF4vGw": ["\".......S-stop it! Please.\""], "HdNpQ863": ["\"Julia, that wasn't a fair question.\""], "3jlv5111": ["\"If you meant sex, then say ", "sex. The answer to that is no.\""], "RDstT6V1": ["\"But if you ask me if I'm 'intimate' with her, then ", "yes. We are indeed 'close and know each other well'.\""], "9FyrGTFL": ["\".........D-did..... you really just call ", "me to argue about semantics?\""], "sWbJ6j1j": ["Yes."], "vJpQ0SQL": ["\"No. I wanted to clear up what ", "was obviously a miscommunication.\""], "85MW6KVC": ["\"Well, it's-, uhh.... it's clear now.... Thanks.\""], "n46nNBGz": ["\".............................\""], "VPPCXDRN": ["\"Look, sorry... I'm sorry. You know how ", "irritating that subject is to me...\""], "7cXlPmsh": ["\" .......... \""], "lX4yHcB5": ["\"I'm sorry for snapping at you. ", "That was way out of line.\""], "7pCqGJxx": ["\"Please let me apologize to you ", "properly. Can I buy you a coffee?\""], "FkLF0H5D": ["\"I... I guess............\""], "y7tymNYp": ["\"Great! Then could you grab me something ", "from the hardware store and--\""], "rGV00V4H": ["\"Ah....................\""], "Nv0mJ9F1": ["\"I'm sorry, what the fuck, Julia?\""], "1vVM06j8": ["\"Are you seriously asking me this right now??\""], "PLg8MMJS": ["\"I--..... s-sorry.\""], "9SJxsz7n": ["\"...........No, I'm sorry. I didn't ", "mean to raise my voice.\""], "cLCn1Ct3": ["\"I'm sure you didn't mean to insult me either.\""], "gVHJbD67": ["\"N-no.... No I didn't, I just--........\""], "dtKG6cG4": ["\"I think Jane has gotten into my head, is all, ahahha... ", "You know she has some strong opinions about you....\""], "ywY0j9RB": ["\"W-well anyway... What did you say about some prank?\""], "bt4wvsm6": ["\"Maaaan, it's really embarrassing, haha...\""], "YfBpY0FW": ["\"We got drunk, and my friend thought it'd ", "be hilarious to chain me to a radiator.\""], "Hr9fZCyX": ["\"Now he's off to work, and I'm stuck here.\""], "Cs6QjTjq": ["\"I never understood the point of pranks.........\""], "lBF0K4Jf": ["\"Yeah, well... If you could drop me some bolt ", "cutters through the mail slot, that'd be great.\""], "TLZhQvY0": ["\"Um.... S-sure. So where are you?\""], "GpHdf7q1": ["You tell her the address."], "ddGM2mF6": ["\"(I should probably clean up ", "a bit before she shows up...)\""], "Vs97fws4": ["You attempt to call her again, but she doesn't pick up."], "PnY980Rz": ["Start over!"], "QWRsF6SF": ["And so! With no means to get out, ", "you're stuck in Carl's apartment."], "1NXcZwK8": ["Ashley won't hear a word about you ", "needing to find somewhere else to stay."], "SpKJ0fqc": ["\"You're just trying to get me to unlock the chain!\""], "lBQJMvDf": ["Soon after, the cops come check up on Carl."], "QMM41WLV": ["At that point, you don't give a rat's ass anymore, and", "invite them to take a look in the fridge yourself."], "z1zHkGSj": ["You can imagine how that went....."], "4SS5G5Bp": ["Anyway, it sucked. So try again!"], "wYyBzQPN": ["\"Put the phone down, Andrew.\""], "sVzhRJhb": ["\"Were we doing something ", "about Carl or what??\""], "bC2fTL2X": ["You don't know where to call."], "RpyVH9j5": ["Call....."], "Cp0yB6gG": ["The ad pamphlet disguised as a ", "newspaper has a list of services."], "15fHPBjl": ["One of them is a sketchy moving company."], "N9CnW1Yk": ["\"(Perfect. I'll get back to these ", "guys once we have a place lined up.)\""], "q5Jq06QB": ["", "Picked a moving company!"], "yf5XgMRZ": ["In the kitchen trash, there are various ", "attempts at a resignation letter."], "SHhyJrFn": ["Some more strongly worded than others."], "z2YS1v3M": ["\"(I'm guessing Carl recently quit his job...)\""], "WHZdj08G": ["\"(I'm guessing whoever lives ", "here recently quit their job...)\""], "wgGdmSRc": ["", "Got Water!"], "TK2l75CK": ["Though you're already used to washing up this", "way, this time it pisses you off to no end."], "L0N50HQg": ["You poured some water into a container."], "csJvhc3d": ["", "Got Water!"], "TPFMh5Rn": ["\"There's nothing but cups and plates ", "here. Does Carl not have any pans??\""], "RRBklb9W": ["\"I threw them away after my last vision.\""], "SXyGvKKd": ["\"...............Great.\""], "YbKlvQ34": ["Some dishes are missing."], "7LxPB2dT": ["Washed some Dishes!"], "gZM36n65": ["The trash is full of Carl's ", "abandoned resignation letters."], "mxHmd9df": ["\"(I don't know whether he actually ", "resigned, or wrote these for fun...)\""], "n9jz8R39": ["\"(I'll call and check... Pretty sure ", "this number must be his boss's.)\""], "7xmRhyvB": ["", "Memorized Boss's Phone Number!"], "zPycbBly": ["In the fridge sit food and plenty of booze."], "G0FfhkXl": ["\"(Well, I know what I'll be doing ", "if I can't get out of here...)\""], "WHBGwH9Z": ["Maybe later."], "R3ffr4lr": ["Get drunk?"], "BlqxHcVL": ["You proceed to drink all the booze in the fridge."], "MVsQyxDt": ["The freezer is far too small."], "RbdcCkkf": ["\"(He's not going to fit in here as he is, ", "and I don't have any means to chop him up.)\""], "4D9CpZGg": ["\"(........Then again rigor mortis hasn't set in yet.)\""], "tdgzxqMX": ["\"(Maybe if I re-arrange things a bit, I can", "fold him in the fridge for the time being.)\""], "CqhT3rH7": ["You remove all items and shelves from the refrigerator."], "Y28Ktr8T": ["A Carl-less refrigerator."], "5Yx3TpDn": ["Arrange the refrigerator contents?"], "SYFMHVyd": ["Carl is still in the fridge."], "RfJGBxHC": ["The fridge and freezer are full of Carl."], "R5l5d6hM": ["This way appears to be the bedroom, ", "however you can't reach it."], "NcJ4zhWz": ["It's out of reach."], "kwK1g41t": ["\"Ashley, are you okay?\""], "vNGzfNZY": ["\"\\fi *Sniff!* \\fr\\c[2] G-go away!\""], "vZDZvqHQ": ["\"I can't sleep because of your crying.\""], "GdSC05yT": ["\"So either get over here so I can ", "comfort you, or shut the hell up.\""], "QL8h45bK": ["\"It's your own fault!\""], "tTb1mVkk": ["\"What did I do?\""], "xMVPw22s": ["\"W-well.... I had another vision just now...\""], "sgh4CC2k": ["\"\\fi *Sniff!* \\fr\\c[2] Why do you want to kill me so bad??\""], "X1kC6XYt": ["\"I don't... You probably just had a nightmare.\""], "yzXDjrlb": ["\"You do! And you already tried", "it in the Realm Between!\""], "ZgYt8bvp": ["\"That's-........\""], "5l9zVVDw": ["\"Man, I don't even know how ", "to apologize for that one...\""], "svmtQgB6": ["\"Forgive me. I lost myself... That was", "an incredible lapse in my judgment.\""], "pD9fDTD8": ["\"I don't want to hurt you.\""], "gm9d77rK": ["\"Then what the fuck is this?! Huh??\""], "zcd4L5yK": ["\"....................I don't \\fi want \\fr\\c[1] to hurt you.\""], "7WcYFLVm": ["\"Can you just tell me what ", "happened in the vision?\""], "H2jDWQhh": ["\"Nothing really. We were just screaming back ", "and forth about your ex or something...\""], "LhB6bB4W": ["\"And then you just snapped! ", "For no fucking reason.\""], "xyYwrkwR": ["\"('No reason' my ass, I bet ", "she drove me to it. Again.)\""], "QQbnTrPN": ["\"\\fi *Sniff!* \\fr\\c[2] I don't-.... Just ", "what am I supposed to do??\""], "zgLk9pjT": ["\"I barely avoided the last vision...\""], "2DSC9XQz": ["\"Ugh...!! I hate this so much.......\""], "j8mqys4x": ["\"I just want everything to go ", "back to how it used to be!\""], "6DM9XSPy": ["\"Back to when we were Andy and Leyley, and ", "everything was fine, and we were happy together....\""], "gXJTYftc": ["\"I wasn't happy.\""], "5bCV5bbN": ["\"..............................\""], "1TJtvMMn": ["\"I mean we had our moments, but it honestly took", "a really, really long time to grow fond of you.\""], "gZY2q8Z5": ["\"What the hell? Don't tell me that!!\""], "4CTP9SbZ": ["\"I thought you knew?\""], "yXZL8FwY": ["\"Well, obviously I thought so! But", "still. Way to wreck my heart...\""], "kdv8gKkm": ["\"Alright. Sorry. I thought we're ", "looking for solutions here...\""], "vNfg4sdH": ["\"So I just wanted to be clear, it's ", "not going to be 'let's go back to that'.\""], "cT9zgbyk": ["\" . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . \""], "dSgDs8V8": ["\"................Were you ever happy?\""], "F8qFB5l1": ["\"Of course.\""], "BW9S0ZZH": ["\"But with me.\""], "G8yGbb5Y": ["\"Only with you, honestly...\""], "tJQdq2q6": ["\"It's not often that we're good, but when", "we are, it's like nothing else, right?\""], "pvTD86qM": ["\"Actually that's kind of alarming ", "now that I say it out loud...\""], "b3ZFs6jZ": ["\"Then when was the last ", "time things were good?\""], "qcnNbN7g": ["\"Hmm....\" "], "BYd7JF5v": ["\"Probably when we joked about jumping ", "off the balcony. That was fun.\""], "pG1jnt6T": ["\"....What was so good about that?\""], "4XYw8fjC": ["\"Well, you're usually all about yourself, ", "but you said you'd join me then.\""], "x2dQ3MCl": ["\" 'Oh, she does care!' I thought.", "And my heart skipped a beat!\""], "hKB10PrT": ["\"HaHAh! But also, screw you! ", "I care all the time.\""], "2PKX15J2": ["\"I don't know about that...\""], "dS4gkr71": ["\"But what about you? When ", "were you last happy?\""], "Rdf7VKM8": ["\"When I bit you! On the couch.\""], "ndqBnKym": ["\"Fucking animal.\""], "5c9WRJzn": ["\"Hah! Shut up, you liked it! I could tell.\""], "1wYYVx1f": ["\"Actually what were you going ", "to do? Before Mom showed up.\""], "DWW4lg0P": ["\"Bite you back, obviously. And teach ", "your dumbass a lesson or two...\""], "9zVP0p5C": ["\" 'I don't wanna hurt you!' he says.\""], "hydn6LdV": ["\"Chomp.\""], "Rkx5mrzc": ["\"...........What is this?\""], "L2xqwqfN": ["\"Chomp.\""], "vHD9zmPV": ["\"Haha! Quit it...\""], "1DDVMbhS": ["\"Chomp, chomp, chomp!!\""], "dftlR73w": ["\"BhaHahHa!! Noooo~!\""], "H4DNwFt8": ["\" ! ! ! \""], "VD7kKc7f": ["\" . . . . . . . \""], "3vqnHc5N": ["\" . .. . ... . . .. . ... . ... . .. . \""], "cRTlKB8m": ["\"Isn't it about time you take this ", "ridiculous thing off of me?\""], "J7tb7mf6": ["\"But you didn't have it in the ", "vision... So I can't risk it.\""], "mztKy51w": ["\"If the day ever comes when I end you,", "it'll be over stupid stunts like this.\""], "tw6qHq8B": ["\"Nothing quite like a death", "threat to make me trust you.\""], "qH2pzRP5": ["\" .......................... \""], "p0WdXkCb": ["\"Seems like you're fine ", "now. Go back to sleep.\""], "Klqycvr7": ["\"Yeah. I better get back to watching you", "beat me to death with a frying pan.\""], "4D654TXf": ["\"(What the hell was that?)\""], "hBvBJlZ2": ["\"(She squeezes out a couple of tears, and suddenly, I'm ", "ready to overlook everything she's ever put me through?)\""], "WPSBsW63": ["\"(.......Is that all it takes to draw me back in?)\""], "mVpzrMRm": ["\"(God, I need to get away from here....)\""], "pk4kVqTQ": ["\"(If not for my own sake, ", "then apparently hers.)\""], "MvkrtV8k": ["And the poor frying pan's!"], "hKDkpTkg": ["\"........Where are you off to?\""], "6yLjJTJk": ["\"I need to offer more souls.\""], "N1L70KK3": ["\"Hey, hey, hey!! Hold up.\""], "mfdz0QwK": ["\"I really need to take a shower, but", "the chain won't reach that far.\""], "S3Srftnv": ["\"I made sure it reaches the ", "kitchen faucet. You'll be fine.\""], "7nDyDyWG": ["\"We have a shower right there, yet you're", "still making me wash up in the sink??\""], "qJhvkksD": ["\"Cry about it.\""], "mCmwnPFx": ["\" . . . . . . . . \""], "s2GqyRJM": ["\".....Alright, enough. Get up. ", "Come here. Up, up, up!\""], "F6nD8g01": ["There are street signs outside, ", "but they're too far away to read."], "nRX2QP1m": ["\"(This is a lot higher than I thought...)\""], "JNBk3Kbk": ["\"(What is this, the seventh floor, maybe??)\""], "SMV08S91": ["\"(At least I'm not in the ", "middle of nowhere I guess...)\""], "glNFmVJD": ["Ready to die?"], "MqYm7Q3H": ["\"Oh boy... I kind of don't want to after all.....\""], "p3FppSWg": ["\"Then get lost.\""], "VgfXRpLW": ["\"No, no. I'm not leaving you!\""], "Zsd5n5sB": ["\"And this way, you won't kill me and", "then run off with some floozy.\""], "ZM4FsCww": ["\"Well, what do you know? ", "It didn't even work.\""], "mk6gccJF": ["\"I could've told you as much.\""], "pydP4mTL": ["\"........Told me what?\""], "mnsrPVXw": ["\"That I couldn't fuck your ", "insecurities out of you.\""], "VhBXcRr4": ["\"Oh, shut up. It was worth trying.\""], "PKhfLk4Q": ["\"Besides, it might have worked if you hadn't been such a ", "gigantic asshole about it first thing in the morning!\""], "N5dXMBwb": ["\"Here we fucking go again...", "Let's just jump already.\""], "GdLyB2lv": ["\"......................\\fiSigh.\\fr\\c[2]\""], "Lv6wgp3R": ["\"Then can I at least get a little", "mishap to say goodbye?\""], "VjdNQrQb": ["\"Like you want it anyway...\""], "5GY6pj5p": ["\"Well, I don't, if you'll ", "just make a face again...\""], "y3TfysX2": ["\"That hurts, y'know? It really does.\""], "g6CFB7zN": ["\"D'aww... Poor thing.\""], "QKVCzZlw": ["\"Hey look! A field trip.\""], "211Wdyqy": ["\"Wanna traumatize the fuck out ", "of a bunch of school kids?\""], "tC9C1q4L": ["\"BhAhHaH!! No, you asshole!\""], "PHwL4Tzh": ["\"Ahh, she's no fun these days......\""], "FHpBmXPr": ["\"HahHa!! Not true!\""], "GKcnyXj8": ["\"..................Say something nice to me.\""], "1GVXtYcv": ["\"Your fake orgasm was kind of cute.\""], "dxQv3y18": ["\"I SAID 'SOMETHING NICE', GODDAMMIT!!! ", "Now I \\fi wanna \\fr\\c[2] die!\""], "kMYDGDv6": ["\"HaHahHa!!\""], "DbkpF4Mh": ["\"Ah, here they are now. Shall we?\""], "MyYjKYZg": ["\"Okay, fine. Fine! Let's do it.\""], "9c47myvX": ["\"\\{ HEY, BRATS!! CHECK THIS OUT!!!!! \\}\""], "ZtGSG5Pp": ["\" ? ? ? ? ? ? \""], "yBmm9Htx": ["\"By the way, are you sure ", "this is high enough?\""], "tjfZRNm8": ["\"Well, you better hope so...\""], "GDwKZdRP": ["\"...W-well, here goes!!!\""], "rs3nHGwg": ["\"HAHhHahHA!!!\""], "crmNs7t9": ["\" ! ! ! ! ! ! ! ! \""], "bZxPNDXz": ["Good riddance."], "DqPLk4pJ": ["DEADEST OF DEAD-ENDS -END!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!"], "jkt0qGbk": ["...............Any regrets?"], "KM7qNgsX": ["Glad to hear it."], "q2v9St85": ["Right. You had one tiny glimmer of hope remaining."], "9jWmRp5J": ["Maybe you were too quick to discard it."], "jnvtkC3C": ["It probably wouldn't have led anywhere ", "good, but somewhere anyway."], "w4L86LZY": ["Wanna see?"], "b46Nz45V": [".....................What? Are you waiting for a retry?"], "1mB918mc": ["There isn't one."], "LyRt2HlD": ["This outcome was caused by a series of fuck-ups ", "so profound there is no quick fix for it."], "XVCM9Q9m": ["Even if I gave you a retry, you'd just ", "end up jumping again sooner or later."], "wj4SJM7W": ["Goodbye forever. Bye bye!"], "V5jSZC3t": ["One end of the chain is padlocked onto ", "the radiator. The other to your ankle."], "vkQt2QfL": ["And you thought you were stuck ", "with Ashley before. Hahaha!!"], "MW8BMF5S": ["There is no escaping on your own."], "X5B0JLH6": ["In the drawer are some spoons ", "and forks, but no knives."], "lkjgzkb6": ["Indeed, not a single knife can be found. Just an ", "empty slot where they presumably once were."], "BZ46jgt3": ["\"(Ah, forethought. So you \\fi can \\fr\\c[1] think, beloved.)\""], "nXb3L3V1": ["\"(Sure would be grand if you used your brain ", "when working with me, instead of against me...)\""], "xMSJkvSM": ["Among the spoons, there are some kitchen utensils..."], "nySJ0J0Y": ["", "Got Tongs!"], "zCC8v03C": ["\"(There's nothing I can use to chop Carl ", "up. I'll have to figure something else...)\""], "WP5YHsvY": ["\"(Thanks, Ashley....)\""], "kZ8RFfq7": ["\"Actually!!!\""], "SM8Gbq4l": ["\" ? ? ? \""], "5vZZqrX9": ["\"Sorry, there's nothing to drink.\""], "tcm5Dx0R": ["\"Can I buy you something? As ", "thanks for helping me out.\""], "JZWW1Zb3": ["\"Oh.... umm.... W-well okay, I guess?\""], "WkyTD98k": ["\"Way to go, asshole.\""], "mz4HYQwj": ["\"We were gonna be safe at the", "demon's place, but nooooo......\""], "tlpgSd62": ["\"You had to go and ruin that for us.\""], "lFmM6k2M": ["\".........What the hell is this?\""], "PXnM7W9v": ["\"Well, I have to keep you in check somehow...\""], "nNQVgFrz": ["\"You are \\fi not \\fr\\c[1] doing this to me, Leyley.\""], "cQ4HXGNS": ["\"You're making me do it! This ", "one is entirely on you!\""], "R4N9BVty": ["\"This is all your fault!! I didn't--\""], "1ylznHkk": ["You stop listening."], "V1Rzbkpq": ["\"Hey, hey, HEY!!! Pay attention!!!\""], "kbFGPJ70": ["\"Look at me, you fucking ", "cunt!! I'm talking to you!!\""], "XFRzWNRQ": ["\"I said, I'm talking to you!! Answer me before ", "I blast your brains all over the wall!\""], "hP1LzC2D": ["\"Blast away. Do you think I want to live like this?\""], "YVVjpKSl": ["\"Careful what you say now. I ", "might take your word for it.\""], "7FnjjMQ2": ["\".....................\""], "LyJDTF9n": ["\"What are you, a fucking child now?? Talk to me!\""], "nch4ZZXW": ["\"Why are you like this?????\""], "QgQKzZvS": ["\"What's the matter? We've pulled ", "through every time so far.\""], "RMB0K95S": ["\"Why is it that when things finally look up, ", "you start fighting me every step of the way??\""], "Br2JjyZk": ["\".................................\""], "fymx961v": ["\"SAY SOMETHING!!\""], "00fZyXhN": ["\".........................................\""], "1QyFyGvy": ["\".....\\fiFine! \\fr\\c[2] Be that way.\""], "CSy5z0cB": ["\"See if I care, Andy! \\fi Oooh noooo, \\fr\\c[2] it's Andrew??\""], "1WJ2WQvx": ["\"I don't give a fuck what your name is!\""], "G4tHmNJ8": ["\"For god's sake! Will you just shoot me", "already and get this shit over with!?\""], "06KxlSkw": ["\"\\fi *Sniff!* \\fr\\c[2] Why are you yelling at me???\""], "d0Y0QLTd": ["\"I'm doing all of this because I love you!\""], "D11kVYY5": ["\"HaHahHAhA!!\""], "Qhs0RF8W": ["\"........W-what's funny?\""], "ZkfNQNkJ": ["\"This is love to you? Really?? \\fi This!? \\fr\\c[1]\""], "7hkdw8MV": ["\"Yes! Because at the end of the day, 'Andy and ", "Leyley and Whatever-the-fuck' is a love story!\""], "bPC8x25W": ["\"HA!\""], "XmqHlFcg": ["\"Shut up! Yes it is!! And I'll mourn your ", "death before I mourn you walking away!!\""], "bQNlf1Bj": ["\"DIVORCE ALREADY!!\""], "JPW57CRq": ["It seems you are bothering the neighbors."], "GB2d7jpl": ["\"..........I've said all I have to say.\""], "4DD4n66T": ["\"Where do you think you're going?\""], "sJXmLQpJ": ["\"Back to the demon. And the next time", "I see you, I'm expecting an apology.\""], "28DGLKw2": ["\"Well, don't hold your breath.\""], "RvShkt9S": ["She summons her Entity and leaves with it."], "NLxPmdd6": ["\"(I need to get out of here......)\""], "X5QzJqF7": ["\"(Figuring out where I am in the first ", "place would be a good start...)\""], "vpRgHKzt": ["\"Hey. Wake up, I got you something...\""], "Qd5l2wSs": ["\"..............Thanks?\""], "Bp7jLG4P": ["\"(It's the wrong brand....)\""], "nrtpjwHJ": ["\"Roll them yourself. I'd never have let you buy ", "packs if I knew how much cheaper this was.\""], "qmJjNL55": ["\" . . . . . . . . . . \""], "LNBTTV0m": ["\"What? You should be grateful, ", "not scowling at me!\""], "DGNC1C8X": ["\"Grateful for what? That you got me tobacco ", "after imprisoning me in this shithole?\""], "B6bg9Psb": ["\"Are we doing this again???\""], "NKm1cWKL": ["\"And yes, you should be grateful for that.\""], "SKzbwn9W": ["\"That, and also for the fact that I ", "work my ass off to keep us safe!\""], "5yvxXslp": ["\"All the demon does now is bark ", "orders at me and demand more souls.\""], "7l7svLyp": ["\"Then maybe you shouldn't have ", "fucking offered yourself to it.\""], "BjhVc63S": ["\" ........................ \""], "rcXfnpQw": ["\"Funny how when it comes to the demon, ", "you're on your knees begging and pleading.\""], "V4c5wHFy": ["\"Meanwhile I can't get a single shred of respect.\""], "rmsxb3lX": ["\"Maybe pick your drunk ass up off the ", "floor before you talk about respect...\""], "6smBxfbx": ["\"Yeah, yeah. And you wanna ", "lecture \\fi me \\fr\\c[1] about gratitude?\""], "xYtKwmxC": ["\"Who was it that provided for you all your life??\""], "FWCJw3Y3": ["\"Oh, boohoo! Here we go. I ", "ruined your life, is that it?\""], "dlVw59Vj": ["\"It's aaaaall my fault, poor you!", "Poor Mr. Wasted Potential!\""], "HM0bVyV6": ["\"Poor golden child! Poor little innocent, ", "helpless, two-faced, lying piece of shit!!\""], "Jlk8cyMl": ["\"Enough of this. Unlock this chain!\""], "bpylP82l": 