...?\""], "V2MQl0bD": ["\"Yup. I'm here.\""], "DzmmDJKj": ["\"Umm.... I'm just gonna-.......", "Okay, I think it fits through....\""], "QrVBnWfN": ["\"There! Can you reach them...?\""], "TWrp4YKb": ["You reach for the Bolt Cutters with your Tongs."], "5NjlPpZv": ["", "Got Bolt Cutters!"], "tbb5z1QH": ["You use them to cut the chain."], "jtqthnPF": ["\"Sorry for the wait.\""], "86pNRl7d": ["\"N-not at all! So, uhh......... Ahahaha..!", "The bolt cutters were kinda pricey......\""], "Zk4LLsKC": ["\"Right. Sorry about that. Let ", "me just go find my wallet...\""], "fPQyBdnX": ["\"(Though Ashley has probably emptied it....)\""], "CdyMyfMC": ["Nope. Try again?"], "6Zvl4H17": ["In 3...."], "rvdFrsRH": ["2...."], "2Rsp98fg": ["1..."], "YXSvNlLv": ["You should at least try to gather ", "your shit before you leave."], "Dt8kqkrn": ["You can't leave now. You're too", "hungry, drunk, and horny."], "fh1Xx145": ["But mostly hungry."], "1byP5rj6": ["And drunk."], "YG7cDBPQ": ["And horny."], "Y4pDGD4x": ["\"Where do you think you're going?\""], "MSz7ZWDK": ["\"MMmmMm.... I need fresh air....\""], "6D2LTYV5": ["\"Not in that state. Go to bed.\""], "sw8nKDBX": ["You can't leave."], "rPxhY5sF": ["God knows, your life just might improve if you did."], "wtT1v7Bj": ["\"What's keeping you?\""], "y66JyGrK": ["\"Just thinking...\""], "y4bgH1vf": ["\"To hell with that... Time to go!\""], "LvGBG2sV": ["\"Wait.\""], "f9SJDhyP": ["\"What? You're not changing your ", "mind again. This is settled.\""], "2cGN8pL4": ["\"It's not that, I just-....\""], "KPWyRbtC": ["\".........Are you sore?\""], "4VyClP8M": ["\"A bit. Why?\""], "YRCZb5xn": ["\"I'd just like to do it properly...\""], "kYnHdqYZ": ["\"Let me make it worth it.\""], "FKcYdBfr": ["\" .......... \""], "s9HmC8qS": ["\"....No?\""], "6FdwjGWP": ["\"You can if you want.\""], "mpzZClsw": ["\"Carl Cultman\" rents a one-bedroom apartment."], "2RRgGlGm": ["He gets a crappy customer service job", "and discovers he has a lot of debt."], "KtTnYpqV": ["It pisses you off because you worked so damn hard", "not to accumulate any while you were studying."], "B9DssXLZ": ["A huge chunk of \"Carl's\" measly salary goes directly to ", "debt collection. The rest barely covers the utilities."], "SWX0LGXn": ["If it weren't for your off-the-books", "\"wife\", you'd starve."], "49zbDfYw": ["She works as a pickpocket,", "stealing souls and wallets."], "MgGMvGMb": ["And occasionally, the pieces that ", "remain of your moldy, rotten heart."], "Gvrf2kwQ": ["", "Some time later..."], "ngq33fgp": ["You're home!"], "qSd7WQxZ": ["The stench of bacon and vomit clings to your clothes."], "3tynwb7f": ["Such is the price of working at ", "the Steakhouse of Steaks & Steaks."], "0dZ6cPT5": ["Andrew Graves's revered English degree means ", "nothing to Carl Cultman's employment."], "zdq7jwzb": ["\"(Maybe I'll lock myself back up....", "She doesn't need to know anything.)\""], "pG85Smf2": ["\".......Ah.\""], "5CXbkq6K": ["\"\\{ AND WHERE THE FUCK WERE YOU?!!? \\}\""], "9xYhDmtp": ["\"Oh, for crying out loud.....\""], "kxn6wKBV": ["\"Weren't you supposed to be ", "out sacrificing people?\""], "tG3Qq5mW": ["\"WEREN'T YOU SUPPOSED TO BE HOME?!!?\""], "tb29vqdF": ["\"I am 'home' now! Against ", "my better judgment.\""], "cKttxgN9": ["\"Where were you? How'd you get out!?\""], "kHqy6DsQ": ["\"I have my ways. And anyway I came ", "back, so what does it even matter?\""], "TY7xxwRd": ["\"Do you have any idea how terrified ", "I was to find you gone??!\""], "M5hgR0Fl": ["\"I just went to grab something from the store.\""], "bJjwQxpV": ["\"Booze again!? I think you might ", "be developing a problem.\""], "0ybWDbz4": ["\"Hah!\""], "8wRqDtnl": ["\"What's funny?\""], "48Ntq8wj": ["\"There are some problems ", "developing alright...\""], "lwWmD8Q4": ["\"Serves me right though.\""], "hysy9BK0": ["\".....You were gone way too long ", "to have just gone to a store.\""], "5rDNcNyB": ["\"I got lost. It's a new area.\""], "ZyLFJ6hR": ["\"......................