ucks..............)\""], "lMYj758y": ["Both the food and the situation."], "jCFfr9dV": ["\"(What the hell did I come back for??)\""], "p7chZJnv": ["\" . . . . . . . \""], "GPwkn2GP": ["\"(Ugh.... Get your shit together.......)\""], "NwW9kWZl": ["\" . . . . . . . . . . . . . \""], "F5c0CW9z": ["\".........That bad, huh?\""], "VpXzQHMH": ["\"It's not the food. It's ", "how you ran off today.\""], "RTRBkMr1": ["\"I came back.\""], "VXTcF5cK": ["\"(Like a fucking addict....)\""], "FNC9hMMh": ["\"And then you pushed me away. Again.\""], "7jNtGSXk": ["\"(Pretty sure I did something else...)\""], "N6wDQn5Y": ["\"Am I gonna find you gone tomorrow?", "And for once in your life, be honest.\""], "csnSTwQM": ["\"If you try to imprison me again, then yes.\""], "1xNFV74R": ["\".................................\""], "mBQK2xt4": ["\"\\fi Sighhh................. \\fi\\c[1] ", "Don't make that face.\""], "Gr4nMT0Q": ["\"I don't think I'm being unreasonable ", "here. What do you want me to say?\""], "2xBGfbk6": ["\" 'Fuck yeah, baby! Chain me up and shove a gun ", "in my face! I deserve that shit. Thanks, sis!' \""], "LjhRzrcV": ["\"In what world would I not run ", "for the hills after that??\""], "2jjFmdpk": ["\"Well, other than this one, since ", "here I am like a fucking moron.\""], "QLwSLR3D": ["\".....Let's talk about this after you sober up.\""], "Z8kwBvm4": ["\"No, I'm feeling chatty. Spit it out. What", "do you wanna hear? You can tell me.\""], "bc1fcQDp": ["\"............I just need you to tell ", "me you won't leave me.\""], "2qfWFB1T": ["\"Doesn't seem to matter! How many more times", "do I need to say it until you believe me?\""], "mNRC1xlq": ["\"I'll believe you after you stop leaving.\""], "v52LMmsm": ["\"Uggghhhrrrhhh..... Where have I ", "gone? I'm sitting right here!\""], "CKjWbWm2": ["\"And so what if I did leave?? Didn't you ", "say you'd have a blast without me?\""], "StHwH3nV": ["\"...................I didn't mean that.\""], "qdtvqWlP": ["\"I'm not so sure.\""], "