], "Yrjk8Q3R": ["\"Don't follow me! I'm sick ", "of arguing with you...\""], "0M1D819C": ["\"I'm not arguing! I'm trying to talk!!\""], "nxJpp77P": ["\"Oh god. Just stop. Please ", "just fucking stop.\""], "5tGGMrtV": ["\"Stop. We can talk later...\""], "Zns6Jrs3": ["\"Later, sure! After you've got ", "your excuses all lined up, huh??\""], "whXWpVmb": ["\"I'm not having this same argument ", "for the millionth time...\""], "pLP1LvYH": ["\"She gets the best of you, and I get... what??\""], "jwNQBrMD": ["\"To pick up the pieces after she turns you down, huh?? ", "That's the only reason your drunk ass came crawling back!\""], "lQXN0Qyc": ["\"Stop making shit up... I don't want to fight.\""], "M3rZHtZD": ["\"I knew there had to be more to you ", "suddenly treating me like that.\""], "9qY68RQV": ["\"Don't. Let's just find a new ", "place for us and go. Please?\""], "PXqhxgYg": ["\"Just you and me, beloved.", "Forget everything else.\""], "T7fRLljw": ["\"Oooh, here we go! Here comes the sweet-talking!\""], "cvYh17RS": ["\"It's me and you, but only until you wanna get some!\""], "K87VJHHf": ["\"Ashley, I'm begging you. ", "I'm so tired of this.......\""], "DjrXn8sL": ["\"Oh, boohoo! You're tired!!\""], "1XgVnJ7B": ["\"Imagine how fucking tired I am!! ", "Putting up with your shit!!\""], "4rzMr84n": ["\"Say you went to fuck her!! Admit it!!\""], "sQscKV2W": ["\"I did!!\""], "ZFHrVP55": ["\"I fucking knew it!!!!\""], "ySKVtXyw": ["\"I'm sorry! I did! I really did!\""], "1ypPhNc0": ["\"But I don't love her. I didn't ", "have her. I came back to you.\""], "kG71yGZP": ["\"I'm sorry! I thought it'd make things better for ", "both of us! But then I thought better of it anyway.\""], "HNwHvyD5": ["\"You think it's better to be with her!?\""], "f9RzHn0Q": ["\"That's not what I fucking said, I just--- ", "I mean, it would be, clearly! But still I'm here!\""], "yfk5YMkV": ["\"Says who!? How is it better????", "Better according to who?!\""], "cfYPvXWq": ["\"Well, society for one.\""], 