other fixing anything ", "when she puts out regardless? "], "Qnf8k8CL": ["So what if she's miserable? So are you!"], "CQWm78BS": ["Nothing matters anymore."], "dWqgPNlq": ["", "Stole Trinket!"], "jP05Mtfw": ["Not this window."], "mgr7gmQg": ["", "Got a Gun!"], "7DkthhMx": ["\" . . . . . . . . . . . . \""], "ZBkPDN9M": ["There's no time to waste!"], "0WWLrkdV": ["You cup your hands and reach into the toilet bowl!"], "ffNhTQ1s": ["", "Got Water!"], "mfKXxkkn": ["...You'll clean up using toilet water?"], "XdwF3dyx": ["", "Got Water!"], "vKsxPLVP": ["", "Got Water!"], "l0kg7zNB": ["", "Got Water!"], "6McKyD8M": ["Then find something else."], "q6WWcK0d": ["A blood circle, most definitely drawn by Ashley."], "NrbdT4bk": ["Suspicious blood that should be washed off."], "Klf8GNBl": ["You splash the blood with water to rinse it off."], "jnqTbptw": ["You should probably rinse this ", "blood away before Julia shows up."], "ctJRYYyY": ["This needs to be cleaned."], "wCz8KdF2": ["After cleaning the blood up, all ", "you can do is wait for Julia...."], "tFnqkcbK": ["You've thrown the cans too far to clean them up."], "THGyzwrL": ["\"(Oh well... I did say we had been drinking. ", "This just reinforces that narrative.)\""], "w8RRWBWR": ["\"So, what's the point of this?\""], "VKtYyKgw": ["\"To make sure Carl's body isn't found, you", "should take it with you to the other realm.\""], "vlmLnkpm": ["\"The demon isn't gonna have it...\""], "P309669Z": ["\"Just ask.\""], "zwsWMxlj": ["\"Demon, demon, come on out...\""], "06RL1RB6": ["\"FiNaLLy, TaR SouL.\""], "27tGTLmJ": ["\"So, uhh... My brother wants to dump ", "this guy's corpse in your realm.\""], "npDkQnJY": ["\"Can you summon it over?\""], "q9PClth8": ["\"I caNnot sUmmOn tHe deAd.\""], "g3WlQ8xN": ["\"Then just open the portal, I'll drag him in.\""], "00bkffSV": ["\"I reFuse.\""], "8B7DwGV6": ["\"Why??? It doesn't cost ", "you anything, right?\""], "HxygVpfg": ["\"We can make a deal out of it.\""], "RrRfSYXh": ["\"nO.\""], "BDPTHrd