me to butcher Carl?"], "Yd3QMV2k": ["\\{ YOU MUST!!! \\}"], "pxrCXcqT": ["You drain the blood and cut ", "Carl into bite-sized chunks."], "PBXCqdR1": ["You stash the chunks in the freezer until ", "you can discreetly dispose of them."], "cz3Y12H9": ["\"(What else is there?)\""], "qNFMrq91": ["You take a rather thorough shower ", "but don't feel any less disgusting."], "W0vvXXkW": ["\"I could use a shower before we die...\""], "VmW1hGYb": ["\"Will you wash my hair for me?\""], "2XRf4n3R": ["\"Why the fuck would I?\""], "H7hkDfh6": ["\"Well, you used to do it a long time ago. ", "I just thought it might be nice.\""], "mMM2xyf8": ["Oh, that's right! You basically raised this woman."], "D6RP3jcM": ["\"(Fuck..... I'm the worst.)\""], "8QwhhMZP": ["\"Oh, get over it! What's done is done!!\""], "dswcVF8V": ["She showers alone while ", "you retch over the toilet."], "Gn1l1pBf": ["Hangovers are fun."], "4PTcV7mp": ["\"We should probably wash all this wine off.\""], "4r0Jmzq5": ["\"Y'know. To at least seem like ", "worthy tenant candidates...\""], "V6MTSs83": ["\"Then let's shower together!\""], "xyhLsXXh": ["Honestly, you thought this might go somewhere."], "ncYDZf37": ["But she doesn't initiate, and seeing her battered ", "body fills you with too much guilt to ask."], "fHxmLQ7S": ["\"(...What the fuck is wrong with me, anyway?)\""], "2lwRgb5Z": ["A talisman hangs from a nail on the wall."], "0sGqQRfw": ["It looks a lot like Ashley's, and", "it seems terribly out of place."], "xfW8gckG": ["You decide to leave it be, in case she", "left it here for some important reason."], "0Hx2MBnP": ["\"Mrs. Graves speaking.\""], "nnRMbf5T": ["\"Er, uhh.... H-hiiiiiii Renee! How are you doing?\""], "bCvnNskg": ["\"Who is this?\""], "SZRhKWb5": ["\"Don't you recognize your own mother?\""], "0vsXltCx": ["\"I don't know anyone by that name. Goodbye.\""], "1fQq8S2s": ["\"No, no, no, no! Wait! Please. ", "Please, it's really important.\""], "S1LPjXKW": ["\"I don't care. Who gave you my number?\""], "WP6zTq7B": ["\"The phonebook?\""], "d8SSlB33": ["\"........What do you want?\""], "pfxJTb3N": ["\"I just wanted to check up on ", "you... We all miss you very much.\""], "S5llKS6x": ["\"Cut the crap. What do you really want?\""], "Dz9FB0Lz": ["\"..................\\fi Sigh. \\fr\\c[4] Okay. It's about Connie.\""], "WZvb5bvq": ["\"She really, really needs a kidney transplant and--\""], "c0FX01NX": ["\"Please Renee!\""], "61lkrTZ8": ["\"Your little sister might die without this", "transplant. Don't you feel anything?\""], "WLpMWwdk": ["\"Hate.\""], "kY0LsMZq": ["\"W-why?? What did we ever do to you?\""], "yhCkqc9S": ["\"You don't get to kick me out and then play ", "happy family again when it suits you.\""], "8srwWZsK": ["\"We didn't kick you out! You \\fi chose \\fr\\c[4] that option.\""], "3dx2Yp8h": ["\"All I wanted was for you to think about the future.\""], "GKjbpnYp": ["\"God. You were only fifteen, ", "Renee. That's no age to--\""], "Dts1y8Gt": ["\"Indeed I was.\""], "BlRGqNrc": ["\"And instead of supporting me, you hit me ", "with, 'Do as I say or get the fuck out.'\""], "tmMy0HgS": ["\"That's not-- I only wanted to snap you out of it!\""], "jgWlkb3D": ["\"I didn't think you'd actually ", "go through with everything.\""], "RtV2hvN8": ["\"Well, I did. And you still didn't support me.\""], "qLPgQQTn": ["\"Renee, I know you want to think ", "of me as some sort of a monster....\""], "3TL6bygc": ["\"But you forget I begged and pleaded ", "for you to come back home.\""], "Wqy68hnp": ["\"Yeah. So you could berate me some more, right?", "Thanks but no thanks. We were fine on our own.\""], "Rv0CF99V": ["\" 'Fine'?? You were staying at that ", "wife-beater's house, for goodness' sake!\""], "H86YTky6": ["\"And what if Douglas turns out just like him?\""], "gnv5Q5s0": ["\"\\{ SHUT THE FUCK UP, YOU WHORE!! \\}\""], "HBdQt21P": ["\" ! ? ! ? \""], "YPQB8Yp8": ["\"H-honey? What's wrong?\""], "QWQ1nj0m": ["\"Douglas is nothing like his father! Fuck you!\""], "1Rpq3zTj": ["\"Don't ever speak the name of my husband again!!!\""], "5x3n2pnX": ["\"I--.... I- I'm sorry. I'm just worried about you....\""], "njlymx2x": ["\"Well, don't be! I don't need you!\""], "V59FxyBd": ["\"And by the way, we have two kids ", "now, and they're both perfect!\""], "Wtm86QXK": ["\"My son is top of his class, and ", "my daughter is an art prodigy.\""], "g6dCqgsq": ["\"Everyone thinks they're just amazing!", "Too bad you'll never get to meet them!\""], "By4Kvk4g": ["\"Oh! And also we have more money ", "than we know what to do with.\""], "fxZj07Ls": ["\"Renee....\""], "W4Sg9yHh": ["\"Things are way better than you could ever imagine! ", "You were wrong about everything as usual.\""], "fkH3bPM9": ["\"....With a life that perfect, can't you ", "spare one thought for poor Connie?\""], "YmJFrgbh": ["The phone keeps ringing..."], "Lsz0VRxT": ["Douglas unplugs the cord."], "jHw16bdR": ["\"Fuck.......\""], "Z2mwlRVQ": ["\"...........Ghosts from the past?\""], "5FwDQWn4": ["\" \\} Yes........\\{ \""], "BM9MYYcK": ["\"I'm so sorry, love. Don't let them get to you......\""], "Rq0ljZCL": ["\"............Have you ever thought", "maybe everyone was right about us?\""], "SsWfcLSy": ["\"Not even for a second.\""], "1Xw35lrs": ["\"Heh...\""], "1HBxdg9k": ["\"And next, the weather!\""], "7PB3YWj3": ["\"Uhh... I think you forgot something there.\""], "zLdCjWv9": ["\"What..? Oooooh!! Oh, that's right!\""], "DBllT7dv": ["\"Today the police have found the missing child ", "we've been on about the last week or so.\""], "Q8TMrTqh": ["\"And yeah, you guessed it. She's dead.\""], "tlcnkjp7": ["\"Poor thing.... She was Ashley's ", "classmate, wasn't she?\""], "Bcm3Y1z3": ["\"Both her and Anders have been ", "really shaken about this, I think.\""], "WRFtg6rs": ["\"Have you noticed? Or maybe I'm imagining it.\""], "6JgQTPv9": ["\"They'll be fine.\""], "Vq4nkmTR": ["\"The body was discovered by a jogger, who noticed an ", "unusual smell right here at Warehouse District Park.\""], "qK277tKN": ["\"Huh... Isn't that where our kids often hang out?\""], "ybfhyQ1Q": ["\" . . . . . . . . . . \""], "XKvHcWg1": ["\\fi \".....What of it?\" \\fr\\c[2]"], "2bWbJ9pV": ["\"Oh shit. She wasn't kidding........\""], "Cd4LDGPs": ["\"....What did you say, honey?\""], "BwvGV0ck": ["You tell your husband it was probably", "your kids that killed the child on TV."], "5wkwsHY9": ["\"That's............ awful, isn't ", "it? But they're just kids.\""], "RL9cZqdP": ["\"The consequences can't be that bad, can they?\""], "n6bmYkST": ["\"I don't wanna be on the news as that bitch ", "who raised her kids so badly someone died!\""], "x5Fct38b": ["\"Well.... You didn't. They don't know that. ", "Actually, we don't know that either.\""], "YjxfHV2v": ["\"Not for sure anyway...\""], "TyGTDMyv": ["\"...........That's true. We don't know anything.\""], "SctfZ2ms": ["\"Right.... I don't think I even saw ", "this news, if I'm quite honest.\""], "8jvYKJBs": ["\"I was dozing off this whole time....\""], "glKzWGY4": ["\"...........Hah!\""], "VnmWcyQb": ["\"Awww, my love. I knew we'd be on the same page.\""], "TdnsfCwV": ["\"Um... We're back....\""], "nw82tB2g": ["\"They didn't have the right coffee,", "so I bought some knock-off brand....\""], "7k3NqXpv": ["\"That's fine. Go do your homework.\""], "FQ0XRzlk": ["\"By the way, Ashley sweetheart... ", "Your friend was found dead.\""], "0GMZPrqS": ["\".....Huh? I don't have any friends.\""], "jW55LZg2": ["\"Well, not anymore you don't!\""], "NNptt4hM": ["\"She was found near that warehouse, so I ", "suggest you don't go play there anymore.\""], "V6yMxL4D": ["\"T-that's right, kids! It's a very dangerous ", "area. And trespassing is no good!\""], "jk5vSHDv": ["\"Exactly! Probably best you don't admit ", "ever being there in the first place.\""], "ljvW23dP": ["\"Got it... We'll never go there again. Sorry......\""], "3Q5T5Snp": ["\"Um....... Do they--, uh...... D-did they ", "catch the killer yet? Who was it?\""], "l0PnbpbJ": ["\" .......................................... \""], "92V9TgnJ": ["\" .. . .. .... .. ... . . . .. . . .. . \""], "xLV3tvJW": ["\"They didn't say anything about any killers.\""], "SNYrdSWh": ["\"O-oh! I just.... I was just assuming...\""], "vzn4VwJT": ["\"Anyway. Dinner will be ready in an hour.\""], "vSGrTjqZ": ["\"Okay..... Thanks.\""], "llPgdBc5": ["\".........................Do you really think they did it?\" "], "C4qHytXL": ["\"Did what?\""], "4x1VHD4v": ["\"C'mon, lets make dinner together!\""], "qKxqksCT": ["\"..............Hey.\""], "qTgFNcRC": ["\"Don't you have classes or something?\""], "NPllxFtH": ["\"You're not actually taking that job, are you?\""], "K3dxV6X8": ["\"Get lost. This has nothing to do with you.\""], "lsQFMXFt": ["\"If you really want a job, I'll ask my ", "boss if they have something for you.\""], "gtlN2Z7N": ["\"It's part-time too, so you'd ", "still have free time and all.\""], "bbByK86S": ["\"Pass.\""], "GHcdSKj1": ["\"\\fi Sigh.... \\fr\\c[1] Look.\""], "bcrXKbpC": ["\"If you're trying to make Mom feel bad, ", "forget it. She's not going to care.\""], "b5kNn1jw": ["\"I don't care that she doesn't care.\""], "tVsvzxQG": ["\"What's this about then? Are you ", "trying to punish me for something?\""], "gC3LVG32": ["\"Man, you really think everything ", "I do is about you, huh?\""], "gF5M7JZg": ["\"Then why?\""], "rqt1ymJv": ["\"\\fi Because. \\fr\\c[2] Now move! I'm gonna be late for work.\""], "Xz3BnWpN": ["\"What are you, fucking five years old??", "Stop being such a brat and talk to me.\""], "KG4RMQKv": ["\"Yeah yeah, I'm a brat! Why don't ", "you go cry about it to Julia??\""], "6wwPjcZG": ["\"Bet she'll comfort the hell out of you!\""], "v05ZqQhQ": ["\"Ohhh, there we go. Is that it?? ", "That's just it, isn't it?\""], "L51ggYXm": ["\" 'Boohoo! Big bro doesn't give me attention, ", "so I better jack off a bunch of random men!' \""], "MSsM23sw": ["\"Holy fuck, get over yourself! It's ", "not even that kind of place!!\""], "y6vz9nnX": ["\"Ha! Yeah right, and you're ", "a qualified physiotherapist.\""], "cx0kmS4x": ["\"Argh!!! Get out of the way!!!\""], "yw6cMs9c": ["\"Where do you think you're ", "going? We're not done here.\""], "P1BM0D8r": ["\"BACK OFF! Don't touch me!!\""], "6ZnVbcLq": ["\"If you wanna touch me, it costs money now!!\""], "Ljc0f52X": ["\"........Kids, what are you doing?\""], "JX1mVWVf": ["\"Andrew's being a jackass!!!\""], "S2bCSr7r": ["\"Son, you know better than to bully your sister...\""], "7Cr4Hf5g": ["\".................I had no idea you were home.\""], "N6Bhwzd1": ["\"It's my sleep day... I was working last night.\""], "SPy7MpfH": ["\"Crap. Really? Sorry.... We'll be quiet.\""], "0mNR4nkx": ["\"Thank you...\""], "sNz5jLRp": ["\"Pfft! You got scolded. Who's the brat now?\""], "4JZ3dRC0": ["\"Quiet, you. Let the old man sleep.\""], "8yXRpPPm": ["\"You owe me a lot of money now, by ", "the way. For how you manhandled me.\""], "jDhrtC8M": ["\"If I give you some money, ", "will you drop this job?\""], "C0rvkBM7": ["\"I'll drop it right after you ", "hand me seven million in cash!\""], "tqDKMbD8": ["\"Alright. Give me a sec.\""], "rjn647cn": ["\"....Huh?\""], "Qm1kHkzj": ["\"(I just need some pen and paper...)\""], "cGnWsNry": ["\"Seven million in cash. That's the final offer.\""], "tGGp8K6G": ["\"Here you go.\""], "HSNd4bLh": ["You hand her the receipt."], "c1jrZ0Cp": ["\".............\""], "d1KzPkZv": ["\"............Well, what do you know? ", "A seven-million-dollar bill.\""], "vkhmgmTK": ["\"All yours.\""], "FwmFHJGV": ["\"It also says beer, frozen pizza, smokes, and detergent.\""], "chgyjC7Q": ["\"A spending suggestion, if you will.\""], "kKFqkwPs": ["\".........Pfft. HahHAHahHA!! Yeah, you'd ", "spent seven million on crap like this!\""], "p2R3ksL7": ["\"Aaaaaaaaaaaah, fine. You win.\""], "B2ppl584": ["\"So you'll turn the job down?\""], "2s1RKvf4": ["\"Sure. That too!\""], "DBpQ6rSt": ["\" ? ? ? \""], "9F6YFR1m": ["\"I've missed you.\""], "crFkBDvf": ["\" . . . . . . . . . . \""], "NNgcQtsn": ["\"....There there?\""], "BWpkKD4Z": ["All good. Now separate."], "0JJBPzT1": ["\" .............. \""], "SnfmrV3P": ["Hurry up. Before it gets weird."], "XLMrt9T6": ["\" . . .. .. ... .. .. .. .... . . .. . \""], "7PNk15wK": ["\"What? I finally forgive you, yet ", "I can't even get a proper hug??\""], "1fDqkp1M": ["\" \\} Goddammit, don't do this to me............. \\{\""], "dhNPZMmW": ["\"Hehee!! What? What?? What did I do??\""], "grpgzb3g": ["\"I'm hungry!!\""], "NzB5QPJ6": ["\"Shocker.\""], "cN4v94td": ["She's hungry."], "5pMJ2JJr": ["\"Well, come on then. Dinner's ready.\""], "pfJkjmQb": ["This episode is titled..."], "9Qy6Fzrp": ["\"Fucking Dumb Bitch Whore Cunt I Need You I Need", "You I Need You I Need You I Need You I Need You.\""], "3zKlx9mn": ["\\{MINE, MINE, MINE, MINE, MINE, MINE, MIN", "E, MINE, MINE, MINE, MINE, MINE, MINE, MI\\}"], "S5GCf9SP": ["\"This one's for Ashley!\""], "GDMXQt7z": ["\"HaHAhHAhA!!!!\""], "PfRPBZTM": ["\"Hah. And while we're on the topic of Ashley...\""], "Dk49lML2": ["\"The nerve of you to hand her over to me", "and then act like I can't have her.\""], "9Swk8lFr": ["\"She's not your fucking problem, is she? She's \\fi mine. \\fr\\c[1]\""], "nf2D4Gsf": ["\"Oops, haha!\""], "4VnjDgDX": ["\"(Wait, no... Don't laugh, that's awful.)\""], "DdbvcjZg": ["\"Pfft....\""], "zNCSTWB4": ["\"HahHahaha!! Take that!\""], "1B0Ytw0b": ["\"(Ah, I'm bored now...)\""], "Jt5gLMSw": ["", "Got a Head!"], "47M7mzv1": ["Dinner's ready!"], "G1KN4vBF": ["\"Well? Go on. Eat.\""], "Nf4WgmqH": ["\"Ewwwww. It's all raw...\""], "mjkKb02m": ["\"I don't wanna eat this! I want soup!!\""], "1C2clCTt": ["\"No. You need to eat, so you'll grow up healthy.\""], "jbKfvqcx": ["\"Grow up, and stop being such a fucking brat.\""], "zwC1m4Yr": ["\"I don't wanna eat this!\""], "lTL29zlJ": ["\"\\{ I DON'T! I DON'T!! I WON'T!! \\}\""], "LrzsYWs3": ["\"Hahah.... Not even in my dreams, huh?\""], "crcCw6Pq": ["\"I just can't imagine you listening.\""], "b176xkR0": ["\"Eat it, or I'll fucking end you, you little shit.\""], "Ltn1DTF7": ["\"HAHahA! No, you won't!! ", "You're aaaaall talk!\""], "QJwk9Pnb": ["Back at your parents' house, you were ", "cutting these two up and wanted to cry."], "6WYbDLR0": ["Not because you felt bad about butchering ", "your parents, or even for their deaths."], "7Xm9vRNx": ["No. You wanted to cry for yourself."], "nb7WvcSj": ["More than the end of their lives, it", "was the end of yours. \"The good son\"."], "yKR0n165": ["Sadly, \"Yes, I killed my family! But it was for ", "the sake of my family!!\" doesn't quite ring true."], "DsMh6c97": ["And then the one you did it for ", "didn't appreciate it anyway..."], "0fJ08n5d": ["\"...........Are you having fun, sir?\""], "mw80mrWb": ["\"Are you asking me?\""], "Lqx5L6zG": ["\"Yeah. How long are you going to ", "keep rummaging through my mind?\""], "b159PCdd": ["\"Grime Soul.\" "], "9XyY3l1s": ["\"It seems you have not parted ", "ways with the Tar Soul.\""], "7YcMqX54": ["\"I have not.\""], "VNHW21zs": ["\"........You are as I remember you.\""], "jtqPJxdh": ["\"I do not hold it against you.\""], "lF8lG0TV": ["\".....Thanks.\""], "SnNxkWDt": ["\"It seems like you feel a lot for the Tar Soul.\""], "rp6z965y": ["\" . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . \""], "T4J9Sd5W": ["\"I will be honest. I am having a difficult ", "time discerning what to make of this.\""], "bPXLbMsq": ["\"What exactly do you want to do?\""], "grVz7ksZ": ["\"I want to keep her safe.\""], "gNvrM6yd": ["\" .............................................. \""], "VqvC7jxd": ["\"......I sense a bit of a contradiction.\""], "xBTBKhSm": ["\"She disappoints me....\""], "fFj1vC8q": ["\"I should fuck her up.\""], "zPSmwZyq": ["And down and over and sideways."], "P1dtrykk": ["\"I need her to--....\""], "YhhHpGd6": ["\"--give me the fucking respect that I deserve.\" ", "is how that sentence would continue."], "8Gh8P9JP": ["But you know you don't really deserve any, so never mind."], "K8mPDNDt": ["\"It's just that I've---....\""], "wdx8SbpZ": ["\"I've tried, and I've tried, ", "and I've tried with her.......\""], "nG78Bj17": ["\"All my life I've tried, but ", "she just won't work with me...\""], "qChd4gBv": ["\"But even still. For her, I--- No. To me she's---...\""], "Wnv4Jk7T": ["\" .. .. . . .. . ... . . .... . \""], "Xz8lM5sQ": ["\"Go on.\""], "9X1vHXTB": ["\" \\} ..........She means so much, but ", "I can't even fucking hold her. \\{\""], "xW1cs5tw": ["\"Why is that?\""], "D2tmnyJb": ["\".......Because it's-... I don't ", "\\fi really \\fr\\c[1] want to. I think.\""], "ZZpBCL2D": ["\"It's pathological.\""], "5QqtbqrB": ["\"If everything hadn't been so screwed up from the start, ", "I know I wouldn't have ever come to see her that way.\""], "crgD9Tfv": ["\"I wouldn't have rotted from the inside out...\""], "8S1Ss3WJ": ["\"That must have been tough.\""], "FDvbf5kY": ["\" .............. \""], "jsQjmJmx": ["\"It will be alright now.\""], "N0Dz199l": ["\" . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . \""], "8DYsVQGg": ["Suddenly you understand why people join cults."], "XDsKBkXy": ["\"I can help you, Grime Soul.\""], "xSqnbB8h": ["\"..........................How?\""], "VqTN6NZC": ["\"I can suggest that you stop having ", "the thoughts you wish not to have.\""], "7fBGNfyF": ["\"Like you've been 'suggesting' that I open up?\""], "sdlKlvb5": ["\"Yes.\""], "LL80tzql": ["\" . . . . . . . . . . . . \""], "M08zCkjJ": ["\"Shall we aid one another?\""], "VKn6b5gL": ["\"...How could I possibly help you with anything?\""], "nxVN5z8B": ["\"Allow me to introduce myself. ", "My name is Lord Unknown.\""], "3JCdQ0Xn": ["\"Or that is what others call me.\""], "GKzqCkmZ": ["\"I'm Andrew. Though you probably ", "picked up on that already...\""], "4y1y8dgz": ["\"Andrew, I am not looking for a simple trade.", "I am looking for a continuing partnership.\""], "Qw4HKZ2w": ["\"What does that entail..?\""], "FxKk8Dtp": ["\"Come with me, Andrew. I will show you.\""], "hjmvXcGD": ["Like you have any choice but to follow..."], "JsWFYVZs": ["You've got nothing to set on the table."], "ZZ9G5J1Z": ["You've got nothing to set on the table."], "wVlyFwHS": ["You've got nothing to set on the table."], "9JLxGg14": ["You've got nothing to set on the table."], "WkcxWhGP": ["Oh, look! It's all your shit ", "you're refusing to sort out."], "NqwwRsQY": ["\"N-no, you won't, right? Andy..?\""], "4Pl2yysV": ["\"I love you, Andy. You're my best friend...\""], "nr1Pk2Vr": ["Well, go on. Don't stop there."], "WwnTPWsL": ["\"\\fi *Sob!* \\fr\\c[2] Why are you doing this?? ", "Why are you so horrible to me?!\""], "BSnXW4Bw": ["\"I didn't make you do anything! ", "I didn't force you to stay!!\""], "g0tzFn8P": ["\"So what? You don't have to stick around either.\""], "NcVJbgdC": ["\"If I can walk away at ", "any point, so can you.\""], "MJWljJJZ": ["\"But unlike you, I've never", "once forced my will on you.\""], "s32JjZv7": ["\"And for what??\""], "ShKyHQ4J": ["\"What am I holding back for at this", "point? We're never getting better!\""], "DMQqhNCR": ["\"I should do whatever the fuck I want with you!\""], "mlrk3MSR": ["\"\\fi *Sob!* \\fr\\c[2]\""], "PVZFSxHV": ["\"How about it, little sister? ", "Would you like that??\""], "swMSzkWD": ["\"You'd think. Given how many ", "passes you've made at me.\""], "qp0JFcwF": ["\"It's not like that! I was ", "just playing around!!\""], "2n2G3lV1": ["\"Yeah? The next time I get my hands ", "on you, we'll play by my rules!\""], "P7j6YXd4": ["\"(No... That's not really it.)\""], "M9Drdqz1": ["\"(Should I ask for it, she'd let me I'm sure...)\""], "Mt4vYjRf": ["\"(But what's the point?)\""], "xZjpBcSs": ["\"\\fi *Sob, sob!* \\fr\\c[2] I haven't done anything wrong!!\""], "yQ4QkJRJ": ["\"(It's not really her. I'm wasting my time...)\""], "z70c58Qc": ["Want to save?"], "tgh3DX8g": ["It's the end of the episode. Are you sure?"], "7zJ7jR8K": ["Alright! Geez....."], "BzX3JW0Z": ["[You can continue here once ", "Episode 4 has updated.]"], "cWzZlMZt": ["Still-life painting."], "j4wyfV15": ["You care very little for visual arts."], "lrfjrqQK": ["A rather tasteless display."], "SzZ12csL": ["It's a wooden plank! Boy oh boy oh boy oh boy!!"], "nSQ7yHxs": ["Start over?"], "MBKVm5FT": ["Your parents are offering you an olive branch..."], "xZhMSCGc": ["What are you, stupid?"], "rjCfXDtG": ["Welcome to Andrew's momentary lapse in judgment."], "0tBKwD5M": ["Here you are in this critical moment in time."], "W3Lq3q0j": ["You have learned that your parents ", "sold you out, and left you to die."], "B6yx4RTG": ["Now your mom says she's \"sooo sowwy!\""], "nxfQS6Fq": ["Normally, you'd figure out she's ", "full of shit in two seconds flat."], "XyhsCv1c": ["This time, however, your brain ", "craps out for some reason..."], "Pwlk4dL4": ["\"Aww, shucks! What's the worst that could happen?\""], "Jbc3NyVw": ["Never mind the fact that you resent this woman for ", "the childhood she put you and your sister through."], "TKYCRk7R": ["Never mind that you know her to be a manipulator who ", "cares more about appearances than your well-being."], "PZ8q4QDJ": ["Never mind that there's evidence she's been ", "lying through her teeth this whole time."], "kdLKjVhy": ["Never mind all that! Who ", "cares? She's faaaaamilyyyyy."], "cQTD00Tl": ["Don't you care about your ", "faaaaaamilyyyyyyyyyyyy???"], "mdbqgB1v": ["You actually don't. "], "kPjCkt9c": ["Not beyond trying to seem normal anyway."], "xbPWnXFT": ["But we've already established you're ", "acting out of character for this bit."], "LSs8Ytq5": ["\"Oh boy!! That one single apology just now ", "has wiped away two decades of neglect!\""], "rrLxMGxZ": ["\"That's all it took? Damn, I should've ", "held you at knifepoint years ago!\""], "szrCJb9m": ["How fortunate that Ashley trusted ", "you alone with your parents! "], "dcyH3nYJ": ["Surely, she trusted you \\fi not \\fr because she has a trinket to ", "blackmail you with, but because you're such a good boy!"], "zR30WQl8": ["And surely she's not eavesdropping in on ", "you to see if you'd betray her or not."], "kZ36gmWp": ["No, never mind. There she is! Go figure."], "zFHHj44Z": ["\"Oh no you don't!! Andy, what the hell!?\""], "mglGvqmL": ["She charges at you to give you ", "what-for, as she sometimes does."], "DvPJVmfS": ["A little domestic violence, ", "just like back at room 302."], "qfGWC2py": ["Except this time, you won't let her! You double down ", "on the dumbest mistake you've made in your life."], "xzXtX8l1": ["Unable to de-escalate, you slice ", "your beloved sister's throat!"], "8TXPYftX": ["Then you untie your parents ", "like the fucking hero you are."], "fzr7NP09": ["The day is saved!! HURRAY!!!!!"], "ln6H6M47": ["\"Good god... What do we do about this mess?\""], "nnTjsfj7": ["She asks, giving zero shits about the girl ", "she gave birth to, now lying dead before her."], "cCfpG0nk": ["She'd totally care if you were ", "dead, though. Totally. Yup, yup."], "3h2CXn8F": ["Your mother says to leave it be for now."], "PF8sj6ky": ["You don't question this, because to get to this point, ", "you'd have to have been fucking brain-dead already."], "NmvxnVyx": ["Instead, you go to sleep."], "8l92sNXy": ["Meanwhile..."], "BSrrXMt2": ["\"Hi. This is Mrs. Graves. We had ", "taken your offer some time ago.\""], "YxcZKpLF": ["\"Yes, well... no. The thing is, I wanted to ask", "why did my kids show up at my house yesterday?\""], "SpPgG92Y": ["\"Yes, alive!\""], "KDVTHn6C": ["\"...........Alright. Thank you. I'll be waiting.\""], "gYVHqYk1": ["\"Fuck you, asshole! I knew it!!\""], "04XY5WzF": ["\" ? ? ? ? ? ? \""], "KgghVgL3": ["Bye Andrew!"], "DVfr82WF": ["Bye Mom!"], "WKVGdrMF": ["Bye Dad!"], "8CTZZcrH": ["Bye Ashley!"], "d9dWLX2m": ["STUPIDITY KILLED THE TWAT - END!!!!"], "3c838R5W": ["Oh, would you look at that?", "How could this be?????"], "CSF6c554": ["The thing your more intelligent self ", "already figured would happen, happened."], "cbs9DSnT": ["Hell, even Ashley had figured it out."], "DZJWbVM9": ["How did you fall for this again?"], "RD2Pgs8B": ["Well, whatever."], "9JDzySHk": ["The hitman takes you and your sister's ", "corpses somewhere to be disposed of."], "cTPL9JjP": ["Mom and Dad continue living happily ever after!"], "xQgFPByB": ["THE PARENTS LIVE -END!!!!"], "w7mjn2v7": ["\"Here you go. A mocha latte ", "with strawberry syrup.\""], "KvKbv3bl": ["\"Th-..... thank you.\""], "8ZPd6SgF": ["\"And the money for the bolt cutter. ", "Sorry for the trouble and thank you.\""], "dMCt4lRM": ["\"Of course.... B-but maybe you ", "should go to the police?\""], "k1G0GsW6": ["\"............Huh?\""], "p0GGQ4Zz": ["\"Even if it was a prank, imprisoning ", "someone is a crime......\""], "srS8DRG7": ["\"It was just a bad joke that went ", "too far. Don't worry about it.\""], "zgqVM9rf": ["\"But if you don't report it, your ", "friend will think doing that is okay...\""], "V2M3790Y": ["\" .......... \""], "CYbyML4k": ["\" ................................ \""], "Ng85CxM0": ["\".......You're right. I'll report him.\""], "qWGNv0RN": ["\"Phew!! Thank goodness...\""], "4FVqM8D4": ["\"Actually, I don't think I should stay", "roommates with someone like that.\""], "5Ybz5yPQ": ["\"But I'm not sure where else to go....\""], "0Bd3zNmj": ["\" .. .. ..... .. ... ... . . .. . .... . . \""], "zXPwj4YK": ["\"(Weird.... I figured she'd jump at the", "opportunity to move in together.)\""], "qkvF8BSL": ["\"...I don't suppose there's any chance ", "in hell you and I could try again?\""], "L2dF5Wb5": ["\"................S-..... sorry...\""], "StTGDxgh": ["\"........Was I that awful?\""], "Cgwh6kpB": ["\"N-no!! It's just--.......\""], "tWYYBMm5": ["\"It's just better this way.....\""], "qLMDVDy2": ["\"Y'know, I didn't really get to ask you this when ", "we broke up, since Ashley was right there...\""], "Sl9pN44S": ["\"But I would like to hear you out properly ", "this time... Why can't we work things out?\""], "hJdxQQ6v": ["\"I--... It's-... I-... uhhh...\""], "KSGh1phh": ["\" ............................I- I mean ", "it's not that we can't, but......\""], "v7J20MZ6": ["\"(Yeah, I thought so. Now that we're ", "face-to-face she folds like paper...)\""], "8hVK1Gp5": ["\"(If I push for it, we'll get ", "back together, I'm sure.)\""], "djq7J3d4": ["\"(I'll ask her to move elsewhere with me ", "right away, so Ashley can't find me.)\""], "RJYnB0zg": ["\"(Then I'll start working under Carl's ", "ID, and live quietly ever after...)\""], "CR3x7P3g": ["\"(Probably put a baby in her ", "just to seal the deal.)\""], "nZfbfPLD": ["\"We-- It's just not going to work, I'm sorry!!\""], "lmZ5JrHj": ["\"H-hey, hey, hey! C'mon, what's the matter?\""], "s6kdFHD8": ["\"Sorry! I-- I just don't want to. I can't...!\""], "QRryR2z9": ["\"What did I do wrong?\""], "SF3mXjvy": ["\"Nothing! .....Or.... um...\""], "CsBX3zbM": ["\" ... .. ..... . .. . . ... .. . . . . .... . \""], "RnLKlz5s": ["\"...........M-maybe it's because that's how", "you're used to acting with Ashley, but...\""], "1xG5mpt4": ["\"I don't like being tiptoed around...\""], "WHCBvNhB": ["\"....But I haven't done that?\""], "DKHw5R5m": ["\"H-haven't you? Everything was always about ", "what I wanted to do, or eat, or talk about...\""], "hfKMQFQd": ["\"And I-- I admit it was nice at first......\""], "0VQh9Zq0": ["\"But then I realized you're not actually ", "interested in any of the things I enjoy...\""], "MlSjdQ1W": ["\"So you were just putting up with ", "me... And building resentment.\""], "RHXmW5j4": ["\"Not at all. Making you ", "happy makes me happy.\""], "bWyyq5GV": ["\"S-still! That's not what I ", "want from a relationship.\""], "6JHQMDBB": ["\"I- .... I want someone equal. ", "Someone to grow with...\""], "NzqtVtbk": ["\"Not a servant who agrees to everything, ", "but doesn't put his heart into anything...\""], "S78NHXBR": ["\"...I'm not sure what to say to that.\""], "b9BJvQ42": ["\"I think-....... M-maybe there's something ", "a little weird about you...\""], "J0ZvR2q4": ["\" . . . . . . . . . . \""], "bzywcC7T": ["\"S-sorry! I'm sorry!! I didn't mean that! ", "It's my own fault that I'm uneasy!\""], "zkcmxFLg": ["\"But... But since I am, it's just...", " better not to meet again. Right?\""], "3Yg4T0fF": ["\"..............That's up to you.\""], "HhMwRcst": ["\"S-sorry... I need to go... ", "Please don't be angry...\""], "tmzL7fkj": ["\"I'm not angry... I'm just really confused.\""], "jzTz1wKn": ["\"Did I do something to you?\""], "SPYvfVGg": ["\"N-no.....\""], "pqbYlTZP": ["\"Then where is this coming from?\""], "j1bP7YBC": ["\"Uhhh... Actually.....\""], "Mk0lRSVB": ["\"Here.....\""], "QCDYfq3p": ["She hands you a letter."], "nT95zqxp": ["\"AH! N-no!! Don't read it now!\""], "YCX87dh9": ["\".......Okay?\""], "Y4dn65rj": ["\"I, uhh.... I wrote it a while ago... with ", "no intention of ever sending it, hahhaha...\""], "FSMBKwJ6": ["\"It's a bit.... harsh. You don't have to read ", "it. I just wanted you to have it. For closure.\""], "bjT8Rh6G": ["\"Well.... thank you? I guess.\""], "sgGRmHk7": ["\"Goodbye, Andrew......\""], "n2MmJpT7": ["\"Somehow it seems like we won't meet again...\""], "ddNWfl9k": ["\"Ahahaha...! Y-yeah.............\""], "ZsR6nz2n": ["\"I see...\""], "J36Lh7yq": ["\"Then I bid you farewell, and wish ", "you all the happiness in this world.\""], "R5jQgj9V": ["\"You too, Andrew............ Take care.\""], "QSRC3PPm": ["\"(Well, that was a bust.)\" "], "sxQcKJp7": ["\"(Oh well. I'm out of the house now.)\""], "bJQxqTrt": ["\"(I should get out of here before Ashley ", "spots me gone and comes looking...)\""], "FdFZQbXm": ["Sit here and wait for a bus?"], "ZPrQfqwX": ["\"(I really don't think it matters ", "whether I read her letter or not...)\""], "frBhsRLn": ["Read what your ex-girlfriend had to say to you?"], "JZlLH5xd": ["\"Dear Andrew, I loved you a lot.\""], "6f4hkLpv": ["\"It took a long time to gather the courage to break it ", "off with you, and it hurt like nothing else ever will...\""], "53lDPKtZ": ["\"Today I learned that your apartment burned down, ", "and I have yet to hear a word from you.\""], "X09LvclQ": ["\"I don't know if you're alive or dead...\""], "JlwxMHgQ": ["\"There's a sick, sick part of me that ", "feels relieved that you might be dead.\""], "lTT0VPPF": ["\"(Haha! Yikes....)\""], "fnp48Gb7": ["\"I thought I loved you, Andrew...\""], "mQC6zgFY": ["\"Whenever we'd meet up, I used to get butterflies.\""], "xJfcrXGr": ["\"Even after we'd been together for so long, my ", "heart would always beat like crazy when we talked.\""], "mR6J9snr": ["\"I thought I was nervous because I liked you so much...\""], "wM5TtWZY": ["\"But looking back, I wasn't ", "nervous, Andrew. I was anxious.\""], "Gs9yCWXW": ["\"It wasn't butterflies. It was every fiber of my being ", "screaming at me to get as far away from you as I can.\""], "sXH6SD3C": ["\"(.....What the hell?)\""], "xDmTMwSR": ["\"I don't love you, Andrew. I'm scared of you.\""], "PjgXnfjL": ["\"These three months away from you have finally ", "opened my eyes. There's something off with you.\""], "lBPrbdPs": ["\"You say all the right things, ", "but you don't mean any of it.\""], "8613qDr3": ["\"There is something cold and dead ", "where your heart should be.\""], "B64DZvxL": ["\"You were just really good at hiding it... ", "Or maybe it was me who didn't want to see it?\""], "G52jQjTQ": ["\"Either way, our paths have diverged, ", "and they will never cross again......\""], "XsyMHWFM": ["\"If you're dead, I hope ", "you're in Heaven with Nina.\" "], "TfmrY0Fl": ["\"But if you're alive, I hope ", "you rot in Hell with Ashley.\""], "96gS3FVn": ["\"You did not protect me. I will not mourn you.\""], "fg3w9HVv": ["\"Never yours again, Julia.\""], "ZqdJS72D": ["\"(Huh...)\""], "FXNhtDz8": ["\"(Well, okay? Kinda sucks, because ", "I really did try to love her.)\""], "60ztmm5L": ["\"(Ah, whatever.)\""], "RVlWdXGg": ["\"(Nah. I should burn this before Ashley finds it.)\""], "ClqvFswd": ["And so you do!"], "czmKRv2f": ["\"(..................I'm assuming she'd find it, huh.)\""], "CKmbHFNX": ["Guess you already know you're going back to her."], "kHr5tKgC": ["\"(Ah, no, no.... It's just a ", "force of habit. I'm leaving.)\""], "G97nXXTD": ["\"No way!\""], "g68N2WVL": ["\"Andrew, my dude! Long time no see.\""], "Sjtxv0xR": ["\"(Who the hell......?)\""], "ytCFfsJj": ["\"(No, I think that's--...", "What was his name...?)\""], "QZDSyKrl": ["You can't recall, though you do recognize him."], "FWQNMwY9": ["\"Hi there, my dude! It's been a while.\""], "y7V2lRDc": ["\"Haha! Man, good to see ", "you! How have you been?\""], "Yh5XqqBm": ["\"Good, good! How are you?\""], "3sh2px5F": ["\"Great! I just got a promotion at work!\""], "HKjSWy95": ["\"Perfect timing, too! My wife is expecting.\""], "glRGjp7F": ["\"That's right, I'm married now!", "Hahaha!! Life is good.\""], "qdCqVvVB": ["\"That's amazing. Congratulations! For", "both the marriage and the promotion.\""], "h6kDSFkR": ["\"Haha! Thanks, dude. Look! ", "I have a picture of her.\""], "4jfxQ48q": ["\"Isn't she gorgeous? Like, dude! I'm stunned ", "every morning I wake up next to this goddess!!\""], "ZLz7fsXt": ["\"I can't believe I'm about to ", "be a dad! Dude! I'm a dad!! Me!\""], "m6XPLwHY": ["\"You must be pretty jealous, ", "huh? Haha! I know I'd be!!\""], "vPq36tCF": ["\"(Jealous? I probably should be, right?)\""], "6dsT5ZhM": ["\"(But yeah, no thanks. I don't want to fuck up", "raising another one the way I did with her...)\""], "9ZMrcN0n": ["\"(And she for sure wouldn't lift ", "a finger to help me.)\""], "fSpXVYs6": ["\"(And even then, it's not like ", "she and I could ever-.....)\""], "b8r69CTB": ["\"(....................Julia. I'm thinking about Julia.)\""], "xJXb631C": ["\"(And anyway, I'm out of her life now..................)\""], "F3N6nJjZ": ["\"So anyway! What about you? ", "What have you been up to?\""], "fZsQNsxw": ["\"H-huh? Oh, y'know... same old, same old.......\""], "YRBLvwyM": ["\"Ahh, okay....\""], "fDzf6HkY": ["\"Cool, cool.......\""], "J7Kk5nKk": ["\"So uhh, how's Julia?\""], "Tv4X7hpd": ["\"Better than ever! She broke ", "up with me some time ago.\""], "q91y9ST5": ["\"Oh. Sorry, dude......\""], "7YvZpYxB": ["\"Err... How's Ashley? You ", "guys still keep in touch?\""], "Rpk2Xnfy": ["\"...She's awful as usual.\""], "Z3VWNd8Z": ["\"Ahahaha..........\""], "1sTNHXsC": ["\" . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . \""], "NybXKCrT": ["This is the part where you admit ", "you've fallen on hard times."], "4HWnR4TD": ["You ask him for advice, and maybe he'll ", "take pity and let you stay on his couch."], "9Bb1Dj9m": ["You take the opportunity to get back on your feet."], "XytfsMBs": ["Find a job and a place as Carl Cultman,", "and turn your whole life around."], "tk4fQTrg": ["Soon you'll repay your friend's kindness by ", "taking his family out to dinner somewhere nice."], "Yt4WLgSP": ["And they'll surprise you by asking you ", "to be the godfather to their child."], "36ZkPFxl": ["You'll live out the rest of your ", "days smiling and helping others."], "xKcVt7L4": ["And none will have the faintest idea ", "of all the horrid shit you've done."], "8cR0gmxP": ["\" . ... . ... ... . . . . .... .. . .. .. . . \""], "RXLqcrfQ": ["\"\\fiBlerrghh....\\fr\\c[1]\""], "dPyJLwzM": ["\"Whoa dude!! Are you alright?\""], "SWMSWJXx": ["\"(The fuck's the point of any ", "of this?? I'm so tired....)\""], "wpNVvN5N": ["\"No, yeah. I'm fine... Sorry, I just ", "remembered I need to be somewhere.\""], "wDynDRrf": ["\"Okay? Well, it was good seeing you...\""], "PQNt8YX8": ["\"Yeah, you too...........\""], "Xx9y3NF9": ["\"Hey, you wouldn't happen ", "to have a twenty on you?\""], "PS8L01F1": ["\"..........Sure. Here you go...\""], "Mhp9j84t": ["\"Thanks. I'll be honest, I don't ", "think I can pay you back.\""], "JvgDW5y3": ["\"No problem, dude.... Just take ", "care of yourself, alright?\""], "MKZmZPcD": ["\"Thanks. You too, my dude.\""], "8BwyfFJ9": ["A mini-mall."], "NgwVtwpS": ["You pick up some excuses ", "before returning to Ashley."], "KdJCqN0N": ["", "Got Groceries and Booze!"], "ZpPPK8r5": ["\"Take care of yourself, alright?\""], "HzjC5n3W": ["\"Take care, man...\""], "GzDGTGLl": ["Here lies what little was in your stomach."], "P1CRq0TW": ["The woman pretends not to see or hear you."], "lDtlTqrb": ["The fence is covered in call girl ads."], "R2sFVDKJ": ["\"(Ugh... I haven't gotten any ", "in months and months now...)\""], "KcBhy25c": ["\"(Goddammit, I should've asked Julia", "to let me have her one last time...)\""], "HYCWYqn5": ["\"(I'm sure if I'd kept chatting, we could've--)\""], "qG2D7bWY": ["\"...........................Nah.\""], "9nCqtvQk": ["\"(She seems better off without me.)\""], "g1gWrfrJ": ["\"(If that's the case, ", "I should leave her be.)\""], "Hxj47Tf0": ["\"(Besides, playing her perfect ", "boyfriend was fucking exhausting...)\""], "k43sMPt5": ["\"Dear customers, we're on strike again. Tee-hee!\""], "qP49sYl1": ["\"Guess today's schedule! HAHAHA!! Fuck you.\""], "ZgVP1S9v": ["The flower pot is empty."], "PXTzKvVG": ["", "Got Sunflower Seeds!"], "ZKpHHyHN": ["The Watering Can is empty."], "3J0QKB56": ["", "Got a Watering Can!"], "b9cBfFdC": ["The flower pot is empty."], "RrtcGsrf": ["The flower pot is empty."], "ng9K8NMJ": ["The flower pot is empty."], "qXTS8s6V": ["The flower pot is empty."], "N9lzM2FW": ["The flower pot is empty."], "lVDB4y6H": ["Trash."], "c6G0x3r8": ["You can't put too much Carl in one trash."], "Fq93g3s9": ["Trash."], "NDYv1BCt": ["You can't put too much Carl in one trash."], "9h5bQPy1": ["Picked up some Carl!"], "ZZQGBKpt": ["Threw away some Carl!"], "xMJdmSbX": ["Trash."], "cQxpHpmX": ["You can't put too much Carl in one trash."], "D3t5f2Py": ["Trash."], "kW01T4nd": ["You can't put too much Carl in one trash."], "lV1W9WRG": ["Trash."], "01f6Zjs4": ["You can't put too much Carl in one trash."], "RV7WnbfB": ["Trash."], "xB4yNx1y": ["You can't put too much Carl in one trash."], "hZv6rbp5": ["There's something on the shelf,", "but you can't reach it."], "ncHLGkfg": ["The something-something is out of reach."], "KXKGd8Vv": ["", "Got an Eye Token!"], "0K5QgJl0": ["Something seems to be missing."], "M8sDR631": ["The chest opens!"], "KD2p0pZW": ["\"What do you make of this?\""], "5mnZ2w3J": ["\"No idea.\""], "YNwP9wXf": ["\"So what's all this about?\""], "zlY0Z8TT": ["\"We HaVe mORe uRgenT MatTerS aT haNd.\""], "RkYZSBxf": ["A small chest. It won't open."], "kBc4qPyx": ["There's an indent for something round."], "x3JbSL48": ["It won't open."], "5W6YFn00": ["Placed the Eye Token on the small chest."], "tCTyPVXR": ["", "It opens!"], "Qshk3Xx7": ["Inside is......."], "GvXzNxF1": ["Whatever this is!!!!!!"], "TgtLDyl6": ["\"............A paperweight?\""], "Z7zcpBMQ": ["\"No... Even if it doesn't look like much, it must ", "be important if the demon is holding onto it.\""], "r7SJT0kw": ["\" 'Possibly a Tar Soul', it says here on the label.\""], "Z6wx7pjc": ["\"Huh??? How could that thing be ", "a Tar Soul? I thought I was one!\""], "2VKvP0sN": ["\"Gimme that!\""], "gTxFbYjB": ["She yanks the thingy from you and..."], "9Zfg5PSm": ["\".....Oops?\""], "qJ8LCYvj": ["", "Found another Whatever-the-fuck!!!"], "p80Y4v0p": ["This one is also labeled \"Possibly a Tar Soul\"."], "0zgsVk0G": ["\"A crystal ball? Does the ", "Entity do fortune telling?\""], "K1sFdfB1": ["\"Hey now, visions of the future might ", "come in all shapes and sizes.\""], "pCLv9Fsn": ["\"Do you use this to see the future?\""], "lbJgmjV0": ["\"No, I dO nOt.\""], "bBHGVtWZ": ["\"So what's it for, then?\""], "MRHVr6Y3": ["\"iT mAtTerS Not.\""], "2j3n2Ssc": ["\"Not one for small talk, are you?\""], "c8pjZ8FX": ["\" . . . . . \""], "8Z6HDQxS": ["\"I swear I know this guy from somewhere....\""], "pB85VnfG": ["\"The Surgeon? Yeah, he's on TV all the time.\""], "hNcXyjKP": ["\"Shilling both ToxiSoda and his hospital.\""], "gNP2xrSF": ["\"Yeah, that's probably it...\""], "211NwMnj": ["\"Should we go kill these two?\" "], "6HsxlY1L": ["\"It kind of sounds like we got ", "wrapped up in their stupid scheme.\""], "4SSwPrrj": ["\"Pass.\""], "jk4ZPWKJ": ["\".....Oh? Okay??\""], "J6pWcYSC": ["\".......Don't you just love our parents?\""], "Cp2qxZKN": ["\"Nope.\""], "yHYnwgqr": ["\"Well, anyway...\""], "NShZ2Lsh": ["\"I guess this is a vision the Entity ", "has stored up for some reason.\""], "rbgJbzqF": ["\"Are there any more?\""], "K47yHlMq": ["\"It kind of looks like your Entity ", "has an interest in this Surgeon guy.\""], "1gSstLsx": ["\"I bet he's the 'possible Tar Soul'.\""], "Vsm5w7sC": ["\"What does the demon care though?\""], "Jwsm1gLG": ["\"It's also got an interest in you, 'Tar Soul'...\""], "spFSNRlT": ["\"Maybe he just wants some friends?\""], "LsJDPc5g": ["\"I don't know, Ashley... I can't ", "shake this awful feeling.\""], "DLFQR73j": ["\"I really think we should ditch this place...\""], "bSbXvlsw": ["\"And possibly the trinket too.\""], "h89p2Gyf": ["\"...Are you being serious!?\""], "8XlgMVLN": ["\"I'm not going back to living in the car!\""], "RHzZTc2Q": ["\"I'm done slinking about all day and night, ", "just because you're scared of everything!\""], "Y1ydxW1g": ["\"If anything, I thought you'd be thrilled ", "to be here, away from all that!!\""], "MHPl6Djs": ["\"There's no way the Entity is housing", "us out of the goodness of its heart.\""], "rXwHNR5Z": ["\"Something is afoot here, and we'd ", "best get away while we still can.\""], "C68JcQm9": ["\"So you'd rather go back to where, according to you, ", "every single cop alive wants revenge on us???\""], "CzC5Qbxw": ["\"I-............\""], "hhl7zJ2n": ["\"Besides!\""], "MH6CZgpG": ["\"Don't you wanna figure out what that whole", "quarantine mess we were in was about?\""], "Vwtyb363": ["\"Or who it was exactly that ", "sent the hitman after us?\""], "bhtQq25c": ["\"With this vision stuff, we could take ", "our revenge for getting locked up!\""], "h9zXNZB0": ["\"According to the letter in his car, the ", "hitman was hired by the water company.\""], "jG4FdZDN": ["\"Brown Water Co. is a sister company to ToxiSoda.\""], "Vnwj1fPy": ["\"And ToxiSoda is a company co-founded ", "by the Surgeon and this 'Sodaman'.\""], "RKZfNj6n": ["\"And then there's whatever hospitals are happily ", "acquiring the organs gained from the quarantine.\""], "yrTDm6qz": ["\"And it seems they've got some 'friends' ", "in media at their disposal too.\""], "qVtjFlJx": ["\".....Yes?\""], "z5x5YgzR": ["\"That's at least four layers of", "corporate bullshit and middlemen.\""], "vcRcvr9S": ["\"So who exactly are you taking ", "revenge on, my little vigilante?\""], "C641C0ws": ["\"Uhh... The Surgeon, I guess?\""], "4Jn2WZHq": ["\"Why? He didn't lock us in, ", "that was the water company.\""], "08QBdQ5W": ["\"W-well... I---... Kill them all, I guess? Why not??\""], "bsLg5GC6": ["\"You're not getting it. ", "Let me put it this way...\""], "kVDfK9xD": ["\"Why the fuck would I re-involve us in that mess?", "We're lucky to have escaped as neatly as we did.\""], "NZkpz75B": ["\".............It could be an episode.\""], "dV41b24F": ["\"Oh great! More of that fucking garbage!\""], "FXnTcCzS": ["\"Boy, oh boy! It's 'Andy and Leyley and", "the Great Conspiracy'! Whoop-de-doo!\""], "MVLRhkf4": ["\"Let's intentionally put ourselves in harm's way! ", "We'll uncover the mystery and..... then what?\""], "dQDf1fpZ": ["\"I was just trying to give ", "you something to focus on...\""], "ZkXVtpt1": ["\"Like I don't have enough on my plate already??\""], "21H5ntgs": ["\"What good would it even do to ", "kill some random guy in charge?\""], "DSYqyS9K": ["\"Some other random guy will just take ", "his place. Will you kill them too?\""], "73fzJtTH": ["\"......\""], "s4gLV4hZ": ["\"What about the workers? Associates? Shareholders? ", "Fuck! The people who received the organs?\""], "Kf48p41G": ["\"I don't know...\""], "x42b2HMs": ["\"And even if we uncovered some ", "grand scheme, what then?\""], "d2LrQJKq": ["\"Will God Almighty descend from the heavens to ", "pardon our sins for being such good snitches??\""], "hcpsHLVx": ["\"........I get it already. ", "It was just a suggestion.\""], "gjpnPlP9": ["\"You think you're so clever, peddling me this ", "revenge crap. Guess you really love it here, huh?\""], "RqP73mJb": ["\"Too bad I'm not the slack-jawed", "fucking moron you take me for.\""], "YSYf3RDg": ["\" . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . \""], "sK80XFHd": ["\"....................................\""], "x4lN32Zg": ["\"........No. Sorry.\""], "9KLgnRHz": ["\"Forgive me. It's not you ", "I'm angry at, okay?\""], "Ftswq0KK": ["\"Or, I am. But not about this.\""], "JbC2WCSz": ["\".........Okay.\""], "l2jl2Ct4": ["\"Ashley, I just want to keep you safe--\""], "SxhZKpx5": ["\"Tar SouL.\""], "qxkPpBmt": ["\"Oh! Err-- Whoops, how did we get in here?\""], "P9xZ01Mg": ["\"Darn, we must've been sleep walking! Aaaahaha!\""], "gwxq9Yxq": ["\"ComE sEe mE iN tHe RitUaL ChaMbeR.\""], "ZBzJxZdJ": ["You are Ashley!"], "0p1QNT7m": ["\"Do you like plants?\""], "Y1c6pj8m": ["\"TheY cAn bE of UsE.\""], "hhjWZc1n": ["\"This one right here isn't doing so hot.\""], "WflFJ3kC": ["\"But I can probably bring it back to life...\""], "cPh9CRjh": ["\"I used to grow some plants too. ", "Never did get them to bloom, though.\""], "K0Bb7fRZ": ["\" ... \""], "pr6klRLB": ["\"Most things don't work out for me, honestly...\""], "0wydpdYN": ["\"But hey! They might not have bloomed, but they ", "didn't die on me either! So that's something, right?\""], "NHlv7dMF": ["\"TaR SouL, tHeSe aRe nOt tHe ", "fLoWerS nEedeD tO cRoss.\""], "cVZ0y4MT": ["Removed plant."], "RsLs8GpQ": ["", "Got Black Flowers!"], "LZhGJcVb": ["Exit?"], "jklfRtS1": ["Maybe the Entity has left itself some sort of", "visual reminder somewhere in this room..."], "ZyRFxRwF": ["A surgeon and an entrepreneur walk into a bar....."], "LcvDZcxK": ["\"Looks like somebody needs a drink. I got you.\""], "40xHsr9m": ["\"Thanks. It's been rough lately. ", "My business is about to tank...\""], "ZLqqw4c8": ["\"Oh no. Really?\""], "Yr8YvTSh": ["\"Yeah. It turns out my company's soda has ", "some long term health consequences...\""], "hKZ18vlG": ["\"Mostly organ failure...\""], "MwQ4tYlL": ["\"Fuck, I love organs.\""], "kjxS58Xb": ["\"Huh?\""], "4CwSmHlb": ["\"Nothing. Go on.\""], "jPkwS6jS": ["\"So now our customers are dying!\""], "BHTH9S0H": ["\"That must be bad for business ", "indeed. Have you been sued yet?\""], "Jyzx5T79": ["\"No, no. We've settled a couple times...\""], "NkzH19WN": ["\"The problem is that with the customers ", "dead, who's left to buy my product??\""], "dk7W2zj1": ["\"I'm such a failure..... What ", "will I tell my wife and kids?\""], "FssNPcHF": ["\"Well, I for one think you're ", "doing God's work!\""], "FxSPkDqx": ["\"Uhhh...?\""], "HGMzjvcH": ["\"I'm a private surgeon. Thanks to you, ", "my business has never been better!\""], "zP2rRdzp": ["\"I have to thank you, my good sir. ", "Here, let me get you another drink!\""], "hGjwlDMn": ["\"Must be grand. Being able to help ", "people instead of poisoning them.\""], "7XYN9QRW": ["\"....Help who?\""], "Y7t9zRTk": ["\"The, uhh... your patients? ", "You save their lives.\""], "kkR76SYS": ["\"Oh, that's right. I guess I do.\""], "7ySyqrm6": ["\"But for me it's not the ", "money or the fanfare.\""], "5wHw8D0g": ["\"It's sexual gratification. ", "Cutting people up is incredible.\""], "vTd1vCsX": ["\"Oh.....\""], "B69Rjdtp": ["\"I hope your soda business keeps going, so ", "I'll have more people to slice and dice.\""], "D49d56nr": ["\"The only problem is that the organ ", "demand far exceeds the supply.\""], "NLvXpkLH": ["\"I'm so fucking pent up these days.....\""], "71xkdl5f": ["\"Well, I hope you get more organs soon. ", "I could really use some living customers.\""], "NR2ztKzf": ["\"Wouldn't it be hot if we could just lock ", "people into their houses like cattle?\""], "PJrGHV13": ["\"I'm sorry, what?\""], "CqJh7Myc": ["\"They'd make great organ donors. Though you'd ", "have to deal with a bunch of useless ones too.\""], "yTCBdB3L": ["\"You can't just pick and mix ", "people's innards all nilly willy.\""], "x9VgRGbb": ["\"No matter how much money you have, ", "that'll never get approved.\""], "80S42hyh": ["\"Well, you'd have to have some cover for it.\""], "CN6LlyrJ": ["\"Such as 'You have to stay here because you're ", "infected' or something along those lines.\""], "Rq9Vprgk": ["\"And conveniently, the organ ", "donors just so happen to die.\""], "h6LxR4CR": ["\"Of entirely natural causes of course, ", "such as the aforementioned infection.\""], "45N8gsy1": ["\"That reminds me of this one disaster ", "we had a couple years ago...\""], "M4ykt0kG": ["\"One of our water plants caused a bunch of ", "filth to leak into the public's water supply.\""], "67tGyHDq": ["\"Everyone on the district got ", "ill. It was a shitshow.\""], "dQ7dwg3m": ["\"And I mean that literally.\""], "wqcW8z8D": ["\"HAHAAH!!\""], "4wWxbgMF": ["\"Ohh, that's funny. It must've cost you a lot.\""], "HRp1Jb7N": ["\"That it did. You don't wanna know the ", "things I had to do to shut the media up.\""], "09D6D5rv": ["\"Though, I did make some ", "friends because of it.\""], "w6DQm4Lt": ["\"You're a funny guy, Mr. Sodaman.\""], "hsXxYlB6": ["\"That's not my name....\""], "yMZ0vHyP": ["\"What is it then? Maybe we ", "could be friends too.\""], "Y6hbVWfR": ["\"And by friends I mean business partners.\""], "BRGB0xCz": ["\"..........................I'm not so sure of that.\""], "cbg2wr6B": ["\"Why not? Let's partner up ", "and make a new company!\""], "4cdrwjM5": ["\"That way, you can even avoid ", "the scandals of your past!\""], "lGDjQbls": ["\"We'll have some 'accidents' with the water,", "quarantine some apartments, get some donors...\""], "w9yr6G9K": ["\"How about it?\""], "qmWLLGt5": ["\"I could certainly diversify in ", "this dire situation, but....\""], "j3QJz1dt": ["\"What would we even call the ", "company? Or the product?\""], "lfdJwPnQ": ["\"Something subtle... like 'Deadly Delight!'\""], "LtJCLB83": ["\"\\fi Sigh. \\fr\\c[3] Looks like my marketing ", "team has to take care of this one...\""], "L93Bf1KT": ["\"So you're in?\""], "cxj8dj6F": ["\"Ahhhhhh..........\""], "S677g0wq": ["\"To hell with it! Why not? My name is--\""], "VyP4BhCk": ["\"Ahh, Mr. Graves. Welcome, welcome!\""], "g6KhYRLh": ["\"Thank you for coming. We have been quite ", "anxious to get in touch with you.\""], "4Yf7L9xh": ["\"Umm... Y-yes. We got your letter. ", "Nice to meet you, Mister.....?\""], "sjDV7BXZ": ["\"No need to be so formal, ", "just call me Surgeon.\""], "tsxMYL3F": ["\"Take a seat, Douglas. Can I call you Douglas?\""], "GVbWG4Sg": ["\"I'd... prefer you didn't.\""], "H9BXw3Wl": ["\"Alright, Douglas, let's get straight to it.\""], "RxCByrdV": ["\"Sure. How much compensation ", "are we talking about?\""], "L5CXm59F": ["\"....Does she often speak out of turn?\""], "1J0KVbdX": ["\"M-my wife can speak whenever ", "she pleases, Mr. Surgeon!\""], "0W062Flp": ["\"I see.... Well, anyhow.\""], "phmTrDbH": ["\"I find it very, very concerning neither you, nor ", "your wife, stayed to be examined when instructed.\""], "rC3KTflm": ["\"Did you not get the memo? It specifically ", "said not to leave your apartment.\""], "HjyJXTYL": ["\"Such was the \\fi recommendation, \\fr\\c[6] yes.\""], "Mv2TCD1L": ["\"However, my husband and I are very busy people.\""], "Smx09VXk": ["\"....Be that as it may, we are ", "concerned for your safety.\""], "0zJPxkMY": ["\"Which is why I insist that you allow the nurse to take", "blood samples from each of you while you're here.\""], "t0vKql3S": ["\"Oh.... Well, oka--\""], "pmSQyvb5": ["\"\\fi Honey. \\fr\\c[6]\""], "TSKW7fSd": ["\"I- I mean, that's okay. We don't wanna ", "get checked at this point in time.\""], "J1PLb239": ["\"Bad health insurance, ahahha... You understand.\""], "4K1fYb6H": ["\"But not to worry! We actually got ", "checked locally on our own accord.\""], "6QgRkhYf": ["\"They said everything was perfectly ", "fine with the both of us.\""], "TqnCcsdk": ["\"...I assure you, Douglas. The public health centers", "do not have the means to spot these parasites.\""], "QLvghL03": ["\"Mr. Surgeon. We're only here to discuss ", "the matter of our compensation.\""], "MlpBzP4c": ["\"You have indeed 'gravely disturbed our ", "lives due to your company's error.' \""], "6kcMjYf3": ["\"I expect you to cover at least the hotel fees.\""], "N3SdCDHH": ["\"Yes of course. However, first ", "things first... The blood samples.\""], "6Dq49jSG": ["\"Ah, I see.\""], "xbTdW1hv": ["\"I did find the choice of our ", "meeting place peculiar....\""], "tnKBgk5x": ["\"Why would that be? An office is an office.\""], "PdwRfb0q": ["\"I was expecting an in-person", "apology from the water company.\""], "gGr6TQ2p": ["\"Why are we here getting pressured ", "into giving blood samples instead?\""], "vlnwfytz": ["\"..................You misunderstand ", "our intentions, Mrs. Graves.\""], "nr34TVB3": ["\"Just like you, our partners at the ", "Brown Water Co. are very busy.\""], "FM2w4RTM": ["\"And so am I. Let's get this matter resolved, ", "so I can get back to saving lives.\""], "FGhfMCzk": ["\"If you're not writing us a check, ", "we'll be on our way. Thank you.\""], "3Xbsg4y3": ["\"C'mon, love. We're out of here.\""], "1GVwlDmH": ["\"N-now now! I understand.\""], "SCB2wQcr": ["\"Douglas, Douglas... I have a suggestion.\""], "RTzfLQqg": ["\"Oh... um... Well, go on?\""], "XpY5d9ch": ["\"As I understand, your dear children are ", "locked in your apartment, isn't that right?\""], "yKWh92n0": ["\"Correct.\""], "Q5970HDk": ["\"You strike me as a man of reason, Douglas. ", "So I will share with you something.\""], "z79rHmsS": ["\"I-.... Okay?\""], "7yh7X0Tl": ["\"It doesn't seem like your son and ", "daughter are going to make it.\""], "drMy6cm4": ["\"It's highly likely you two are ", "also infected with parasites.\""], "Zsc9YxHG": ["\"Wouldn't you prefer spending your ", "last days together as a family?\""], "HLgv22px": ["\"No.\""], "McKz6VyR": ["\"That was fast...\""], "3XQjvB32": ["\"Was that everything?\""], "sP22tnZK": ["\"Alright, fine. I tried...\""], "Rk2Wl0qN": ["\"Brown Water Co. is truly sorry your ", "water got fucked and blah, blah, blah....\""], "GYdwSK28": ["\"How much to shut you up?\""], "1qBBQtKC": ["\"How much can you make it?\""], "qvbr8CGS": ["\"Not that much, but if you ", "want my professional opinion....\""], "sr5ppgZc": ["\"I'd recommend getting life insurance ", "for your kids right about now.\""], "YRSDpLHN": ["\"Doesn't sound like we'd get a good deal, given ", "they're both about to kick the bucket.\""], "BVdYDxt9": ["\"That information isn't out yet. It says ", "here they are two healthy young adults.\""], "RZbj5JzM": ["\" ........ \""], "CMHNt4mf": ["\"And... you're sure there isn't any ", "chance my kids could make it..?\""], "cPWb7KtX": ["\"That would be my opinion as a doctor.\""], "rPzkPCVh": ["\"But, uhh..... A-aren't we gonna die too ", "then? If the parasites are that bad.\""], "pvlxQs1g": ["\"Honey, there are no parasites.\""], "nhbyvkw4": ["\"This fucking quack is trying to kill us.\""], "DZvbqWL0": ["\"W-wHAT?!?!?\""], "qDndNQDz": ["\"Ha-ha! Women come up with the silliest things...\""], "37lFXsYm": ["\"We're not giving you blood samples so you ", "can mess with them and throw us in quarantine.\""], "jW8HzPf4": ["\"So if you're not giving us money, we can ", "continue this conversation through lawyers.\""], "yQ1ljnfb": ["\"I am \\fi trying \\fr\\c[4] to give you money, Douglas! ", "My good man. Calm your wife and think.\""], "0f5rSYjc": ["\"The parasites are very real, very deadly, ", "and your kids will soon be very dead.\""], "WdRB7KTs": ["\"Accept our company's apology, buy your", "kids some life insurance, and begone.\""], "lMFvw076": ["\".........\""], "rSDShZX9": ["\"Well, I mean... if you're telling us there's ", "nothing we can do to help them anyway...\""], "3ctytZ8H": ["\"Ah, Douglas. I knew you were a man of reason!\""], "8gCK4LSV": ["\"So........ What's going to happen to the kids?\""], "fb2x30B1": ["\"Parasites, Mrs. Graves. Have you ", "not been paying attention?\""], "JS8RRjbC": ["\".......I see.\""], "s6nrj4Fk": ["\"It's okay, honey... I'm one hundred percent with", "you. Besides, there's nothing we can do.\""], "SgvnV0Nd": ["\"Bigger forces are at play here. It's not ", "our place to get in the way of that, love...\""], "rKj1GtXR": ["\"Exactly! And \\fi besides \\fr\\c[6] besides! Had they just moved ", "out like I kept telling them, they'd be fine now!\""], "jwgfqPWj": ["\"It's terrible, but it's their own fault.\""], "pr750Jny": ["\"You're a good man in a tough spot, Douglas. ", "I do believe you're making the right choice.\""], "XdCRNRWC": ["\"Now then, let us get the paperwork all sorted out.\""], "NB1V9g1M": ["\"Hey........\""], "T3bvy27m": ["\"I'm sorry for taking things out on you.\""], "dCGhRP4C": ["\".......................Whatever.\""], "Ymz1V32B": ["\"Ashley, can we talk?\""], "GMtmLHdP": ["\"Don't you think you've said enough?\""], "S1jSmD8g": ["\"Even if I expressed it like an ass, my ", "point still stands. We're not safe here.\""], "ZHZpSgfS": ["\"The Entity isn't 'our friend',", "or not mine anyway....\""], "NSmRJNnq": ["\"It wants something...\""], "jSbc7PcR": ["\"And what exactly do ", "you plan to do instead?\""], "1RN8YSWf": ["\"Well.......... uh...\""], "Wssv0Vst": ["\"What say thee? O', wise, smart, calm, ", "collected, brave, Andrew Graves??\""], "xDW0sLQ8": ["\"Hmm? What's that?? You've got no ", "plans? You never do, do you??\""], "DJ2n14nf": ["\" . . . . . . . . . \""], "xXxplvGh": ["\"Just pissing and moaning as usual. ", "Nothing but complaints and no solutions!\""], "8FN77rd6": ["\"..........Are you done yet?\""], "d5tCD7js": ["\"Yeah, I'm fucking done. Fuck this ", "conversation, and fuck you.\""], "lJswXBDL": ["\"Ashley--\""], "HQvYvc0Y": ["\"FUCKING STOP!!!!\""], "6dp6KMfQ": ["\"How many fucking deals do you think ", "I've already made with the demon?\""], "sHJ2fZ0J": ["\"And it's been fucking fine every", "single fucking time! FUCK!!!\""], "R8jhmXQm": ["\"It didn't use to have you", "captive in its house...\""], "JT9LCd1m": ["\"I swear, Andrew, if you cry about this", "same damn thing one more time..!\""], "mzfxpMBV": ["\"...........Gotcha, Leyley. At your behest.\""], "ZkJ2dzTt": ["\"(The fuck....?)\""], "FvQ69gCd": ["There's nothing to step on."], "qp1jgftK": ["There's nothing to step on."], "jyCYdJ3x": ["There's nothing to step on."], "lStmb4Ql": ["An empty slot."], "Zb6wSrx9": ["An empty slot."], "9jxWNL0S": ["An empty slot."], "dj9qv3b9": ["There's nothing to step on."], "QGFRz6f8": ["The road cuts off."], "nc1lMLR1": ["\"...You don't suppose the Entity ", "just dropped us off here to die?\""], "wb6gwdRQ": ["\"No, I don't suppose that at ", "all. Stop being mad at me!\""], "N66yJ1nc": ["\"I'm not mad!?\""], "7tkkSMN9": ["The road cuts off."], "F4fKt4ys": ["\"Oh my... What is this? Where are we?\""], "P1yyCgHC": ["\"\\fi Sigh........ \\fr\\c[1]\""], "64r8GF7V": ["\"What?\""], "3lTc4wKG": ["\"I told you not to sacrifice the officers.\""], "PcxY94jy": ["\"Oh, for crying out loud... ", "Is this gonna be a fight?\""], "6nkr7Wl0": ["\" . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . \""], "3SWR0vPk": ["\"I'm sorry, okay? It had to be done.\""], "dyTySvJM": ["\"....Whatever. Now's not the time.\""], "FwGQxT8G": ["\"Where are we? Did we die....?\""], "5pV8ZW1j": ["\"Nah, don't worry about it. I've ", "been here before. In my dream!\""], "NrQnyXHN": ["\"Or, well... Not \\fi here \\fr\\c[2] here, ", "but definitely this place...\""], "sGbV7M2Z": ["\"The demon calls this the ", "Realm Between! I think.\""], "nPkNnh6T": ["\"It does look similar to ", "that place in the vision...\""], "qN0W5lf6": ["\" . . . . . . . . . . \""], "zmBrwg91": ["\"So then are we asleep right now?\""], "WdlwZDD8": ["\" ... .. . . .. ... . . . .. . \""], "yg3Qj77k": ["\".....Ashley?\""], "sMQ9Cwz2": ["\"Oh! Uhhh.... I don't think so. We", "went through some portal, right?\""], "KgLMBdg4": ["\"Anyway, get over it!! I ", "already said I'm sorry!\""], "CNqgr131": ["\"I'm not arguing??\""], "mghDFxBl": ["\"That's right! Let's not fight.", "We should kiss and make out.\""], "cx8FPbn0": ["\"................Pardon?\""], "2fQwdYrW": ["\"No, wait... It's 'kiss and make up', isn't it?\""], "s2VJFlMY": ["\"Ah, same difference...", "What do you say?\""], "g6nCKVmw": ["\"(I'm sure there's some joke ", "here that I'm not getting....)\""], "qWzTXDJ2": ["\"I say let's find a way out of here.\""], "s5T1Czcw": ["\"And since you said you've been here", "before, you should lead the way.\""], "r0NMFPGS": ["\"Leave it to me!\""], "tgR5SFtK": ["You are Ashley!"], "9h6v9qfw": ["The pink star is almost close enough to touch."], "1CgPykcx": ["It's a little out of reach."], "zjWJCkdl": ["There's nothing to step on."], "DPHHx3zd": ["\"You are \\fi not \\fr\\c[1] throwing the flowers down here.\""], "2NvbHFyK": ["\"There's no way in hell we have ", "enough to reach the other side.\""], "gkZ47Z1K": ["\"Then I'll just have to find some more.\""], "qqLnFMB7": ["\"Find them where? There's only so ", "much ground, and I barely saw any.\""], "tkP9VRvr": ["\"Let's figure something else...\""], "0137gScX": ["\"Oh........ The bridge thing went back down.\""], "QZ9zWcB3": ["\" . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . \""], "YHpHlKxb": ["\"..............Whoops.\""], "dPWmmhXw": ["\"\\fi Sighhhh..... \\fr\\c[1]\""], "Fh5j9sZk": ["\"Well, the good thing is, that we definitely don't", "need to worry about the police while stuck in here!\""], "Y1pngZFr": ["\"Oh yeah! And if we kill ourselves, ", "we won't even be stuck here!\""], "HzKK5682": ["\"S-stop being so dramatic. It'll be fine...\""], "wLdQF8Gd": ["There's nothing to step on."], "PR90V8jV": ["", "Got a Pink Star!"], "9rh7JJCw": ["There's nothing to step on."], "mfvgHNVM": ["The chain won't go lower."], "60CYVBb4": ["The handle won't move further."], "hYDGXPrb": ["", "Got a Handle!"], "5YXWnWld": ["The chain won't go lower."], "DSgKfqGn": ["The handle won't move further."], "nGGtJ8Cz": ["", "Got a Handle!"], "qDqtqxCt": ["The chain won't go lower."], "0QNwDCKz": ["The handle won't move further."], "YMXqtyxd": ["", "Got a Handle!"], "XXPvRHwF": ["\"Well, well, well!\""], "RtFbjLWk": ["\"I'm not stepping on these...\""], "Cfk7jNvj": ["\"Oh, the flowers were fine. But ", "actual stairs? Heaven forbid!\""], "x61KKM83": ["\"What if they go down while we're on ", "them? Just like the other path?\""], "8GkFchfX": ["\"It's either the stairs or staying ", "stuck here until we die.\""], "J393kX2R": ["\"............Alright.\""], "yVZjkk1m": ["\"Aw, cheer up! If we die, it'll be ", "romantic! By your own definition.\""], "tbFpQcn5": ["\"Get up the stairs already!!\""], "pd8Qv4yS": ["\"I think one of these star things fell off.\""], "pfCr5Xd1": ["\"Is this relevant?\""], "H0mvBRF6": ["\"It might be. Since this place ", "runs on demon logic or something.\""], "Xk50nbt7": ["A star-less chain dangles by itself."], "zJgQRgPW": ["\"I can't reach the damn chain!\""], "QV1rrQ1z": ["\"Please stop. You'll fall...\""], "YwVyyL7h": ["The chain is too high to reach."], "r3XYbN9t": ["You hook the Pink Star onto the chain."], "cqrL9qqZ": ["\"There! That looks about right.\""], "C8xyBmy6": ["\"..........Nothing is happening.\""], "Kgr65QVt": ["\"I said 'about right'. Something ", "must still be a little off...\""], "VCmz50YB": ["\"............Okay, never mind. I don't ", "think I've been here before.\""], "vL3JTqV7": ["\"Should we turn back?\""], "T3KylYNk": ["\"Yeah. This area looks like a dead end anyway...\""], "sr94SN8z": ["Some flowers grow on the wall..."], "p8mTrfqP": ["The door is blocked from the other side."], "0VFvrQnX": ["\"...........Thoughts on this?\""], "tj6KM8Bd": ["\"What the fuck ever......\""], "3D4KF9Cr": ["\"Pfft.... HahhaHAHahHA!!\""], "TZt8Wf7r": ["\"Is this thing of any use?\""], "m5FlWj5b": ["\"Probably not. It's missing a handle.\""], "cb45Yg1W": ["\"Can't we just shove a stick ", "in it, for a makeshift handle?\""], "x4vjPrQB": ["\"I mean, if your goal is to jam ", "up the whole thing, then sure...\""], "Wn689JLz": ["\"I'm sure there's something usable around...\""], "nq9TvXZl": ["\"Wait here! I'll be right back.\""], "47vH4tnk": ["It needs a handle."], "46gHnlRT": ["", "The handle fits!"], "k54BD0X7": ["", "...........Kinda."], "XJYThlJf": ["\"Tadaaaaaah!!\""], "Vv74zCln": ["\"Nice work. Now what?\""], "12zvCTxX": ["\".....Once more, with feeling.\""], "Jx16r5bg": ["\"Yeah, yeah. You're smart, resourceful, sexy, cute,", "and clever. Now what are we supposed to do??\""], "N7x9V5Dd": ["\"Well, obviously we'll see if it works now.\""], "8nc4Tf0X": ["The chain won't go lower."], "z9QcxcdV": ["The handle won't move further."], "nk3fVZr6": ["\"Shall we?\""], "PWY9GJJq": ["\"Like we have other options...\""], "nfbMRzQP": ["The moon is out of reach."], "BCRch3Cn": ["The moon is still too high up."], "Bq8mjg9M": ["\"Hmm... Still too high. Can you reach it?\""], "F2MFDH6b": ["\"You're lighter, so you should do it.\""], "N0zYGWDj": ["\"...Huh? What??\""], "R5RHzhn7": ["\"Getting on this moon, right?\""], "rFWvrc3R": ["\"I'll use the crane to lift ", "it up, with you on it.\""], "q0KSyrnz": ["\"....I was going to take the moon down", "and figure what to do from there.\""], "gMh1pWzx": ["\"Fuck that. We're using human logic now.\""], "Y3shcv5j": ["\"There's bound to be something ", "here you can use to climb.\""], "F2NCB0hD": ["TOO HIGH!!"], "Sqy1pGdy": ["\"We could do with a few more bricks...\""], "yX7DRnGl": ["\"There! A pile of bricks.\""], "Kt5Rk6nF": ["\"Perfect. Up you go.\""], "GgF5xv40": ["A brick."], "nQND38gJ": ["\"Okay... What now?\""], "8c1QtXNq": ["\"Just a second...\""], "sf85cVD8": ["\"Well? Think you can make the jump?\""], "QB4dGPy2": ["\"P-probably..........\""], "WLDmRSFP": ["\"Hmph! Didn't even break my ankles.\""], "mBhVVRjh": ["\"Great! Anything in there?\""], "9gsvs09K": ["\"Let's take a look-see...\""], "dNJNwF8N": ["", "Got a Brick!"], "JkYBthv0": ["\"Rejoice! For I have returned.\""], "gfLX5HZS": ["\"My joy is immeasurable.\""], "dP0Tkhdw": ["A brick."], "mgrbnXbf": ["A brick."], "0LklxSSN": ["A brick."], "ZDLGVV5w": ["A brick."], "3rl2n0GX": ["A brick."], "mBDhkMgg": ["\"Andrew.\""], "2SMxl1ZL": ["\"Yeah?\""], "6Gs7WZb8": ["\"Aaaaandrew.\""], "2MVrgPgS": ["\"Uh-huh. What's up?\""], "fYGKmyBT": ["\"Be nice to me, Andrew.\""], "c4GB1W08": ["\"Aren't I...?\""], "QsvY3y4X": ["\"Heh. Give us a hug!\""], "TpMfsV90": ["\"....I don't mind. But why?\""], "7XvvJsCB": ["\"No reason!\""], "NzRGZtfk": ["\"(We're getting along, right?)\""], "CWVwV3xX": ["\"(We're fine................)\""], "HyPL6zVB": ["\"Did you find a handle yet?\""], "WNlP8JXK": ["\"(He didn't kiss my hair......................)\""], "vq40cnMs": ["\"Well, this thing on the ground", "is clearly something relevant...\""], "0cBhxNqH": ["\"Whatever it is, it doesn't seem active.\""], "Zn7MVHlZ": ["\"Get this shit out of the way...\""], "5mNTyMmz": ["The stairs are out of reach."], "SlTcvdFT": ["The unreachable stairs taunt you."], "7tx7fGf9": ["\"..............Wanna try bricks again?\""], "QzLSZ4wR": ["\"I don't think there's enough of them available.\""], "rZGvMDrY": ["\"Lies! This whole building is made of bricks!\""], "nbk7sYdp": ["\"You start deconstructing it then. Have fun!\""], "skDyZ5KD": ["\"Ahhhh.... I'm going back to demon logic. ", "It worked with the previous stairs.\""], "FPh75CnT": ["\"Right...... Let's see what we've got here.\""], "NfHf7Xnq": ["Even Andrew can't reach the stairs."], "Ylw0l588": ["A pressure plate with a waxing moon on it."], "31y97Qtc": ["This is too heavy for you to move."], "FxrzgGT0": ["TOO HEAVY!!"], "LJxQRYHN": ["\"Can you help me move this?\""], "7zCBNwVj": ["\"There you go.\""], "qdtR3Y2h": ["\"Looks like something was under it...\""], "ww0jT7pH": ["A pressure plate with a full moon on it."], "C6dY5LcX": ["\"A-ha! There \\fi was \\fr\\c[2] a gimmick to it!\""], "bpcWWx9c": ["\"Ughhh... I hate this place.\""], "qctKZ3BD": ["\"Really? I kinda like it...\""], "RqCXj9gD": ["\"Yeah, I can tell.......\""], "FDxKqp9l": ["\"For whatever reason, you seem ", "to be in tune with this place...\""], "bmq1yH9S": ["\"How lucky you are to have me here then!\""], "01frV9yt": ["\"Well? Anything in there?\""], "P72KlZ9X": ["\"I think I can unblock the door for you!\""], "9XjmrkVB": ["\"That's not what I asked...\""], "2X4txHyr": ["\"There's zero need to exit this way!\""], "wF6lv5g8": ["\"Just use the door like the rest of humanity.\""], "8RQcCZ1T": ["A pile of useless junk."], "3sTyJYBd": ["\"Look at that! I'm a genius! Why'd ", "you let me drop out of high school??\""], "cmQKBy8N": ["\"It might've had something to do with being told ", "to shut the fuck up and mind my own business...\""], "Pn22sySq": ["\"Pfft... Oh yeah. Hahah!!\""], "MWdSG4yt": ["From the window, you see a moon."], "tLq7dBCz": ["From the window, you see a planet."], "QMljn1wV": ["The view from this window is obscured by clouds."], "b3KzKhxk": ["Through this window, a cluster of stars is visible."], "Z5MbFMl5": ["\"Another victory!\""], "N5qrFVt8": ["\"Yes, yes. Well done.\""], "CXV8yWXs": ["\"Hehee!\""], "Wb2WSvtn": ["\"Aaaaand there's nothing here.\""], "5mJDJQ44": ["\"Surely, there's another trick to it...\""], "3gjg0yMP": ["\"But I'm tired... Can we rest for a bit?\""], "gFGp4Y3z": ["\"Go ahead. I'll look around....\""], "Lll8B3xw": ["\"Come sit down.\""], "PgQ2YcbL": ["\"That's okay, I'm not tired yet.\""], "BgGJPtZr": ["\"Come sit with me, goddammit!!!\""], "MXt2G6yD": ["\"I was thinking this place isn't so bad.\""], "QvnYLFdY": ["\"In fact it's not bad at all!\""], "wfNsrG7Q": ["\"Maybe we could even live here....\""], "cyKQf8D3": ["\"You're kidding me.....\""], "Q80jPDpJ": ["\"Why not? Staying here would ", "solve all our problems!\""], "Hv69Ckd4": ["\"I--.... Okay, first of all....\""], "8QX6jKTR": ["\"What are we going to eat?\""], "Gcy7D68V": ["\"Well-...\""], "Z079X4qJ": ["\"Where will we clean ourselves?\""], "VjTcZ7Yj": ["\"That--\""], "2zX3QQWW": ["\"Are there demons here?\""], "1YT4gScm": ["\".........\""], "PfGjNDG8": ["\"What are the short and long-term effects ", "of staying in this environment?\""], "VKC0s9Rh": ["\"What if we get sick or injured?\""], "Ly3TZDRR": ["\"Where do we get clothes, and other necessities?\""], "4ZmrbVbS": ["\"......Are you done yet??\""], "d9ntyNj7": ["\"Not at all. But you get my point, right?\""], "ljSRrRgZ": ["\"I just thought there'd be no one here ", "to put us in jail for our wicked deeds.\""], "d03wB2l5": ["\"Even if we solved how to sustain ", "ourselves, then what?\""], "XJymXjLQ": ["\"What would we even do here??\""], "YY9SnDp1": ["\"Take over this realm with our ", "malformed, brain-dead kids.\""], "qQ2rzWgB": ["\"BHahHAhaHA!! Hard pass!\""], "zzGxJ6nk": ["\"HahahHA!! Why not? We could raise them for food.\""], "nwzD3Rd3": ["\"What a hellish future. No thanks.\""], "qc5LV0Mm": ["\"Okay, but why not??\""], "mMSkRvnC": ["\"....................Is this an actual question?\""], "zShQ2DsJ": ["\"No. Or well, maybe...\""], "z2R79Qrj": ["\"Just... No. Absolutely not.\""], "mw5nwm6C": ["\"Because it's illegal to kill your kids??\""], "RQ7Yt897": ["\"Well, even before that-......................\""], "vbkqxClC": ["\"It's not like this is planet Earth anyway.", "What country's laws would apply here??\""], "4MkrkyrH": ["\".................Why are you pushing for this?\""], "crgrftDX": ["\"Pushing for what??\""], "nYnpgNS9": ["\".......\""], "jrSYG6gw": ["\"Aaaaalright. You got me. It's for you!\""], "KKh60lkQ": ["\"You're so gloomy lately. So I'm being ", "unhinged on purpose to make you laugh.\""], "QFlZ5T7s": ["\"Well, don't. It's really uncomfortable.\""], "djg1rC8f": ["\".....Fine. If you say so.\""], "yq1FphXp": ["\"Let's get going then. There's probably--\""], "8PtDcr4h": ["\".......\""], "plhMGCnM": ["\"That was a bullshit answer.\""], "PD0PgG5z": ["\"Give me the real reason.\""], "phZ3GDH9": ["\"That was it, jackass!\""], "3dR25RW8": ["\"Alright. Forget it then...\""], "LXJWrQqk": ["\"What's with the attitude? ", "Why are you angry at me??\""], "xZyz2H8x": ["\"I'm angry because you're playing games.\""], "Gg49klJW": ["\"I'm not! Why do you always think the worst of me??\""], "LBDT0txP": ["\"Because how is 'Let's inbreed!' a joke??\""], "kGtsYjpk": ["\"It made you laugh, didn't it!?\""], "NTvdg84r": ["\"Seems to me there's been a lot of jokes lately......\""], "CkNgRj0T": ["\"Haha!! What's that??\""], "Ks6KY9MS": ["\"An observation.\""], "NnkHz0sC": ["\"Yeah, right. Is it getting to you? ", "Aren't you overthinking it??\""], "QMZ3j6c6": ["\"Is that why you're asking about it?\""], "7kXB9T5n": ["\".....What did you hope I'd say??\""], "Sr1NLfpt": ["\" ! ! ! \""], "0wcdkRgV": ["\"You can either explain what's ", "going on with you.....\""], "phFJ8QPr": ["\"Or you can stop whatever it is", "that you think you're doing.\""], "LVGPbs8l": ["\"One or the other.\""], "QvK7V8n2": ["\"..............\""], "YjRyfGg2": ["\" . . . . . . . ... .. .. .............It's just--...........\""], "Dz2NFSgB": ["\"Lately, we don't-..... really get along, do we?\""], "ZNXYrW35": ["\"And then there've been those visions...\""], "9zjHQrzT": ["\"Ahh, okay... I see where this is going...\""], "zXpFqS9D": ["\"I think you're the happiest when we're", "messing about and being stupid...\""], "P56rWbh4": ["\"So I figured you'd like me ", "better if I ramped it up a bit...\""], "nQsD0STt": ["\"And if we got together, then you ", "wouldn't... you know... kill me.\""], "NKQ84n26": ["\"You don't need to go that far.", "Why is that even on the table?\""], "DPW5xZ1Q": ["\"What..? Sex?\""], "8TLW40P5": ["\"I dunno. It could be fun. For you.\""], "Qq0gkywq": ["\"No, it wouldn't be! This kind of shit ", "shouldn't even come up in conversation.\""], "mPwV13yV": ["\"So we roll around and basically dry-hump on Mom's", "couch, but god forbid either of us ever gets off?\""], "sV1wxHXV": ["\".......Ashley, I can appreciate you're trying to", "fix us in your own shitty and misguided way...\""], "J7RKgPp3": ["\"But do you really think I'd be happy to extort", "my own sister into having sex with me??\""], "CJTpbfY1": ["\"How the hell did you twist this into that??\""], "jrpbmhmS": ["\" 'Let's fuck so you won't kill me.' \""], "TrYZ02HW": ["\"Is that how you see me? I think ", "I might actually cry...\""], "tKk1qmLh": ["\"Well, what the hell do you want then?? This was", "my Hail Mary here. I got nothing else for you!\""], "qsVrcTBk": ["\"I want to get us somewhere safe, and then live ", "out our lives peacefully. What do \\fi you \\fr\\c[1] want?\""], "fdqsnKrW": ["\"Your undying love and affection!! But I guess", "I'll just die because I'm too ugly to fuck!\""], "gVGK272r": ["\"Goddammit, Ashley... I'm ", "not going to kill you.\""], "76TfclVQ": ["\".......No matter how much ", "your dumbass deserves it.\""], "BpYsvQwC": ["\"But how can I be sure? You've ", "been really nasty to me lately.\""], "pWQpQYTl": ["\"You've been pretty nasty to me too.\""], "9c2b46Jq": ["\"Have I?\""], "jdZ4Ls52": ["\"You don't think it's nasty to tell me I'm useless and ", "disloyal after I've sacrificed and slaughtered for you?\""], "7zp4x8JK": ["\".....Um?\""], "BXcXmmtb": ["\"That was the most effective way possible to tell me ", "everything I do for you means fucking nothing to you.\""], "zpl3sv6K": ["\"......When was this?\""], "7xhbTcW6": ["\"You don't even remember....\""], "NMYMnH0F": ["\"Well, sorry. But I only mean what I say ", "the moment I say it. You know that.\""], "S6JCp0Sx": ["\"Whatever... It's on me for expecting ", "anything else. I should know you by now.\""], "w05Dj5Gb": ["\"Andrew seriously, I'm sorry if I said that.", "I was talking out of my ass. Get over it.\""], "Nnjf1zfV": ["\"It's not the fact that you said it, it's how ", "you think it's fine to treat me like that.\""], "VydkgGLs": ["\"I don't think it's fine!\""], "d2RTRXmb": ["\"Clearly, you do. It didn't even register ", "that you did it. Talk about second nature...\""], "1x516Ksy": ["\"Or maybe it was harmless snark and", "you're blowing it out of proportion?\""], "CYKVH2vy": ["\"Ashley, I threw away all of me, ", "and everything I could ever be.\""], "Tc4VRXzG": ["\"And your response was to make sure I knew ", "exactly how dissatisfied you are with me.\""], "Pt61VPBh": ["\"Forgive me for being a little sour about it.\""], "KqYVqyl6": ["\"................\""], "rSLvHvPL": ["\"But I'm not so sour that I'd want you dead.", "Or in my bed for that matter.\""], "c3tW15KT": ["\" . . . . . . . . . . \""], "NlMh2T86": ["\"Listen, forget it.... Like I said, it's my bad.\""], "m4TQvncq": ["\"Just get us out of this place.", "Can you do that much for me?\""], "5Y4Zwj8d": ["\".................I guess.\""], "x3N6rqts": ["\"Alright, good. Let's go then.\""], "hjwGlJKC": ["\".........What is it?\""], "LTgFnBf9": ["\"You didn't answer me.\""], "XDw3S1vQ": ["\"How do I know you won't kill me?\""], "qvjXN0Xt": ["\"Sunk-cost fallacy, I guess.\""], "p07KPVH1": ["\"Man, fuck you.\""], "k3CXxzzG": ["\"Pfft!!\""], "fVBTrJg7": ["\"Be serious!! I really--... ", "I feel awful right now!\""], "xtvlngqy": ["\"I don't know what to tell you.\""], "2p9J0yBF": ["\"Just like you, my words don't ", "really mean much anyway.\""], "rxhrGHCV": ["\"\\fi Sigh........ \\fr\\c[2]\""], "tZTkkD50": ["\"Aaaah. No, Ashley... Stop ", "making that face. I just-....\""], "12LnlTzN": ["\" ....... \""], "fnncrQn5": ["\"O-okay, look...\""], "SL42zG81": ["\"It's fine now. We're fine. I'm glad", "we had this bizarre conversation...\""], "4QNtkJ88": ["\"I'm sorry for being upset.\""], "tsqjQXbP": ["\"Thank you for listening...\""], "lyzbnKdf": ["\" . . . . . . . . \""], "3w9fHV9H": ["\"You suck, but at least you're fun.\""], "dxsrVnLQ": ["\"HahHa!!\""], "rrK9zDxD": ["\"Really? I'm fun and I suck ", "too? I sound like a good time.\""], "0d8RTglq": ["\"Pfft--.... HAHahHahHAHaha!!!\""], "S1Z3KHGj": ["\"Hah! And you \\fi still \\fr\\c[2] didn't ", "give me a real answer.\""], "sLFfxVN4": ["\"If you can't convince me with", "words, swear on it with a kiss!\""], "t52ZKTpd": ["\"Well, aren't you being poetic?", "Besides, didn't I just do that?\""], "9ClSV9Ds": ["\"On the lips, jackass! Obviously!!", "Like a proper vow!!\""], "pGlfXSDY": ["\"I don't see why I should have to go that far...\""], "jMfDpLvh": ["\"Ohh, I see! It was a lie, huh? Liar.\""], "w323FKnb": ["\"Look at this liar, planning to ", "murder his own sister.\""], "LQ323X2R": ["\"C'mon now. You know I'm not...\""], "04tkJ5Xr": ["\"Liar, liar, liar, liar, liar....\""], "3M1fzmRj": ["\"Stop that.\""], "qWj1G8Xr": ["\"Liar, liar, liar, liar, liar, ", "liar, liar, liar, liar, liar....\""], "dPy0bbNb": ["\"Shut up, or I'll do it.\""], "rCb11wLZ": ["\"Liiiiiiar, liar, liar, liar, liar...!\""], "5RXc4pF9": ["\"Alright then. You asked for it!\""], "8kPQZ03L": ["\"Ah..?\""], "3BMMhd4N": ["\" . . . . . . . . . . \""], "wDn4g13r": ["\".................Ahah!\""], "8ZWjdv8p": ["\"HahHahahHAHa!!\""], "Wqxm1xJK": ["\"Ooooooh! HahaHa!! Now you've done it!!\""], "PwG2TW7z": ["\"Me? You made me!\""], "NvH8G3l2": ["\"Hear ye, hear ye! Here come them excuses!\""], "KPxzVFkz": ["\"Hah! Alright, alright... Are you happy ", "now? Can we move on from this already?\""], "88Z3jlv6": ["\"Of course. After all, I won!\""], "5Lcx7RW8": ["\"......I'm not even going to ask.\""], "HCNSb7ql": ["There are indents for what are clearly tiny stars."], "xmhlqTyf": ["You're missing some stars."], "wfFJfzzM": ["\"What was that..?\""], "16Kbg8d8": ["You look outside the window..."], "ZSnzT9XG": ["\"Huh... I guess that's active now.\""], "N2ScrDbH": ["\"I really don't want to, but ", "we should go take a look...\""], "S7yb8XML": ["", "Found a tiny Star!"], "mZGNWKBy": ["", "Found a tiny Star!"], "yb6MJDlz": ["", "Found a tiny Star!"], "CwSkd5GY": ["", "Found a tiny Star!"], "MGx7thFC": ["There's nothing interesting in the bag."], "wr9XNK1v": ["Just some junk."], "2rQQqZLz": ["Bottles. They're all empty."], "N1LhRbJK": ["Exit?"], "463N7vMN": ["", "Got a Sun Stone!"], "b52TGvCz": ["", "Got a Moon Stone!"], "ftPW30Sn": ["", "Got a Star Stone!"], "5QCVrJ18": ["\"There you are! I need this signed.\""], "W8tkwH54": ["She hands you a notice for a two-day", "suspension from school."], "G26cg7N0": ["\"...Why are you bringing this to me? ", "It's Mom or Dad that needs to sign it.\""], "v9rd8k4c": ["\"Huh....... Why \\fi did \\fr\\c[2] I bring it to you..?\""], "4QTdfnwz": ["\"\\fi Sigh... \\fr\\c[1] Mom's going to throw ", "another fit... Why did you---\""], "khF23wRK": ["\"Actually, no... Yeah. I'll sign this.", "She doesn't need to know anything.\""], "PDSdrKvW": ["\"I'm hungry! When are you ", "going to make food?\""], "y131V7ky": ["\"I already showed you how to use the stove.", "Fry yourself an egg or something.\""], "n3g1YcH6": ["\"Bleeeeehhh.... What a pain!", "Why can't you do it?\""], "D6nwRNdT": ["\"(This isn't worth the argument....)\""], "55Tq9hcq": ["\"Fine. I'll fix us something...\""], "XLyrS8MW": ["She's hungry."], "NcJ3kkLR": ["\"There you go. Enjoy.\""], "n3V52lZj": ["\"Ugh... This same crap again?\""], "Qgxc4RP3": ["She's eating, but she doesn't look pleased about it."], "fD2R8870": ["\"Here. It's signed now.\""], "FN3y4k29": ["\"And forget what I said earlier, you can ", "bring these all to me from now on.\""], "9mNBQPLv": ["\".....It looks kinda crappy though.\""], "0X6Xfb1v": ["\"Well, if anyone asks, say Mom was drinking--\""], "p9rSkzRZ": ["\"Wait, no. No, don't say that. ", "Say she was in a hurry.\""], "hyY54ZG3": ["\"I don't have to explain anything!\""], "7pQx0F8m": ["\"Okay, that's--........\""], "zxDyJq8j": ["\"The correct response, actually....\""], "lLM0smXk": ["\"Over explaining would make it", "more suspicious. Good thinking!\""], "tpsTmRCk": ["\"Hehee!\""], "HvncYTPj": ["\"You know, you really do have ", "a knack for these things.\""], "TvBN1Gln": ["\"If you played nice, you could make ", "life so much easier for yourself...\""], "LrxLB867": ["\"Why bother? No one likes me anyway.\""], "3XJhb7df": ["\"The thing about 